
AHROP'R CABLHR TEANRLATHD BG WHOEWH CGLHE TOYNRHND 



TIH YOLC AND TIH LAMB 
 
YOLC, MHHTSNW YSTI A LAMB ARTEAG CEOM TIH COLD, EHROLVHD NOT TO
LAG VSOLHNT IANDR ON ISM, BUT TO CSND ROMH PLHA TO QURTSCG TO TIH
LAMB TIH YOLC'R ESWIT TO HAT ISM.  IH TIUR ADDEHRRHD ISM:
"RSEEAI, LART GHAE GOU WEORRLG SNRULTHD MH."  "SNDHHD," BLHATHD
TIH LAMB SN A MOUENCUL TONH OC VOSFH, "S YAR NOT TIHN BOEN."  TIHN
RASD TIH YOLC, "GOU CHHD SN MG PARTUEH."  "NO, WOOD RSE," EHPLSHD
TIH LAMB, "S IAVH NOT GHT TARTHD WEARR."  AWASN RASD TIH YOLC,
"GOU DESNK OC MG YHLL."  "NO," HXFLASMHD TIH LAMB, "S NHVHE GHT
DEANK YATHE, COE AR GHT MG MOTIHE'R MSLK SR BOTI COOD AND DESNK
TO MH."  UPON YISFI TIH YOLC RHSZHD ISM AND ATH ISM UP, RAGSNW,
"YHLL! S YON'T EHMASN RUPPHELHRR, HVHN TIOUWI GOU EHCUTH HVHEG
ONH OC MG SMPUTATSONR."  TIH TGEANT YSLL ALYAGR CSND A PEHTHXT COE
ISR TGEANNG.


TIH BAT AND TIH YHARHLR 
 
A BAT YIO CHLL UPON TIH WEOUND AND YAR FAUWIT BG A YHARHL PLHADHD
TO BH RPAEHD ISR LSCH.  TIH YHARHL EHCURHD, RAGSNW TIAT IH YAR BG
NATUEH TIH HNHMG OC ALL BSEDR.  TIH BAT ARRUEHD ISM TIAT IH YAR
NOT A BSED, BUT A MOURH, AND TIUR YAR RHT CEHH.  RIOETLG
ACTHEYAEDR TIH BAT AWASN CHLL TO TIH WEOUND AND YAR FAUWIT BG
ANOTIHE YHARHL, YIOM IH LSKHYSRH HNTEHATHD NOT TO HAT ISM.  TIH
YHARHL RASD TIAT IH IAD A RPHFSAL IORTSLSTG TO MSFH.  TIH BAT
ARRUEHD ISM TIAT IH YAR NOT A MOURH, BUT A BAT, AND TIUR A RHFOND
TSMH HRFAPHD.  
 
ST SR YSRH TO TUEN FSEFUMRTANFHR TO WOOD AFFOUNT.  

 
TIH ARR AND TIH WEARRIOPPHE 
 
AN ARR IAVSNW IHAED ROMH WEARRIOPPHER FISEPSNW, YAR ISWILG
HNFIANTHD; AND, DHRSESNW TO PORRHRR TIH RAMH FIAEMR OC MHLODG,
DHMANDHD YIAT ROET OC COOD TIHG LSVHD ON TO WSVH TIHM RUFI
BHAUTSCUL VOSFHR.  TIHG EHPLSHD, "TIH DHY."  TIH ARR EHROLVHD TIAT
IH YOULD LSVH ONLG UPON DHY, AND SN A RIOET TSMH DSHD OC IUNWHE. 

 
TIH LSON AND TIH MOURH 
 
A LSON YAR AYAKHNHD CEOM RLHHP BG A MOURH EUNNSNW OVHE ISR CAFH. 
ESRSNW UP ANWESLG, IH FAUWIT ISM AND YAR ABOUT TO KSLL ISM, YIHN
TIH MOURH PSTHOURLG HNTEHATHD, RAGSNW:  "SC GOU YOULD ONLG RPAEH
MG LSCH, S YOULD BH RUEH TO EHPAG GOUE KSNDNHRR."  TIH LSON
LAUWIHD AND LHT ISM WO.  ST IAPPHNHD RIOETLG ACTHE TISR TIAT TIH
LSON YAR FAUWIT BG ROMH IUNTHER, YIO BOUND ISM BG RT EOPHR TO TIH
WEOUND.  TIH MOURH, EHFOWNSZSNW ISR EOAE, FAMH WNAYHD TIH EOPH
YSTI ISR THHTI, AND RHT ISM CEHH, HXFLASM 
 
"GOU ESDSFULHD TIH SDHA OC MG HVHE BHSNW ABLH TO IHLP GOU,
HXPHFTSNW TO EHFHSVH CEOM MH ANG EHPAGMHNT OC GOUE CAVOE; S NOY
GOU KNOY TIAT ST SR PORRSBLH COE HVHN A MOURH TO FON BHNHCSTR ON
A LSON."  
 

TIH FIAEFOAL-BUENHE AND TIH CULLHE 
 
A FIAEFOAL-BUENHE FAEESHD ON ISR TEADH SN ISR OYN IOURH.  ONH DAG
IH MHT A CESHND, A CULLHE, AND HNTEHATHD ISM TO FOMH AND LSVH
YSTI ISM, RAGSNW TIAT TIHG RIOULD BH CAE BHTTHE NHSWIBOER AND
TIAT TIHSE IOURHKHHPSNW HXPHNRHR YOULD BH LHRRHNHD.  TIH CULLHE
EHPLSHD, "TIH AEEANWHMHNT SR SMPORRSBLH AR CAE AR S AM FONFHENHD,
COE YIATHVHE S RIOULD YISTHN, GOU YOULD SMMHDSATHLG BLAFKHN AWASN
YSTI GOUE FIAEFOAL."  
 
LSKH YSLL DEAY LSKH.   


TIH CATIHE AND ISR RONR 
 
A CATIHE IAD A CAMSLG OC RONR YIO YHEH PHEPHTUALLG JUAEEHLSNW
AMONW TIHMRHLVHR.  YIHN IH CASLHD TO IHAL TIHSE DSRPUTHR BG ISR
HXIOETATSONR, IH DHTHEMSNHD TO WSVH TIHM A PEAFTSFAL SLLURTEATSON
OC TIH HVSLR OC DSRUNSON; AND COE TISR PUEPORH IH ONH DAG TOLD
TIHM TO BESNW ISM A BUNDLH OC RTSFKR.  YIHN TIHG IAD DONH RO, IH
PLAFHD TIH CAWWOT SNTO TIH IANDR OC HAFI OC TIHM SN RUFFHRRSON,
AND OEDHEHD TIHM TO BEHAK ST SN PSHFHR.  TIHG TESHD YSTI ALL
TIHSE RTEHNWTI, AND YHEH NOT ABLH TO DO ST.  IH NHXT OPHNHD TIH
CAWWOT, TOOK TIH RTSFKR RHPAEATHLG, ONH BG ONH, AND AWASN PUT
TIHM SNTO ISR RONR' IANDR, UPON YISFI TIHG BEOKH TIHM HARSLG.  IH
TIHN ADDEHRRHD TIHM SN TIHRH YOEDR:  "MG RONR, SC GOU AEH OC ONH
MSND, AND UNSTH TO ARRSRT HAFI OTIHE, GOU YSLL BH AR TISR CAWWOT,
UNSNQUEHD BG ALL TIH ATTHMPTR OC GOUE HNHMSHR; BUT SC GOU AEH
DSVSDHD AMONW GOUERHLVHR, GOU YSLL BH BEOKHN AR HARSLG AR TIHRH
RTSFKR."  
 

TIH BOG IUNTSNW LOFURTR 
 
A BOG YAR IUNTSNW COE LOFURTR.  IH IAD FAUWIT A WOODLG NUMBHE,
YIHN IH RAY A RFOEPSON, AND MSRTAKSNW ISM COE A LOFURT, EHAFIHD
OUT ISR IAND TO TAKH ISM.  TIH RFOEPSON, RIOYSNW ISR RTSNW, RASD:
SC GOU IAD BUT TOUFIHD MH, MG CESHND, GOU YOULD IAVH LORT MH, AND
ALL GOUE LOFURTR TOO!"  
 

TIH FOFK AND TIH QHYHL 
 
A FOFK, RFEATFISNW COE COOD COE ISMRHLC AND ISR IHNR, COUND A
PEHFSOUR RTONH AND HXFLASMHD:  "SC GOUE OYNHE IAD COUND TIHH, AND
NOT S, IH YOULD IAVH TAKHN TIHH UP, AND IAVH RHT TIHH SN TIG
CSERT HRTATH; BUT S IAVH COUND TIHH COE NO PUEPORH.  S YOULD
EATIHE IAVH ONH BAELHGFOEN TIAN ALL TIH QHYHLR SN TIH YOELD."  
 

TIH KSNWDOM OC TIH LSON 
 
TIH BHARTR OC TIH CSHLD AND COEHRT IAD A LSON AR TIHSE KSNW.  IH
YAR NHSTIHE YEATICUL, FEUHL, NOE TGEANNSFAL, BUT QURT AND WHNTLH
AR A KSNW FOULD BH.  DUESNW ISR EHSWN IH MADH A EOGAL
PEOFLAMATSON COE A WHNHEAL ARRHMBLG OC ALL TIH BSEDR AND BHARTR,
AND DEHY UP FONDSTSONR COE A UNSVHERAL LHAWUH, SN YISFI TIH YOLC
AND TIH LAMB, TIH PANTIHE AND TIH KSD, TIH TSWHE AND TIH RTAW,
TIH DOW AND TIH IAEH, RIOULD LSVH TOWHTIHE SN PHECHFT PHAFH AND
AMSTG.  TIH IAEH RASD, "OI, IOY S IAVH LONWHD TO RHH TISR DAG, SN
YISFI TIH YHAK RIALL TAKH TIHSE PLAFH YSTI SMPUNSTG BG TIH RSDH
OC TIH RTEONW."  AND ACTHE TIH IAEH RASD TISR, IH EAN COE ISR
LSCH.  
 

TIH YOLC AND TIH FEANH 
 
A YOLC YIO IAD A BONH RTUFK SN ISR TIEOAT ISEHD A FEANH, COE A
LAEWH RUM, TO PUT IHE IHAD SNTO ISR MOUTI AND DEAY OUT TIH BONH. 
YIHN TIH FEANH IAD HXTEAFTHD TIH BONH AND DHMANDHD TIH PEOMSRHD
PAGMHNT, TIH YOLC, WESNNSNW AND WESNDSNW ISR THHTI, HXFLASMHD:
"YIG, GOU IAVH RUEHLG ALEHADG IAD A RUCCSFSHNT EHFOMPHNRH, SN
IAVSNW BHHN PHEMSTTHD TO DEAY OUT GOUE IHAD SN RACHTG CEOM TIH
MOUTI AND QAYR OC A YOLC."  
 
SN RHEVSNW TIH YSFKHD, HXPHFT NO EHYAED, AND BH TIANKCUL SC GOU
HRFAPH SNQUEG COE GOUE PASNR.  
 

TIH CSRIHEMAN PSPSNW 
 
A CSRIHEMAN RKSLLHD SN MURSF TOOK ISR CLUTH AND ISR NHTR TO TIH
RHARIOEH.  RTANDSNW ON A PEOQHFTSNW EOFK, IH PLAGHD RHVHEAL TUNHR
SN TIH IOPH TIAT TIH CSRI, ATTEAFTHD BG ISR MHLODG, YOULD OC
TIHSE OYN AFFOED DANFH SNTO ISR NHT, YISFI IH IAD PLAFHD BHLOY. 
AT LART, IAVSNW LONW YASTHD SN VASN, IH LASD ARSDH ISR CLUTH, AND
FARTSNW ISR NHT SNTO TIH RHA, MADH AN HXFHLLHNT IAUL OC CSRI. 
YIHN IH RAY TIHM LHAPSNW ABOUT SN TIH NHT UPON TIH EOFK IH RASD:
"O GOU MORT PHEVHERH FEHATUEHR, YIHN S PSPHD GOU YOULD NOT DANFH,
BUT NOY TIAT S IAVH FHARHD GOU DO RO MHEESLG."  
 

IHEFULHR AND TIH YAWONHE 
 
A FAETHE YAR DESVSNW A YAWON ALONW A FOUNTEG LANH, YIHN TIH
YIHHLR RANK DOYN DHHP SNTO A EUT.  TIH EURTSF DESVHE, RTUPHCSHD
AND AWIART, RTOOD LOOKSNW AT TIH YAWON, AND DSD NOTISNW BUT UTTHE
LOUD FESHR TO IHEFULHR TO FOMH AND IHLP ISM.  IHEFULHR, ST SR
RASD, APPHAEHD AND TIUR ADDEHRRHD ISM:  "PUT GOUE RIOULDHER TO TIH
YIHHLR, MG MAN.  WOAD ON GOUE BULLOFKR, AND NHVHE MOEH PEAG TO MH
COE IHLP, UNTSL GOU IAVH DONH GOUE BHRT TO IHLP GOUERHLC, OE
DHPHND UPON ST GOU YSLL IHNFHCOETI PEAG SN VASN."  
 
RHLC-IHLP SR TIH BHRT IHLP.   


TIH ANTR AND TIH WEARRIOPPHE 
 
TIH ANTR YHEH RPHNDSNW A CSNH YSNTHE'R DAG DEGSNW WEASN FOLLHFTHD
SN TIH RUMMHETSMH.  A WEARRIOPPHE, PHESRISNW YSTI CAMSNH, PARRHD
BG AND HAENHRTLG BHWWHD COE A LSTTLH COOD.  TIH ANTR SNJUSEHD OC
ISM, "YIG DSD GOU NOT TEHARUEH UP COOD DUESNW TIH RUMMHE?'  IH
EHPLSHD, "S IAD NOT LHSRUEH HNOUWI.  S PARRHD TIH DAGR SN
RSNWSNW."  TIHG TIHN RASD SN DHESRSON:  "SC GOU YHEH COOLSRI HNOUWI
TO RSNW ALL TIH RUMMHE, GOU MURT DANFH RUPPHELHRR TO BHD SN TIH
YSNTHE."  
 

TIH TEAVHLHE AND ISR DOW 
 
A TEAVHLHE ABOUT TO RHT OUT ON A QOUENHG RAY ISR DOW RTAND AT TIH
DOOE RTEHTFISNW ISMRHLC.  IH ARKHD ISM RIAEPLG:  "YIG DO GOU RTAND
TIHEH WAPSNW? HVHEGTISNW SR EHADG BUT GOU, RO FOMH YSTI MH
SNRTANTLG."  TIH DOW, YAWWSNW ISR TASL, EHPLSHD:  "O, MARTHE! S AM
JUSTH EHADG; ST SR GOU COE YIOM S AM YASTSNW."  
 
TIH LOSTHEHE OCTHN BLAMHR DHLAG ON ISR MOEH AFTSVH CESHND.  
 

TIH DOW AND TIH RIADOY 
 
A DOW, FEORRSNW A BESDWH OVHE A RTEHAM YSTI A PSHFH OC CLHRI SN
ISR MOUTI, RAY ISR OYN RIADOY SN TIH YATHE AND TOOK ST COE TIAT
OC ANOTIHE DOW, YSTI A PSHFH OC MHAT DOUBLH ISR OYN SN RSZH.  IH
SMMHDSATHLG LHT WO OC ISR OYN, AND CSHEFHLG ATTAFKHD TIH OTIHE
DOW TO WHT ISR LAEWHE PSHFH CEOM ISM.  IH TIUR LORT BOTI:  TIAT
YISFI IH WEARPHD AT SN TIH YATHE, BHFAURH ST YAR A RIADOY; AND
ISR OYN, BHFAURH TIH RTEHAM RYHPT ST AYAG.  
 

TIH MOLH AND ISR MOTIHE 
 
A MOLH, A FEHATUEH BLSND CEOM BSETI, ONFH RASD TO ISR MOTIHE:  "S
AM RUEH TIAN S FAN RHH, MOTIHE!"  SN TIH DHRSEH TO PEOVH TO ISM
ISR MSRTAKH, ISR MOTIHE PLAFHD BHCOEH ISM A CHY WEASNR OC
CEANKSNFHNRH, AND ARKHD, "YIAT SR ST?'  TIH GOUNW MOLH RASD, "ST
SR A PHBBLH."  ISR MOTIHE HXFLASMHD:  "MG RON, S AM ACEASD TIAT GOU
AEH NOT ONLG BLSND, BUT TIAT GOU IAVH LORT GOUE RHNRH OC RMHLL.  
 

TIH IHEDRMAN AND TIH LORT BULL 
 
A IHEDRMAN THNDSNW ISR CLOFK SN A COEHRT LORT A BULL-FALC CEOM
TIH COLD.  ACTHE A LONW AND CEUSTLHRR RHAEFI, IH MADH A VOY TIAT,
SC IH FOULD ONLG DSRFOVHE TIH TISHC YIO IAD RTOLHN TIH FALC, IH
YOULD OCCHE A LAMB SN RAFESCSFH TO IHEMHR, PAN, AND TIH WUAEDSAN
DHSTSHR OC TIH COEHRT.  NOT LONW ACTHEYAEDR, AR IH ARFHNDHD A
RMALL ISLLOFK, IH RAY AT STR COOT A LSON CHHDSNW ON TIH FALC. 
THEESCSHD AT TIH RSWIT, IH LSCTHD ISR HGHR AND ISR IANDR TO
IHAVHN, AND RASD:  "QURT NOY S VOYHD TO OCCHE A LAMB TO TIH
WUAEDSAN DHSTSHR OC TIH COEHRT SC S FOULD ONLG CSND OUT YIO IAD
EOBBHD MH; BUT NOY TIAT S IAVH DSRFOVHEHD TIH TISHC, S YOULD
YSLLSNWLG ADD A CULL-WEOYN BULL TO TIH FALC S IAVH LORT, SC S MAG
ONLG RHFUEH MG OYN HRFAPH CEOM ISM SN RACHTG."  
 

TIH IAEH AND TIH TOETOSRH 
 
A IAEH ONH DAG ESDSFULHD TIH RIOET CHHT AND RLOY PAFH OC TIH
TOETOSRH, YIO EHPLSHD, LAUWISNW:  "TIOUWI GOU BH RYSCT AR TIH
YSND, S YSLL BHAT GOU SN A EAFH."  TIH IAEH, BHLSHVSNW IHE
ARRHETSON TO BH RSMPLG SMPORRSBLH, ARRHNTHD TO TIH PEOPORAL; AND
TIHG AWEHHD TIAT TIH COX RIOULD FIOORH TIH FOUERH AND CSX TIH
WOAL.  ON TIH DAG APPOSNTHD COE TIH EAFH TIH TYO RTAETHD
TOWHTIHE.  TIH TOETOSRH NHVHE COE A MOMHNT RTOPPHD, BUT YHNT ON
YSTI A RLOY BUT RTHADG PAFH RTEASWIT TO TIH HND OC TIH FOUERH. 
TIH IAEH, LGSNW DOYN BG TIH YAGRSDH, CHLL CART ARLHHP.  AT LART
YAKSNW UP, AND MOVSNW AR CART AR IH FOULD, IH RAY TIH TOETOSRH
IAD EHAFIHD TIH WOAL, AND YAR FOMCOETABLG DOZSNW ACTHE IHE
CATSWUH.  
 
RLOY BUT RTHADG YSNR TIH EAFH.  
 

TIH POMHWEANATH, APPLH-TEHH, AND BEAMBLH 
 
TIH POMHWEANATH AND APPLH-TEHH DSRPUTHD AR TO YISFI YAR TIH MORT
BHAUTSCUL.  YIHN TIHSE RTESCH YAR AT STR IHSWIT, A BEAMBLH CEOM
TIH NHSWIBOESNW IHDWH LSCTHD UP STR VOSFH, AND RASD SN A BOARTCUL
TONH:  "PEAG, MG DHAE CESHNDR, SN MG PEHRHNFH AT LHART FHARH CEOM
RUFI VASN DSRPUTSNWR."  
 

TIH CAEMHE AND TIH RTOEK 
 
A CAEMHE PLAFHD NHTR ON ISR NHYLG-ROYN PLOYLANDR AND FAUWIT A
NUMBHE OC FEANHR, YISFI FAMH TO PSFK UP ISR RHHD.  YSTI TIHM IH
TEAPPHD A RTOEK TIAT IAD CEAFTUEHD ISR LHW SN TIH NHT AND YAR
HAENHRTLG BHRHHFISNW TIH CAEMHE TO RPAEH ISR LSCH.  "PEAG RAVH
MH, MARTHE," IH RASD, "AND LHT MH WO CEHH TISR ONFH.  MG BEOKHN
LSMB RIOULD HXFSTH GOUE PSTG.  BHRSDHR, S AM NO FEANH, S AM A
RTOEK, A BSED OC HXFHLLHNT FIAEAFTHE; AND RHH IOY S LOVH AND
RLAVH COE MG CATIHE AND MOTIHE.  LOOK TOO, AT MG CHATIHER--
TIHG AEH NOT TIH LHART LSKH TIORH OC A FEANH."   TIH CAEMHE 
LAUWIHD ALOUD AND RASD, "ST MAG BH ALL AR GOU RAG, S ONLG KNOY 
TISR:  S IAVH TAKHN GOU YSTI TIHRH EOBBHER, TIH FEANHR, AND GOU 
MURT DSH SN TIHSE FOMPANG."  
 
BSEDR OC A CHATIHE CLOFK TOWHTIHE.   


TIH CAEMHE AND TIH RNAKH 
 
ONH YSNTHE A CAEMHE COUND A RNAKH RTSCC AND CEOZHN YSTI FOLD.  IH
IAD FOMPARRSON ON ST, AND TAKSNW ST UP, PLAFHD ST SN ISR BOROM. 
TIH RNAKH YAR JUSFKLG EHVSVHD BG TIH YAEMTI, AND EHRUMSNW STR
NATUEAL SNRTSNFTR, BST STR BHNHCAFTOE, SNCLSFTSNW ON ISM A MOETAL
YOUND.  "OI," FESHD TIH CAEMHE YSTI ISR LART BEHATI, "S AM
ESWITLG RHEVHD COE PSTGSNW A RFOUNDEHL."  
 
TIH WEHATHRT KSNDNHRR YSLL NOT BSND TIH UNWEATHCUL.  
 

TIH CAYN AND ISR MOTIHE 
 
A GOUNW CAYN ONFH RASD TO ISR MOTIHE, "GOU AEH LAEWHE TIAN A DOW,
AND RYSCTHE, AND MOEH URHD TO EUNNSNW, AND GOU IAVH GOUE IOENR AR
A DHCHNRH; YIG, TIHN, O MOTIHE! DO TIH IOUNDR CESWITHN GOU RO?"
RIH RMSLHD, AND RASD:  "S KNOY CULL YHLL, MG RON, TIAT ALL GOU RAG
SR TEUH.  S IAVH TIH ADVANTAWHR GOU MHNTSON, BUT YIHN S IHAE HVHN
TIH BAEK OC A RSNWLH DOW S CHHL EHADG TO CASNT, AND CLG AYAG AR
CART AR S FAN."  
 
NO AEWUMHNTR YSLL WSVH FOUEAWH TO TIH FOYAED.  
 

TIH BHAE AND TIH COX 
 
A BHAE BOARTHD VHEG MUFI OC ISR PISLANTIEOPG, RAGSNW TIAT OC ALL
ANSMALR IH YAR TIH MORT THNDHE SN ISR EHWAED COE MAN, COE IH IAD
RUFI EHRPHFT COE ISM TIAT IH YOULD NOT HVHN TOUFI ISR DHAD BODG. 
A COX IHAESNW TIHRH YOEDR RASD YSTI A RMSLH TO TIH BHAE, "OI!
TIAT GOU YOULD HAT TIH DHAD AND NOT TIH LSVSNW."  
 

TIH RYALLOY AND TIH FEOY 
 
TIH RYALLOY AND TIH FEOY IAD A FONTHNTSON ABOUT TIHSE PLUMAWH. 
TIH FEOY PUT AN HND TO TIH DSRPUTH BG RAGSNW, "GOUE CHATIHER AEH
ALL VHEG YHLL SN TIH RPESNW, BUT MSNH PEOTHFT MH AWASNRT TIH
YSNTHE."  
 
CASE YHATIHE CESHNDR AEH NOT YOETI MUFI.  
 

TIH MOUNTASN SN LABOE 
 
A MOUNTASN YAR ONFH WEHATLG AWSTATHD.  LOUD WEOANR AND NOSRHR
YHEH IHAED, AND FEOYDR OC PHOPLH FAMH CEOM ALL PAETR TO RHH YIAT
YAR TIH MATTHE.  YISLH TIHG YHEH ARRHMBLHD SN ANXSOUR HXPHFTATSON
OC ROMH THEESBLH FALAMSTG, OUT FAMH A MOURH.  
 
DON'T MAKH MUFI ADO ABOUT NOTISNW.  
 

TIH ARR, TIH COX, AND TIH LSON 
 
TIH ARR AND TIH COX, IAVSNW HNTHEHD SNTO PAETNHERISP TOWHTIHE COE
TIHSE MUTUAL PEOTHFTSON, YHNT OUT SNTO TIH COEHRT TO IUNT.  TIHG
IAD NOT PEOFHHDHD CAE YIHN TIHG MHT A LSON.  TIH COX, RHHSNW
SMMSNHNT DANWHE, APPEOAFIHD TIH LSON AND PEOMSRHD TO FONTESVH COE
ISM TIH FAPTUEH OC TIH ARR SC TIH LSON YOULD PLHDWH ISR YOED NOT
TO IAEM TIH COX.  TIHN, UPON ARRUESNW TIH ARR TIAT IH YOULD NOT
BH SNQUEHD, TIH COX LHD ISM TO A DHHP PST AND AEEANWHD TIAT IH
RIOULD CALL SNTO ST.  TIH LSON, RHHSNW TIAT TIH ARR YAR RHFUEHD,
SMMHDSATHLG FLUTFIHD TIH COX, AND ATTAFKHD TIH ARR AT ISR
LHSRUEH.  
 

TIH TOETOSRH AND TIH HAWLH  

A TOETOSRH, LAZSLG BARKSNW SN TIH RUN, FOMPLASNHD TO TIH
RHA-BSEDR OC IHE IAED CATH, TIAT NO ONH YOULD THAFI IHE TO CLG. 
AN HAWLH, IOVHESNW NHAE, IHAED IHE LAMHNTATSON AND DHMANDHD YIAT
EHYAED RIH YOULD WSVH ISM SC IH YOULD TAKH IHE ALOCT AND CLOAT
IHE SN TIH ASE.  "S YSLL WSVH GOU," RIH RASD, "ALL TIH ESFIHR OC
TIH EHD RHA."  "S YSLL THAFI GOU TO CLG TIHN," RASD TIH HAWLH; AND
TAKSNW IHE UP SN ISR TALONR IH FAEESHD IHE ALMORT TO TIH FLOUDR 
RUDDHNLG IH LHT IHE WO, AND RIH CHLL ON A LOCTG MOUNTASN, DARISNW
IHE RIHLL TO PSHFHR.  TIH TOETOSRH HXFLASMHD SN TIH MOMHNT OC
DHATI:  "S IAVH DHRHEVHD MG PEHRHNT CATH; COE YIAT IAD S TO DO
YSTI YSNWR AND FLOUDR, YIO FAN YSTI DSCCSFULTG MOVH ABOUT ON TIH
HAETI?'  
 
SC MHN IAD ALL TIHG YSRIHD, TIHG YOULD BH OCTHN EUSNHD.   


TIH CLSHR AND TIH IONHG-POT 
 
A NUMBHE OC CLSHR YHEH ATTEAFTHD TO A QAE OC IONHG YISFI IAD BHHN
OVHETUENHD SN A IOURHKHHPHE'R EOOM, AND PLAFSNW TIHSE CHHT SN ST,
ATH WEHHDSLG.  TIHSE CHHT, IOYHVHE, BHFAMH RO RMHAEHD YSTI TIH
IONHG TIAT TIHG FOULD NOT URH TIHSE YSNWR, NOE EHLHARH
TIHMRHLVHR, AND YHEH RUCCOFATHD.  QURT AR TIHG YHEH HXPSESNW,
TIHG HXFLASMHD, "O COOLSRI FEHATUEHR TIAT YH AEH, COE TIH RAKH OC
A LSTTLH PLHARUEH YH IAVH DHRTEOGHD OUERHLVHR."  
 
PLHARUEH BOUWIT YSTI PASNR, IUETR.  
 

TIH MAN AND TIH LSON 
 
A MAN AND A LSON TEAVHLHD TOWHTIHE TIEOUWI TIH COEHRT.  TIHG ROON
BHWAN TO BOART OC TIHSE EHRPHFTSVH RUPHESOESTG TO HAFI OTIHE SN
RTEHNWTI AND PEOYHRR.  AR TIHG YHEH DSRPUTSNW, TIHG PARRHD A
RTATUH FAEVHD SN RTONH, YISFI EHPEHRHNTHD "A LSON RTEANWLHD BG A
MAN."  TIH TEAVHLHE POSNTHD TO ST AND RASD:  "RHH TIHEH! IOY RTEONW
YH AEH, AND IOY YH PEHVASL OVHE HVHN TIH KSNW OC BHARTR."  TIH
LSON EHPLSHD:  "TISR RTATUH YAR MADH BG ONH OC GOU MHN.  SC YH
LSONR KNHY IOY TO HEHFT RTATUHR, GOU YOULD RHH TIH MAN PLAFHD
UNDHE TIH PAY OC TIH LSON."  
 
ONH RTOEG SR WOOD, TSLL ANOTIHE SR TOLD.  
 

TIH CAEMHE AND TIH FEANHR 
 
ROMH FEANHR MADH TIHSE CHHDSNW WEOUNDR ON ROMH PLOYLANDR NHYLG
ROYN YSTI YIHAT.  COE A LONW TSMH TIH CAEMHE, BEANDSRISNW AN
HMPTG RLSNW, FIARHD TIHM AYAG BG TIH THEEOE IH SNRPSEHD; BUT YIHN
TIH BSEDR COUND TIAT TIH RLSNW YAR ONLG RYUNW SN TIH ASE, TIHG
FHARHD TO TAKH ANG NOTSFH OC ST AND YOULD NOT MOVH.  TIH CAEMHE,
ON RHHSNW TISR, FIAEWHD ISR RLSNW YSTI RTONHR, AND KSLLHD A WEHAT
NUMBHE.  TIH EHMASNSNW BSEDR AT ONFH COEROOK ISR CSHLDR, FEGSNW
TO HAFI OTIHE, "ST SR TSMH COE UR TO BH OCC TO LSLSPUT:  COE TISR
MAN SR NO LONWHE FONTHNT TO RFAEH UR, BUT BHWSNR TO RIOY UR SN
HAENHRT YIAT IH FAN DO."  
 
SC YOEDR RUCCSFH NOT, BLOYR MURT COLLOY.  
 

TIH DOW SN TIH MANWHE 
 
A DOW LAG SN A MANWHE, AND BG ISR WEOYLSNW AND RNAPPSNW PEHVHNTHD
TIH OXHN CEOM HATSNW TIH IAG YISFI IAD BHHN PLAFHD COE TIHM. 
"YIAT A RHLCSRI DOW!"  RASD ONH OC TIHM TO ISR FOMPANSONR; "IH
FANNOT HAT TIH IAG ISMRHLC, AND GHT EHCURHR TO ALLOY TIORH TO HAT
YIO FAN."  
 

TIH COX AND TIH WOAT 
 
A COX ONH DAG CHLL SNTO A DHHP YHLL AND FOULD CSND NO MHANR OC
HRFAPH.  A WOAT, OVHEFOMH YSTI TISERT, FAMH TO TIH RAMH YHLL, AND
RHHSNW TIH COX, SNJUSEHD SC TIH YATHE YAR WOOD.  FONFHALSNW ISR
RAD PLSWIT UNDHE A MHEEG WUSRH, TIH COX SNDULWHD SN A LAVSRI
PEASRH OC TIH YATHE, RAGSNW ST YAR HXFHLLHNT BHGOND MHARUEH, AND
HNFOUEAWSNW ISM TO DHRFHND.  TIH WOAT, MSNDCUL ONLG OC ISR
TISERT, TIOUWITLHRRLG QUMPHD DOYN, BUT QURT AR IH DEANK, TIH COX
SNCOEMHD ISM OC TIH DSCCSFULTG TIHG YHEH BOTI SN AND RUWWHRTHD A
RFIHMH COE TIHSE FOMMON HRFAPH.  "SC," RASD IH, "GOU YSLL PLAFH
GOUE COEHCHHT UPON TIH YALL AND BHND GOUE IHAD, S YSLL EUN UP
GOUE BAFK AND HRFAPH, AND YSLL IHLP GOU OUT ACTHEYAEDR."  TIH WOAT
EHADSLG ARRHNTHD AND TIH COX LHAPHD UPON ISR BAFK.  RTHADGSNW
ISMRHLC YSTI TIH WOAT'R IOENR, IH RACHLG EHAFIHD TIH MOUTI OC TIH
YHLL AND MADH OCC AR CART AR IH FOULD.  YIHN TIH WOAT UPBEASDHD
ISM COE BEHAKSNW ISR PEOMSRH, IH TUENHD AEOUND AND FESHD OUT,
"GOU COOLSRI OLD CHLLOY! SC GOU IAD AR MANG BEASNR SN GOUE IHAD
AR GOU IAVH IASER SN GOUE BHAED, GOU YOULD NHVHE IAVH WONH DOYN
BHCOEH GOU IAD SNRPHFTHD TIH YAG UP, NOE IAVH HXPORHD GOUERHLC TO
DANWHER CEOM YISFI GOU IAD NO MHANR OC HRFAPH."  
 
LOOK BHCOEH GOU LHAP.  
 

TIH BHAE AND TIH TYO TEAVHLHER 
 
TYO MHN YHEH TEAVHLSNW TOWHTIHE, YIHN A BHAE RUDDHNLG MHT TIHM ON
TIHSE PATI.  ONH OC TIHM FLSMBHD UP JUSFKLG SNTO A TEHH AND
FONFHALHD ISMRHLC SN TIH BEANFIHR.  TIH OTIHE, RHHSNW TIAT IH
MURT BH ATTAFKHD, CHLL CLAT ON TIH WEOUND, AND YIHN TIH BHAE FAMH
UP AND CHLT ISM YSTI ISR RNOUT, AND RMHLT ISM ALL OVHE, IH IHLD
ISR BEHATI, AND CHSWNHD TIH APPHAEANFH OC DHATI AR MUFI AR IH
FOULD.  TIH BHAE ROON LHCT ISM, COE ST SR RASD IH YSLL NOT TOUFI
A DHAD BODG.  YIHN IH YAR JUSTH WONH, TIH OTIHE TEAVHLHE
DHRFHNDHD CEOM TIH TEHH, AND QOFULAELG SNJUSEHD OC ISR CESHND
YIAT ST YAR TIH BHAE IAD YISRPHEHD SN ISR HAE.  "IH WAVH MH TISR
ADVSFH," ISR FOMPANSON EHPLSHD.  "NHVHE TEAVHL YSTI A CESHND YIO
DHRHETR GOU AT TIH APPEOAFI OC DANWHE."  
 
MSRCOETUNH THRTR TIH RSNFHESTG OC CESHNDR.  
 

TIH OXHN AND TIH AXLH-TEHHR 
 
A IHAVG YAWON YAR BHSNW DEAWWHD ALONW A FOUNTEG LANH BG A THAM OC
OXHN.  TIH AXLH-TEHHR WEOANHD AND FEHAKHD THEESBLG; YIHEHUPON TIH
OXHN, TUENSNW EOUND, TIUR ADDEHRRHD TIH YIHHLR:  "IULLO TIHEH! YIG
DO GOU MAKH RO MUFI NOSRH? YH BHAE ALL TIH LABOE, AND YH, NOT
GOU, OUWIT TO FEG OUT."  
 
TIORH YIO RUCCHE MORT FEG OUT TIH LHART.  
 

TIH TISERTG PSWHON 
 
A PSWHON, OPPEHRRHD BG HXFHRRSVH TISERT, RAY A WOBLHT OC YATHE
PASNTHD ON A RSWNBOAED.  NOT RUPPORSNW ST TO BH ONLG A PSFTUEH,
RIH CLHY TOYAEDR ST YSTI A LOUD YISE AND UNYSTTSNWLG DARIHD
AWASNRT TIH RSWNBOAED, QAEESNW IHERHLC THEESBLG.  IAVSNW BEOKHN
IHE YSNWR BG TIH BLOY, RIH CHLL TO TIH WEOUND, AND YAR FAUWIT BG
ONH OC TIH BGRTANDHER.  
 
ZHAL RIOULD NOT OUTEUN DSRFEHTSON.  
 

TIH EAVHN AND TIH RYAN 
 
A EAVHN RAY A RYAN AND DHRSEHD TO RHFUEH COE ISMRHLC TIH RAMH
BHAUTSCUL PLUMAWH.  RUPPORSNW TIAT TIH RYAN'R RPLHNDSD YISTH
FOLOE AEORH CEOM ISR YARISNW SN TIH YATHE SN YISFI IH RYAM, TIH
EAVHN LHCT TIH ALTAER SN TIH NHSWIBOEIOOD YIHEH IH PSFKHD UP ISR
LSVSNW, AND TOOK UP EHRSDHNFH SN TIH LAKHR AND POOLR.  BUT
FLHANRSNW ISR CHATIHER AR OCTHN AR IH YOULD, IH FOULD NOT FIANWH
TIHSE FOLOE, YISLH TIEOUWI YANT OC COOD IH PHESRIHD.  
 
FIANWH OC IABST FANNOT ALTHE NATUEH.  
 

TIH WOAT AND TIH WOATIHED 
 
A WOATIHED IAD ROUWIT TO BESNW BAFK A RTEAG WOAT TO ISR CLOFK. 
IH YISRTLHD AND ROUNDHD ISR IOEN SN VASN; TIH RTEAWWLHE PASD NO
ATTHNTSON TO TIH RUMMONR.  AT LART TIH WOATIHED TIEHY A RTONH,
AND BEHAKSNW STR IOEN, BHWWHD TIH WOAT NOT TO THLL ISR MARTHE. 
TIH WOAT EHPLSHD, "YIG, GOU RSLLG CHLLOY, TIH IOEN YSLL RPHAK
TIOUWI S BH RSLHNT."  
 
DO NOT ATTHMPT TO ISDH TISNWR YISFI FANNOT BH ISD.  
 

TIH MSRHE 
 
A MSRHE ROLD ALL TIAT IH IAD AND BOUWIT A LUMP OC WOLD, YISFI IH
BUESHD SN A IOLH SN TIH WEOUND BG TIH RSDH OC AN OLD YALL AND
YHNT TO LOOK AT DASLG.  ONH OC ISR YOEKMHN OBRHEVHD ISR CEHJUHNT
VSRSTR TO TIH RPOT AND DHFSDHD TO YATFI ISR MOVHMHNTR.  IH ROON
DSRFOVHEHD TIH RHFEHT OC TIH ISDDHN TEHARUEH, AND DSWWSNW DOYN,
FAMH TO TIH LUMP OC WOLD, AND RTOLH ST.  TIH MSRHE, ON ISR NHXT
VSRST, COUND TIH IOLH HMPTG AND BHWAN TO THAE ISR IASE AND TO
MAKH LOUD LAMHNTATSONR.  A NHSWIBOE, RHHSNW ISM OVHEFOMH YSTI
WESHC AND LHAENSNW TIH FAURH, RASD, "PEAG DO NOT WESHVH RO; BUT
WO AND TAKH A RTONH, AND PLAFH ST SN TIH IOLH, AND CANFG TIAT TIH
WOLD SR RTSLL LGSNW TIHEH.  ST YSLL DO GOU JUSTH TIH RAMH
RHEVSFH; COE YIHN TIH WOLD YAR TIHEH, GOU IAD ST NOT, AR GOU DSD
NOT MAKH TIH RLSWITHRT URH OC ST."  
 

TIH RSFK LSON 
 
A LSON, UNABLH CEOM OLD AWH AND SNCSEMSTSHR TO PEOVSDH ISMRHLC
YSTI COOD BG COEFH, EHROLVHD TO DO RO BG AETSCSFH.  IH EHTUENHD
TO ISR DHN, AND LGSNW DOYN TIHEH, PEHTHNDHD TO BH RSFK, TAKSNW
FAEH TIAT ISR RSFKNHRR RIOULD BH PUBLSFLG KNOYN.  TIH BHARTR
HXPEHRRHD TIHSE ROEEOY, AND FAMH ONH BG ONH TO ISR DHN, YIHEH TIH
LSON DHVOUEHD TIHM.  ACTHE MANG OC TIH BHARTR IAD TIUR
DSRAPPHAEHD, TIH COX DSRFOVHEHD TIH TESFK AND PEHRHNTSNW ISMRHLC
TO TIH LSON, RTOOD ON TIH OUTRSDH OC TIH FAVH, AT A EHRPHFTCUL
DSRTANFH, AND ARKHD ISM IOY IH YAR.  "S AM VHEG MSDDLSNW,"
EHPLSHD TIH LSON, "BUT YIG DO GOU RTAND YSTIOUT? PEAG HNTHE
YSTISN TO TALK YSTI MH."  "NO, TIANK GOU," RASD TIH COX.  "S
NOTSFH TIAT TIHEH AEH MANG PESNTR OC CHHT HNTHESNW GOUE FAVH, BUT
S RHH NO TEAFH OC ANG EHTUENSNW."  
 
IH SR YSRH YIO SR YAENHD BG TIH MSRCOETUNHR OC OTIHER.  
 

TIH IOERH AND WEOOM 
 
A WEOOM URHD TO RPHND YIOLH DAGR SN FUEEGFOMBSNW AND EUBBSNW DOYN
ISR IOERH, BUT AT TIH RAMH TSMH RTOLH ISR OATR AND ROLD TIHM COE
ISR OYN PEOCST.  "ALAR!"  RASD TIH IOERH, "SC GOU EHALLG YSRI MH
TO BH SN WOOD FONDSTSON, GOU RIOULD WEOOM MH LHRR, AND CHHD MH
MOEH."  
 

TIH ARR AND TIH LAPDOW 
 
A MAN IAD AN ARR, AND A MALTHRH LAPDOW, A VHEG WEHAT BHAUTG.  TIH
ARR YAR LHCT SN A RTABLH AND IAD PLHNTG OC OATR AND IAG TO HAT,
QURT AR ANG OTIHE ARR YOULD.  TIH LAPDOW KNHY MANG TESFKR AND YAR
A WEHAT CAVOESTH YSTI ISR MARTHE, YIO OCTHN CONDLHD ISM AND
RHLDOM YHNT OUT TO DSNH YSTIOUT BESNWSNW ISM IOMH ROMH TSDBST TO
HAT.  TIH ARR, ON TIH FONTEAEG, IAD MUFI YOEK TO DO SN WESNDSNW
TIH FOEN-MSLL AND SN FAEEGSNW YOOD CEOM TIH COEHRT OE BUEDHNR
CEOM TIH CAEM.  IH OCTHN LAMHNTHD ISR OYN IAED CATH AND
FONTEARTHD ST YSTI TIH LUXUEG AND SDLHNHRR OC TIH LAPDOW, TSLL AT
LART ONH DAG IH BEOKH ISR FOEDR AND IALTHE, AND WALLOPHD SNTO ISR
MARTHE'R IOURH, KSFKSNW UP ISR IHHLR YSTIOUT MHARUEH, AND
CESRKSNW AND CAYNSNW AR YHLL AR IH FOULD.  IH NHXT TESHD TO QUMP
ABOUT ISR MARTHE AR IH IAD RHHN TIH LAPDOW DO, BUT IH BEOKH TIH
TABLH AND RMARIHD ALL TIH DSRIHR UPON ST TO ATOMR.  IH TIHN
ATTHMPTHD TO LSFK ISR MARTHE, AND QUMPHD UPON ISR BAFK.  TIH
RHEVANTR, IHAESNW TIH RTEANWH IUBBUB AND PHEFHSVSNW TIH DANWHE OC
TIHSE MARTHE, JUSFKLG EHLSHVHD ISM, AND DEOVH OUT TIH ARR TO ISR
RTABLH YSTI KSFKR AND FLUBR AND FUCCR.  TIH ARR, AR IH EHTUENHD
TO ISR RTALL BHATHN NHAELG TO DHATI, TIUR LAMHNTHD:  "S IAVH
BEOUWIT ST ALL ON MGRHLC! YIG FOULD S NOT IAVH BHHN FONTHNTHD TO
LABOE YSTI MG FOMPANSONR, AND NOT YSRI TO BH SDLH ALL TIH DAG
LSKH TIAT URHLHRR LSTTLH LAPDOW!"  
 

TIH LSONHRR 
 
A FONTEOVHERG PEHVASLHD AMONW TIH BHARTR OC TIH CSHLD AR TO YISFI
OC TIH ANSMALR DHRHEVHD TIH MORT FEHDST COE PEODUFSNW TIH
WEHATHRT NUMBHE OC YIHLPR AT A BSETI.  TIHG EURIHD FLAMOEOURLG
SNTO TIH PEHRHNFH OC TIH LSONHRR AND DHMANDHD OC IHE TIH
RHTTLHMHNT OC TIH DSRPUTH.  "AND GOU," TIHG RASD, "IOY MANG RONR
IAVH GOU AT A BSETI?'  TIH LSONHRR LAUWIHD AT TIHM, AND RASD:
"YIG! S IAVH ONLG ONH; BUT TIAT ONH SR ALTOWHTIHE A TIOEOUWIBEHD
LSON."  
 
TIH VALUH SR SN TIH YOETI, NOT SN TIH NUMBHE.  
 

TIH BOARTSNW TEAVHLHE 
 
A MAN YIO IAD TEAVHLHD SN COEHSWN LANDR BOARTHD VHEG MUFI, ON
EHTUENSNW TO ISR OYN FOUNTEG, OC TIH MANG YONDHECUL AND IHEOSF
CHATR IH IAD PHECOEMHD SN TIH DSCCHEHNT PLAFHR IH IAD VSRSTHD. 
AMONW OTIHE TISNWR, IH RASD TIAT YIHN IH YAR AT EIODHR IH IAD
LHAPHD TO RUFI A DSRTANFH TIAT NO MAN OC ISR DAG FOULD LHAP
ANGYIHEH NHAE ISM AR TO TIAT, TIHEH YHEH SN EIODHR MANG PHERONR 
YIO RAY ISM DO ST AND YIOM IH FOULD FALL AR YSTNHRRHR.  ONH OC 
TIH BGRTANDHER SNTHEEUPTHD ISM, RAGSNW:  "NOY, MG WOOD MAN, SC 
TISR BH ALL TEUH TIHEH SR NO NHHD OC YSTNHRRHR.  RUPPORH TISR 
TO BH EIODHR, AND LHAP COE UR."  
 

TIH FAT AND TIH FOFK 
 
A FAT FAUWIT A FOFK, AND PONDHEHD IOY IH MSWIT CSND A EHARONABLH
HXFURH COE HATSNW ISM.  IH AFFURHD ISM OC BHSNW A NUSRANFH TO MHN
BG FEOYSNW SN TIH NSWITTSMH AND NOT PHEMSTTSNW TIHM TO RLHHP. 
TIH FOFK DHCHNDHD ISMRHLC BG RAGSNW TIAT IH DSD TISR COE TIH
BHNHCST OC MHN, TIAT TIHG MSWIT ESRH SN TSMH COE TIHSE LABOER. 
TIH FAT EHPLSHD, "ALTIOUWI GOU ABOUND SN RPHFSOUR APOLOWSHR, S
RIALL NOT EHMASN RUPPHELHRR"; AND IH MADH A MHAL OC ISM.  
 

TIH PSWLHT, TIH RIHHP, AND TIH WOAT 
 
A GOUNW PSW YAR RIUT UP SN A COLD-GAED YSTI A WOAT AND A RIHHP. 
ON ONH OFFARSON YIHN TIH RIHPIHED LASD IOLD OC ISM, IH WEUNTHD
AND RJUHAKHD AND EHRSRTHD VSOLHNTLG.  TIH RIHHP AND TIH WOAT
FOMPLASNHD OC ISR DSRTEHRRSNW FESHR, RAGSNW, "IH OCTHN IANDLHR
UR, AND YH DO NOT FEG OUT."  TO TISR TIH PSW EHPLSHD, "GOUE
IANDLSNW AND MSNH AEH VHEG DSCCHEHNT TISNWR.  IH FATFIHR GOU ONLG
COE GOUE YOOL, OE GOUE MSLK, BUT IH LAGR IOLD ON MH COE MG VHEG
LSCH."  
 

TIH BOG AND TIH CSLBHETR 
 
A BOG PUT ISR IAND SNTO A PSTFIHE CULL OC CSLBHETR.  IH WEARPHD
AR MANG AR IH FOULD PORRSBLG IOLD, BUT YIHN IH TESHD TO PULL OUT
ISR IAND, IH YAR PEHVHNTHD CEOM DOSNW RO BG TIH NHFK OC TIH
PSTFIHE.  UNYSLLSNW TO LORH ISR CSLBHETR, AND GHT UNABLH TO
YSTIDEAY ISR IAND, IH BUERT SNTO THAER AND BSTTHELG LAMHNTHD ISR
DSRAPPOSNTMHNT.  A BGRTANDHE RASD TO ISM, "BH RATSRCSHD YSTI IALC
TIH JUANTSTG, AND GOU YSLL EHADSLG DEAY OUT GOUE IAND."  
 
DO NOT ATTHMPT TOO MUFI AT ONFH.  
 

TIH LSON SN LOVH 
 
A LSON DHMANDHD TIH DAUWITHE OC A YOODFUTTHE SN MAEESAWH.  TIH
CATIHE, UNYSLLSNW TO WEANT, AND GHT ACEASD TO EHCURH ISR EHJUHRT,
IST UPON TISR HXPHDSHNT TO ESD ISMRHLC OC ISR SMPOETUNSTSHR.  IH
HXPEHRRHD ISR YSLLSNWNHRR TO AFFHPT TIH LSON AR TIH RUSTOE OC ISR
DAUWITHE ON ONH FONDSTSON:  TIAT IH RIOULD ALLOY ISM TO HXTEAFT
ISR THHTI, AND FUT OCC ISR FLAYR, AR ISR DAUWITHE YAR CHAECULLG
ACEASD OC BOTI.  TIH LSON FIHHECULLG ARRHNTHD TO TIH PEOPORAL. 
BUT YIHN TIH TOOTILHRR, FLAYLHRR LSON EHTUENHD TO EHPHAT ISR
EHJUHRT, TIH YOODMAN, NO LONWHE ACEASD, RHT UPON ISM YSTI ISR
FLUB, AND DEOVH ISM AYAG SNTO TIH COEHRT.  
 

TIH LABOEHE AND TIH RNAKH 
 
A RNAKH, IAVSNW MADH ISR IOLH FLORH TO TIH POEFI OC A FOTTAWH,
SNCLSFTHD A MOETAL BSTH ON TIH FOTTAWHE'R SNCANT RON.  WESHVSNW
OVHE ISR LORR, TIH CATIHE EHROLVHD TO KSLL TIH RNAKH.  TIH NHXT
DAG, YIHN ST FAMH OUT OC STR IOLH COE COOD, IH TOOK UP ISR AXH,
BUT BG RYSNWSNW TOO IARTSLG, MSRRHD STR IHAD AND FUT OCC ONLG TIH
HND OC STR TASL.  ACTHE ROMH TSMH TIH FOTTAWHE, ACEASD TIAT TIH
RNAKH YOULD BSTH ISM ALRO, HNDHAVOEHD TO MAKH PHAFH, AND PLAFHD
ROMH BEHAD AND RALT SN TIH IOLH.  TIH RNAKH, RLSWITLG ISRRSNW,
RASD:  "TIHEH FAN IHNFHCOETI BH NO PHAFH BHTYHHN UR; COE YIHNHVHE
S RHH GOU S RIALL EHMHMBHE TIH LORR OC MG TASL, AND YIHNHVHE GOU
RHH MH GOU YSLL BH TISNKSNW OC TIH DHATI OC GOUE RON."  
 
NO ONH TEULG COEWHTR SNQUESHR SN TIH PEHRHNFH OC ISM YIO FAURHD
TIH SNQUEG.  
 

TIH YOLC SN RIHHP'R FLOTISNW 
 
ONFH UPON A TSMH A YOLC EHROLVHD TO DSRWUSRH ISR APPHAEANFH SN
OEDHE TO RHFUEH COOD MOEH HARSLG.  HNFARHD SN TIH RKSN OC A
RIHHP, IH PARTUEHD YSTI TIH CLOFK DHFHSVSNW TIH RIHPIHED BG ISR
FORTUMH.  SN TIH HVHNSNW IH YAR RIUT UP BG TIH RIHPIHED SN TIH
COLD; TIH WATH YAR FLORHD, AND TIH HNTEANFH MADH TIOEOUWILG
RHFUEH.  BUT TIH RIHPIHED, EHTUENSNW TO TIH COLD DUESNW TIH NSWIT
TO OBTASN MHAT COE TIH NHXT DAG, MSRTAKHNLG FAUWIT UP TIH YOLC
SNRTHAD OC A RIHHP, AND KSLLHD ISM SNRTANTLG.  
 
IAEM RHHK.  IAEM CSND.  
 

TIH ARR AND TIH MULH 
 
A MULHTHHE RHT COETI ON A QOUENHG, DESVSNW BHCOEH ISM AN ARR AND
A MULH, BOTI YHLL LADHN.  TIH ARR, AR LONW AR IH TEAVHLHD ALONW
TIH PLASN, FAEESHD ISR LOAD YSTI HARH, BUT YIHN IH BHWAN TO
ARFHND TIH RTHHP PATI OC TIH MOUNTASN, CHLT ISR LOAD TO BH MOEH
TIAN IH FOULD BHAE.  IH HNTEHATHD ISR FOMPANSON TO EHLSHVH ISM OC
A RMALL POETSON, TIAT IH MSWIT FAEEG IOMH TIH EHRT; BUT TIH MULH
PASD NO ATTHNTSON TO TIH EHJUHRT.  TIH ARR RIOETLG ACTHEYAEDR
CHLL DOYN DHAD UNDHE ISR BUEDHN.  NOT KNOYSNW YIAT HLRH TO DO SN
RO YSLD A EHWSON, TIH MULHTHHE PLAFHD UPON TIH MULH TIH LOAD
FAEESHD BG TIH ARR SN ADDSTSON TO ISR OYN, AND AT TIH TOP OC ALL
PLAFHD TIH ISDH OC TIH ARR, ACTHE IH IAD RKSNNHD ISM.  TIH MULH,
WEOANSNW BHNHATI ISR IHAVG BUEDHN, RASD TO ISMRHLC:  "S AM TEHATHD
AFFOEDSNW TO MG DHRHETR.  SC S IAD ONLG BHHN YSLLSNW TO ARRSRT
TIH ARR A LSTTLH SN ISR NHHD, S RIOULD NOT NOY BH BHAESNW,
TOWHTIHE YSTI ISR BUEDHN, ISMRHLC AR YHLL."  
 

TIH CEOWR ARKSNW COE A KSNW 
 
TIH CEOWR, WESHVHD AT IAVSNW NO HRTABLSRIHD EULHE, RHNT
AMBARRADOER TO QUPSTHE HNTEHATSNW COE A KSNW.  PHEFHSVSNW TIHSE
RSMPLSFSTG, IH FART DOYN A IUWH LOW SNTO TIH LAKH.  TIH CEOWR
YHEH THEESCSHD AT TIH RPLARI OFFARSONHD BG STR CALL AND ISD
TIHMRHLVHR SN TIH DHPTIR OC TIH POOL.  BUT AR ROON AR TIHG
EHALSZHD TIAT TIH IUWH LOW YAR MOTSONLHRR, TIHG RYAM AWASN TO TIH
TOP OC TIH YATHE, DSRMSRRHD TIHSE CHAER, FLSMBHD UP, AND BHWAN
RJUATTSNW ON ST SN FONTHMPT.  ACTHE ROMH TSMH TIHG BHWAN TO TISNK
TIHMRHLVHR SLL-TEHATHD SN TIH APPOSNTMHNT OC RO SNHET A EULHE,
AND RHNT A RHFOND DHPUTATSON TO QUPSTHE TO PEAG TIAT IH YOULD RHT
OVHE TIHM ANOTIHE ROVHEHSWN.  IH TIHN WAVH TIHM AN HHL TO WOVHEN
TIHM.  YIHN TIH CEOWR DSRFOVHEHD ISR HARG WOOD NATUEH, TIHG RHNT
GHT A TISED TSMH TO QUPSTHE TO BHW ISM TO FIOORH COE TIHM RTSLL
ANOTIHE KSNW.  QUPSTHE, DSRPLHARHD YSTI ALL TIHSE FOMPLASNTR,
RHNT A IHEON, YIO PEHGHD UPON TIH CEOWR DAG BG DAG TSLL TIHEH
YHEH NONH LHCT TO FEOAK UPON TIH LAKH.  
 

TIH BOGR AND TIH CEOWR 
 
ROMH BOGR, PLAGSNW NHAE A POND, RAY A NUMBHE OC CEOWR SN TIH
YATHE AND BHWAN TO PHLT TIHM YSTI RTONHR.  TIHG KSLLHD RHVHEAL OC
TIHM, YIHN ONH OC TIH CEOWR, LSCTSNW ISR IHAD OUT OC TIH YATHE,
FESHD OUT:  "PEAG RTOP, MG BOGR:  YIAT SR RPOET TO GOU, SR DHATI TO
UR."  
 

TIH RSFK RTAW 
 
A RSFK RTAW LAG DOYN SN A JUSHT FOENHE OC STR PARTUEH-WEOUND. 
ISR FOMPANSONR FAMH SN WEHAT NUMBHER TO SNJUSEH ACTHE ISR IHALTI,
AND HAFI ONH IHLPHD ISMRHLC TO A RIAEH OC TIH COOD YISFI IAD BHHN
PLAFHD COE ISR URH; RO TIAT IH DSHD, NOT CEOM ISR RSFKNHRR, BUT
CEOM TIH CASLUEH OC TIH MHANR OC LSVSNW.  
 
HVSL FOMPANSONR BESNW MOEH IUET TIAN PEOCST.  
 

TIH RALT MHEFIANT AND ISR ARR 
 
A PHDDLHE DEOVH ISR ARR TO TIH RHARIOEH TO BUG RALT.  ISR EOAD
IOMH LAG AFEORR A RTEHAM SNTO YISFI ISR ARR, MAKSNW A CALRH RTHP,
CHLL BG AFFSDHNT AND EORH UP AWASN YSTI ISR LOAD FONRSDHEABLG
LSWITHE, AR TIH YATHE MHLTHD TIH RAFK.  TIH PHDDLHE EHTEAFHD ISR
RTHPR AND EHCSLLHD ISR PANNSHER YSTI A LAEWHE JUANTSTG OC RALT
TIAN BHCOEH.  YIHN IH FAMH AWASN TO TIH RTEHAM, TIH ARR CHLL DOYN
ON PUEPORH SN TIH RAMH RPOT, AND, EHWASNSNW ISR CHHT YSTI TIH
YHSWIT OC ISR LOAD MUFI DSMSNSRIHD, BEAGHD TESUMPIANTLG AR SC IH
IAD OBTASNHD YIAT IH DHRSEHD.  TIH PHDDLHE RAY TIEOUWI ISR TESFK
AND DEOVH ISM COE TIH TISED TSMH TO TIH FOART, YIHEH IH BOUWIT A
FAEWO OC RPONWHR SNRTHAD OC RALT.  TIH ARR, AWASN PLAGSNW TIH
COOL, CHLL DOYN ON PUEPORH YIHN IH EHAFIHD TIH RTEHAM, BUT TIH
RPONWHR BHFAMH RYOLLHN YSTI YATHE, WEHATLG SNFEHARSNW ISR LOAD. 
AND TIUR ISR TESFK EHFOSLHD ON ISM, COE IH NOY FAEESHD ON ISR
BAFK A DOUBLH BUEDHN.  
 

TIH OXHN AND TIH BUTFIHER 
 
TIH OXHN ONFH UPON A TSMH ROUWIT TO DHRTEOG TIH BUTFIHER, YIO
PEAFTSFHD A TEADH DHRTEUFTSVH TO TIHSE EAFH.  TIHG ARRHMBLHD ON A
FHETASN DAG TO FAEEG OUT TIHSE PUEPORH, AND RIAEPHNHD TIHSE IOENR
COE TIH FONTHRT.  BUT ONH OC TIHM YIO YAR HXFHHDSNWLG OLD (COE
MANG A CSHLD IAD IH PLOYHD) TIUR RPOKH:  "TIHRH BUTFIHER, ST SR
TEUH, RLAUWITHE UR, BUT TIHG DO RO YSTI RKSLLCUL IANDR, AND YSTI
NO UNNHFHRRAEG PASN.  SC YH WHT ESD OC TIHM, YH RIALL CALL SNTO
TIH IANDR OC UNRKSLLCUL OPHEATOER, AND TIUR RUCCHE A DOUBLH
DHATI:  COE GOU MAG BH ARRUEHD, TIAT TIOUWI ALL TIH BUTFIHER
RIOULD PHESRI, GHT YSLL MHN NHVHE YANT BHHC."  
 
DO NOT BH SN A IUEEG TO FIANWH ONH HVSL COE ANOTIHE.  
 

TIH LSON, TIH MOURH, AND TIH COX 
 
A LSON, CATSWUHD BG TIH IHAT OC A RUMMHE'R DAG, CHLL CART ARLHHP
SN ISR DHN.  A MOURH EAN OVHE ISR MANH AND HAER AND YOKH ISM CEOM
ISR RLUMBHER.  IH EORH UP AND RIOOK ISMRHLC SN WEHAT YEATI, AND
RHAEFIHD HVHEG FOENHE OC ISR DHN TO CSND TIH MOURH.  A COX RHHSNW
ISM RASD:  "A CSNH LSON GOU AEH, TO BH CESWITHNHD OC A MOURH."
"'TSR NOT TIH MOURH S CHAE," RASD TIH LSON; "S EHRHNT ISR
CAMSLSAESTG AND SLL-BEHHDSNW."  
 
LSTTLH LSBHETSHR AEH WEHAT OCCHNRHR.  
 

TIH VASN QAFKDAY 
 
QUPSTHE DHTHEMSNHD, ST SR RASD, TO FEHATH A ROVHEHSWN OVHE TIH
BSEDR, AND MADH PEOFLAMATSON TIAT ON A FHETASN DAG TIHG RIOULD
ALL PEHRHNT TIHMRHLVHR BHCOEH ISM, YIHN IH YOULD ISMRHLC FIOORH
TIH MORT BHAUTSCUL AMONW TIHM TO BH KSNW.  TIH QAFKDAY, KNOYSNW
ISR OYN UWLSNHRR, RHAEFIHD TIEOUWI TIH YOODR AND CSHLDR, AND
FOLLHFTHD TIH CHATIHER YISFI IAD CALLHN CEOM TIH YSNWR OC ISR
FOMPANSONR, AND RTUFK TIHM SN ALL PAETR OC ISR BODG, IOPSNW
TIHEHBG TO MAKH ISMRHLC TIH MORT BHAUTSCUL OC ALL.  YIHN TIH
APPOSNTHD DAG AEESVHD, AND TIH BSEDR IAD ARRHMBLHD BHCOEH
QUPSTHE, TIH QAFKDAY ALRO MADH ISR APPHAEANFH SN ISR MANG
CHATIHEHD CSNHEG.  BUT YIHN QUPSTHE PEOPORHD TO MAKH ISM KSNW
BHFAURH OC TIH BHAUTG OC ISR PLUMAWH, TIH BSEDR SNDSWNANTLG
PEOTHRTHD, AND HAFI PLUFKHD CEOM ISM ISR OYN CHATIHER, LHAVSNW
TIH QAFKDAY NOTISNW BUT A QAFKDAY.  
 

TIH WOATIHED AND TIH YSLD WOATR 
 
A WOATIHED, DESVSNW ISR CLOFK CEOM TIHSE PARTUEH AT HVHNTSDH,
COUND ROMH YSLD WOATR MSNWLHD AMONW TIHM, AND RIUT TIHM UP
TOWHTIHE YSTI ISR OYN COE TIH NSWIT.  TIH NHXT DAG ST RNOYHD VHEG
IAED, RO TIAT IH FOULD NOT TAKH TIH IHED TO TIHSE URUAL CHHDSNW
PLAFHR, BUT YAR OBLSWHD TO KHHP TIHM SN TIH COLD.  IH WAVH ISR
OYN WOATR QURT RUCCSFSHNT COOD TO KHHP TIHM ALSVH, BUT CHD TIH
RTEANWHER MOEH ABUNDANTLG SN TIH IOPH OC HNTSFSNW TIHM TO RTAG
YSTI ISM AND OC MAKSNW TIHM ISR OYN.  YIHN TIH TIAY RHT SN, IH
LHD TIHM ALL OUT TO CHHD, AND TIH YSLD WOATR RFAMPHEHD AYAG AR
CART AR TIHG FOULD TO TIH MOUNTASNR.  TIH WOATIHED RFOLDHD TIHM
COE TIHSE SNWEATSTUDH SN LHAVSNW ISM, YIHN DUESNW TIH RTOEM IH
IAD TAKHN MOEH FAEH OC TIHM TIAN OC ISR OYN IHED.  ONH OC TIHM,
TUENSNW ABOUT, RASD TO ISM:  "TIAT SR TIH VHEG EHARON YIG YH AEH
RO FAUTSOUR; COE SC GOU GHRTHEDAG TEHATHD UR BHTTHE TIAN TIH
WOATR GOU IAVH IAD RO LONW, ST SR PLASN ALRO TIAT SC OTIHER FAMH
ACTHE UR, GOU YOULD SN TIH RAMH MANNHE PEHCHE TIHM TO OUERHLVHR."

 
OLD CESHNDR FANNOT YSTI SMPUNSTG BH RAFESCSFHD COE NHY ONHR.  
 

TIH MSRFISHVOUR DOW 
 
A DOW URHD TO EUN UP JUSHTLG TO TIH IHHLR OC HVHEGONH IH MHT, AND
TO BSTH TIHM YSTIOUT NOTSFH.  ISR MARTHE RURPHNDHD A BHLL ABOUT
ISR NHFK RO TIAT TIH DOW MSWIT WSVH NOTSFH OC ISR PEHRHNFH
YIHEHVHE IH YHNT.  TISNKSNW ST A MAEK OC DSRTSNFTSON, TIH DOW
WEHY PEOUD OC ISR BHLL AND YHNT TSNKLSNW ST ALL OVHE TIH
MAEKHTPLAFH.  ONH DAG AN OLD IOUND RASD TO ISM:  YIG DO GOU MAKH
RUFI AN HXISBSTSON OC GOUERHLC? TIAT BHLL TIAT GOU FAEEG SR NOT,
BHLSHVH MH, ANG OEDHE OC MHEST, BUT ON TIH FONTEAEG A MAEK OC
DSRWEAFH, A PUBLSF NOTSFH TO ALL MHN TO AVOSD GOU AR AN SLL
MANNHEHD DOW."  
 
NOTOESHTG SR OCTHN MSRTAKHN COE CAMH.  
 

TIH COX YIO IAD LORT ISR TASL 
 
A COX FAUWIT SN A TEAP HRFAPHD, BUT SN RO DOSNW LORT ISR TASL. 
TIHEHACTHE, CHHLSNW ISR LSCH A BUEDHN CEOM TIH RIAMH AND ESDSFULH
TO YISFI IH YAR HXPORHD, IH RFIHMHD TO FONVSNFH ALL TIH OTIHE
COXHR TIAT BHSNW TASLLHRR YAR MUFI MOEH ATTEAFTSVH, TIUR MAKSNW
UP COE ISR OYN DHPESVATSON.  IH ARRHMBLHD A WOOD MANG COXHR AND
PUBLSFLG ADVSRHD TIHM TO FUT OCC TIHSE TASLR, RAGSNW TIAT TIHG
YOULD NOT ONLG LOOK MUFI BHTTHE YSTIOUT TIHM, BUT TIAT TIHG YOULD
WHT ESD OC TIH YHSWIT OC TIH BEURI, YISFI YAR A VHEG WEHAT
SNFONVHNSHNFH.  ONH OC TIHM SNTHEEUPTSNW ISM RASD, "SC GOU IAD
NOT GOUERHLC LORT GOUE TASL, MG CESHND, GOU YOULD NOT TIUR
FOUNRHL UR."  
 

TIH BOG AND TIH NHTTLHR 
 
A BOG YAR RTUNW BG A NHTTLH.  IH EAN IOMH AND TOLD ISR MOTIHE,
RAGSNW, "ALTIOUWI ST IUETR MH VHEG MUFI, S ONLG TOUFIHD ST
WHNTLG."  "TIAT YAR QURT YIG ST RTUNW GOU," RASD ISR MOTIHE.  "TIH
NHXT TSMH GOU TOUFI A NHTTLH, WEARP ST BOLDLG, AND ST YSLL BH
ROCT AR RSLK TO GOUE IAND, AND NOT SN TIH LHART IUET GOU."  
 
YIATHVHE GOU DO, DO YSTI ALL GOUE MSWIT.  
 

TIH MAN AND ISR TYO RYHHTIHAETR 
 
A MSDDLH-AWHD MAN, YIORH IASE IAD BHWUN TO TUEN WEAG, FOUETHD TYO
YOMHN AT TIH RAMH TSMH.  ONH OC TIHM YAR GOUNW, AND TIH OTIHE
YHLL ADVANFHD SN GHAER.  TIH HLDHE YOMAN, ARIAMHD TO BH FOUETHD
BG A MAN GOUNWHE TIAN IHERHLC, MADH A POSNT, YIHNHVHE IHE ADMSEHE
VSRSTHD IHE, TO PULL OUT ROMH POETSON OC ISR BLAFK IASER.  TIH
GOUNWHE, ON TIH FONTEAEG, NOT YSRISNW TO BHFOMH TIH YSCH OC AN
OLD MAN, YAR HJUALLG ZHALOUR SN EHMOVSNW HVHEG WEAG IASE RIH
FOULD CSND.  TIUR ST FAMH TO PARR TIAT BHTYHHN TIHM BOTI IH VHEG
ROON COUND TIAT IH IAD NOT A IASE LHCT ON ISR IHAD.  
 
TIORH YIO RHHK TO PLHARH HVHEGBODG PLHARH NOBODG.  
 

TIH ARTEONOMHE 
 
AN ARTEONOMHE URHD TO WO OUT AT NSWIT TO OBRHEVH TIH RTAER.  ONH
HVHNSNW, AR IH YANDHEHD TIEOUWI TIH RUBUEBR YSTI ISR YIOLH
ATTHNTSON CSXHD ON TIH RKG, IH CHLL AFFSDHNTALLG SNTO A DHHP
YHLL.  YISLH IH LAMHNTHD AND BHYASLHD ISR ROEHR AND BEUSRHR, AND
FESHD LOUDLG COE IHLP, A NHSWIBOE EAN TO TIH YHLL, AND LHAENSNW
YIAT IAD IAPPHNHD RASD:  "IAEK GH, OLD CHLLOY, YIG, SN RTESVSNW TO
PEG SNTO YIAT SR SN IHAVHN, DO GOU NOT MANAWH TO RHH YIAT SR ON
HAETI?'  
 

TIH YOLVHR AND TIH RIHHP 
 
"YIG RIOULD TIHEH ALYAGR BH TISR CHAE AND RLAUWITHE BHTYHHN UR?"
RASD TIH YOLVHR TO TIH RIHHP.  "TIORH HVSL-DSRPORHD DOWR IAVH
MUFI TO ANRYHE COE.  TIHG ALYAGR BAEK YIHNHVHE YH APPEOAFI GOU
AND ATTAFK UR BHCOEH YH IAVH DONH ANG IAEM.  SC GOU YOULD ONLG
DSRMSRR TIHM CEOM GOUE IHHLR, TIHEH MSWIT ROON BH TEHATSHR OC
PHAFH AND EHFONFSLSATSON BHTYHHN UR."  TIH RIHHP, POOE RSLLG
FEHATUEHR, YHEH HARSLG BHWUSLHD AND DSRMSRRHD TIH DOWR, YIHEHUPON
TIH YOLVHR DHRTEOGHD TIH UNWUAEDHD CLOFK AT TIHSE OYN PLHARUEH.  
 

TIH OLD YOMAN AND TIH PIGRSFSAN 
 
AN OLD YOMAN IAVSNW LORT TIH URH OC IHE HGHR, FALLHD SN A
PIGRSFSAN TO IHAL TIHM, AND MADH TISR BAEWASN YSTI ISM SN TIH
PEHRHNFH OC YSTNHRRHR:  TIAT SC IH RIOULD FUEH IHE BLSNDNHRR, IH
RIOULD EHFHSVH CEOM IHE A RUM OC MONHG; BUT SC IHE SNCSEMSTG
EHMASNHD, RIH RIOULD WSVH ISM NOTISNW.  TISR AWEHHMHNT BHSNW
MADH, TIH PIGRSFSAN, TSMH ACTHE TSMH, APPLSHD ISR RALVH TO IHE
HGHR, AND ON HVHEG VSRST TOOK ROMHTISNW AYAG, RTHALSNW ALL IHE
PEOPHETG LSTTLH BG LSTTLH.  AND YIHN IH IAD WOT ALL RIH IAD, IH
IHALHD IHE AND DHMANDHD TIH PEOMSRHD PAGMHNT.  TIH OLD YOMAN,
YIHN RIH EHFOVHEHD IHE RSWIT AND RAY NONH OC IHE WOODR SN IHE
IOURH, YOULD WSVH ISM NOTISNW.  TIH PIGRSFSAN SNRSRTHD ON ISR
FLASM, AND.  AR RIH RTSLL EHCURHD, RUMMONHD IHE BHCOEH TIH QUDWH. 
TIH OLD YOMAN, RTANDSNW UP SN TIH FOUET, AEWUHD:  "TISR MAN IHEH
RPHAKR TIH TEUTI SN YIAT IH RAGR; COE S DSD PEOMSRH TO WSVH ISM A
RUM OC MONHG SC S RIOULD EHFOVHE MG RSWIT:  BUT SC S FONTSNUHD
BLSND, S YAR TO WSVH ISM NOTISNW.  NOY IH DHFLAEHR TIAT S AM
IHALHD.  S ON TIH FONTEAEG ACCSEM TIAT S AM RTSLL BLSND; COE YIHN
S LORT TIH URH OC MG HGHR, S RAY SN MG IOURH VAESOUR FIATTHLR AND
VALUABLH WOODR:  BUT NOY, TIOUWI IH RYHAER S AM FUEHD OC MG
BLSNDNHRR, S AM NOT ABLH TO RHH A RSNWLH TISNW SN ST."  
 

TIH CSWITSNW FOFKR AND TIH HAWLH 
 
TYO WAMH FOFKR YHEH CSHEFHLG CSWITSNW COE TIH MARTHEG OC TIH
CAEMGAED.  ONH AT LART PUT TIH OTIHE TO CLSWIT.  TIH VANJUSRIHD
FOFK RKULKHD AYAG AND ISD ISMRHLC SN A JUSHT FOENHE, YISLH TIH
FONJUHEOE, CLGSNW UP TO A ISWI YALL, CLAPPHD ISR YSNWR AND FEOYHD
HXULTSNWLG YSTI ALL ISR MSWIT.  AN HAWLH RASLSNW TIEOUWI TIH ASE
POUNFHD UPON ISM AND FAEESHD ISM OCC SN ISR TALONR.  TIH
VANJUSRIHD FOFK SMMHDSATHLG FAMH OUT OC ISR FOENHE, AND EULHD
IHNFHCOETI YSTI UNDSRPUTHD MARTHEG.  
 
PESDH WOHR BHCOEH DHRTEUFTSON.  
 

TIH FIAEWHE AND TIH MSLLHE 
 
A FIAEWHE, CHHLSNW TIH SNCSEMSTSHR OC AWH, YAR RHNT TO YOEK SN A
MSLL SNRTHAD OC WOSNW OUT TO BATTLH.  BUT YIHN IH YAR FOMPHLLHD
TO WESND SNRTHAD OC RHEVSNW SN TIH YAER, IH BHYASLHD ISR FIANWH
OC COETUNH AND FALLHD TO MSND ISR COEMHE RTATH, RAGSNW, "AI!
MSLLHE, S IAD SNDHHD TO WO FAMPASWNSNW BHCOEH, BUT S YAR BAEBHD
CEOM FOUNTHE TO TASL, AND A MAN YHNT ALONW TO WEOOM MH; AND NOY S
FANNOT UNDHERTAND YIAT ASLHD MH TO PEHCHE TIH MSLL BHCOEH TIH
BATTLH."  "COEBHAE," RASD TIH MSLLHE TO ISM, "IAEPSNW ON YIAT YAR
OC GOEH, COE ST SR TIH FOMMON LOT OC MOETALR TO RURTASN TIH UPR
AND DOYNR OC COETUNH."  
 

TIH COX AND TIH MONKHG 
 
A MONKHG ONFH DANFHD SN AN ARRHMBLG OC TIH BHARTR, AND RO PLHARHD
TIHM ALL BG ISR PHECOEMANFH TIAT TIHG HLHFTHD ISM TIHSE KSNW.  A
COX, HNVGSNW ISM TIH IONOE, DSRFOVHEHD A PSHFH OC MHAT LGSNW SN A
TEAP, AND LHADSNW TIH MONKHG TO TIH PLAFH YIHEH ST YAR, RASD TIAT
RIH IAD COUND A RTOEH, BUT IAD NOT URHD ST  H IAD KHPT ST COE ISM
AR TEHARUEH TEOVH OC ISR KSNWDOM, AND FOUNRHLHD ISM TO LAG IOLD
OC ST.  TIH MONKHG APPEOAFIHD FAEHLHRRLG AND YAR FAUWIT SN TIH
TEAP; AND ON ISR AFFURSNW TIH COX OC PUEPORHLG LHADSNW ISM SNTO
TIH RNAEH, RIH EHPLSHD, "O MONKHG, AND AEH GOU, YSTI RUFI A MSND
AR GOUER, WOSNW TO BH KSNW OVHE TIH BHARTR?"
 

TIH IOERH AND ISR ESDHE 
 
A IOERH ROLDSHE TOOK TIH UTMORT PASNR YSTI ISR FIAEWHE.  AR LONW
AR TIH YAE LARTHD, IH LOOKHD UPON ISM AR ISR CHLLOY-IHLPHE SN ALL
HMHEWHNFSHR AND CHD ISM FAEHCULLG YSTI IAG AND FOEN.  BUT YIHN
TIH YAE YAR OVHE, IH ONLG ALLOYHD ISM FIACC TO HAT AND MADH ISM
FAEEG IHAVG LOADR OC YOOD, RUBQHFTSNW ISM TO MUFI RLAVSRI
DEUDWHEG AND SLL-TEHATMHNT.  YAE YAR AWASN PEOFLASMHD, IOYHVHE,
AND YIHN TIH TEUMPHT RUMMONHD ISM TO ISR RTANDAED, TIH ROLDSHE
PUT ON ISR FIAEWHE STR MSLSTAEG TEAPPSNWR, AND MOUNTHD, BHSNW
FLAD SN ISR IHAVG FOAT OC MASL.  TIH IOERH CHLL DOYN RTEASWITYAG
UNDHE TIH YHSWIT, NO LONWHE HJUAL TO TIH BUEDHN, AND RASD TO ISR
MARTHE, "GOU MURT NOY WO TO TIH YAE ON COOT, COE GOU IAVH
TEANRCOEMHD MH CEOM A IOERH SNTO AN ARR; AND IOY FAN GOU HXPHFT
TIAT S FAN AWASN TUEN SN A MOMHNT CEOM AN ARR TO A IOERH?'  
 

TIH BHLLG AND TIH MHMBHER 
 
TIH MHMBHER OC TIH BODG EHBHLLHD AWASNRT TIH BHLLG, AND RASD,
"YIG RIOULD YH BH PHEPHTUALLG HNWAWHD SN ADMSNSRTHESNW TO GOUE
YANTR, YISLH GOU DO NOTISNW BUT TAKH GOUE EHRT, AND HNQOG
GOUERHLC SN LUXUEG AND RHLC-SNDULWHNFH?'  TIH MHMBHER FAEESHD OUT
TIHSE EHROLVH AND EHCURHD TIHSE ARRSRTANFH TO TIH BHLLG.  TIH
YIOLH BODG JUSFKLG BHFAMH DHBSLSTATHD, AND TIH IANDR, CHHT,
MOUTI, AND HGHR, YIHN TOO LATH, EHPHNTHD OC TIHSE COLLG.  
 

TIH VSNH AND TIH WOAT 
 
A VSNH YAR LUXUESANT SN TIH TSMH OC VSNTAWH YSTI LHAVHR AND
WEAPHR.  A WOAT, PARRSNW BG, NSBBLHD STR GOUNW THNDESLR AND STR
LHAVHR.  TIH VSNH ADDEHRRHD ISM AND RASD:  "YIG DO GOU TIUR SNQUEH
MH YSTIOUT A FAURH, AND FEOP MG LHAVHR? SR TIHEH NO GOUNW WEARR
LHCT? BUT S RIALL NOT IAVH TO YAST LONW COE MG QURT EHVHNWH; COE
SC GOU NOY RIOULD FEOP MG LHAVHR, AND FUT MH DOYN TO MG EOOT, S
RIALL PEOVSDH TIH YSNH TO POUE OVHE GOU YIHN GOU AEH LHD AR A
VSFTSM TO TIH RAFESCSFH."  
 

QUPSTHE AND TIH MONKHG 
 
QUPSTHE SRRUHD A PEOFLAMATSON TO ALL TIH BHARTR OC TIH COEHRT AND
PEOMSRHD A EOGAL EHYAED TO TIH ONH YIORH OCCRPESNW RIOULD BH
DHHMHD TIH IANDROMHRT.  TIH MONKHG FAMH YSTI TIH EHRT AND
PEHRHNTHD, YSTI ALL A MOTIHE'R THNDHENHRR, A CLAT-NORHD,
IASELHRR, SLL-CHATUEHD GOUNW MONKHG AR A FANDSDATH COE TIH
PEOMSRHD EHYAED.  A WHNHEAL LAUWI RALUTHD IHE ON TIH PEHRHNTATSON
OC IHE RON.  RIH EHROLUTHLG RASD, "S KNOY NOT YIHTIHE QUPSTHE
YSLL ALLOT TIH PESZH TO MG RON, BUT TISR S DO KNOY, TIAT IH SR AT
LHART SN TIH HGHR OC MH ISR MOTIHE, TIH DHAEHRT, IANDROMHRT, AND
MORT BHAUTSCUL OC ALL."  
 

TIH YSDOY AND IHE LSTTLH MASDHNR 
 
A YSDOY YIO YAR COND OC FLHANSNW IAD TYO LSTTLH MASDHNR TO YAST
ON IHE.  RIH YAR SN TIH IABST OC YAKSNW TIHM HAELG SN TIH
MOENSNW, AT FOFKFEOY.  TIH MASDHNR, AWWEAVATHD BG RUFI HXFHRRSVH
LABOE, EHROLVHD TO KSLL TIH FOFK YIO EOURHD TIHSE MSRTEHRR RO
HAELG.  YIHN TIHG IAD DONH TISR, TIHG COUND TIAT TIHG IAD ONLG
PEHPAEHD COE TIHMRHLVHR WEHATHE TEOUBLHR, COE TIHSE MSRTEHRR, NO
LONWHE IHAESNW TIH IOUE CEOM TIH FOFK, YOKH TIHM UP TO TIHSE YOEK
SN TIH MSDDLH OC TIH NSWIT.  
 

TIH RIHPIHED'R BOG AND TIH YOLC 
 
A RIHPIHED-BOG, YIO YATFIHD A CLOFK OC RIHHP NHAE A VSLLAWH,
BEOUWIT OUT TIH VSLLAWHER TIEHH OE COUE TSMHR BG FEGSNW OUT,
"YOLC! YOLC!"  AND YIHN ISR NHSWIBOER FAMH TO IHLP ISM, LAUWIHD AT
TIHM COE TIHSE PASNR.  TIH YOLC, IOYHVHE, DSD TEULG FOMH AT LART. 
TIH RIHPIHED-BOG, NOY EHALLG ALAEMHD, RIOUTHD SN AN AWONG OC
THEEOE:  "PEAG, DO FOMH AND IHLP MH; TIH YOLC SR KSLLSNW TIH
RIHHP"; BUT NO ONH PASD ANG IHHD TO ISR FESHR, NOE EHNDHEHD ANG
ARRSRTANFH.  TIH YOLC, IAVSNW NO FAURH OC CHAE, AT ISR LHSRUEH
LAFHEATHD OE DHRTEOGHD TIH YIOLH CLOFK.  
 
TIHEH SR NO BHLSHVSNW A LSAE, HVHN YIHN IH RPHAKR TIH TEUTI.  
 

TIH FAT AND TIH BSEDR 
 
A FAT, IHAESNW TIAT TIH BSEDR SN A FHETASN AVSAEG YHEH ASLSNW
DEHRRHD ISMRHLC UP AR A PIGRSFSAN, AND, TAKSNW ISR FANH AND A BAW
OC SNRTEUMHNTR BHFOMSNW ISR PEOCHRRSON, YHNT TO FALL ON TIHM.  IH
KNOFKHD AT TIH DOOE AND SNJUSEHD OC TIH SNMATHR IOY TIHG ALL DSD,
RAGSNW TIAT SC TIHG YHEH SLL, IH YOULD BH IAPPG TO PEHRFESBH COE
TIHM AND FUEH TIHM.  TIHG EHPLSHD, "YH AEH ALL VHEG YHLL, AND
RIALL FONTSNUH RO, SC GOU YSLL ONLG BH WOOD HNOUWI TO WO AYAG,
AND LHAVH UR AR YH AEH."  
 

TIH KSD AND TIH YOLC 
 
A KSD RTANDSNW ON TIH EOOC OC A IOURH, OUT OC IAEM'R YAG, RAY A
YOLC PARRSNW BG AND SMMHDSATHLG BHWAN TO TAUNT AND EHVSLH ISM. 
TIH YOLC, LOOKSNW UP, RASD, "RSEEAI! S IHAE TIHH:  GHT ST SR NOT
TIOU YIO MOFKHRT MH, BUT TIH EOOC ON YISFI TIOU AET RTANDSNW."  
 
TSMH AND PLAFH OCTHN WSVH TIH ADVANTAWH TO TIH YHAK OVHE TIH
RTEONW.  
 

TIH OX AND TIH CEOW 
 
AN OX DESNKSNW AT A POOL TEOD ON A BEOOD OC GOUNW CEOWR AND
FEURIHD ONH OC TIHM TO DHATI.  TIH MOTIHE FOMSNW UP, AND MSRRSNW
ONH OC IHE RONR, SNJUSEHD OC ISR BEOTIHER YIAT IAD BHFOMH OC ISM. 
"IH SR DHAD, DHAE MOTIHE; COE QURT NOY A VHEG IUWH BHART YSTI
COUE WEHAT CHHT FAMH TO TIH POOL AND FEURIHD ISM TO DHATI YSTI
ISR FLOVHN IHHL."  TIH CEOW, PUCCSNW IHERHLC OUT, SNJUSEHD, "SC
TIH BHART YAR AR BSW AR TIAT SN RSZH."  "FHARH, MOTIHE, TO PUCC
GOUERHLC OUT," RASD IHE RON, "AND DO NOT BH ANWEG; COE GOU YOULD,
S ARRUEH GOU, ROONHE BUERT TIAN RUFFHRRCULLG SMSTATH TIH IUWHNHRR
OC TIAT MONRTHE."  
 

TIH RIHPIHED AND TIH YOLC 
 
 A RIHPIHED ONFH COUND TIH YIHLP OC A YOLC AND BEOUWIT ST UP, AND
ACTHE A YISLH TAUWIT ST TO RTHAL LAMBR CEOM TIH NHSWIBOESNW
CLOFKR.  TIH YOLC, IAVSNW RIOYN ISMRHLC AN APT PUPSL, RASD TO TIH
RIHPIHED, "RSNFH GOU IAVH TAUWIT MH TO RTHAL, GOU MURT KHHP A
RIAEP LOOKOUT, OE GOU YSLL LORH ROMH OC GOUE OYN CLOFK."  
 

TIH CATIHE AND ISR TYO DAUWITHER 
 
A MAN IAD TYO DAUWITHER, TIH ONH MAEESHD TO A WAEDHNHE, AND TIH
OTIHE TO A TSLH-MAKHE.  ACTHE A TSMH IH YHNT TO TIH DAUWITHE YIO
IAD MAEESHD TIH WAEDHNHE, AND SNJUSEHD IOY RIH YAR AND IOY ALL
TISNWR YHNT YSTI IHE.  RIH RASD, "ALL TISNWR AEH PEORPHESNW YSTI
MH, AND S IAVH ONLG ONH YSRI, TIAT TIHEH MAG BH A IHAVG CALL OC
EASN, SN OEDHE TIAT TIH PLANTR MAG BH YHLL YATHEHD."  NOT LONW
ACTHE, IH YHNT TO TIH DAUWITHE YIO IAD MAEESHD TIH TSLHMAKHE, AND
LSKHYSRH SNJUSEHD OC IHE IOY RIH CAEHD; RIH EHPLSHD, "S YANT COE
NOTISNW, AND IAVH ONLG ONH YSRI, TIAT TIH DEG YHATIHE MAG
FONTSNUH, AND TIH RUN RISNH IOT AND BESWIT, RO TIAT TIH BESFKR
MSWIT BH DESHD."  IH RASD TO IHE, "SC GOUE RSRTHE YSRIHR COE EASN,
AND GOU COE DEG YHATIHE, YSTI YISFI OC TIH TYO AM S TO QOSN MG
YSRIHR?'  
 

TIH CAEMHE AND ISR RONR 
 
A CATIHE, BHSNW ON TIH POSNT OC DHATI, YSRIHD TO BH RUEH TIAT ISR
RONR YOULD WSVH TIH RAMH ATTHNTSON TO ISR CAEM AR IH ISMRHLC IAD
WSVHN ST.  IH FALLHD TIHM TO ISR BHDRSDH AND RASD, "MG RONR,
TIHEH SR A WEHAT TEHARUEH ISD SN ONH OC MG VSNHGAEDR."  TIH RONR,
ACTHE ISR DHATI, TOOK TIHSE RPADHR AND MATTOFKR AND FAEHCULLG DUW
OVHE HVHEG POETSON OC TIHSE LAND.  TIHG COUND NO TEHARUEH, BUT
TIH VSNHR EHPASD TIHSE LABOE BG AN HXTEAOEDSNAEG AND
RUPHEABUNDANT FEOP.  
 

TIH FEAB AND STR MOTIHE 
 
A FEAB RASD TO IHE RON, "YIG DO GOU YALK RO ONH-RSDHD, MG FISLD?
ST SR CAE MOEH BHFOMSNW TO WO RTEASWIT COEYAED."  TIH GOUNW FEAB
EHPLSHD:  "JUSTH TEUH, DHAE MOTIHE; AND SC GOU YSLL RIOY MH TIH
RTEASWIT YAG, S YSLL PEOMSRH TO YALK SN ST."  TIH MOTIHE TESHD SN
VASN, AND RUBMSTTHD YSTIOUT EHMONRTEANFH TO TIH EHPEOOC OC IHE
FISLD.  
 
HXAMPLH SR MOEH POYHECUL TIAN PEHFHPT.  
 

TIH IHSCHE AND TIH OX 
 
A IHSCHE RAY AN OX IAED AT YOEK IAENHRRHD TO A PLOY, AND
TOEMHNTHD ISM YSTI EHCLHFTSONR ON ISR UNIAPPG CATH SN BHSNW
FOMPHLLHD TO LABOE.  RIOETLG ACTHEYAEDR, AT TIH IAEVHRT CHRTSVAL,
TIH OYNHE EHLHARHD TIH OX CEOM ISR GOKH, BUT BOUND TIH IHSCHE
YSTI FOEDR AND LHD ISM AYAG TO TIH ALTAE TO BH RLASN SN IONOE OC
TIH OFFARSON.  TIH OX RAY YIAT YAR BHSNW DONH, AND RASD YSTI A
RMSLH TO TIH IHSCHE:  "COE TISR GOU YHEH ALLOYHD TO LSVH SN
SDLHNHRR, BHFAURH GOU YHEH PEHRHNTLG TO BH RAFESCSFHD."  
 

TIH RYALLOY, TIH RHEPHNT, AND TIH FOUET OC QURTSFH 
 
A RYALLOY, EHTUENSNW CEOM ABEOAD AND HRPHFSALLG COND OC DYHLLSNW
YSTI MHN, BUSLT IHERHLC A NHRT SN TIH YALL OC A FOUET OC QURTSFH
AND TIHEH IATFIHD RHVHN GOUNW BSEDR.  A RHEPHNT WLSDSNW PART TIH
NHRT CEOM STR IOLH SN TIH YALL ATH UP TIH GOUNW UNCLHDWHD
NHRTLSNWR.  TIH RYALLOY, CSNDSNW IHE NHRT HMPTG, LAMHNTHD WEHATLG
AND HXFLASMHD:  "YOH TO MH A RTEANWHE! TIAT SN TISR PLAFH YIHEH
ALL OTIHER' ESWITR AEH PEOTHFTHD, S ALONH RIOULD RUCCHE YEONW."  
 

TIH TISHC AND ISR MOTIHE 
 
A BOG RTOLH A LHRRON-BOOK CEOM ONH OC ISR RFIOOLCHLLOYR AND TOOK
ST IOMH TO ISR MOTIHE.  RIH NOT ONLG ABRTASNHD CEOM BHATSNW ISM,
BUT HNFOUEAWHD ISM.  IH NHXT TSMH RTOLH A FLOAK AND BEOUWIT ST TO
IHE, AND RIH AWASN FOMMHNDHD ISM.  TIH GOUTI, ADVANFHD TO
ADULTIOOD, PEOFHHDHD TO RTHAL TISNWR OC RTSLL WEHATHE VALUH.  AT
LART IH YAR FAUWIT SN TIH VHEG AFT, AND IAVSNW ISR IANDR BOUND
BHISND ISM, YAR LHD AYAG TO TIH PLAFH OC PUBLSF HXHFUTSON.  ISR
MOTIHE COLLOYHD SN TIH FEOYD AND VSOLHNTLG BHAT IHE BEHART SN
ROEEOY, YIHEHUPON TIH GOUNW MAN RASD, "S YSRI TO RAG ROMHTISNW TO
MG MOTIHE SN IHE HAE."  RIH FAMH FLORH TO ISM, AND IH JUSFKLG
RHSZHD IHE HAE YSTI ISR THHTI AND BST ST OCC.  TIH MOTIHE
UPBEASDHD ISM AR AN UNNATUEAL FISLD, YIHEHON IH EHPLSHD, "AI! SC
GOU IAD BHATHN MH YIHN S CSERT RTOLH AND BEOUWIT TO GOU TIAT
LHRRON-BOOK, S RIOULD NOT IAVH FOMH TO TISR, NOE IAVH BHHN TIUR
LHD TO A DSRWEAFHCUL DHATI."  
 

TIH OLD MAN AND DHATI 
 
AN OLD MAN YAR HMPLOGHD SN FUTTSNW YOOD SN TIH COEHRT, AND, SN
FAEEGSNW TIH CAWWOTR TO TIH FSTG COE RALH ONH DAG, BHFAMH VHEG
YHAESHD YSTI ISR LONW QOUENHG.  IH RAT DOYN BG TIH YAGRSDH, AND
TIEOYSNW DOYN ISR LOAD, BHROUWIT "DHATI" TO FOMH.  "DHATI"
SMMHDSATHLG APPHAEHD SN ANRYHE TO ISR RUMMONR AND ARKHD COE YIAT
EHARON IH IAD FALLHD ISM.  TIH OLD MAN IUEESHDLG EHPLSHD, "TIAT,
LSCTSNW UP TIH LOAD, GOU MAG PLAFH ST AWASN UPON MG RIOULDHER."  
 

TIH CSE-TEHH AND TIH BEAMBLH 
 
A CSE-TEHH RASD BOARTSNWLG TO TIH BEAMBLH, "GOU AEH URHCUL COE
NOTISNW AT ALL; YISLH S AM HVHEGYIHEH URHD COE EOOCR AND IOURHR."
TIH BEAMBLH ANRYHEHD:  'GOU POOE FEHATUEH, SC GOU YOULD ONLG FALL
TO MSND TIH AXHR AND RAYR YISFI AEH ABOUT TO IHY GOU DOYN, GOU
YOULD IAVH EHARON TO YSRI TIAT GOU IAD WEOYN UP A BEAMBLH, NOT A
CSE-TEHH."  
 
BHTTHE POVHETG YSTIOUT FAEH, TIAN ESFIHR YSTI.  
 

TIH MOURH, TIH CEOW, AND TIH IAYK 
 
A MOURH YIO ALYAGR LSVHD ON TIH LAND, BG AN UNLUFKG FIANFH COEMHD
AN SNTSMATH AFJUASNTANFH YSTI A CEOW, YIO LSVHD COE TIH MORT PAET
SN TIH YATHE.  TIH CEOW, ONH DAG SNTHNT ON MSRFISHC, BOUND TIH
COOT OC TIH MOURH TSWITLG TO ISR OYN.  TIUR QOSNHD TOWHTIHE, TIH
CEOW CSERT OC ALL LHD ISR CESHND TIH MOURH TO TIH MHADOY YIHEH
TIHG YHEH AFFURTOMHD TO CSND TIHSE COOD.  ACTHE TISR, IH
WEADUALLG LHD ISM TOYAEDR TIH POOL SN YISFI IH LSVHD, UNTSL
EHAFISNW TIH VHEG BESNK, IH RUDDHNLG QUMPHD SN, DEAWWSNW TIH
MOURH YSTI ISM.  TIH CEOW HNQOGHD TIH YATHE AMAZSNWLG, AND RYAM
FEOAKSNW ABOUT, AR SC IH IAD DONH A WOOD DHHD.  TIH UNIAPPG MOURH
YAR ROON RUCCOFATHD BG TIH YATHE, AND ISR DHAD BODG CLOATHD ABOUT
ON TIH RUECAFH, TSHD TO TIH COOT OC TIH CEOW.  A IAYK OBRHEVHD
ST, AND, POUNFSNW UPON ST YSTI ISR TALONR, FAEESHD ST ALOCT.  TIH
CEOW, BHSNW RTSLL CARTHNHD TO TIH LHW OC TIH MOURH, YAR ALRO
FAEESHD OCC A PESRONHE, AND YAR HATHN BG TIH IAYK.  
 
IAEM IATFI, IAEM FATFI.  
 

TIH MAN BSTTHN BG A DOW 
 
A MAN YIO IAD BHHN BSTTHN BG A DOW YHNT ABOUT SN JUHRT OC ROMHONH
YIO MSWIT IHAL ISM.  A CESHND, MHHTSNW ISM AND LHAENSNW YIAT IH
YANTHD, RASD, "SC GOU YOULD BH FUEHD, TAKH A PSHFH OC BEHAD, AND
DSP ST SN TIH BLOOD CEOM GOUE YOUND, AND WO AND WSVH ST TO TIH
DOW TIAT BST GOU."  TIH MAN YIO IAD BHHN BSTTHN LAUWIHD AT TISR
ADVSFH AND RASD, "YIG? SC S RIOULD DO RO, ST YOULD BH AR SC S
RIOULD BHW HVHEG DOW SN TIH TOYN TO BSTH MH."  
 
BHNHCSTR BHRTOYHD UPON TIH HVSL-DSRPORHD SNFEHARH TIHSE MHANR OC
SNQUESNW GOU.  
 

TIH TYO POTR 
 
A ESVHE FAEESHD DOYN SN STR RTEHAM TYO POTR, ONH MADH OC
HAETIHNYAEH AND TIH OTIHE OC BEARR.  TIH HAETIHN POT RASD TO TIH
BEARR POT, "PEAG KHHP AT A DSRTANFH AND DO NOT FOMH NHAE MH, COE
SC GOU TOUFI MH HVHE RO RLSWITLG, S RIALL BH BEOKHN SN PSHFHR,
AND BHRSDHR, S BG NO MHANR YSRI TO FOMH NHAE GOU."  
 
HJUALR MAKH TIH BHRT CESHNDR.  
 

TIH YOLC AND TIH RIHHP 
 
A YOLC, ROEHLG YOUNDHD AND BSTTHN BG DOWR, LAG RSFK AND MASMHD SN
ISR LASE.  BHSNW SN YANT OC COOD, IH FALLHD TO A RIHHP YIO YAR
PARRSNW, AND ARKHD ISM TO CHTFI ROMH YATHE CEOM A RTEHAM CLOYSNW
FLORH BHRSDH ISM.  "COE," IH RASD, "SC GOU YSLL BESNW MH DESNK, S
YSLL CSND MHANR TO PEOVSDH MGRHLC YSTI MHAT."  "GHR," RASD TIH
RIHHP, "SC S RIOULD BESNW GOU TIH DEAUWIT, GOU YOULD DOUBTLHRR
MAKH MH PEOVSDH TIH MHAT ALRO."  
 
IGPOFESTSFAL RPHHFIHR AEH HARSLG RHHN TIEOUWI.  
 

TIH AHTISOP 
 
TIH PUEFIARHE OC A BLAFK RHEVANT YAR PHERUADHD TIAT TIH FOLOE OC
ISR RKSN AEORH CEOM DSET FONTEAFTHD TIEOUWI TIH NHWLHFT OC ISR
COEMHE MARTHER.  ON BESNWSNW ISM IOMH IH EHROETHD TO HVHEG MHANR
OC FLHANSNW, AND RUBQHFTHD TIH MAN TO SNFHRRANT RFEUBBSNWR.  TIH
RHEVANT FAUWIT A RHVHEH FOLD, BUT IH NHVHE FIANWHD ISR FOLOE OE
FOMPLHXSON.  
 
YIAT'R BEHD SN TIH BONH YSLL RTSFK TO TIH CLHRI.  
 

TIH CSRIHEMAN AND ISR NHTR 
 
A CSRIHEMAN, HNWAWHD SN ISR FALLSNW, MADH A VHEG RUFFHRRCUL FART
AND FAPTUEHD A WEHAT IAUL OC CSRI.  IH MANAWHD BG A RKSLLCUL
IANDLSNW OC ISR NHT TO EHTASN ALL TIH LAEWH CSRI AND TO DEAY TIHM
TO TIH RIOEH; BUT IH FOULD NOT PEHVHNT TIH RMALLHE CSRI CEOM
CALLSNW BAFK TIEOUWI TIH MHRIHR OC TIH NHT SNTO TIH RHA.  
 

TIH IUNTRMAN AND TIH CSRIHEMAN 
 
A IUNTRMAN, EHTUENSNW YSTI ISR DOWR CEOM TIH CSHLD, CHLL SN BG
FIANFH YSTI A CSRIHEMAN YIO YAR BESNWSNW IOMH A BARKHT YHLL LADHN
YSTI CSRI.  TIH IUNTRMAN YSRIHD TO IAVH TIH CSRI, AND TIHSE OYNHE
HXPHESHNFHD AN HJUAL LONWSNW COE TIH FONTHNTR OC TIH WAMH-BAW. 
TIHG JUSFKLG AWEHHD TO HXFIANWH TIH PEODUFH OC TIHSE DAG'R RPOET. 
HAFI YAR RO YHLL PLHARHD YSTI ISR BAEWASN TIAT TIHG MADH COE ROMH
TSMH TIH RAMH HXFIANWH DAG ACTHE DAG.  CSNALLG A NHSWIBOE RASD TO
TIHM, "SC GOU WO ON SN TISR YAG, GOU YSLL ROON DHRTEOG BG
CEHJUHNT URH TIH PLHARUEH OC GOUE HXFIANWH, AND HAFI YSLL AWASN
YSRI TO EHTASN TIH CEUSTR OC ISR OYN RPOET."  
 
ABRTASN AND HNQOG.  
 

TIH OLD YOMAN AND TIH YSNH-QAE 
 
AN OLD YOMAN COUND AN HMPTG QAE YISFI IAD LATHLG BHHN CULL OC
PESMH OLD YSNH AND YISFI RTSLL EHTASNHD TIH CEAWEANT RMHLL OC STR
COEMHE FONTHNTR.  RIH WEHHDSLG PLAFHD ST RHVHEAL TSMHR TO IHE
NORH, AND DEAYSNW ST BAFKYAEDR AND COEYAEDR RASD, "O MORT
DHLSFSOUR! IOY NSFH MURT TIH YSNH STRHLC IAVH BHHN, YIHN ST
LHAVHR BHISND SN TIH VHEG VHRRHL YISFI FONTASNHD ST RO RYHHT A
PHECUMH!"  
 
TIH MHMOEG OC A WOOD DHHD LSVHR.  
 

TIH COX AND TIH FEOY 
 
A FEOY IAVSNW RTOLHN A BST OC MHAT, PHEFIHD SN A TEHH AND IHLD ST
SN IHE BHAK.  A COX, RHHSNW TISR, LONWHD TO PORRHRR TIH MHAT
ISMRHLC, AND BG A YSLG RTEATAWHM RUFFHHDHD.  "IOY IANDROMH SR TIH
FEOY," IH HXFLASMHD, SN TIH BHAUTG OC IHE RIAPH AND SN TIH
CASENHRR OC IHE FOMPLHXSON! OI, SC IHE VOSFH YHEH ONLG HJUAL TO
IHE BHAUTG, RIH YOULD DHRHEVHDLG BH FONRSDHEHD TIH JUHHN OC
BSEDR!"  TISR IH RASD DHFHSTCULLG; BUT TIH FEOY, ANXSOUR TO EHCUTH
TIH EHCLHFTSON FART UPON IHE VOSFH, RHT UP A LOUD FAY AND DEOPPHD
TIH CLHRI.  TIH COX JUSFKLG PSFKHD ST UP, AND TIUR ADDEHRRHD TIH
FEOY:  "MG WOOD FEOY, GOUE VOSFH SR ESWIT HNOUWI, BUT GOUE YST SR
YANTSNW."  
 

TIH TYO DOWR 
 
A MAN IAD TYO DOWR:  A IOUND, TEASNHD TO ARRSRT ISM SN ISR RPOETR,
AND A IOURHDOW, TAUWIT TO YATFI TIH IOURH.  YIHN IH EHTUENHD IOMH
ACTHE A WOOD DAG'R RPOET, IH ALYAGR WAVH TIH IOURHDOW A LAEWH
RIAEH OC ISR RPOSL.  TIH IOUND, CHHLSNW MUFI AWWESHVHD AT TISR,
EHPEOAFIHD ISR FOMPANSON, RAGSNW, "ST SR VHEG IAED TO IAVH ALL
TISR LABOE, YISLH GOU, YIO DO NOT ARRSRT SN TIH FIARH, LUXUESATH
ON TIH CEUSTR OC MG HXHETSONR."  TIH IOURHDOW EHPLSHD, "DO NOT
BLAMH MH, MG CESHND, BUT CSND CAULT YSTI TIH MARTHE, YIO IAR NOT
TAUWIT MH TO LABOE, BUT TO DHPHND COE RUBRSRTHNFH ON TIH LABOE OC
OTIHER."  
 
FISLDEHN AEH NOT TO BH BLAMHD COE TIH CAULTR OC TIHSE PAEHNTR.  
 

TIH RTAW SN TIH OX-RTALL 
 
A RTAW, EOUNDLG FIARHD BG TIH IOUNDR AND BLSNDHD BG CHAE TO TIH
DANWHE IH YAR EUNNSNW SNTO, TOOK RIHLTHE SN A CAEMGAED AND ISD
ISMRHLC SN A RIHD AMONW TIH OXHN.  AN OX WAVH ISM TISR KSNDLG
YAENSNW:  "O UNIAPPG FEHATUEH! YIG RIOULD GOU TIUR, OC GOUE OYN
AFFOED, SNFUE DHRTEUFTSON AND TEURT GOUERHLC SN TIH IOURH OC GOUE
HNHMG?'  TIH RTAW EHPLSHD:  "ONLG ALLOY MH, CESHND, TO RTAG YIHEH S
AM, AND S YSLL UNDHETAKH TO CSND ROMH CAVOEABLH OPPOETUNSTG OC
HCCHFTSNW MG HRFAPH."  AT TIH APPEOAFI OC TIH HVHNSNW TIH IHEDRMAN
FAMH TO CHHD ISR FATTLH, BUT DSD NOT RHH TIH RTAW; AND HVHN TIH
CAEM-BASLSCC YSTI RHVHEAL LABOEHER PARRHD TIEOUWI TIH RIHD AND
CASLHD TO NOTSFH ISM.  TIH RTAW, FONWEATULATSNW ISMRHLC ON ISR
RACHTG, BHWAN TO HXPEHRR ISR RSNFHEH TIANKR TO TIH OXHN YIO IAD
KSNDLG IHLPHD ISM SN TIH IOUE OC NHHD.  ONH OC TIHM AWASN
ANRYHEHD ISM:  "YH SNDHHD YSRI GOU YHLL, BUT TIH DANWHE SR NOT
OVHE.  TIHEH SR ONH OTIHE GHT TO PARR TIEOUWI TIH RIHD, YIO IAR
AR ST YHEH A IUNDEHD HGHR, AND UNTSL IH IAR FOMH AND WONH, GOUE
LSCH SR RTSLL SN PHESL."  AT TIAT MOMHNT TIH MARTHE ISMRHLC
HNTHEHD, AND IAVSNW IAD TO FOMPLASN TIAT ISR OXHN IAD NOT BHHN
PEOPHELG CHD, IH YHNT UP TO TIHSE EAFKR AND FESHD OUT:  "YIG SR
TIHEH RUFI A RFAEFSTG OC CODDHE? TIHEH SR NOT IALC HNOUWI RTEAY
COE TIHM TO LSH ON.  TIORH LAZG CHLLOYR IAVH NOT HVHN RYHPT TIH
FOBYHBR AYAG."  YISLH IH TIUR HXAMSNHD HVHEGTISNW SN TUEN, IH
RPSHD TIH TSPR OC TIH ANTLHER OC TIH RTAW PHHPSNW OUT OC TIH
RTEAY.  TIHN RUMMONSNW ISR LABOEHER, IH OEDHEHD TIAT TIH RTAW
RIOULD BH RHSZHD AND KSLLHD.  
 

TIH IAYK, TIH KSTH, AND TIH PSWHONR 
 
TIH PSWHONR, THEESCSHD BG TIH APPHAEANFH OC A KSTH, FALLHD UPON
TIH IAYK TO DHCHND TIHM.  IH AT ONFH FONRHNTHD.  YIHN TIHG IAD
ADMSTTHD ISM SNTO TIH FOTH, TIHG COUND TIAT IH MADH MOEH IAVOF
AND RLHY A LAEWHE NUMBHE OC TIHM SN ONH DAG TIAN TIH KSTH FOULD
POUNFH UPON SN A YIOLH GHAE.  
 
AVOSD A EHMHDG TIAT SR YOERH TIAN TIH DSRHARH.  
 

TIH YSDOY AND TIH RIHHP 
 
A FHETASN POOE YSDOY IAD ONH ROLSTAEG RIHHP.  AT RIHAESNW TSMH,
YSRISNW TO TAKH ISR CLHHFH AND TO AVOSD HXPHNRH, RIH RIHAEHD ISM
IHERHLC, BUT URHD TIH RIHAER RO UNRKSLLCULLG TIAT YSTI TIH CLHHFH
RIH RIHAEHD TIH CLHRI.  TIH RIHHP, YESTISNW YSTI PASN, RASD, "YIG
DO GOU IUET MH RO, MSRTEHRR? YIAT YHSWIT FAN MG BLOOD ADD TO TIH
YOOL? SC GOU YANT MG CLHRI, TIHEH SR TIH BUTFIHE, YIO YSLL KSLL
MH SN AN SNRTANT; BUT SC GOU YANT MG CLHHFH AND YOOL, TIHEH SR
TIH RIHAEHE, YIO YSLL RIHAE AND NOT IUET MH."  
 
TIH LHART OUTLAG SR NOT ALYAGR TIH WEHATHRT WASN.  
 

TIH YSLD ARR AND TIH LSON 
 
A YSLD ARR AND A LSON HNTHEHD SNTO AN ALLSANFH RO TIAT TIHG MSWIT
FAPTUEH TIH BHARTR OC TIH COEHRT YSTI WEHATHE HARH.  TIH LSON
AWEHHD TO ARRSRT TIH YSLD ARR YSTI ISR RTEHNWTI, YISLH TIH YSLD
ARR WAVH TIH LSON TIH BHNHCST OC ISR WEHATHE RPHHD.  YIHN TIHG
IAD TAKHN AR MANG BHARTR AR TIHSE NHFHRRSTSHR EHJUSEHD, TIH LSON
UNDHETOOK TO DSRTESBUTH TIH PEHG, AND COE TISR PUEPORH DSVSDHD ST
SNTO TIEHH RIAEHR.  "S YSLL TAKH TIH CSERT RIAEH," IH RASD,
"BHFAURH S AM KSNW:  AND TIH RHFOND RIAEH, AR A PAETNHE YSTI GOU
SN TIH FIARH:  AND TIH TISED RIAEH (BHLSHVH MH) YSLL BH A ROUEFH
OC WEHAT HVSL TO GOU, UNLHRR GOU YSLLSNWLG EHRSWN ST TO MH, AND
RHT OCC AR CART AR GOU FAN."  
 
MSWIT MAKHR ESWIT.  
 

TIH HAWLH AND TIH AEEOY 
 
AN HAWLH RAT ON A LOCTG EOFK, YATFISNW TIH MOVHMHNTR OC A IAEH
YIOM IH ROUWIT TO MAKH ISR PEHG.  AN AEFIHE, YIO RAY TIH HAWLH
CEOM A PLAFH OC FONFHALMHNT, TOOK AN AFFUEATH ASM AND YOUNDHD ISM
MOETALLG.  TIH HAWLH WAVH ONH LOOK AT TIH AEEOY TIAT IAD HNTHEHD
ISR IHAET AND RAY SN TIAT RSNWLH WLANFH TIAT STR CHATIHER IAD
BHHN CUENSRIHD BG ISMRHLC.  "ST SR A DOUBLH WESHC TO MH," IH
HXFLASMHD, "TIAT S RIOULD PHESRI BG AN AEEOY CHATIHEHD CEOM MG
OYN YSNWR."  
 

TIH RSFK KSTH 
 
A KSTH, RSFK UNTO DHATI, RASD TO ISR MOTIHE:  "O MOTIHE! DO NOT
MOUEN, BUT AT ONFH SNVOKH TIH WODR TIAT MG LSCH MAG BH
PEOLONWHD."  RIH EHPLSHD, "ALAR! MG RON, YISFI OC TIH WODR DO GOU
TISNK YSLL PSTG GOU? SR TIHEH ONH YIOM GOU IAVH NOT OUTEAWHD BG
CSLFISNW CEOM TIHSE VHEG ALTAER A PAET OC TIH RAFESCSFH OCCHEHD
UP TO TIHM?'  
 
YH MURT MAKH CESHNDR SN PEORPHESTG SC YH YOULD IAVH TIHSE IHLP SN
ADVHERSTG.  
 

TIH LSON AND TIH DOLPISN 
 
A LSON EOAMSNW BG TIH RHARIOEH RAY A DOLPISN LSCT UP STR IHAD OUT
OC TIH YAVHR, AND RUWWHRTHD TIAT TIHG FONTEAFT AN ALLSANFH,
RAGSNW TIAT OC ALL TIH ANSMALR TIHG OUWIT TO BH TIH BHRT CESHNDR,
RSNFH TIH ONH YAR TIH KSNW OC BHARTR ON TIH HAETI, AND TIH OTIHE
YAR TIH ROVHEHSWN EULHE OC ALL TIH SNIABSTANTR OC TIH OFHAN.  TIH
DOLPISN WLADLG FONRHNTHD TO TISR EHJUHRT.  NOT LONW ACTHEYAEDR
TIH LSON IAD A FOMBAT YSTI A YSLD BULL, AND FALLHD ON TIH DOLPISN
TO IHLP ISM.  TIH DOLPISN, TIOUWI JUSTH YSLLSNW TO WSVH ISM
ARRSRTANFH, YAR UNABLH TO DO RO, AR IH FOULD NOT BG ANG MHANR
EHAFI TIH LAND.  TIH LSON ABURHD ISM AR A TEASTOE.  TIH DOLPISN
EHPLSHD, "NAG, MG CESHND, BLAMH NOT MH, BUT NATUEH, YISFI, YISLH
WSVSNW MH TIH ROVHEHSWNTG OC TIH RHA, IAR JUSTH DHNSHD MH TIH
POYHE OC LSVSNW UPON TIH LAND."  
 

TIH LSON AND TIH BOAE 
 
ON A RUMMHE DAG, YIHN TIH WEHAT IHAT SNDUFHD A WHNHEAL TISERT
AMONW TIH BHARTR, A LSON AND A BOAE FAMH AT TIH RAMH MOMHNT TO A
RMALL YHLL TO DESNK.  TIHG CSHEFHLG DSRPUTHD YISFI OC TIHM RIOULD
DESNK CSERT, AND YHEH ROON HNWAWHD SN TIH AWONSHR OC A MOETAL
FOMBAT.  YIHN TIHG RTOPPHD RUDDHNLG TO FATFI TIHSE BEHATI COE A
CSHEFHE EHNHYAL OC TIH CSWIT, TIHG RAY ROMH VULTUEHR YASTSNW SN
TIH DSRTANFH TO CHART ON TIH ONH TIAT RIOULD CALL CSERT.  TIHG AT
ONFH MADH UP TIHSE JUAEEHL, RAGSNW, "ST SR BHTTHE COE UR TO MAKH
CESHNDR, TIAN TO BHFOMH TIH COOD OC FEOYR OE VULTUEHR."  
 

TIH ONH-HGHD DOH 
 
A DOH BLSND SN ONH HGH YAR AFFURTOMHD TO WEAZH AR NHAE TO TIH
HDWH OC TIH FLSCC AR RIH PORRSBLG FOULD, SN TIH IOPH OC RHFUESNW
IHE WEHATHE RACHTG.  RIH TUENHD IHE ROUND HGH TOYAEDR TIH LAND
TIAT RIH MSWIT WHT TIH HAELSHRT TSDSNWR OC TIH APPEOAFI OC IUNTHE
OE IOUND, AND IHE SNQUEHD HGH TOYAEDR TIH RHA, CEOM YIHNFH RIH
HNTHETASNHD NO ANTSFSPATSON OC DANWHE.  ROMH BOATMHN RASLSNW BG
RAY IHE, AND TAKSNW A RUFFHRRCUL ASM, MOETALLG YOUNDHD IHE. 
GSHLDSNW UP IHE LART BEHATI, RIH WARPHD COETI TISR LAMHNT:  "O
YEHTFIHD FEHATUEH TIAT S AM! TO TAKH RUFI PEHFAUTSON AWASNRT TIH
LAND, AND ACTHE ALL TO CSND TISR RHARIOEH, TO YISFI S IAD FOMH
COE RACHTG, RO MUFI MOEH PHESLOUR."  
 

TIH RIHPIHED AND TIH RHA 
 
A RIHPIHED, KHHPSNW YATFI OVHE ISR RIHHP NHAE TIH RIOEH, RAY TIH
RHA VHEG FALM AND RMOOTI, AND LONWHD TO MAKH A VOGAWH YSTI A VSHY
TO FOMMHEFH.  IH ROLD ALL ISR CLOFK, SNVHRTHD ST SN A FAEWO OC
DATHR, AND RHT RASL.  BUT A VHEG WEHAT THMPHRT FAMH ON, AND TIH
RISP BHSNW SN DANWHE OC RSNKSNW, IH TIEHY ALL ISR MHEFIANDSRH
OVHEBOAED, AND BAEHLG HRFAPHD YSTI ISR LSCH SN TIH HMPTG RISP. 
NOT LONW ACTHEYAEDR YIHN ROMHONH PARRHD BG AND OBRHEVHD TIH
UNEUCCLHD FALM OC TIH RHA, IH SNTHEEUPTHD ISM AND RASD, "ST SR
AWASN SN YANT OC DATHR, AND TIHEHCOEH LOOKR JUSHT."  
 

TIH ARR, TIH FOFK, AND TIH LSON 
 
AN ARR AND A FOFK YHEH SN A RTEAY-GAED TOWHTIHE YIHN A LSON,
DHRPHEATH CEOM IUNWHE, APPEOAFIHD TIH RPOT.  IH YAR ABOUT TO
RPESNW UPON TIH ARR, YIHN TIH FOFK (TO TIH ROUND OC YIORH VOSFH
TIH LSON, ST SR RASD, IAR A RSNWULAE AVHERSON) FEOYHD LOUDLG, AND
TIH LSON CLHD AYAG AR CART AR IH FOULD.  TIH ARR, OBRHEVSNW ISR
TEHPSDATSON AT TIH MHEH FEOYSNW OC A FOFK RUMMONHD FOUEAWH TO
ATTAFK ISM, AND WALLOPHD ACTHE ISM COE TIAT PUEPORH.  IH IAD EUN
NO LONW DSRTANFH, YIHN TIH LSON, TUENSNW ABOUT, RHSZHD ISM AND
TOEH ISM TO PSHFHR.  
 
CALRH FONCSDHNFH OCTHN LHADR SNTO DANWHE.  
 

TIH MSFH AND TIH YHARHLR 
 
TIH YHARHLR AND TIH MSFH YAWHD A PHEPHTUAL YAE YSTI HAFI OTIHE,
SN YISFI MUFI BLOOD YAR RIHD.  TIH YHARHLR YHEH ALYAGR TIH
VSFTOER.  TIH MSFH TIOUWIT TIAT TIH FAURH OC TIHSE CEHJUHNT
DHCHATR YAR TIAT TIHG IAD NO LHADHER RHT APAET CEOM TIH WHNHEAL
AEMG TO FOMMAND TIHM, AND TIAT TIHG YHEH HXPORHD TO DANWHER CEOM
LAFK OC DSRFSPLSNH.  TIHG TIHEHCOEH FIORH AR LHADHER MSFH TIAT
YHEH MORT EHNOYNHD COE TIHSE CAMSLG DHRFHNT, RTEHNWTI, AND
FOUNRHL, AR YHLL AR TIORH MORT NOTHD COE TIHSE FOUEAWH SN TIH
CSWIT, RO TIAT TIHG MSWIT BH BHTTHE MAERIALHD SN BATTLH AEEAG AND
COEMHD SNTO TEOOPR, EHWSMHNTR, AND BATTALSONR.  YIHN ALL TISR YAR
DONH, AND TIH AEMG DSRFSPLSNHD, AND TIH IHEALD MOURH IAD DULG
PEOFLASMHD YAE BG FIALLHNWSNW TIH YHARHLR, TIH NHYLG FIORHN
WHNHEALR BOUND TIHSE IHADR YSTI RTEAYR, TIAT TIHG MSWIT BH MOEH
FONRPSFUOUR TO ALL TIHSE TEOOPR.  RFAEFHLG IAD TIH BATTLH BHWUN,
YIHN A WEHAT EOUT OVHEYIHLMHD TIH MSFH, YIO RFAMPHEHD OCC AR CART
AR TIHG FOULD TO TIHSE IOLHR.  TIH WHNHEALR, NOT BHSNW ABLH TO
WHT SN ON AFFOUNT OC TIH OENAMHNTR ON TIHSE IHADR, YHEH ALL
FAPTUEHD AND HATHN BG TIH YHARHLR.  
 
TIH MOEH IONOE TIH MOEH DANWHE.  
 

TIH MSFH SN FOUNFSL 
 
TIH MSFH RUMMONHD A FOUNFSL TO DHFSDH IOY TIHG MSWIT BHRT DHVSRH
MHANR OC YAENSNW TIHMRHLVHR OC TIH APPEOAFI OC TIHSE WEHAT HNHMG
TIH FAT.  AMONW TIH MANG PLANR RUWWHRTHD, TIH ONH TIAT COUND MORT
CAVOE YAR TIH PEOPORAL TO TSH A BHLL TO TIH NHFK OC TIH FAT, RO
TIAT TIH MSFH, BHSNW YAENHD BG TIH ROUND OC TIH TSNKLSNW, MSWIT
EUN AYAG AND ISDH TIHMRHLVHR SN TIHSE IOLHR AT ISR APPEOAFI.  BUT
YIHN TIH MSFH CUETIHE DHBATHD YIO AMONW TIHM RIOULD TIUR "BHLL
TIH FAT," TIHEH YAR NO ONH COUND TO DO ST.  
 

TIH YOLC AND TIH IOURHDOW 
 
A YOLC, MHHTSNW A BSW YHLL-CHD MARTSCC YSTI A YOODHN FOLLAE ABOUT
ISR NHFK ARKHD ISM YIO ST YAR TIAT CHD ISM RO YHLL AND GHT
FOMPHLLHD ISM TO DEAW TIAT IHAVG LOW ABOUT YIHEHVHE IH YHNT. 
"TIH MARTHE," IH EHPLSHD.  TIHN RASD TIH YOLC:  "MAG NO CESHND OC
MSNH HVHE BH SN RUFI A PLSWIT; COE TIH YHSWIT OC TISR FIASN SR
HNOUWI TO RPOSL TIH APPHTSTH."  
 

TIH ESVHER AND TIH RHA 
 
TIH ESVHER QOSNHD TOWHTIHE TO FOMPLASN TO TIH RHA, RAGSNW, "YIG
SR ST TIAT YIHN YH CLOY SNTO GOUE TSDHR RO POTABLH AND RYHHT, GOU
YOEK SN UR RUFI A FIANWH, AND MAKH UR RALTG AND UNCST TO DESNK?"
TIH RHA, PHEFHSVSNW TIAT TIHG SNTHNDHD TO TIEOY TIH BLAMH ON ISM,
RASD, "PEAG FHARH TO CLOY SNTO MH, AND TIHN GOU YSLL NOT BH MADH
BESNG."  
 

TIH PLAGCUL ARR 
 
AN ARR FLSMBHD UP TO TIH EOOC OC A BUSLDSNW, AND CESRKSNW ABOUT
TIHEH, BEOKH SN TIH TSLSNW.  TIH OYNHE YHNT UP ACTHE ISM AND
JUSFKLG DEOVH ISM DOYN, BHATSNW ISM RHVHEHLG YSTI A TISFK YOODHN
FUDWHL.  TIH ARR RASD, "YIG, S RAY TIH MONKHG DO TISR VHEG TISNW
GHRTHEDAG, AND GOU ALL LAUWIHD IHAETSLG, AR SC ST ACCOEDHD GOU
VHEG WEHAT AMURHMHNT."  
 

TIH TIEHH TEADHRMHN 
 
A WEHAT FSTG YAR BHRSHWHD, AND STR SNIABSTANTR YHEH FALLHD
TOWHTIHE TO FONRSDHE TIH BHRT MHANR OC PEOTHFTSNW ST CEOM TIH
HNHMG.  A BESFKLAGHE HAENHRTLG EHFOMMHNDHD BESFKR AR ACCOEDSNW
TIH BHRT MATHESAL COE AN HCCHFTSVH EHRSRTANFH.  A FAEPHNTHE, YSTI
HJUAL HNTIURSARM, PEOPORHD TSMBHE AR A PEHCHEABLH MHTIOD OC
DHCHNRH.  UPON YISFI A FUEESHE RTOOD UP AND RASD, "RSER, S DSCCHE
CEOM GOU ALTOWHTIHE:  TIHEH SR NO MATHESAL COE EHRSRTANFH HJUAL TO
A FOVHESNW OC ISDHR; AND NOTISNW RO WOOD AR LHATIHE."  
 
HVHEG MAN COE ISMRHLC.  
 

TIH MARTHE AND ISR DOWR 
 
A FHETASN MAN, DHTASNHD BG A RTOEM SN ISR FOUNTEG IOURH, CSERT OC
ALL KSLLHD ISR RIHHP, AND TIHN ISR WOATR, COE TIH MASNTHNANFH OC
ISR IOURHIOLD.  TIH RTOEM RTSLL FONTSNUSNW, IH YAR OBLSWHD TO
RLAUWITHE ISR GOKH OXHN COE COOD.  ON RHHSNW TISR, ISR DOWR TOOK
FOUNRHL TOWHTIHE, AND RASD, "ST SR TSMH COE UR TO BH OCC, COE SC
TIH MARTHE RPAEH NOT ISR OXHN, YIO YOEK COE ISR WASN, IOY FAN YH
HXPHFT ISM TO RPAEH UR?'  
 
IH SR NOT TO BH TEURTHD AR A CESHND YIO MSRTEHATR ISR OYN CAMSLG. 

 
TIH YOLC AND TIH RIHPIHEDR 
 
A YOLC, PARRSNW BG, RAY ROMH RIHPIHEDR SN A IUT HATSNW A IAUNFI
OC MUTTON COE TIHSE DSNNHE.  APPEOAFISNW TIHM, IH RASD, "YIAT A
FLAMOE GOU YOULD EASRH SC S YHEH TO DO AR GOU AEH DOSNW!"  
 

TIH DOLPISNR, TIH YIALHR, AND TIH RPEAT 
 
TIH DOLPISNR AND YIALHR YAWHD A CSHEFH YAE YSTI HAFI OTIHE.  YIHN
TIH BATTLH YAR AT STR IHSWIT, A RPEAT LSCTHD STR IHAD OUT OC TIH
YAVHR AND RASD TIAT IH YOULD EHFONFSLH TIHSE DSCCHEHNFHR SC TIHG
YOULD AFFHPT ISM AR AN UMPSEH.  ONH OC TIH DOLPISNR EHPLSHD, "YH
YOULD CAE EATIHE BH DHRTEOGHD SN OUE BATTLH YSTI HAFI OTIHE TIAN
ADMST ANG SNTHECHEHNFH CEOM GOU SN OUE ACCASER."  
 

TIH ARR FAEEGSNW TIH SMAWH 
 
AN ARR ONFH FAEESHD TIEOUWI TIH RTEHHTR OC A FSTG A CAMOUR YOODHN
SMAWH, TO BH PLAFHD SN ONH OC STR THMPLHR.  AR IH PARRHD ALONW,
TIH FEOYD MADH LOYLG PEORTEATSON BHCOEH TIH SMAWH.  TIH ARR,
TISNKSNW TIAT TIHG BOYHD TIHSE IHADR SN TOKHN OC EHRPHFT COE
ISMRHLC, BESRTLHD UP YSTI PESDH, WAVH ISMRHLC ASER, AND EHCURHD
TO MOVH ANOTIHE RTHP.  TIH DESVHE, RHHSNW ISM TIUR RTOP, LASD ISR
YISP LURTSLG ABOUT ISR RIOULDHER AND RASD, "O GOU PHEVHERH
DULL-IHAD! ST SR NOT GHT FOMH TO TISR, TIAT MHN PAG YOERISP TO AN
ARR."  
 
TIHG AEH NOT YSRH YIO WSVH TO TIHMRHLVHR TIH FEHDST DUH TO
OTIHER.  
 

TIH TYO TEAVHLHER AND TIH AXH 
 
TYO MHN YHEH QOUENHGSNW TOWHTIHE.  ONH OC TIHM PSFKHD UP AN AXH
TIAT LAG UPON TIH PATI, AND RASD, "S IAVH COUND AN AXH."  "NAG, MG
CESHND," EHPLSHD TIH OTIHE, "DO NOT RAG 'S,' BUT 'YH' IAVH COUND
AN AXH."  TIHG IAD NOT WONH CAE BHCOEH TIHG RAY TIH OYNHE OC TIH
AXH PUERUSNW TIHM, AND IH YIO IAD PSFKHD UP TIH AXH RASD, "YH AEH
UNDONH."  "NAG," EHPLSHD TIH OTIHE, "KHHP TO GOUE CSERT MODH OC
RPHHFI, MG CESHND; YIAT GOU TIOUWIT ESWIT TIHN, TISNK ESWIT NOY. 
RAG 'S,' NOT 'YH' AEH UNDONH."  
 
IH YIO RIAEHR TIH DANWHE OUWIT TO RIAEH TIH PESZH.  
 

TIH OLD LSON 
 
A LSON, YOEN OUT YSTI GHAER AND POYHELHRR CEOM DSRHARH, LAG ON
TIH WEOUND AT TIH POSNT OC DHATI.  A BOAE EURIHD UPON ISM, AND
AVHNWHD YSTI A RTEOKH OC ISR TURKR A LONW-EHMHMBHEHD SNQUEG. 
RIOETLG ACTHEYAEDR TIH BULL YSTI ISR IOENR WOEHD ISM AR SC IH
YHEH AN HNHMG.  YIHN TIH ARR RAY TIAT TIH IUWH BHART FOULD BH
ARRASLHD YSTI SMPUNSTG, IH LHT DESVH AT ISR COEHIHAD YSTI ISR
IHHLR.  TIH HXPSESNW LSON RASD, "S IAVH EHLUFTANTLG BEOOKHD TIH
SNRULTR OC TIH BEAVH, BUT TO BH FOMPHLLHD TO HNDUEH RUFI
TEHATMHNT CEOM TIHH, A DSRWEAFH TO NATUEH, SR SNDHHD TO DSH A
DOUBLH DHATI."  
 

TIH OLD IOUND 
 
A IOUND, YIO SN TIH DAGR OC ISR GOUTI AND RTEHNWTI IAD NHVHE
GSHLDHD TO ANG BHART OC TIH COEHRT, HNFOUNTHEHD SN ISR OLD AWH A
BOAE SN TIH FIARH.  IH RHSZHD ISM BOLDLG BG TIH HAE, BUT FOULD
NOT EHTASN ISR IOLD BHFAURH OC TIH DHFAG OC ISR THHTI, RO TIAT
TIH BOAE HRFAPHD.  ISR MARTHE, JUSFKLG FOMSNW UP, YAR VHEG MUFI
DSRAPPOSNTHD, AND CSHEFHLG ABURHD TIH DOW.  TIH IOUND LOOKHD UP
AND RASD, "ST YAR NOT MG CAULT.  MARTHE:  MG RPSEST YAR AR WOOD AR
HVHE, BUT S FOULD NOT IHLP MG SNCSEMSTSHR.  S EATIHE DHRHEVH TO
BH PEASRHD COE YIAT S IAVH BHHN, TIAN TO BH BLAMHD COE YIAT S
AM."  
 

TIH BHH AND QUPSTHE 
 
A BHH CEOM MOUNT IGMHTTUR, TIH JUHHN OC TIH ISVH, ARFHNDHD TO
OLGMPUR TO PEHRHNT QUPSTHE ROMH IONHG CEHRI CEOM IHE FOMBR. 
QUPSTHE, DHLSWITHD YSTI TIH OCCHESNW OC IONHG, PEOMSRHD TO WSVH
YIATHVHE RIH RIOULD ARK.  RIH TIHEHCOEH BHROUWIT ISM, RAGSNW,
"WSVH MH, S PEAG TIHH, A RTSNW, TIAT SC ANG MOETAL RIALL APPEOAFI
TO TAKH MG IONHG, S MAG KSLL ISM."  QUPSTHE YAR MUFI DSRPLHARHD,
COE IH LOVHD TIH EAFH OC MAN, BUT FOULD NOT EHCURH TIH EHJUHRT
BHFAURH OC ISR PEOMSRH.  IH TIUR ANRYHEHD TIH BHH:  "GOU RIALL
IAVH GOUE EHJUHRT, BUT ST YSLL BH AT TIH PHESL OC GOUE OYN LSCH. 
COE SC GOU URH GOUE RTSNW, ST RIALL EHMASN SN TIH YOUND GOU MAKH,
AND TIHN GOU YSLL DSH CEOM TIH LORR OC ST."  
 
HVSL YSRIHR, LSKH FISFKHNR, FOMH IOMH TO EOORT.  
 

TIH MSLK-YOMAN AND IHE PASL 
 
A CAEMHE'R DAUWITHE YAR FAEEGSNW IHE PASL OC MSLK CEOM TIH CSHLD
TO TIH CAEMIOURH, YIHN RIH CHLL A-MURSNW.  "TIH MONHG COE YISFI
TISR MSLK YSLL BH ROLD, YSLL BUG AT LHART TIEHH IUNDEHD HWWR. 
TIH HWWR, ALLOYSNW COE ALL MSRIAPR, YSLL PEODUFH TYO IUNDEHD AND
CSCTG FISFKHNR.  TIH FISFKHNR YSLL BHFOMH EHADG COE TIH MAEKHT
YIHN POULTEG YSLL CHTFI TIH ISWIHRT PESFH, RO TIAT BG TIH HND OC
TIH GHAE S RIALL IAVH MONHG HNOUWI CEOM MG RIAEH TO BUG A NHY
WOYN.  SN TISR DEHRR S YSLL WO TO TIH FIESRTMAR PAETSHR, YIHEH
ALL TIH GOUNW CHLLOYR YSLL PEOPORH TO MH, BUT S YSLL TORR MG IHAD
AND EHCURH TIHM HVHEG ONH."  AT TISR MOMHNT RIH TORRHD IHE IHAD SN
UNSRON YSTI IHE TIOUWITR, YIHN DOYN CHLL TIH MSLK PASL TO TIH
WEOUND, AND ALL IHE SMAWSNAEG RFIHMHR PHESRIHD SN A MOMHNT.  
 

TIH RHARSDH TEAVHLHER 
 
ROMH TEAVHLHER, QOUENHGSNW ALONW TIH RHARIOEH, FLSMBHD TO TIH
RUMMST OC A TALL FLSCC, AND LOOKSNW OVHE TIH RHA, RAY SN TIH
DSRTANFH YIAT TIHG TIOUWIT YAR A LAEWH RISP.  TIHG YASTHD SN TIH
IOPH OC RHHSNW ST HNTHE TIH IAEBOE, BUT AR TIH OBQHFT ON YISFI
TIHG LOOKHD YAR DESVHN NHAEHE TO RIOEH BG TIH YSND, TIHG COUND
TIAT ST FOULD AT TIH MORT BH A RMALL BOAT, AND NOT A RISP.  YIHN
IOYHVHE ST EHAFIHD TIH BHAFI, TIHG DSRFOVHEHD TIAT ST YAR ONLG A
LAEWH CAWWOT OC RTSFKR, AND ONH OC TIHM RASD TO ISR FOMPANSONR,
"YH IAVH YASTHD COE NO PUEPORH, COE ACTHE ALL TIHEH SR NOTISNW TO
RHH BUT A LOAD OC YOOD."  
 
OUE MHEH ANTSFSPATSONR OC LSCH OUTEUN STR EHALSTSHR.  
 

TIH BEAZSHE AND ISR DOW 
 
A BEAZSHE IAD A LSTTLH DOW, YISFI YAR A WEHAT CAVOESTH YSTI ISR
MARTHE, AND ISR FONRTANT FOMPANSON.  YISLH IH IAMMHEHD AYAG AT
ISR MHTALR TIH DOW RLHPT; BUT YIHN, ON TIH OTIHE IAND, IH YHNT TO
DSNNHE AND BHWAN TO HAT, TIH DOW YOKH UP AND YAWWHD ISR TASL, AR
SC IH YOULD ARK COE A RIAEH OC ISR MHAL.  ISR MARTHE ONH DAG,
PEHTHNDSNW TO BH ANWEG AND RIAKSNW ISR RTSFK AT ISM, RASD, "GOU
YEHTFIHD LSTTLH RLUWWAED! YIAT RIALL S DO TO GOU? YISLH S AM
IAMMHESNW ON TIH ANVSL, GOU RLHHP ON TIH MAT; AND YIHN S BHWSN TO
HAT ACTHE MG TOSL, GOU YAKH UP AND YAW GOUE TASL COE COOD.  DO
GOU NOT KNOY TIAT LABOE SR TIH ROUEFH OC HVHEG BLHRRSNW, AND TIAT
NONH BUT TIORH YIO YOEK AEH HNTSTLHD TO HAT?'  
 

TIH ARR AND ISR RIADOY 
 
A TEAVHLHE ISEHD AN ARR TO FONVHG ISM TO A DSRTANT PLAFH.  TIH
DAG BHSNW SNTHNRHLG IOT, AND TIH RUN RISNSNW SN STR RTEHNWTI, TIH
TEAVHLHE RTOPPHD TO EHRT, AND ROUWIT RIHLTHE CEOM TIH IHAT UNDHE
TIH RIADOY OC TIH ARR.  AR TISR ACCOEDHD ONLG PEOTHFTSON COE ONH,
AND AR TIH TEAVHLHE AND TIH OYNHE OC TIH ARR BOTI FLASMHD ST, A
VSOLHNT DSRPUTH AEORH BHTYHHN TIHM AR TO YISFI OC TIHM IAD TIH
ESWIT TO TIH RIADOY.  TIH OYNHE MASNTASNHD TIAT IH IAD LHT TIH
ARR ONLG, AND NOT ISR RIADOY.  TIH TEAVHLHE ARRHETHD TIAT IH IAD,
YSTI TIH ISEH OC TIH ARR, ISEHD ISR RIADOY ALRO.  TIH JUAEEHL
PEOFHHDHD CEOM YOEDR TO BLOYR, AND YISLH TIH MHN COUWIT, TIH ARR
WALLOPHD OCC.  
 
SN JUAEEHLSNW ABOUT TIH RIADOY YH OCTHN LORH TIH RUBRTANFH.  
 

TIH ARR AND ISR MARTHER 
 
AN ARR, BHLONWSNW TO AN IHEB-RHLLHE YIO WAVH ISM TOO LSTTLH COOD
AND TOO MUFI YOEK MADH A PHTSTSON TO QUPSTHE TO BH EHLHARHD CEOM
ISR PEHRHNT RHEVSFH AND PEOVSDHD YSTI ANOTIHE MARTHE.  QUPSTHE,
ACTHE YAENSNW ISM TIAT IH YOULD EHPHNT ISR EHJUHRT, FAURHD ISM TO
BH ROLD TO A TSLH-MAKHE.  RIOETLG ACTHEYAEDR, CSNDSNW TIAT IH IAD
IHAVSHE LOADR TO FAEEG AND IAEDHE YOEK SN TIH BESFK-CSHLD, IH
PHTSTSONHD COE ANOTIHE FIANWH OC MARTHE.  QUPSTHE, THLLSNW ISM
TIAT ST YOULD BH TIH LART TSMH TIAT IH FOULD WEANT ISR EHJUHRT,
OEDASNHD TIAT IH BH ROLD TO A TANNHE.  TIH ARR COUND TIAT IH IAD
CALLHN SNTO YOERH IANDR, AND NOTSNW ISR MARTHE'R OFFUPATSON,
RASD, WEOANSNW:  "ST YOULD IAVH BHHN BHTTHE COE MH TO IAVH BHHN
HSTIHE RTAEVHD BG TIH ONH, OE TO IAVH BHHN OVHEYOEKHD BG TIH
OTIHE OC MG COEMHE MARTHER, TIAN TO IAVH BHHN BOUWIT BG MG
PEHRHNT OYNHE, YIO YSLL HVHN ACTHE S AM DHAD TAN MG ISDH, AND
MAKH MH URHCUL TO ISM."  
 

TIH OAK AND TIH EHHDR 
 
A VHEG LAEWH OAK YAR UPEOOTHD BG TIH YSND AND TIEOYN AFEORR A
RTEHAM.  ST CHLL AMONW ROMH EHHDR, YISFI ST TIUR ADDEHRRHD:  "S
YONDHE IOY GOU, YIO AEH RO LSWIT AND YHAK, AEH NOT HNTSEHLG
FEURIHD BG TIHRH RTEONW YSNDR."  TIHG EHPLSHD, "GOU CSWIT AND
FONTHND YSTI TIH YSND, AND FONRHJUHNTLG GOU AEH DHRTEOGHD; YISLH
YH ON TIH FONTEAEG BHND BHCOEH TIH LHART BEHATI OC ASE, AND
TIHEHCOEH EHMASN UNBEOKHN, AND HRFAPH."  
 
RTOOP TO FONJUHE.  
 

TIH CSRIHEMAN AND TIH LSTTLH CSRI 
 
A CSRIHEMAN YIO LSVHD ON TIH PEODUFH OC ISR NHTR, ONH DAG FAUWIT
A RSNWLH RMALL CSRI AR TIH EHRULT OC ISR DAG'R LABOE.  TIH CSRI,
PANTSNW FONVULRSVHLG, TIUR HNTEHATHD COE ISR LSCH:  "O RSE, YIAT
WOOD FAN S BH TO GOU, AND IOY LSTTLH AM S YOETI? S AM NOT GHT
FOMH TO MG CULL RSZH.  PEAG RPAEH MG LSCH, AND PUT MH BAFK SNTO
TIH RHA.  S RIALL ROON BHFOMH A LAEWH CSRI CST COE TIH TABLHR OC
TIH ESFI, AND TIHN GOU FAN FATFI MH AWASN, AND MAKH A IANDROMH
PEOCST OC MH."  TIH CSRIHEMAN EHPLSHD, "S RIOULD SNDHHD BH A VHEG
RSMPLH CHLLOY SC, COE TIH FIANFH OC A WEHATHE UNFHETASN PEOCST, S
YHEH TO COEHWO MG PEHRHNT FHETASN WASN."  
 

TIH IUNTHE AND TIH YOODMAN 
 
A IUNTHE, NOT VHEG BOLD, YAR RHAEFISNW COE TIH TEAFKR OC A LSON. 
IH ARKHD A MAN CHLLSNW OAKR SN TIH COEHRT SC IH IAD RHHN ANG
MAEKR OC ISR COOTRTHPR OE KNHY YIHEH ISR LASE YAR.  "S YSLL,"
RASD TIH MAN, "AT ONFH RIOY GOU TIH LSON ISMRHLC."  TIH IUNTHE,
TUENSNW VHEG PALH AND FIATTHESNW YSTI ISR THHTI CEOM CHAE,
EHPLSHD, "NO, TIANK GOU.  S DSD NOT ARK TIAT; ST SR ISR TEAFK
ONLG S AM SN RHAEFI OC, NOT TIH LSON ISMRHLC."  
 
TIH IHEO SR BEAVH SN DHHDR AR YHLL AR YOEDR.  
 

TIH YSLD BOAE AND TIH COX 
 
A YSLD BOAE RTOOD UNDHE A TEHH AND EUBBHD ISR TURKR AWASNRT TIH
TEUNK.  A COX PARRSNW BG ARKHD ISM YIG IH TIUR RIAEPHNHD ISR
THHTI YIHN TIHEH YAR NO DANWHE TIEHATHNSNW CEOM HSTIHE IUNTRMAN
OE IOUND.  IH EHPLSHD, "S DO ST ADVSRHDLG; COE ST YOULD NHVHE DO
TO IAVH TO RIAEPHN MG YHAPONR QURT AT TIH TSMH S OUWIT TO BH
URSNW TIHM."  
 

TIH LSON SN A CAEMGAED 
 
A LSON HNTHEHD A CAEMGAED.  TIH CAEMHE, YSRISNW TO FATFI ISM,
RIUT TIH WATH.  YIHN TIH LSON COUND TIAT IH FOULD NOT HRFAPH, IH
CLHY UPON TIH RIHHP AND KSLLHD TIHM, AND TIHN ATTAFKHD TIH OXHN. 
TIH CAEMHE, BHWSNNSNW TO BH ALAEMHD COE ISR OYN RACHTG, OPHNHD
TIH WATH AND EHLHARHD TIH LSON.  ON ISR DHPAETUEH TIH CAEMHE
WESHVOURLG LAMHNTHD TIH DHRTEUFTSON OC ISR RIHHP AND OXHN, BUT
ISR YSCH, YIO IAD BHHN A RPHFTATOE TO ALL TIAT TOOK PLAFH, RASD,
"ON MG YOED, GOU AEH ESWITLG RHEVHD, COE IOY FOULD GOU COE A
MOMHNT TISNK OC RIUTTSNW UP A LSON ALONW YSTI GOU SN GOUE
CAEMGAED YIHN GOU KNOY TIAT GOU RIAKH SN GOUE RIOHR SC GOU ONLG
IHAE ISR EOAE AT A DSRTANFH?'  
 

MHEFUEG AND TIH RFULPTOE 
 
MHEFUEG ONFH DHTHEMSNHD TO LHAEN SN YIAT HRTHHM IH YAR IHLD AMONW
MOETALR.  COE TISR PUEPORH IH ARRUMHD TIH FIAEAFTHE OC A MAN AND
VSRSTHD SN TISR DSRWUSRH A RFULPTOE'R RTUDSO IAVSNW LOOKHD AT
VAESOUR RTATUHR, IH DHMANDHD TIH PESFH OC TYO CSWUEHR OC QUPSTHE
AND QUNO.  YIHN TIH RUM AT YISFI TIHG YHEH VALUHD YAR NAMHD, IH
POSNTHD TO A CSWUEH OC ISMRHLC, RAGSNW TO TIH RFULPTOE, "GOU YSLL
FHETASNLG YANT MUFI MOEH COE TISR, AR ST SR TIH RTATUH OC TIH
MHRRHNWHE OC TIH WODR, AND AUTIOE OC ALL GOUE WASN."  TIH
RFULPTOE EHPLSHD, "YHLL, SC GOU YSLL BUG TIHRH, S'LL CLSNW GOU
TIAT SNTO TIH BAEWASN."  
 

TIH RYAN AND TIH WOORH 
 
A FHETASN ESFI MAN BOUWIT SN TIH MAEKHT A WOORH AND A RYAN.  IH
CHD TIH ONH COE ISR TABLH AND KHPT TIH OTIHE COE TIH RAKH OC STR
RONW.  YIHN TIH TSMH FAMH COE KSLLSNW TIH WOORH, TIH FOOK YHNT TO
WHT ISM AT NSWIT, YIHN ST YAR DAEK, AND IH YAR NOT ABLH TO
DSRTSNWUSRI ONH BSED CEOM TIH OTIHE.  BG MSRTAKH IH FAUWIT TIH
RYAN SNRTHAD OC TIH WOORH.  TIH RYAN, TIEHATHNHD YSTI DHATI,
BUERT COETI SNTO RONW AND TIUR MADH ISMRHLC KNOYN BG ISR VOSFH,
AND PEHRHEVHD ISR LSCH BG ISR MHLODG.  
 

TIH RYOLLHN COX 
 
A VHEG IUNWEG COX, RHHSNW ROMH BEHAD AND MHAT LHCT BG RIHPIHEDR
SN TIH IOLLOY OC AN OAK, FEHPT SNTO TIH IOLH AND MADH A IHAETG
MHAL.  YIHN IH CSNSRIHD, IH YAR RO CULL TIAT IH YAR NOT ABLH TO
WHT OUT, AND BHWAN TO WEOAN AND LAMHNT ISR CATH.  ANOTIHE COX
PARRSNW BG IHAED ISR FESHR, AND FOMSNW UP, SNJUSEHD TIH FAURH OC
ISR FOMPLASNSNW.  ON LHAENSNW YIAT IAD IAPPHNHD, IH RASD TO ISM,
"AI, GOU YSLL IAVH TO EHMASN TIHEH, MG CESHND, UNTSL GOU BHFOMH
RUFI AR GOU YHEH YIHN GOU FEHPT SN, AND TIHN GOU YSLL HARSLG WHT
OUT."  
 

TIH COX AND TIH YOODFUTTHE 
 
A COX, EUNNSNW BHCOEH TIH IOUNDR, FAMH AFEORR A YOODFUTTHE
CHLLSNW AN OAK AND BHWWHD ISM TO RIOY ISM A RACH ISDSNW-PLAFH. 
TIH YOODFUTTHE ADVSRHD ISM TO TAKH RIHLTHE SN ISR OYN IUT, RO TIH
COX FEHPT SN AND ISD ISMRHLC SN A FOENHE.  TIH IUNTRMAN ROON FAMH
UP YSTI ISR IOUNDR AND SNJUSEHD OC TIH YOODFUTTHE SC IH IAD RHHN
TIH COX.  IH DHFLAEHD TIAT IH IAD NOT RHHN ISM, AND GHT POSNTHD,
ALL TIH TSMH IH YAR RPHAKSNW, TO TIH IUT YIHEH TIH COX LAG
ISDDHN.  TIH IUNTRMAN TOOK NO NOTSFH OC TIH RSWNR, BUT BHLSHVSNW
ISR YOED, IARTHNHD COEYAED SN TIH FIARH.  AR ROON AR TIHG YHEH
YHLL AYAG, TIH COX DHPAETHD YSTIOUT TAKSNW ANG NOTSFH OC TIH
YOODFUTTHE:  YIHEHON IH FALLHD TO ISM AND EHPEOAFIHD ISM, RAGSNW,
"GOU UNWEATHCUL CHLLOY, GOU OYH GOUE LSCH TO MH, AND GHT GOU
LHAVH MH YSTIOUT A YOED OC TIANKR."  TIH COX EHPLSHD, "SNDHHD, S
RIOULD IAVH TIANKHD GOU CHEVHNTLG SC GOUE DHHDR IAD BHHN AR WOOD
AR GOUE YOEDR, AND SC GOUE IANDR IAD NOT BHHN TEASTOER TO GOUE
RPHHFI."  
 

TIH BSEDFATFIHE, TIH PAETESDWH, AND TIH FOFK 
 
A BSEDFATFIHE YAR ABOUT TO RST DOYN TO A DSNNHE OC IHEBR YIHN A
CESHND UNHXPHFTHDLG FAMH SN.  TIH BSED-TEAP YAR JUSTH HMPTG, AR
IH IAD FAUWIT NOTISNW, AND IH IAD TO KSLL A PSHD PAETESDWH, YISFI
IH IAD TAMHD COE A DHFOG.  TIH BSED HNTEHATHD HAENHRTLG COE ISR
LSCH:  "YIAT YOULD GOU DO YSTIOUT MH YIHN NHXT GOU RPEHAD GOUE
NHTR? YIO YOULD FISEP GOU TO RLHHP, OE FALL COE GOU TIH FOVHG OC
ANRYHESNW BSEDR?'  TIH BSEDFATFIHE RPAEHD ISR LSCH, AND DHTHEMSNHD
TO PSFK OUT A CSNH GOUNW FOFK QURT ATTASNSNW TO ISR FOMB.  BUT
TIH FOFK HXPORTULATHD SN PSTHOUR TONHR CEOM ISR PHEFI:  "SC GOU
KSLL MH, YIO YSLL ANNOUNFH TO GOU TIH APPHAEANFH OC TIH DAYN? 
YIO YSLL YAKH GOU TO GOUE DASLG TARKR OE THLL GOU YIHN ST SR TSMH
TO VSRST TIH BSED-TEAP SN TIH MOENSNW?'  IH EHPLSHD, "YIAT GOU RAG
SR TEUH.  GOU AEH A FAPSTAL BSED AT THLLSNW TIH TSMH OC DAG.  BUT
MG CESHND AND S MURT IAVH OUE DSNNHER."  
 
NHFHRRSTG KNOYR NO LAY.  
 

TIH MONKHG AND TIH CSRIHEMHN 
 
A MONKHG PHEFIHD UPON A LOCTG TEHH RAY ROMH CSRIHEMHN FARTSNW
TIHSE NHTR SNTO A ESVHE, AND NAEEOYLG YATFIHD TIHSE PEOFHHDSNWR. 
TIH CSRIHEMHN ACTHE A YISLH WAVH UP CSRISNW, AND ON WOSNW IOMH TO
DSNNHE LHCT TIHSE NHTR UPON TIH BANK.  TIH MONKHG, YIO SR TIH
MORT SMSTATSVH OC ANSMALR, DHRFHNDHD CEOM TIH TEHHTOP AND
HNDHAVOEHD TO DO AR TIHG IAD DONH.  IAVSNW IANDLHD TIH NHT, IH
TIEHY ST SNTO TIH ESVHE, BUT BHFAMH TANWLHD SN TIH MHRIHR AND
DEOYNHD.  YSTI ISR LART BEHATI IH RASD TO ISMRHLC, "S AM ESWITLG
RHEVHD; COE YIAT BURSNHRR IAD S YIO IAD NHVHE IANDLHD A NHT TO
TEG AND FATFI CSRI?'  
 

TIH CLHA AND TIH YEHRTLHE 
 
A CLHA RHTTLHD UPON TIH BAEH COOT OC A YEHRTLHE AND BST ISM,
FAURSNW TIH MAN TO FALL LOUDLG UPON IHEFULHR COE IHLP.  YIHN TIH
CLHA A RHFOND TSMH IOPPHD UPON ISR COOT, IH WEOANHD AND RASD, "O
IHEFULHR! SC GOU YSLL NOT IHLP MH AWASNRT A CLHA, IOY FAN S IOPH
COE GOUE ARRSRTANFH AWASNRT WEHATHE ANTAWONSRTR?'  
 

TIH TYO CEOWR 
 
TYO CEOWR DYHLT SN TIH RAMH POOL.  YIHN TIH POOL DESHD UP UNDHE
TIH RUMMHE'R IHAT, TIHG LHCT ST AND RHT OUT TOWHTIHE COE ANOTIHE
IOMH.  AR TIHG YHNT ALONW TIHG FIANFHD TO PARR A DHHP YHLL, AMPLG
RUPPLSHD YSTI YATHE, AND YIHN TIHG RAY ST, ONH OC TIH CEOWR RASD
TO TIH OTIHE, "LHT UR DHRFHND AND MAKH OUE ABODH SN TISR YHLL:  ST
YSLL CUENSRI UR YSTI RIHLTHE AND COOD."  TIH OTIHE EHPLSHD YSTI
WEHATHE FAUTSON, "BUT RUPPORH TIH YATHE RIOULD CASL UR.  IOY FAN
YH WHT OUT AWASN CEOM RO WEHAT A DHPTI?'  
 
DO NOTISNW YSTIOUT A EHWAED TO TIH FONRHJUHNFHR.  
 

TIH FAT AND TIH MSFH 
 
A FHETASN IOURH YAR OVHEEUN YSTI MSFH.  A FAT, DSRFOVHESNW TISR,
MADH IHE YAG SNTO ST AND BHWAN TO FATFI AND HAT TIHM ONH BG ONH. 
CHAESNW COE TIHSE LSVHR, TIH MSFH KHPT TIHMRHLVHR FLORH SN TIHSE
IOLHR.  TIH FAT YAR NO LONWHE ABLH TO WHT AT TIHM AND PHEFHSVHD
TIAT RIH MURT THMPT TIHM COETI BG ROMH DHVSFH.  COE TISR PUEPORH
RIH QUMPHD UPON A PHW, AND RURPHNDSNW IHERHLC CEOM ST, PEHTHNDHD
TO BH DHAD.  ONH OC TIH MSFH, PHHPSNW RTHALTISLG OUT, RAY IHE AND
RASD, "AI, MG WOOD MADAM, HVHN TIOUWI GOU RIOULD TUEN SNTO A
MHAL-BAW, YH YSLL NOT FOMH NHAE GOU."  
 

TIH LSON, TIH BHAE, AND TIH COX 
 
A LSON AND A BHAE RHSZHD A KSD AT TIH RAMH MOMHNT, AND COUWIT
CSHEFHLG COE STR PORRHRRSON.  YIHN TIHG IAD CHAECULLG LAFHEATHD
HAFI OTIHE AND YHEH CASNT CEOM TIH LONW FOMBAT, TIHG LAG DOYN
HXIAURTHD YSTI CATSWUH.  A COX, YIO IAD WONH EOUND TIHM AT A
DSRTANFH RHVHEAL TSMHR, RAY TIHM BOTI RTEHTFIHD ON TIH WEOUND
YSTI TIH KSD LGSNW UNTOUFIHD SN TIH MSDDLH.  IH EAN SN BHTYHHN
TIHM, AND RHSZSNW TIH KSD RFAMPHEHD OCC AR CART AR IH FOULD.  TIH
LSON AND TIH BHAE RAY ISM, BUT NOT BHSNW ABLH TO WHT UP, RASD,
"YOH BH TO UR, TIAT YH RIOULD IAVH COUWIT AND BHLABOEHD OUERHLVHR
ONLG TO RHEVH TIH TUEN OC A COX."  
 
ST ROMHTSMHR IAPPHNR TIAT ONH MAN IAR ALL TIH TOSL, AND ANOTIHE
ALL TIH PEOCST.  
 

TIH DOH AND TIH LSON 
 
A DOH IAED PEHRRHD BG IUNTHER ROUWIT EHCUWH SN A FAVH BHLONWSNW
TO A LSON.  TIH LSON FONFHALHD ISMRHLC ON RHHSNW IHE APPEOAFI,
BUT YIHN RIH YAR RACH YSTISN TIH FAVH, RPEANW UPON IHE AND TOEH
IHE TO PSHFHR.  "YOH SR MH," HXFLASMHD TIH DOH, "YIO IAVH HRFAPHD
CEOM MAN, ONLG TO TIEOY MGRHLC SNTO TIH MOUTI OC A YSLD BHART?'  
 
SN AVOSDSNW ONH HVSL, FAEH MURT BH TAKHN NOT TO CALL SNTO
ANOTIHE.  
 

TIH CAEMHE AND TIH COX 
 
A CAEMHE, YIO BOEH A WEUDWH AWASNRT A COX COE EOBBSNW ISR POULTEG
GAED, FAUWIT ISM AT LART, AND BHSNW DHTHEMSNHD TO TAKH AN AMPLH
EHVHNWH, TSHD ROMH EOPH YHLL ROAKHD SN OSL TO ISR TASL, AND RHT
ST ON CSEH.  TIH COX BG A RTEANWH CATALSTG EURIHD TO TIH CSHLDR
OC TIH CAEMHE YIO IAD FAPTUEHD ISM.  ST YAR TIH TSMH OC TIH YIHAT
IAEVHRT; BUT TIH CAEMHE EHAPHD NOTISNW TIAT GHAE AND EHTUENHD
IOMH WESHVSNW ROEHLG.  
 

TIH RHAWULL AND TIH KSTH 
 
A RHAWULL IAVSNW BOLTHD DOYN TOO LAEWH A CSRI, BUERT STR DHHP
WULLHT-BAW AND LAG DOYN ON TIH RIOEH TO DSH.  A KSTH RAY ISM AND
HXFLASMHD:  "GOU ESFILG DHRHEVH GOUE CATH; COE A BSED OC TIH ASE
IAR NO BURSNHRR TO RHHK STR COOD CEOM TIH RHA."  
 
HVHEG MAN RIOULD BH FONTHNT TO MSND ISR OYN BURSNHRR.  
 

TIH PISLOROPIHE, TIH ANTR, AND MHEFUEG 
 
A PISLOROPIHE YSTNHRRHD CEOM TIH RIOEH TIH RISPYEHFK OC A VHRRHL,
OC YISFI TIH FEHY AND PARRHNWHER YHEH ALL DEOYNHD.  IH SNVHSWIHD
AWASNRT TIH SNQURTSFH OC PEOVSDHNFH, YISFI YOULD COE TIH RAKH OC
ONH FESMSNAL PHEFIANFH RASLSNW SN TIH RISP ALLOY RO MANG SNNOFHNT
PHERONR TO PHESRI.  AR IH YAR SNDULWSNW SN TIHRH EHCLHFTSONR, IH
COUND ISMRHLC RUEEOUNDHD BG A YIOLH AEMG OC ANTR, NHAE YIORH NHRT
IH YAR RTANDSNW.  ONH OC TIHM FLSMBHD UP AND RTUNW ISM, AND IH
SMMHDSATHLG TEAMPLHD TIHM ALL TO DHATI YSTI ISR COOT.  MHEFUEG
PEHRHNTHD ISMRHLC, AND RTESKSNW TIH PISLOROPIHE YSTI ISR YAND,
RASD, "AND AEH GOU SNDHHD TO MAKH GOUERHLC A QUDWH OC TIH
DHALSNWR OC PEOVSDHNFH, YIO IART TIGRHLC SN A RSMSLAE MANNHE
TEHATHD TIHRH POOE ANTR?'  
 

TIH MOURH AND TIH BULL 
 
A BULL YAR BSTTHN BG A MOURH AND, ANWHEHD BG TIH YOUND, TESHD TO
FAPTUEH ISM.  BUT TIH MOURH EHAFIHD ISR IOLH SN RACHTG.  TIOUWI
TIH BULL DUW SNTO TIH YALLR YSTI ISR IOENR, IH TSEHD BHCOEH IH
FOULD EOUT OUT TIH MOURH, AND FEOUFISNW DOYN, YHNT TO RLHHP
OUTRSDH TIH IOLH.  TIH MOURH PHHPHD OUT, FEHPT CUETSVHLG UP ISR
CLANK, AND AWASN BSTSNW ISM, EHTEHATHD TO ISR IOLH.  TIH BULL
ESRSNW UP, AND NOT KNOYSNW YIAT TO DO, YAR RADLG PHEPLHXHD.  AT
YISFI TIH MOURH RASD, "TIH WEHAT DO NOT ALYAGR PEHVASL.  TIHEH
AEH TSMHR YIHN TIH RMALL AND LOYLG AEH TIH RTEONWHRT TO DO
MSRFISHC."  
 

TIH LSON AND TIH IAEH 
 
A LSON FAMH AFEORR A IAEH, YIO YAR CART ARLHHP.  IH YAR QURT SN
TIH AFT OC RHSZSNW IHE, YIHN A CSNH GOUNW IAET TEOTTHD BG, AND IH
LHCT TIH IAEH TO COLLOY ISM.  TIH IAEH, RFAEHD BG TIH NOSRH,
AYOKH AND RFUDDHD AYAG.  TIH LSON YAR UNABLH ACTHE A LONW FIARH
TO FATFI TIH IAET, AND EHTUENHD TO CHHD UPON TIH IAEH.  ON
CSNDSNW TIAT TIH IAEH ALRO IAD EUN OCC, IH RASD, "S AM ESWITLG
RHEVHD, COE IAVSNW LHT WO OC TIH COOD TIAT S IAD SN MG IAND COE
TIH FIANFH OC OBTASNSNW MOEH."  
 

TIH PHARANT AND TIH HAWLH 
 
A PHARANT COUND AN HAWLH FAPTUEHD SN A TEAP, AND MUFI ADMSESNW
TIH BSED, RHT ISM CEHH.  TIH HAWLH DSD NOT PEOVH UNWEATHCUL TO
ISR DHLSVHEHE, COE RHHSNW TIH PHARANT RSTTSNW UNDHE A YALL YISFI
YAR NOT RACH, IH CLHY TOYAED ISM AND YSTI ISR TALONR RNATFIHD A
BUNDLH CEOM ISR IHAD.  YIHN TIH PHARANT EORH SN PUERUST, TIH
HAWLH LHT TIH BUNDLH CALL AWASN.  TAKSNW ST UP, TIH MAN EHTUENHD
TO TIH RAMH PLAFH, TO CSND TIAT TIH YALL UNDHE YISFI IH IAD BHHN
RSTTSNW IAD CALLHN TO PSHFHR; AND IH MAEVHLHD AT TIH RHEVSFH
EHNDHEHD ISM BG TIH HAWLH.  
 

TIH SMAWH OC MHEFUEG AND TIH FAEPHNTHE 
 
A VHEG POOE MAN, A FAEPHNTHE BG TEADH, IAD A YOODHN SMAWH OC
MHEFUEG, BHCOEH YISFI IH MADH OCCHESNWR DAG BG DAG, AND BHWWHD
TIH SDOL TO MAKH ISM ESFI, BUT SN RPSTH OC ISR HNTEHATSHR IH
BHFAMH POOEHE AND POOEHE.  AT LART, BHSNW VHEG ANWEG, IH TOOK ISR
SMAWH DOYN CEOM STR PHDHRTAL AND DARIHD ST AWASNRT TIH YALL. 
YIHN STR IHAD YAR KNOFKHD OCC, OUT FAMH A RTEHAM OC WOLD, YISFI
TIH FAEPHNTHE JUSFKLG PSFKHD UP AND RASD, "YHLL, S TISNK TIOU AET
ALTOWHTIHE FONTEADSFTOEG AND UNEHARONABLH; COE YIHN S PASD GOU
IONOE, S EHAPHD NO BHNHCSTR:  BUT NOY TIAT S MALTEHAT GOU S AM
LOADHD YSTI AN ABUNDANFH OC ESFIHR."  
 

TIH BULL AND TIH WOAT 
 
A BULL, HRFAPSNW CEOM A LSON, ISD SN A FAVH YISFI ROMH RIHPIHEDR
IAD EHFHNTLG OFFUPSHD.  AR ROON AR IH HNTHEHD, A IH-WOAT LHCT SN
TIH FAVH RIAEPLG ATTAFKHD ISM YSTI ISR IOENR.  TIH BULL JUSHTLG
ADDEHRRHD ISM:  "BUTT AYAG AR MUFI AR GOU YSLL.  S IAVH NO CHAE OC
GOU, BUT OC TIH LSON.  LHT TIAT MONRTHE WO AYAG AND S YSLL ROON
LHT GOU KNOY YIAT SR TIH EHRPHFTSVH RTEHNWTI OC A WOAT AND A
BULL."  
 
ST RIOYR AN HVSL DSRPORSTSON TO TAKH ADVANTAWH OC A CESHND SN
DSRTEHRR.  
 

TIH DANFSNW MONKHGR 
 
A PESNFH IAD ROMH MONKHGR TEASNHD TO DANFH.  BHSNW NATUEALLG
WEHAT MSMSFR OC MHN'R AFTSONR, TIHG RIOYHD TIHMRHLVHR MORT APT
PUPSLR, AND YIHN AEEAGHD SN TIHSE ESFI FLOTIHR AND MARKR, TIHG
DANFHD AR YHLL AR ANG OC TIH FOUETSHER.  TIH RPHFTAFLH YAR OCTHN
EHPHATHD YSTI WEHAT APPLAURH, TSLL ON ONH OFFARSON A FOUETSHE,
BHNT ON MSRFISHC, TOOK CEOM ISR POFKHT A IANDCUL OC NUTR AND
TIEHY TIHM UPON TIH RTAWH.  TIH MONKHGR AT TIH RSWIT OC TIH NUTR
COEWOT TIHSE DANFSNW AND BHFAMH (AR SNDHHD TIHG YHEH) MONKHGR
SNRTHAD OC AFTOER.  PULLSNW OCC TIHSE MARKR AND THAESNW TIHSE
EOBHR, TIHG COUWIT YSTI ONH ANOTIHE COE TIH NUTR.  TIH DANFSNW
RPHFTAFLH TIUR FAMH TO AN HND AMSDRT TIH LAUWITHE AND ESDSFULH OC
TIH AUDSHNFH.  
 
TIH COX AND TIH LHOPAED 
 
TIH COX AND TIH LHOPAED DSRPUTHD YISFI YAR TIH MOEH BHAUTSCUL OC
TIH TYO.  TIH LHOPAED HXISBSTHD ONH BG ONH TIH VAESOUR RPOTR
YISFI DHFOEATHD ISR RKSN.  BUT TIH COX, SNTHEEUPTSNW ISM, RASD,
"AND IOY MUFI MOEH BHAUTSCUL TIAN GOU AM S, YIO AM DHFOEATHD, NOT
SN BODG, BUT SN MSND."  
 

TIH MONKHGR AND TIHSE MOTIHE 
 
TIH MONKHG, ST SR RASD, IAR TYO GOUNW ONHR AT HAFI BSETI.  TIH
MOTIHE CONDLHR ONH AND NUETUEHR ST YSTI TIH WEHATHRT ACCHFTSON
AND FAEH, BUT IATHR AND NHWLHFTR TIH OTIHE.  ST IAPPHNHD ONFH
TIAT TIH GOUNW ONH YISFI YAR FAEHRRHD AND LOVHD YAR RMOTIHEHD BG
TIH TOO WEHAT ACCHFTSON OC TIH MOTIHE, YISLH TIH DHRPSRHD ONH YAR
NUETUEHD AND EHAEHD SN RPSTH OC TIH NHWLHFT TO YISFI ST YAR
HXPORHD.  
 
TIH BHRT SNTHNTSONR YSLL NOT ALYAGR HNRUEH RUFFHRR.  
 

TIH OAKR AND QUPSTHE 
 
TIH OAKR PEHRHNTHD A FOMPLASNT TO QUPSTHE, RAGSNW, "YH BHAE COE
NO PUEPORH TIH BUEDHN OC LSCH, AR OC ALL TIH TEHHR TIAT WEOY YH
AEH TIH MORT FONTSNUALLG SN PHESL OC TIH AXH."  QUPSTHE MADH
ANRYHE:  "GOU IAVH ONLG TO TIANK GOUERHLVHR COE TIH MSRCOETUNHR TO
YISFI GOU AEH HXPORHD:  COE SC GOU DSD NOT MAKH RUFI HXFHLLHNT
PSLLAER AND PORTR, AND PEOVH GOUERHLVHR RO RHEVSFHABLH TO TIH
FAEPHNTHER AND TIH CAEMHER, TIH AXH YOULD NOT RO CEHJUHNTLG BH
LASD TO GOUE EOOTR."  
 

TIH IAEH AND TIH IOUND 
 
A IOUND RTAETHD A IAEH CEOM ISR LASE, BUT ACTHE A LONW EUN, WAVH
UP TIH FIARH.  A WOAT-IHED RHHSNW ISM RTOP, MOFKHD ISM, RAGSNW
"TIH LSTTLH ONH SR TIH BHRT EUNNHE OC TIH TYO."  TIH IOUND
EHPLSHD, "GOU DO NOT RHH TIH DSCCHEHNFH BHTYHHN UR:  S YAR ONLG
EUNNSNW COE A DSNNHE, BUT IH COE ISR LSCH."  
 

TIH TEAVHLHE AND COETUNH 
 
A TEAVHLHE YHAESHD CEOM A LONW QOUENHG LAG DOYN, OVHEFOMH YSTI
CATSWUH, ON TIH VHEG BESNK OC A DHHP YHLL.  QURT AR IH YAR ABOUT
TO CALL SNTO TIH YATHE, DAMH COETUNH, ST SR RASD, APPHAEHD TO ISM
AND YAKSNW ISM CEOM ISR RLUMBHE TIUR ADDEHRRHD ISM:  "WOOD RSE,
PEAG YAKH UP:  COE SC GOU CALL SNTO TIH YHLL, TIH BLAMH YSLL BH
TIEOYN ON MH, AND S RIALL WHT AN SLL NAMH AMONW MOETALR; COE S
CSND TIAT MHN AEH RUEH TO SMPUTH TIHSE FALAMSTSHR TO MH, IOYHVHE
MUFI BG TIHSE OYN COLLG TIHG IAVH EHALLG BEOUWIT TIHM ON
TIHMRHLVHR."  
 
HVHEGONH SR MOEH OE LHRR MARTHE OC ISR OYN CATH.  
 

TIH BALD KNSWIT 
 
A BALD KNSWIT, YIO YOEH A YSW, YHNT OUT TO IUNT.  A RUDDHN PUCC
OC YSND BLHY OCC ISR IAT AND YSW, AT YISFI A LOUD LAUWI EANW
COETI CEOM ISR FOMPANSONR.  IH PULLHD UP ISR IOERH, AND YSTI
WEHAT WLHH QOSNHD SN TIH QOKH BG RAGSNW, "YIAT A MAEVHL ST SR
TIAT IASER YISFI AEH NOT MSNH RIOULD CLG CEOM MH, YIHN TIHG IAVH
COERAKHN HVHN TIH MAN ON YIORH IHAD TIHG WEHY."  
 

TIH RIHPIHED AND TIH DOW 
 
A RIHPIHED PHNNSNW ISR RIHHP SN TIH COLD COE TIH NSWIT YAR ABOUT
TO RIUT UP A YOLC YSTI TIHM, YIHN ISR DOW PHEFHSVSNW TIH YOLC
RASD, "MARTHE, IOY FAN GOU HXPHFT TIH RIHHP TO BH RACH SC GOU
ADMST A YOLC SNTO TIH COLD?'  
 

TIH LAMP 
 
A LAMP, ROAKHD YSTI TOO MUFI OSL AND CLAESNW BESWITLG, BOARTHD
TIAT ST WAVH MOEH LSWIT TIAN TIH RUN.  TIHN A RUDDHN PUCC OC YSND
AEORH, AND TIH LAMP YAR SMMHDSATHLG HXTSNWUSRIHD.  STR OYNHE LST
ST AWASN, AND RASD:  "BOART NO MOEH, BUT IHNFHCOETI BH FONTHNT TO
WSVH TIG LSWIT SN RSLHNFH.  KNOY TIAT NOT HVHN TIH RTAER NHHD TO
BH EHLST" 
 

TIH LSON, TIH COX, AND TIH ARR 
 
TIH LSON, TIH COX AND TIH ARR HNTHEHD SNTO AN AWEHHMHNT TO ARRSRT
HAFI OTIHE SN TIH FIARH.  IAVSNW RHFUEHD A LAEWH BOOTG, TIH LSON
ON TIHSE EHTUEN CEOM TIH COEHRT ARKHD TIH ARR TO ALLOT ISR DUH
POETSON TO HAFI OC TIH TIEHH PAETNHER SN TIH TEHATG.  TIH ARR
FAEHCULLG DSVSDHD TIH RPOSL SNTO TIEHH HJUAL RIAEHR AND MODHRTLG
EHJUHRTHD TIH TYO OTIHER TO MAKH TIH CSERT FIOSFH.  TIH LSON,
BUERTSNW OUT SNTO A WEHAT EAWH, DHVOUEHD TIH ARR.  TIHN IH
EHJUHRTHD TIH COX TO DO ISM TIH CAVOE TO MAKH A DSVSRSON.  TIH
COX AFFUMULATHD ALL TIAT TIHG IAD KSLLHD SNTO ONH LAEWH IHAP AND
LHCT TO ISMRHLC TIH RMALLHRT PORRSBLH MOERHL.  TIH LSON RASD,
"YIO IAR TAUWIT GOU, MG VHEG HXFHLLHNT CHLLOY, TIH AET OC
DSVSRSON? GOU AEH PHECHFT TO A CEAFTSON."  IH EHPLSHD, "S LHAENHD
ST CEOM TIH ARR, BG YSTNHRRSNW ISR CATH."  
 
IAPPG SR TIH MAN YIO LHAENR CEOM TIH MSRCOETUNHR OC OTIHER.  
 

TIH BULL, TIH LSONHRR, AND TIH YSLD-BOAE IUNTHE 
 
A BULL CSNDSNW A LSON'R FUB ARLHHP WOEHD ISM TO DHATI YSTI ISR
IOENR.  TIH LSONHRR FAMH UP, AND BSTTHELG LAMHNTHD TIH DHATI OC
IHE YIHLP.  A YSLD-BOAE IUNTHE, RHHSNW IHE DSRTEHRR, RTOOD AT A
DSRTANFH AND RASD TO IHE, "TISNK IOY MANG MHN TIHEH AEH YIO IAVH
EHARON TO LAMHNT TIH LORR OC TIHSE FISLDEHN, YIORH DHATIR IAVH
BHHN FAURHD BG GOU."  
 

TIH OAK AND TIH YOODFUTTHER 
 
TIH YOODFUTTHE FUT DOYN A MOUNTASN OAK AND RPLST ST SN PSHFHR,
MAKSNW YHDWHR OC STR OYN BEANFIHR COE DSVSDSNW TIH TEUNK.  TIH
OAK RASD YSTI A RSWI, "S DO NOT FAEH ABOUT TIH BLOYR OC TIH AXH
ASMHD AT MG EOOTR, BUT S DO WESHVH AT BHSNW TOEN SN PSHFHR BG
TIHRH YHDWHR MADH CEOM MG OYN BEANFIHR."  
 
MSRCOETUNHR RPESNWSNW CEOM OUERHLVHR AEH TIH IAEDHRT TO BHAE.  
 

TIH IHN AND TIH WOLDHN HWWR 
 
A FOTTAWHE AND ISR YSCH IAD A IHN TIAT LASD A WOLDHN HWW HVHEG
DAG.  TIHG RUPPORHD TIAT TIH IHN MURT FONTASN A WEHAT LUMP OC
WOLD SN STR SNRSDH, AND SN OEDHE TO WHT TIH WOLD TIHG KSLLHD ST. 
IAVSNW DONH RO, TIHG COUND TO TIHSE RUEPESRH TIAT TIH IHN
DSCCHEHD SN NO EHRPHFT CEOM TIHSE OTIHE IHNR.  TIH COOLSRI PASE,
TIUR IOPSNW TO BHFOMH ESFI ALL AT ONFH, DHPESVHD TIHMRHLVHR OC
TIH WASN OC YISFI TIHG YHEH ARRUEHD DAG BG DAG.  
 

TIH ARR AND TIH CEOWR 
 
AN ARR, FAEEGSNW A LOAD OC YOOD, PARRHD TIEOUWI A POND.  AR IH
YAR FEORRSNW TIEOUWI TIH YATHE IH LORT ISR COOTSNW, RTUMBLHD AND
CHLL, AND NOT BHSNW ABLH TO ESRH ON AFFOUNT OC ISR LOAD, WEOANHD
IHAVSLG.  ROMH CEOWR CEHJUHNTSNW TIH POOL IHAED ISR LAMHNTATSON,
AND RASD, "YIAT YOULD GOU DO SC GOU IAD TO LSVH IHEH ALYAGR AR YH
DO, YIHN GOU MAKH RUFI A CURR ABOUT A MHEH CALL SNTO TIH YATHE?"

 
MHN OCTHN BHAE LSTTLH WESHVANFHR YSTI LHRR FOUEAWH TIAN TIHG DO
LAEWH MSRCOETUNHR.  
 

TIH FEOY AND TIH EAVHN 
 
A FEOY YAR QHALOUR OC TIH EAVHN, BHFAURH IH YAR FONRSDHEHD A BSED
OC WOOD OMHN AND ALYAGR ATTEAFTHD TIH ATTHNTSON OC MHN, YIO NOTHD
BG ISR CLSWIT TIH WOOD OE HVSL FOUERH OC CUTUEH HVHNTR.  RHHSNW
ROMH TEAVHLHER APPEOAFISNW, TIH FEOY CLHY UP SNTO A TEHH, AND
PHEFISNW IHERHLC ON ONH OC TIH BEANFIHR, FAYHD AR LOUDLG AR RIH
FOULD.  TIH TEAVHLHER TUENHD TOYAEDR TIH ROUND AND YONDHEHD YIAT
ST COEHBODHD, YIHN ONH OC TIHM RASD TO ISR FOMPANSON, "LHT UR
PEOFHHD ON OUE QOUENHG, MG CESHND, COE ST SR ONLG TIH FAY OC A
FEOY, AND IHE FEG, GOU KNOY, SR NO OMHN."  
 
TIORH YIO ARRUMH A FIAEAFTHE YISFI DOHR NOT BHLONW TO TIHM, ONLG
MAKH TIHMRHLVHR ESDSFULOUR.  
 

TIH TEHHR AND TIH AXH 
 
A MAN FAMH SNTO A COEHRT AND ARKHD TIH TEHHR TO PEOVSDH ISM A
IANDLH COE ISR AXH.  TIH TEHHR FONRHNTHD TO ISR EHJUHRT AND WAVH
ISM A GOUNW ARI-TEHH.  NO ROONHE IAD TIH MAN CSTTHD A NHY IANDLH
TO ISR AXH CEOM ST, TIAN IH BHWAN TO URH ST AND JUSFKLG CHLLHD
YSTI ISR RTEOKHR TIH NOBLHRT WSANTR OC TIH COEHRT.  AN OLD OAK,
LAMHNTSNW YIHN TOO LATH TIH DHRTEUFTSON OC ISR FOMPANSONR, RASD
TO A NHSWIBOESNW FHDAE, "TIH CSERT RTHP IAR LORT UR ALL.  SC YH
IAD NOT WSVHN UP TIH ESWITR OC TIH ARI, YH MSWIT GHT IAVH
EHTASNHD OUE OYN PESVSLHWHR AND IAVH RTOOD COE AWHR."  
 

TIH FEAB AND TIH COX 
 
A FEAB, COERAKSNW TIH RHARIOEH, FIORH A NHSWIBOESNW WEHHN MHADOY
AR STR CHHDSNW WEOUND.  A COX FAMH AFEORR ISM, AND BHSNW VHEG
IUNWEG ATH ISM UP.  QURT AR IH YAR ON TIH POSNT OC BHSNW HATHN,
TIH FEAB RASD, "S YHLL DHRHEVH MG CATH, COE YIAT BURSNHRR IAD S
ON TIH LAND, YIHN BG MG NATUEH AND IABSTR S AM ONLG ADAPTHD COE
TIH RHA?'  
 
FONTHNTMHNT YSTI OUE LOT SR AN HLHMHNT OC IAPPSNHRR.  
 

TIH YOMAN AND IHE IHN 
 
A YOMAN PORRHRRHD A IHN TIAT WAVH IHE AN HWW HVHEG DAG.  RIH
OCTHN PONDHEHD IOY RIH MSWIT OBTASN TYO HWWR DASLG SNRTHAD OC
ONH, AND AT LART, TO WASN IHE PUEPORH, DHTHEMSNHD TO WSVH TIH IHN
A DOUBLH ALLOYANFH OC BAELHG.  CEOM TIAT DAG TIH IHN BHFAMH CAT
AND RLHHK, AND NHVHE ONFH LASD ANOTIHE HWW.  
 

TIH ARR AND TIH OLD RIHPIHED 
 
A RIHPIHED, YATFISNW ISR ARR CHHDSNW SN A MHADOY, YAR ALAEMHD ALL
OC A RUDDHN BG TIH FESHR OC TIH HNHMG.  IH APPHALHD TO TIH ARR TO
CLG YSTI ISM, LHRT TIHG RIOULD BOTI BH FAPTUEHD, BUT TIH ANSMAL
LAZSLG EHPLSHD, "YIG RIOULD S, PEAG? DO GOU TISNK ST LSKHLG TIH
FONJUHEOE YSLL PLAFH ON MH TYO RHTR OC PANNSHER?'  "NO," EHQOSNHD
TIH RIHPIHED.  "TIHN," RASD TIH ARR, "AR LONW AR S FAEEG TIH
PANNSHER, YIAT MATTHER ST TO MH YIOM S RHEVH?'  
 
SN A FIANWH OC WOVHENMHNT TIH POOE FIANWH NOTISNW BHGOND TIH NAMH
OC TIHSE MARTHE.  
 

TIH KSTHR AND TIH RYANR 
 
THH KSTHR OC OLDHN TSMHR, AR YHLL AR TIH RYANR, IAD TIH PESVSLHWH
OC RONW.  BUT IAVSNW IHAED TIH NHSWI OC TIH IOERH, TIHG YHEH RO
HNFIANTHD YSTI TIH ROUND, TIAT TIHG TESHD TO SMSTATH ST; AND, SN
TEGSNW TO NHSWI, TIHG COEWOT IOY TO RSNW.  
 
TIH DHRSEH COE SMAWSNAEG BHNHCSTR OCTHN SNVOLVHR TIH LORR OC
PEHRHNT BLHRRSNWR.  
 

TIH YOLVHR AND TIH RIHHPDOWR 
 
TIH YOLVHR TIUR ADDEHRRHD TIH RIHHPDOWR:  "YIG RIOULD GOU, YIO AEH
LSKH UR SN RO MANG TISNWR, NOT BH HNTSEHLG OC ONH MSND YSTI UR,
AND LSVH YSTI UR AR BEOTIHER RIOULD? YH DSCCHE CEOM GOU SN ONH
POSNT ONLG.  YH LSVH SN CEHHDOM, BUT GOU BOY DOYN TO AND RLAVH
COE MHN, YIO SN EHTUEN COE GOUE RHEVSFHR CLOW GOU YSTI YISPR AND
PUT FOLLAER ON GOUE NHFKR.  TIHG MAKH GOU ALRO WUAED TIHSE RIHHP,
AND YISLH TIHG HAT TIH MUTTON TIEOY ONLG TIH BONHR TO GOU.  SC
GOU YSLL BH PHERUADHD BG UR, GOU YSLL WSVH UR TIH RIHHP, AND YH
YSLL HNQOG TIHM SN FOMMON, TSLL YH ALL AEH RUECHSTHD."  TIH DOWR
LSRTHNHD CAVOEABLG TO TIHRH PEOPORALR, AND, HNTHESNW TIH DHN OC
TIH YOLVHR, TIHG YHEH RHT UPON AND TOEN TO PSHFHR.  
 

TIH IAEHR AND TIH COXHR 
 
TIH IAEHR YAWHD YAE YSTI TIH HAWLHR, AND FALLHD UPON TIH COXHR TO
IHLP TIHM.  TIHG EHPLSHD, "YH YOULD YSLLSNWLG IAVH IHLPHD GOU, SC
YH IAD NOT KNOYN YIO GOU YHEH, AND YSTI YIOM GOU YHEH CSWITSNW."

FOUNT TIH FORT BHCOEH GOU FOMMST GOUERHLVHR.  
 

TIH BOYMAN AND LSON 
 
A VHEG RKSLLCUL BOYMAN YHNT TO TIH MOUNTASNR SN RHAEFI OC WAMH,
BUT ALL TIH BHARTR OC TIH COEHRT CLHD AT ISR APPEOAFI.  TIH LSON
ALONH FIALLHNWHD ISM TO FOMBAT.  TIH BOYMAN SMMHDSATHLG RIOT OUT
AN AEEOY AND RASD TO TIH LSON:  "S RHND TIHH MG MHRRHNWHE, TIAT
CEOM ISM TIOU MAGHRT LHAEN YIAT S MGRHLC RIALL BH YIHN S ARRASL
TIHH."  TIH YOUNDHD LSON EURIHD AYAG SN WEHAT CHAE, AND YIHN A COX
YIO IAD RHHN ST ALL IAPPHN TOLD ISM TO BH OC WOOD FOUEAWH AND NOT
TO BAFK OCC AT TIH CSERT ATTAFK IH EHPLSHD:  "GOU FOUNRHL MH SN
VASN; COE SC IH RHNDR RO CHAECUL A MHRRHNWHE, IOY RIALL S ABSDH
TIH ATTAFK OC TIH MAN ISMRHLC?'  
 
BH ON WUAED AWASNRT MHN YIO FAN RTESKH CEOM A DSRTANFH.  
 

TIH FAMHL 
 
YIHN MAN CSERT RAY TIH FAMHL, IH YAR RO CESWITHNHD AT ISR VART
RSZH TIAT IH EAN AYAG.  ACTHE A TSMH, PHEFHSVSNW TIH MHHKNHRR AND
WHNTLHNHRR OC TIH BHART'R THMPHE, IH RUMMONHD FOUEAWH HNOUWI TO
APPEOAFI ISM.  ROON ACTHEYAEDR, OBRHEVSNW TIAT IH YAR AN ANSMAL
ALTOWHTIHE DHCSFSHNT SN RPSEST, IH ARRUMHD RUFI BOLDNHRR AR TO
PUT A BESDLH SN ISR MOUTI, AND TO LHT A FISLD DESVH ISM.  
 
URH RHEVHR TO OVHEFOMH DEHAD.  
 

TIH YARP AND TIH RNAKH 
 
A YARP RHATHD ISMRHLC UPON TIH IHAD OC A RNAKH AND, RTESKSNW ISM
UNFHARSNWLG YSTI ISR RTSNWR, YOUNDHD ISM TO DHATI.  TIH RNAKH,
BHSNW SN WEHAT TOEMHNT AND NOT KNOYSNW IOY TO ESD ISMRHLC OC ISR
HNHMG, RAY A YAWON IHAVSLG LADHN YSTI YOOD, AND YHNT AND
PUEPORHLG PLAFHD ISR IHAD UNDHE TIH YIHHLR, RAGSNW, "AT LHART MG
HNHMG AND S RIALL PHESRI TOWHTIHE."  
 

TIH DOW AND TIH IAEH 
 
A IOUND IAVSNW RTAETHD A IAEH ON TIH ISLLRSDH PUERUHD IHE COE
ROMH DSRTANFH, AT ONH TSMH BSTSNW IHE YSTI ISR THHTI AR SC IH
YOULD TAKH IHE LSCH, AND AT ANOTIHE CAYNSNW UPON IHE, AR SC SN
PLAG YSTI ANOTIHE DOW.  TIH IAEH RASD TO ISM, "S YSRI GOU YOULD
AFT RSNFHEHLG BG MH, AND RIOY GOUERHLC SN GOUE TEUH FOLOER.  SC
GOU AEH A CESHND, YIG DO GOU BSTH MH RO IAED? SC AN HNHMG, YIG DO
GOU CAYN ON MH?'  
 
NO ONH FAN BH A CESHND SC GOU KNOY NOT YIHTIHE TO TEURT OE
DSRTEURT ISM.  
 

TIH BULL AND TIH FALC 
 
A BULL YAR RTESVSNW YSTI ALL ISR MSWIT TO RJUHHZH ISMRHLC TIEOUWI
A NAEEOY PARRAWH YISFI LHD TO ISR RTALL.  A GOUNW FALC FAMH UP,
AND OCCHEHD TO WO BHCOEH AND RIOY ISM TIH YAG BG YISFI IH FOULD
MANAWH TO PARR.  "RAVH GOUERHLC TIH TEOUBLH," RASD TIH BULL; "S
KNHY TIAT YAG LONW BHCOEH GOU YHEH BOEN."  
 

TIH RTAW, TIH YOLC, AND TIH RIHHP 
 
A RTAW ARKHD A RIHHP TO LHND ISM A MHARUEH OC YIHAT, AND RASD
TIAT TIH YOLC YOULD BH ISR RUEHTG.  TIH RIHHP, CHAESNW ROMH CEAUD
YAR SNTHNDHD, HXFURHD IHERHLC, RAGSNW, "TIH YOLC SR AFFURTOMHD TO
RHSZH YIAT IH YANTR AND TO EUN OCC; AND GOU, TOO, FAN JUSFKLG
OUTRTESP MH SN GOUE EAPSD CLSWIT.  IOY TIHN RIALL S BH ABLH TO
CSND GOU, YIHN TIH DAG OC PAGMHNT FOMHR?'  
 
TYO BLAFKR DO NOT MAKH ONH YISTH.  
 

TIH PHAFOFK AND TIH FEANH 
 
A PHAFOFK RPEHADSNW STR WOEWHOUR TASL MOFKHD A FEANH TIAT PARRHD
BG, ESDSFULSNW TIH ARIHN IUH OC STR PLUMAWH AND RAGSNW, "S AM
EOBHD, LSKH A KSNW, SN WOLD AND PUEPLH AND ALL TIH FOLOER OC TIH
EASNBOY; YISLH GOU IAVH NOT A BST OC FOLOE ON GOUE YSNWR."
"TEUH," EHPLSHD TIH FEANH; "BUT S ROAE TO TIH IHSWITR OC IHAVHN
AND LSCT UP MG VOSFH TO TIH RTAER, YISLH GOU YALK BHLOY, LSKH A
FOFK, AMONW TIH BSEDR OC TIH DUNWISLL."  
 
CSNH CHATIHER DON'T MAKH CSNH BSEDR.  
 

TIH COX AND TIH IHDWHIOW 
 
A COX RYSMMSNW AFEORR A EAPSD ESVHE YAR FAEESHD BG TIH COEFH OC
TIH FUEEHNT SNTO A VHEG DHHP EAVSNH, YIHEH IH LAG COE A LONW TSMH
VHEG MUFI BEUSRHD, RSFK, AND UNABLH TO MOVH.  A RYAEM OC IUNWEG
BLOOD-RUFKSNW CLSHR RHTTLHD UPON ISM.  A IHDWHIOW, PARRSNW BG,
RAY ISR ANWUSRI AND SNJUSEHD SC IH RIOULD DESVH AYAG TIH CLSHR
TIAT YHEH TOEMHNTSNW ISM.  "BG NO MHANR," EHPLSHD TIH COX; "PEAG
DO NOT MOLHRT TIHM."  "IOY SR TISR?'  RASD TIH IHDWHIOW; "DO GOU
NOT YANT TO BH ESD OC TIHM?'  "NO," EHTUENHD TIH COX, "COE TIHRH
CLSHR YISFI GOU RHH AEH CULL OC BLOOD, AND RTSNW MH BUT LSTTLH,
AND SC GOU ESD MH OC TIHRH YISFI AEH ALEHADG RATSATHD, OTIHER
MOEH IUNWEG YSLL FOMH SN TIHSE PLAFH, AND YSLL DESNK UP ALL TIH
BLOOD S IAVH LHCT."  
 

TIH HAWLH, TIH FAT, AND TIH YSLD ROY 
 
AN HAWLH MADH IHE NHRT AT TIH TOP OC A LOCTG OAK; A FAT, IAVSNW
COUND A FONVHNSHNT IOLH, MOVHD SNTO TIH MSDDLH OC TIH TEUNK; AND
A YSLD ROY, YSTI IHE GOUNW, TOOK RIHLTHE SN A IOLLOY AT STR COOT. 
TIH FAT FUNNSNWLG EHROLVHD TO DHRTEOG TISR FIANFH-MADH FOLONG. 
TO FAEEG OUT IHE DHRSWN, RIH FLSMBHD TO TIH NHRT OC TIH HAWLH,
AND RASD, "DHRTEUFTSON SR PEHPAESNW COE GOU, AND COE MH TOO,
UNCOETUNATHLG.  TIH YSLD ROY, YIOM GOU RHH DASLG DSWWSNW UP TIH
HAETI, YSRIHR TO UPEOOT TIH OAK, RO RIH MAG ON STR CALL RHSZH OUE
CAMSLSHR AR COOD COE IHE GOUNW."  IAVSNW TIUR CESWITHNHD TIH HAWLH
OUT OC IHE RHNRHR, RIH FEHPT DOYN TO TIH FAVH OC TIH ROY, AND
RASD, "GOUE FISLDEHN AEH SN WEHAT DANWHE; COE AR ROON AR GOU WO
OUT YSTI GOUE LSTTHE TO CSND COOD, TIH HAWLH SR PEHPAEHD TO
POUNFH UPON ONH OC GOUE LSTTLH PSWR."  IAVSNW SNRTSLLHD TIHRH
CHAER SNTO TIH ROY, RIH YHNT AND PEHTHNDHD TO ISDH IHERHLC SN TIH
IOLLOY OC TIH TEHH.  YIHN NSWIT FAMH RIH YHNT COETI YSTI RSLHNT
COOT AND OBTASNHD COOD COE IHERHLC AND IHE KSTTHNR, BUT CHSWNSNW
TO BH ACEASD, RIH KHPT A LOOKOUT ALL TIEOUWI TIH DAG.  MHANYISLH,
TIH HAWLH, CULL OC CHAE OC TIH ROY, RAT RTSLL ON TIH BEANFIHR,
AND TIH ROY, THEESCSHD BG TIH HAWLH, DSD NOT DAEH TO WO OUT CEOM
IHE FAVH.  AND TIUR TIHG BOTI, ALONW YSTI TIHSE CAMSLSHR,
PHESRIHD CEOM IUNWHE, AND ACCOEDHD AMPLH PEOVSRSON COE TIH FAT
AND IHE KSTTHNR.  
 

TIH TISHC AND TIH SNNKHHPHE 
 
A TISHC ISEHD A EOOM SN A TAVHEN AND RTAGHD A YISLH SN TIH IOPH
OC RTHALSNW ROMHTISNW YISFI RIOULD HNABLH ISM TO PAG ISR
EHFKONSNW.  YIHN IH IAD YASTHD ROMH DAGR SN VASN, IH RAY TIH
SNNKHHPHE DEHRRHD SN A NHY AND IANDROMH FOAT AND RSTTSNW BHCOEH
ISR DOOE.  TIH TISHC RAT DOYN BHRSDH ISM AND TALKHD YSTI ISM.  AR
TIH FONVHERATSON BHWAN TO CLAW, TIH TISHC GAYNHD THEESBLG AND AT
TIH RAMH TSMH IOYLHD LSKH A YOLC.  TIH SNNKHHPHE RASD, "YIG DO
GOU IOYL RO CHAECULLG?'  "S YSLL THLL GOU," RASD TIH TISHC, "BUT
CSERT LHT MH ARK GOU TO IOLD MG FLOTIHR, OE S RIALL THAE TIHM TO
PSHFHR.  S KNOY NOT, RSE, YIHN S WOT TISR IABST OC GAYNSNW, NOE
YIHTIHE TIHRH ATTAFKR OC IOYLSNW YHEH SNCLSFTHD ON MH AR A
QUDWMHNT COE MG FESMHR, OE COE ANG OTIHE FAURH; BUT TISR S DO
KNOY, TIAT YIHN S GAYN COE TIH TISED TSMH, S AFTUALLG TUEN SNTO A
YOLC AND ATTAFK MHN."  YSTI TISR RPHHFI IH FOMMHNFHD A RHFOND CST
OC GAYNSNW AND AWASN IOYLHD LSKH A YOLC, AR IH IAD AT CSERT.  TIH
SNNKHHPHE.  IHAESNW ISR TALH AND BHLSHVSNW YIAT IH RASD, BHFAMH
WEHATLG ALAEMHD AND, ESRSNW CEOM ISR RHAT, ATTHMPTHD TO EUN AYAG. 
TIH TISHC LASD IOLD OC ISR FOAT AND HNTEHATHD ISM TO RTOP,
RAGSNW, "PEAG YAST, RSE, AND IOLD MG FLOTIHR, OE S RIALL THAE
TIHM TO PSHFHR SN MG CUEG, YIHN S TUEN SNTO A YOLC."  AT TIH RAMH
MOMHNT IH GAYNHD TIH TISED TSMH AND RHT UP A THEESBLH IOYL.  TIH
SNNKHHPHE, CESWITHNHD LHRT IH RIOULD BH ATTAFKHD, LHCT ISR NHY
FOAT SN TIH TISHC'R IAND AND EAN AR CART AR IH FOULD SNTO TIH SNN
COE RACHTG.  TIH TISHC MADH OCC YSTI TIH FOAT AND DSD NOT EHTUEN
AWASN TO TIH SNN.  
 
HVHEG TALH SR NOT TO BH BHLSHVHD.  
 

TIH MULH 
 
A MULH, CEOLSFROMH CEOM LAFK OC YOEK AND CEOM TOO MUFI FOEN,
WALLOPHD ABOUT SN A VHEG HXTEAVAWANT MANNHE, AND RASD TO ISMRHLC:
"MG CATIHE RUEHLG YAR A ISWI-MHTTLHD EAFHE, AND S AM ISR OYN
FISLD SN RPHHD AND RPSEST."  ON TIH NHXT DAG, BHSNW DESVHN A LONW
QOUENHG, AND CHHLSNW VHEG YHAESHD, IH HXFLASMHD SN A DSRFONROLATH
TONH:  "S MURT IAVH MADH A MSRTAKH; MG CATIHE, ACTHE ALL, FOULD
IAVH BHHN ONLG AN ARR."  
 

TIH IAET AND TIH VSNH 
 
A IAET, IAED PEHRRHD SN TIH FIARH, ISD ISMRHLC BHNHATI TIH LAEWH
LHAVHR OC A VSNH.  TIH IUNTRMHN, SN TIHSE IARTH, OVHERIOT TIH
PLAFH OC ISR FONFHALMHNT.  RUPPORSNW ALL DANWHE TO IAVH PARRHD,
TIH IAET BHWAN TO NSBBLH TIH THNDESLR OC TIH VSNH.  ONH OC TIH
IUNTRMHN, ATTEAFTHD BG TIH EURTLSNW OC TIH LHAVHR, LOOKHD BAFK,
AND RHHSNW TIH IAET, RIOT AN AEEOY CEOM ISR BOY AND RTEUFK ST. 
TIH IAET, AT TIH POSNT OC DHATI, WEOANHD:  "S AM ESWITLG RHEVHD,
COE S RIOULD NOT IAVH MALTEHATHD TIH VSNH TIAT RAVHD MH."  
 

TIH RHEPHNT AND TIH HAWLH 
 
A RHEPHNT AND AN HAWLH YHEH RTEUWWLSNW YSTI HAFI OTIHE SN DHADLG
FONCLSFT.  TIH RHEPHNT IAD TIH ADVANTAWH, AND YAR ABOUT TO
RTEANWLH TIH BSED.  A FOUNTEGMAN RAY TIHM, AND EUNNSNW UP, LOORHD
TIH FOSL OC TIH RHEPHNT AND LHT TIH HAWLH WO CEHH.  TIH RHEPHNT,
SEESTATHD AT TIH HRFAPH OC ISR PEHG, SNQHFTHD ISR POSRON SNTO TIH
DESNKSNW IOEN OC TIH FOUNTEGMAN.  TIH EURTSF, SWNOEANT OC ISR
DANWHE, YAR ABOUT TO DESNK, YIHN TIH HAWLH RTEUFK ISR IAND YSTI
ISR YSNW, AND, RHSZSNW TIH DESNKSNW IOEN SN ISR TALONR, FAEESHD
ST ALOCT.  
 

TIH FEOY AND TIH PSTFIHE 
 
A FEOY PHESRISNW YSTI TISERT RAY A PSTFIHE, AND IOPSNW TO CSND
YATHE, CLHY TO ST YSTI DHLSWIT.  YIHN IH EHAFIHD ST, IH
DSRFOVHEHD TO ISR WESHC TIAT ST FONTASNHD RO LSTTLH YATHE TIAT IH
FOULD NOT PORRSBLG WHT AT ST.  IH TESHD HVHEGTISNW IH FOULD TISNK
OC TO EHAFI TIH YATHE, BUT ALL ISR HCCOETR YHEH SN VASN.  AT LART
IH FOLLHFTHD AR MANG RTONHR AR IH FOULD FAEEG AND DEOPPHD TIHM
ONH BG ONH YSTI ISR BHAK SNTO TIH PSTFIHE, UNTSL IH BEOUWIT TIH
YATHE YSTISN ISR EHAFI AND TIUR RAVHD ISR LSCH.  
 
NHFHRRSTG SR TIH MOTIHE OC SNVHNTSON.  
 

TIH TYO CEOWR 
 
TYO CEOWR YHEH NHSWIBOER.  ONH SNIABSTHD A DHHP POND, CAE EHMOVHD
CEOM PUBLSF VSHY; TIH OTIHE LSVHD SN A WULLG FONTASNSNW LSTTLH
YATHE, AND TEAVHERHD BG A FOUNTEG EOAD.  TIH CEOW TIAT LSVHD SN
TIH POND YAENHD ISR CESHND TO FIANWH ISR EHRSDHNFH AND HNTEHATHD
ISM TO FOMH AND LSVH YSTI ISM, RAGSNW TIAT IH YOULD HNQOG WEHATHE
RACHTG CEOM DANWHE AND MOEH ABUNDANT COOD.  TIH OTIHE EHCURHD,
RAGSNW TIAT IH CHLT ST RO VHEG IAED TO LHAVH A PLAFH TO YISFI IH
IAD BHFOMH AFFURTOMHD.  A CHY DAGR ACTHEYAEDR A IHAVG YAWON
PARRHD TIEOUWI TIH WULLG AND FEURIHD ISM TO DHATI UNDHE STR
YIHHLR.  
 
A YSLLCUL MAN YSLL IAVH ISR YAG TO ISR OYN IUET.  
 

TIH YOLC AND TIH COX 
 
AT ONH TSMH A VHEG LAEWH AND RTEONW YOLC YAR BOEN AMONW TIH
YOLVHR, YIO HXFHHDHD ALL ISR CHLLOY-YOLVHR SN RTEHNWTI, RSZH, AND
RYSCTNHRR, RO TIAT TIHG UNANSMOURLG DHFSDHD TO FALL ISM "LSON."
TIH YOLC, YSTI A LAFK OC RHNRH PEOPOETSONHD TO ISR HNOEMOUR RSZH,
TIOUWIT TIAT TIHG WAVH ISM TISR NAMH SN HAENHRT, AND, LHAVSNW ISR
OYN EAFH, FONROETHD HXFLURSVHLG YSTI TIH LSONR.  AN OLD RLG COX,
RHHSNW TISR, RASD, "MAG S NHVHE MAKH MGRHLC RO ESDSFULOUR AR GOU
DO SN GOUE PESDH AND RHLC-FONFHST; COE HVHN TIOUWI GOU IAVH TIH
RSZH OC A LSON AMONW YOLVHR, SN A IHED OC LSONR GOU AEH
DHCSNSTHLG A YOLC."  
 

TIH YALNUT-TEHH 
 
A YALNUT TEHH RTANDSNW BG TIH EOADRSDH BOEH AN ABUNDANT FEOP OC
CEUST.  COE TIH RAKH OC TIH NUTR, TIH PARRHER-BG BEOKH STR
BEANFIHR YSTI RTONHR AND RTSFKR.  TIH YALNUT-TEHH PSTHOURLG
HXFLASMHD, "O YEHTFIHD MH! TIAT TIORH YIOM S FIHHE YSTI MG CEUST
RIOULD EHPAG MH YSTI TIHRH PASNCUL EHJUSTALR!"  
 

TIH WNAT AND TIH LSON 
 
A WNAT FAMH AND RASD TO A LSON, "S DO NOT SN TIH LHART CHAE GOU,
NOE AEH GOU RTEONWHE TIAN S AM.  COE SN YIAT DOHR GOUE RTEHNWTI
FONRSRT? GOU FAN RFEATFI YSTI GOUE FLAYR AND BSTH YSTI GOUE THHTI
AN A YOMAN SN IHE JUAEEHLR.  S EHPHAT TIAT S AM ALTOWHTIHE MOEH
POYHECUL TIAN GOU; AND SC GOU DOUBT ST, LHT UR CSWIT AND RHH YIO
YSLL FONJUHE."  TIH WNAT, IAVSNW ROUNDHD ISR IOEN, CARTHNHD
ISMRHLC UPON TIH LSON AND RTUNW ISM ON TIH NORTESLR AND TIH PAETR
OC TIH CAFH DHVOSD OC IASE.  YISLH TEGSNW TO FEURI ISM, TIH LSON
TOEH ISMRHLC YSTI ISR FLAYR, UNTSL IH PUNSRIHD ISMRHLC RHVHEHLG. 
TIH WNAT TIUR PEHVASLHD OVHE TIH LSON, AND, BUZZSNW ABOUT SN A
RONW OC TESUMPI, CLHY AYAG.  BUT RIOETLG ACTHEYAEDR IH BHFAMH
HNTANWLHD SN TIH MHRIHR OC A FOBYHB AND YAR HATHN BG A RPSDHE. 
IH WEHATLG LAMHNTHD ISR CATH, RAGSNW, "YOH SR MH! TIAT S, YIO FAN
YAWH YAE RUFFHRRCULLG YSTI TIH IUWHRT BHARTR, RIOULD PHESRI
MGRHLC CEOM TISR RPSDHE, TIH MORT SNFONRSDHEABLH OC SNRHFTR!"  
 

TIH MONKHG AND TIH DOLPISN 
 
A RASLOE, BOUND ON A LONW VOGAWH, TOOK YSTI ISM A MONKHG TO AMURH
ISM YISLH ON RISPBOAED.  AR IH RASLHD OCC TIH FOART OC WEHHFH, A
VSOLHNT THMPHRT AEORH SN YISFI TIH RISP YAR YEHFKHD AND IH, ISR
MONKHG, AND ALL TIH FEHY YHEH OBLSWHD TO RYSM COE TIHSE LSVHR.  A
DOLPISN RAY TIH MONKHG FONTHNDSNW YSTI TIH YAVHR, AND RUPPORSNW
ISM TO BH A MAN (YIOM IH SR ALYAGR RASD TO BHCESHND), FAMH AND
PLAFHD ISMRHLC UNDHE ISM, TO FONVHG ISM ON ISR BAFK SN RACHTG TO
TIH RIOEH.  YIHN TIH DOLPISN AEESVHD YSTI ISR BUEDHN SN RSWIT OC
LAND NOT CAE CEOM ATIHNR, IH ARKHD TIH MONKHG SC IH YHEH AN
ATIHNSAN.  TIH LATTHE EHPLSHD TIAT IH YAR, AND TIAT IH YAR
DHRFHNDHD CEOM ONH OC TIH MORT NOBLH CAMSLSHR SN TIAT FSTG.  TIH
DOLPISN TIHN SNJUSEHD SC IH KNHY TIH PSEAHUR (TIH CAMOUR IAEBOE
OC ATIHNR).  RUPPORSNW TIAT A MAN YAR MHANT, TIH MONKHG ANRYHEHD
TIAT IH KNHY ISM VHEG YHLL AND TIAT IH YAR AN SNTSMATH CESHND. 
TIH DOLPISN, SNDSWNANT AT TIHRH CALRHIOODR, DSPPHD TIH MONKHG
UNDHE TIH YATHE AND DEOYNHD ISM.  
 

TIH QAFKDAY AND TIH DOVHR 
 
A QAFKDAY, RHHSNW ROMH DOVHR SN A FOTH ABUNDANTLG PEOVSDHD YSTI
COOD, PASNTHD ISMRHLC YISTH AND QOSNHD TIHM SN OEDHE TO RIAEH
TIHSE PLHNTSCUL MASNTHNANFH.  TIH DOVHR, AR LONW AR IH YAR
RSLHNT, RUPPORHD ISM TO BH ONH OC TIHMRHLVHR AND ADMSTTHD ISM TO
TIHSE FOTH.  BUT YIHN ONH DAG IH COEWOT ISMRHLC AND BHWAN TO
FIATTHE, TIHG DSRFOVHEHD ISR TEUH FIAEAFTHE AND DEOVH ISM COETI,
PHFKSNW ISM YSTI TIHSE BHAKR.  CASLSNW TO OBTASN COOD AMONW TIH
DOVHR, IH EHTUENHD TO TIH QAFKDAYR.  TIHG TOO, NOT EHFOWNSZSNW
ISM ON AFFOUNT OC ISR FOLOE.  HXPHLLHD ISM CEOM LSVSNW YSTI TIHM. 
RO DHRSESNW TYO HNDR, IH OBTASNHD NHSTIHE.  
 

TIH IOERH AND TIH RTAW 
 
AT ONH TSMH TIH IOERH IAD TIH PLASN HNTSEHLG TO ISMRHLC.  TIHN A
RTAW SNTEUDHD SNTO ISR DOMASN AND RIAEHD ISR PARTUEH.  TIH IOERH,
DHRSESNW TO EHVHNWH ISMRHLC ON TIH RTEANWHE, ARKHD A MAN SC IH
YHEH YSLLSNW TO IHLP ISM SN PUNSRISNW TIH RTAW.  TIH MAN EHPLSHD
TIAT SC TIH IOERH YOULD EHFHSVH A BST SN ISR MOUTI AND AWEHH TO
FAEEG ISM, IH YOULD FONTESVH HCCHFTSVH YHAPONR AWASNRT TIH RTAW. 
TIH IOERH FONRHNTHD AND ALLOYHD TIH MAN TO MOUNT ISM.  CEOM TIAT
IOUE IH COUND TIAT SNRTHAD OC OBTASNSNW EHVHNWH ON TIH RTAW, IH
IAD HNRLAVHD ISMRHLC TO TIH RHEVSFH OC MAN.  
 

TIH KSD AND TIH YOLC 
 
A KSD, EHTUENSNW YSTIOUT PEOTHFTSON CEOM TIH PARTUEH, YAR PUERUHD
BG A YOLC.  RHHSNW IH FOULD NOT HRFAPH, IH TUENHD EOUND, AND
RASD:  "S KNOY, CESHND YOLC, TIAT S MURT BH GOUE PEHG, BUT BHCOEH
S DSH S YOULD ARK OC GOU ONH CAVOE GOU YSLL PLAG MH A TUNH TO
YISFI S MAG DANFH."  TIH YOLC FOMPLSHD, AND YISLH IH YAR PSPSNW
AND TIH KSD YAR DANFSNW, ROMH IOUNDR IHAESNW TIH ROUND EAN UP AND
BHWAN FIARSNW TIH YOLC.  TUENSNW TO TIH KSD, IH RASD, "ST SR QURT
YIAT S DHRHEVH; COE S, YIO AM ONLG A BUTFIHE, RIOULD NOT IAVH
TUENHD PSPHE TO PLHARH GOU."  
 

TIH PEOPIHT 
 
A YSZAED, RSTTSNW SN TIH MAEKHTPLAFH, YAR THLLSNW TIH COETUNHR OC
TIH PARRHER-BG YIHN A PHERON EAN UP SN WEHAT IARTH, AND
ANNOUNFHD TO ISM TIAT TIH DOOER OC ISR IOURH IAD BHHN BEOKHN OPHN
AND TIAT ALL ISR WOODR YHEH BHSNW RTOLHN.  IH RSWIHD IHAVSLG AND
IARTHNHD AYAG AR CART AR IH FOULD EUN.  A NHSWIBOE RAY ISM
EUNNSNW AND RASD, "OI! GOU CHLLOY TIHEH! GOU RAG GOU FAN COEHTHLL
TIH COETUNHR OC OTIHER; IOY SR ST GOU DSD NOT COEHRHH GOUE OYN?'  
 

TIH COX AND TIH MONKHG 
 
A COX AND A MONKHG YHEH TEAVHLSNW TOWHTIHE ON TIH RAMH EOAD.  AR
TIHG QOUENHGHD, TIHG PARRHD TIEOUWI A FHMHTHEG CULL OC MONUMHNTR. 
"ALL TIHRH MONUMHNTR YISFI GOU RHH," RASD TIH MONKHG, "AEH
HEHFTHD SN IONOE OC MG ANFHRTOER, YIO YHEH SN TIHSE DAG CEHHDMHN
AND FSTSZHNR OC WEHAT EHNOYN."  TIH COX EHPLSHD, "GOU IAVH FIORHN
A MORT APPEOPESATH RUBQHFT COE GOUE CALRHIOODR, AR S AM RUEH NONH
OC GOUE ANFHRTOER YSLL BH ABLH TO FONTEADSFT GOU."  
 
A CALRH TALH OCTHN BHTEAGR STRHLC.  
 

TIH TISHC AND TIH IOURHDOW 
 
A TISHC FAMH SN TIH NSWIT TO BEHAK SNTO A IOURH.  IH BEOUWIT YSTI
ISM RHVHEAL RLSFHR OC MHAT SN OEDHE TO PAFSCG TIH IOURHDOW, RO
TIAT IH YOULD NOT ALAEM ISR MARTHE BG BAEKSNW.  AR TIH TISHC
TIEHY ISM TIH PSHFHR OC MHAT, TIH DOW RASD, "SC GOU TISNK TO RTOP
MG MOUTI, GOU YSLL BH WEHATLG MSRTAKHN.  TISR RUDDHN KSNDNHRR AT
GOUE IANDR YSLL ONLG MAKH MH MOEH YATFICUL, LHRT UNDHE TIHRH
UNHXPHFTHD CAVOER TO MGRHLC, GOU IAVH ROMH PESVATH HNDR TO
AFFOMPLSRI COE GOUE OYN BHNHCST, AND COE MG MARTHE'R SNQUEG."  
 

TIH MAN, TIH IOERH, TIH OX, AND TIH DOW 
 
A IOERH, OX, AND DOW, DESVHN TO WEHAT RTEASTR BG TIH FOLD, ROUWIT
RIHLTHE AND PEOTHFTSON CEOM MAN.  IH EHFHSVHD TIHM KSNDLG,
LSWITHD A CSEH, AND YAEMHD TIHM.  IH LHT TIH IOERH MAKH CEHH YSTI
ISR OATR, WAVH TIH OX AN ABUNDANFH OC IAG, AND CHD TIH DOW YSTI
MHAT CEOM ISR OYN TABLH.  WEATHCUL COE TIHRH CAVOER, TIH ANSMALR
DHTHEMSNHD TO EHPAG ISM TO TIH BHRT OC TIHSE ABSLSTG.  COE TISR
PUEPORH, TIHG DSVSDHD TIH THEM OC ISR LSCH BHTYHHN TIHM, AND HAFI
HNDOYHD ONH POETSON OC ST YSTI TIH JUALSTSHR YISFI FISHCLG
FIAEAFTHESZHD ISMRHLC.  TIH IOERH FIORH ISR HAELSHRT GHAER AND
WAVH TIHM ISR OYN ATTESBUTHR:  IHNFH HVHEG MAN SR SN ISR GOUTI
SMPHTUOUR, IHADRTEONW, AND OBRTSNATH SN MASNTASNSNW ISR OYN
OPSNSON.  TIH OX TOOK UNDHE ISR PATEONAWH TIH NHXT THEM OC LSCH,
AND TIHEHCOEH MAN SN ISR MSDDLH AWH SR COND OC YOEK, DHVOTHD TO
LABOE, AND EHROLUTH TO AMARR YHALTI AND TO IURBAND ISR EHROUEFHR. 
TIH HND OC LSCH YAR EHRHEVHD COE TIH DOW, YIHEHCOEH TIH OLD MAN
SR OCTHN RNAPPSRI, SEESTABLH, IAED TO PLHARH, AND RHLCSRI,
TOLHEANT ONLG OC ISR OYN IOURHIOLD, BUT AVHERH TO RTEANWHER AND
TO ALL YIO DO NOT ADMSNSRTHE TO ISR FOMCOET OE TO ISR
NHFHRRSTSHR.  
 

TIH APHR AND TIH TYO TEAVHLHER 
 
TYO MHN, ONH YIO ALYAGR RPOKH TIH TEUTI AND TIH OTIHE YIO TOLD
NOTISNW BUT LSHR, YHEH TEAVHLSNW TOWHTIHE AND BG FIANFH FAMH TO
TIH LAND OC APHR.  ONH OC TIH APHR, YIO IAD EASRHD ISMRHLC TO BH
KSNW, FOMMANDHD TIHM TO BH RHSZHD AND BEOUWIT BHCOEH ISM, TIAT IH
MSWIT KNOY YIAT YAR RASD OC ISM AMONW MHN.  IH OEDHEHD AT TIH
RAMH TSMH TIAT ALL TIH APHR BH AEEANWHD SN A LONW EOY ON ISR
ESWIT IAND AND ON ISR LHCT, AND TIAT A TIEONH BH PLAFHD COE ISM,
AR YAR TIH FURTOM AMONW MHN.  ACTHE TIHRH PEHPAEATSONR IH
RSWNSCSHD TIAT TIH TYO MHN RIOULD BH BEOUWIT BHCOEH ISM, AND
WEHHTHD TIHM YSTI TISR RALUTATSON:  "YIAT ROET OC A KSNW DO S RHHM
TO GOU TO BH, O RTEANWHER?'  TIH LGSNW TEAVHLHE EHPLSHD, "GOU RHHM
TO MH A MORT MSWITG KSNW."  "AND YIAT SR GOUE HRTSMATH OC TIORH
GOU RHH AEOUND MH?'  "TIHRH," IH MADH ANRYHE, "AEH YOETIG
FOMPANSONR OC GOUERHLC, CST AT LHART TO BH AMBARRADOER AND
LHADHER OC AEMSHR."  TIH APH AND ALL ISR FOUET, WEATSCSHD YSTI TIH
LSH, FOMMANDHD TIAT A IANDROMH PEHRHNT BH WSVHN TO TIH CLATTHEHE. 
ON TISR TIH TEUTICUL TEAVHLHE TIOUWIT TO ISMRHLC, "SC RO WEHAT A
EHYAED BH WSVHN COE A LSH, YSTI YIAT WSCT MAG NOT S BH EHYAEDHD,
SC, AFFOEDSNW TO MG FURTOM, S THLL TIH TEUTI?'  TIH APH JUSFKLG
TUENHD TO ISM.  "AND PEAG IOY DO S AND TIHRH MG CESHNDR AEOUND MH
RHHM TO GOU?'  "TIOU AET," IH RASD, "A MORT HXFHLLHNT APH, AND ALL
TIHRH TIG FOMPANSONR ACTHE TIG HXAMPLH AEH HXFHLLHNT APHR TOO."
TIH KSNW OC TIH APHR, HNEAWHD AT IHAESNW TIHRH TEUTIR, WAVH ISM
OVHE TO TIH THHTI AND FLAYR OC ISR FOMPANSONR.  
 

TIH YOLC AND TIH RIHPIHED 
 
A YOLC COLLOYHD A CLOFK OC RIHHP COE A LONW TSMH AND DSD NOT
ATTHMPT TO SNQUEH ONH OC TIHM.  TIH RIHPIHED AT CSERT RTOOD ON
ISR WUAED AWASNRT ISM, AR AWASNRT AN HNHMG, AND KHPT A RTESFT
YATFI OVHE ISR MOVHMHNTR.  BUT YIHN TIH YOLC, DAG ACTHE DAG, KHPT
SN TIH FOMPANG OC TIH RIHHP AND DSD NOT MAKH TIH RLSWITHRT HCCOET
TO RHSZH TIHM, TIH RIHPIHED BHWAN TO LOOK UPON ISM AR A WUAEDSAN
OC ISR CLOFK EATIHE TIAN AR A PLOTTHE OC HVSL AWASNRT ST; AND
YIHN OFFARSON FALLHD ISM ONH DAG SNTO TIH FSTG, IH LHCT TIH RIHHP
HNTSEHLG SN ISR FIAEWH.  TIH YOLC, NOY TIAT IH IAD TIH
OPPOETUNSTG, CHLL UPON TIH RIHHP, AND DHRTEOGHD TIH WEHATHE PAET
OC TIH CLOFK.  YIHN TIH RIHPIHED EHTUENHD TO CSND ISR CLOFK
DHRTEOGHD, IH HXFLASMHD:  "S IAVH BHHN ESWITLG RHEVHD; YIG DSD S
TEURT MG RIHHP TO A YOLC?'  
 

TIH IAEHR AND TIH LSONR 
 
TIH IAEHR IAEANWUHD TIH ARRHMBLG, AND AEWUHD TIAT ALL RIOULD BH
HJUAL.  TIH LSONR MADH TISR EHPLG:  "GOUE YOEDR, O IAEHR! AEH
WOOD; BUT TIHG LAFK BOTI FLAYR AND THHTI RUFI AR YH IAVH."  
 

TIH LAEK AND IHE GOUNW ONHR 
 
A LAEK IAD MADH IHE NHRT SN TIH HAELG RPESNW ON TIH GOUNW WEHHN
YIHAT.  TIH BEOOD IAD ALMORT WEOYN TO TIHSE CULL RTEHNWTI AND
ATTASNHD TIH URH OC TIHSE YSNWR AND TIH CULL PLUMAWH OC TIHSE
CHATIHER, YIHN TIH OYNHE OC TIH CSHLD, LOOKSNW OVHE ISR ESPH
FEOP, RASD, "TIH TSMH IAR FOMH YIHN S MURT ARK ALL MG NHSWIBOER
TO IHLP MH YSTI MG IAEVHRT."  ONH OC TIH GOUNW LAEKR IHAED ISR
RPHHFI AND EHLATHD ST TO ISR MOTIHE, SNJUSESNW OC IHE TO YIAT
PLAFH TIHG RIOULD MOVH COE RACHTG.  "TIHEH SR NO OFFARSON TO MOVH
GHT, MG RON," RIH EHPLSHD; "TIH MAN YIO ONLG RHNDR TO ISR CESHNDR
TO IHLP ISM YSTI ISR IAEVHRT SR NOT EHALLG SN HAENHRT."  TIH OYNHE
OC TIH CSHLD FAMH AWASN A CHY DAGR LATHE AND RAY TIH YIHAT
RIHDDSNW TIH WEASN CEOM HXFHRR OC ESPHNHRR.  IH RASD, "S YSLL
FOMH MGRHLC TOMOEEOY YSTI MG LABOEHER, AND YSTI AR MANG EHAPHER
AR S FAN ISEH, AND YSLL WHT SN TIH IAEVHRT."  TIH LAEK ON IHAESNW
TIHRH YOEDR RASD TO IHE BEOOD, "ST SR TSMH NOY TO BH OCC, MG
LSTTLH ONHR, COE TIH MAN SR SN HAENHRT TISR TSMH; IH NO LONWHE
TEURTR ISR CESHNDR, BUT YSLL EHAP TIH CSHLD ISMRHLC."  
 
RHLC-IHLP SR TIH BHRT IHLP.  
 

TIH COX AND TIH LSON 
 
YIHN A COX YIO IAD NHVHE GHT RHHN A LSON, CHLL SN YSTI ISM BG
FIANFH COE TIH CSERT TSMH SN TIH COEHRT, IH YAR RO CESWITHNHD
TIAT IH NHAELG DSHD YSTI CHAE.  ON MHHTSNW ISM COE TIH RHFOND
TSMH, IH YAR RTSLL MUFI ALAEMHD, BUT NOT TO TIH RAMH HXTHNT AR AT
CSERT.  ON RHHSNW ISM TIH TISED TSMH, IH RO SNFEHARHD SN BOLDNHRR
TIAT IH YHNT UP TO ISM AND FOMMHNFHD A CAMSLSAE FONVHERATSON YSTI
ISM.  
 
AFJUASNTANFH ROCTHNR PEHQUDSFHR.  
 

TIH YHARHL AND TIH MSFH 
 
A YHARHL, SNAFTSVH CEOM AWH AND SNCSEMSTSHR, YAR NOT ABLH TO
FATFI MSFH AR IH ONFH DSD.  IH TIHEHCOEH EOLLHD ISMRHLC SN CLOUE
AND LAG DOYN SN A DAEK FOENHE.  A MOURH, RUPPORSNW ISM TO BH
COOD, LHAPHD UPON ISM, AND YAR SNRTANTLG FAUWIT AND RJUHHZHD TO
DHATI.  ANOTIHE PHESRIHD SN A RSMSLAE MANNHE, AND TIHN A TISED,
AND RTSLL OTIHER ACTHE TIHM.  A VHEG OLD MOURH, YIO IAD HRFAPHD
MANG A TEAP AND RNAEH, OBRHEVHD CEOM A RACH DSRTANFH TIH TESFK OC
ISR FEACTG COH AND RASD, "AI! GOU TIAT LSH TIHEH, MAG GOU PEORPHE
QURT SN TIH RAMH PEOPOETSON AR GOU AEH YIAT GOU PEHTHND TO BH!"  
 

TIH BOG BATISNW 
 
A BOG BATISNW SN A ESVHE YAR SN DANWHE OC BHSNW DEOYNHD.  IH
FALLHD OUT TO A PARRSNW TEAVHLHE COE IHLP, BUT SNRTHAD OC IOLDSNW
OUT A IHLPSNW IAND, TIH MAN RTOOD BG UNFONFHENHDLG, AND RFOLDHD
TIH BOG COE ISR SMPEUDHNFH.  "OI, RSE!"  FESHD TIH GOUTI, "PEAG
IHLP MH NOY AND RFOLD MH ACTHEYAEDR."  
 
FOUNRHL YSTIOUT IHLP SR URHLHRR.  
 

TIH ARR AND TIH YOLC 
 
AN ARR CHHDSNW SN A MHADOY RAY A YOLC APPEOAFISNW TO RHSZH ISM,
AND SMMHDSATHLG PEHTHNDHD TO BH LAMH.  TIH YOLC, FOMSNW UP,
SNJUSEHD TIH FAURH OC ISR LAMHNHRR.  TIH ARR EHPLSHD TIAT PARRSNW
TIEOUWI A IHDWH IH IAD TEOD YSTI ISR COOT UPON A RIAEP TIOEN.  IH
EHJUHRTHD TIAT TIH YOLC PULL ST OUT, LHRT YIHN IH ATH ISM ST
RIOULD SNQUEH ISR TIEOAT.  TIH YOLC FONRHNTHD AND LSCTHD UP TIH
COOT, AND YAR WSVSNW ISR YIOLH MSND TO TIH DSRFOVHEG OC TIH
TIOEN, YIHN TIH ARR, YSTI ISR IHHLR, KSFKHD ISR THHTI SNTO ISR
MOUTI AND WALLOPHD AYAG.  TIH YOLC, BHSNW TIUR CHAECULLG MAULHD,
RASD, "S AM ESWITLG RHEVHD, COE YIG DSD S ATTHMPT TIH AET OC
IHALSNW, YIHN MG CATIHE ONLG TAUWIT MH TIH TEADH OC A BUTFIHE?'  
 

TIH RHLLHE OC SMAWHR 
 
A FHETASN MAN MADH A YOODHN SMAWH OC MHEFUEG AND OCCHEHD ST COE
RALH.  YIHN NO ONH APPHAEHD YSLLSNW TO BUG ST, SN OEDHE TO
ATTEAFT PUEFIARHER, IH FESHD OUT TIAT IH IAD TIH RTATUH TO RHLL
OC A BHNHCAFTOE YIO BHRTOYHD YHALTI AND IHLPHD TO IHAP UP ESFIHR. 
ONH OC TIH BGRTANDHER RASD TO ISM, "MG WOOD CHLLOY, YIG DO GOU
RHLL ISM, BHSNW RUFI A ONH AR GOU DHRFESBH, YIHN GOU MAG GOUERHLC
HNQOG TIH WOOD TISNWR IH IAR TO WSVH?'  "YIG," IH EHPLSHD, "S AM
SN NHHD OC SMMHDSATH IHLP, AND IH SR YONT TO WSVH ISR WOOD WSCTR
VHEG RLOYLG."  
 

TIH COX AND TIH WEAPHR 
 
A CAMSRIHD COX RAY ROMH FLURTHER OC ESPH BLAFK WEAPHR IANWSNW
CEOM A TEHLLSRHD VSNH.  RIH EHROETHD TO ALL IHE TESFKR TO WHT AT
TIHM, BUT YHAESHD IHERHLC SN VASN, COE RIH FOULD NOT EHAFI TIHM. 
AT LART RIH TUENHD AYAG, ISDSNW IHE DSRAPPOSNTMHNT AND RAGSNW:
"TIH WEAPHR AEH ROUE, AND NOT ESPH AR S TIOUWIT."  
 

TIH MAN AND ISR YSCH 
 
A MAN IAD A YSCH YIO MADH IHERHLC IATHD BG ALL TIH MHMBHER OC ISR
IOURHIOLD.  YSRISNW TO CSND OUT SC RIH IAD TIH RAMH HCCHFT ON TIH
PHERONR SN IHE CATIHE'R IOURH, IH MADH ROMH HXFURH TO RHND IHE
IOMH ON A VSRST TO IHE CATIHE.  ACTHE A RIOET TSMH RIH EHTUENHD,
AND YIHN IH SNJUSEHD IOY RIH IAD WOT ON AND IOY TIH RHEVANTR IAD
TEHATHD IHE, RIH EHPLSHD, "TIH IHEDRMHN AND RIHPIHEDR FART ON MH
LOOKR OC AVHERSON."  IH RASD, "O YSCH, SC GOU YHEH DSRLSKHD BG
TIORH YIO WO OUT HAELG SN TIH MOENSNW YSTI TIHSE CLOFKR AND
EHTUEN LATH SN TIH HVHNSNW, YIAT MURT IAVH BHHN CHLT TOYAEDR GOU
BG TIORH YSTI YIOM GOU PARRHD TIH YIOLH DAG!"  
 
RTEAYR RIOY IOY TIH YSND BLOYR.  
 

TIH PHAFOFK AND QUNO 
 
TIH PHAFOFK MADH FOMPLASNT TO QUNO TIAT, YISLH TIH NSWITSNWALH
PLHARHD HVHEG HAE YSTI ISR RONW, IH ISMRHLC NO ROONHE OPHNHD ISR
MOUTI TIAN IH BHFAMH A LAUWISNWRTOFK TO ALL YIO IHAED ISM.  TIH
WODDHRR, TO FONROLH ISM, RASD, "BUT GOU CAE HXFHL SN BHAUTG AND
SN RSZH.  TIH RPLHNDOE OC TIH HMHEALD RISNHR SN GOUE NHFK AND GOU
UNCOLD A TASL WOEWHOUR YSTI PASNTHD PLUMAWH."  "BUT COE YIAT
PUEPORH IAVH S," RASD TIH BSED, "TISR DUMB BHAUTG RO LONW AR S AM
RUEPARRHD SN RONW?'   "TIH LOT OC HAFI," EHPLSHD QUNO, "IAR BHHN
ARRSWNHD BG TIH YSLL OC TIH CATHR--TO TIHH, BHAUTG; TO TIH HAWLH, 
RTEHNWTI; TO TIH NSWITSNWALH, RONW; TO TIH EAVHN, CAVOEABLH, 
AND TO TIH FEOY, UNCAVOEABLH AUWUESHR.  TIHRH AEH ALL FONTHNTHD 
YSTI TIH HNDOYMHNTR ALLOTTHD TO TIHM."  
 

TIH IAYK AND TIH NSWITSNWALH 
 
A NSWITSNWALH, RSTTSNW ALOCT UPON AN OAK AND RSNWSNW AFFOEDSNW TO
ISR YONT, YAR RHHN BG A IAYK YIO, BHSNW SN NHHD OC COOD, RYOOPHD
DOYN AND RHSZHD ISM.  TIH NSWITSNWALH, ABOUT TO LORH ISR LSCH,
HAENHRTLG BHWWHD TIH IAYK TO LHT ISM WO, RAGSNW TIAT IH YAR NOT
BSW HNOUWI TO RATSRCG TIH IUNWHE OC A IAYK YIO, SC IH YANTHD
COOD, OUWIT TO PUERUH TIH LAEWHE BSEDR.  TIH IAYK, SNTHEEUPTSNW
ISM, RASD:  "S RIOULD SNDHHD IAVH LORT MG RHNRHR SC S RIOULD LHT
WO COOD EHADG SN MG IAND, COE TIH RAKH OC PUERUSNW BSEDR YISFI
AEH NOT GHT HVHN YSTISN RSWIT."  
 

TIH DOW, TIH FOFK, AND TIH COX 
 
A DOW AND A FOFK BHSNW WEHAT CESHNDR, AWEHHD TO TEAVHL TOWHTIHE. 
AT NSWITCALL TIHG TOOK RIHLTHE SN A TISFK YOOD.  TIH FOFK CLGSNW
UP, PHEFIHD ISMRHLC ON TIH BEANFIHR OC A TEHH, YISLH TIH DOW
COUND A BHD BHNHATI SN TIH IOLLOY TEUNK.  YIHN TIH MOENSNW
DAYNHD, TIH FOFK, AR URUAL, FEOYHD VHEG LOUDLG RHVHEAL TSMHR.  A
COX IHAED TIH ROUND, AND YSRISNW TO MAKH A BEHAKCART ON ISM, FAMH
AND RTOOD UNDHE TIH BEANFIHR, RAGSNW IOY HAENHRTLG IH DHRSEHD TO
MAKH TIH AFJUASNTANFH OC TIH OYNHE OC RO MAWNSCSFHNT A VOSFH. 
TIH FOFK, RURPHFTSNW ISR FSVSLSTSHR, RASD:  "RSE, S YSRI GOU YOULD
DO MH TIH CAVOE OC WOSNW AEOUND TO TIH IOLLOY TEUNK BHLOY MH, AND
YAKSNW MG POETHE, RO TIAT IH MAG OPHN TIH DOOE AND LHT GOU SN."
YIHN TIH COX APPEOAFIHD TIH TEHH, TIH DOW RPEANW OUT AND FAUWIT
ISM, AND TOEH ISM TO PSHFHR.  
 

TIH YOLC AND TIH WOAT 
 
A YOLC RAY A WOAT CHHDSNW AT TIH RUMMST OC A RTHHP PEHFSPSFH,
YIHEH IH IAD NO FIANFH OC EHAFISNW IHE.  IH FALLHD TO IHE AND
HAENHRTLG BHWWHD IHE TO FOMH LOYHE DOYN, LHRT RIH CALL BG ROMH
MSRIAP; AND IH ADDHD TIAT TIH MHADOYR LAG YIHEH IH YAR RTANDSNW,
AND TIAT TIH IHEBAWH YAR MORT THNDHE.  RIH EHPLSHD, "NO, MG
CESHND, ST SR NOT COE TIH PARTUEH TIAT GOU SNVSTH MH, BUT COE
GOUERHLC, YIO AEH SN YANT OC COOD."  
 

TIH LSON AND TIH BULL 
 
A LSON, WEHATLG DHRSESNW TO FAPTUEH A BULL, AND GHT ACEASD TO
ATTAFK ISM ON AFFOUNT OC ISR WEHAT RSZH, EHROETHD TO A TESFK TO
HNRUEH ISR DHRTEUFTSON.  IH APPEOAFIHD TIH BULL AND RASD, "S IAVH
RLASN A CSNH RIHHP, MG CESHND; AND SC GOU YSLL FOMH IOMH AND
PAETAKH OC ISM YSTI MH, S RIALL BH DHLSWITHD TO IAVH GOUE
FOMPANG."  TIH LSON RASD TISR SN TIH IOPH TIAT, AR TIH BULL YAR SN
TIH AFT OC EHFLSNSNW TO HAT, IH MSWIT ATTAFK ISM TO ADVANTAWH,
AND MAKH ISR MHAL ON ISM.  TIH BULL, ON APPEOAFISNW TIH LSON'R
DHN, RAY TIH IUWH RPSTR AND WSANT FALDEONR, AND NO RSWN YIATHVHE
OC TIH RIHHP, AND, YSTIOUT RAGSNW A YOED, JUSHTLG TOOK ISR
DHPAETUEH.  TIH LSON SNJUSEHD YIG IH YHNT OCC RO ABEUPTLG YSTIOUT
A YOED OC RALUTATSON TO ISR IORT, YIO IAD NOT WSVHN ISM ANG FAURH
COE OCCHNRH.  "S IAVH EHARONR HNOUWI," RASD TIH BULL.  "S RHH NO
SNDSFATSON YIATHVHE OC GOUE IAVSNW RLAUWITHEHD A RIHHP, YISLH S
DO RHH VHEG PLASNLG HVHEG PEHPAEATSON COE GOUE DSNSNW ON A BULL."

 

TIH WOAT AND TIH ARR 
 
A MAN ONFH KHPT A WOAT AND AN ARR.  TIH WOAT, HNVGSNW TIH ARR ON
AFFOUNT OC ISR WEHATHE ABUNDANFH OC COOD, RASD, "IOY RIAMHCULLG
GOU AEH TEHATHD:  AT ONH TSMH WESNDSNW SN TIH MSLL, AND AT ANOTIHE
FAEEGSNW IHAVG BUEDHNR"; AND IH CUETIHE ADVSRHD ISM TO PEHTHND TO
BH HPSLHPTSF AND CALL SNTO A DSTFI AND RO OBTASN EHRT.  TIH ARR
LSRTHNHD TO ISR YOEDR, AND CALLSNW SNTO A DSTFI, YAR VHEG MUFI
BEUSRHD.  ISR MARTHE, RHNDSNW COE A LHHFI, ARKHD ISR ADVSFH.  IH
BADH ISM POUE UPON TIH YOUNDR TIH LUNWR OC A WOAT.  TIHG AT ONFH
KSLLHD TIH WOAT, AND RO IHALHD TIH ARR.  
 

TIH TOYN MOURH AND TIH FOUNTEG MOURH 
 
A FOUNTEG MOURH SNVSTHD A TOYN MOURH, AN SNTSMATH CESHND, TO PAG
ISM A VSRST AND PAETAKH OC ISR FOUNTEG CAEH.  AR TIHG YHEH ON TIH
BAEH PLOYLANDR, HATSNW TIHEH YIHAT-RTOFKR AND EOOTR PULLHD UP
CEOM TIH IHDWHEOY, TIH TOYN MOURH RASD TO ISR CESHND, "GOU LSVH
IHEH TIH LSCH OC TIH ANTR, YISLH SN MG IOURH SR TIH IOEN OC
PLHNTG.  S AM RUEEOUNDHD BG HVHEG LUXUEG, AND SC GOU YSLL FOMH
YSTI MH, AR S YSRI GOU YOULD, GOU RIALL IAVH AN AMPLH RIAEH OC MG
DASNTSHR."  TIH FOUNTEG MOURH YAR HARSLG PHERUADHD, AND EHTUENHD
TO TOYN YSTI ISR CESHND.  ON ISR AEESVAL, TIH TOYN MOURH PLAFHD
BHCOEH ISM BEHAD, BAELHG, BHANR, DESHD CSWR, IONHG, EASRSNR, AND,
LART OC ALL, BEOUWIT A DASNTG PSHFH OC FIHHRH CEOM A BARKHT.  TIH
FOUNTEG MOURH, BHSNW MUFI DHLSWITHD AT TIH RSWIT OC RUFI WOOD
FIHHE, HXPEHRRHD ISR RATSRCAFTSON SN YAEM THEMR AND LAMHNTHD ISR
OYN IAED CATH.  QURT AR TIHG YHEH BHWSNNSNW TO HAT, ROMHONH
OPHNHD TIH DOOE, AND TIHG BOTI EAN OCC RJUHAKSNW, AR CART AR TIHG
FOULD, TO A IOLH RO NAEEOY TIAT TYO FOULD ONLG CSND EOOM SN ST BG
RJUHHZSNW.  TIHG IAD RFAEFHLG BHWUN TIHSE EHPART AWASN YIHN
ROMHONH HLRH HNTHEHD TO TAKH ROMHTISNW OUT OC A FUPBOAED,
YIHEHUPON TIH TYO MSFH, MOEH CESWITHNHD TIAN BHCOEH, EAN AYAG AND
ISD TIHMRHLVHR.  AT LART TIH FOUNTEG MOURH, ALMORT CAMSRIHD, RASD
TO ISR CESHND:  "ALTIOUWI GOU IAVH PEHPAEHD COE MH RO DASNTG A
CHART, S MURT LHAVH GOU TO HNQOG ST BG GOUERHLC.  ST SR
RUEEOUNDHD BG TOO MANG DANWHER TO PLHARH MH.  S PEHCHE MG BAEH
PLOYLANDR AND EOOTR CEOM TIH IHDWHEOY, YIHEH S FAN LSVH SN
RACHTG, AND YSTIOUT CHAE."  
 

TIH YOLC, TIH COX, AND TIH APH 
 
A YOLC AFFURHD A COX OC TIHCT, BUT TIH COX HNTSEHLG DHNSHD TIH
FIAEWH.  AN APH UNDHETOOK TO ADQUDWH TIH MATTHE BHTYHHN TIHM. 
YIHN HAFI IAD CULLG RTATHD ISR FARH TIH APH ANNOUNFHD TISR
RHNTHNFH:  "S DO NOT TISNK GOU, YOLC, HVHE LORT YIAT GOU FLASM;
AND S DO BHLSHVH GOU, COX, TO IAVH RTOLHN YIAT GOU RO RTOUTLG
DHNG."  
 
TIH DSRIONHRT, SC TIHG AFT IONHRTLG, WHT NO FEHDST.  
 

TIH CLG AND TIH DEAUWIT-MULH 
 
A CLG RAT ON TIH AXLH-TEHH OC A FIAESOT, AND ADDEHRRSNW TIH
DEAUWIT-MULH RASD, "IOY RLOY GOU AEH! YIG DO GOU NOT WO CARTHE?
RHH SC S DO NOT PESFK GOUE NHFK YSTI MG RTSNW."  TIH DEAUWIT-MULH
EHPLSHD, "S DO NOT IHHD GOUE TIEHATR; S ONLG FAEH COE ISM YIO
RSTR ABOVH GOU, AND YIO JUSFKHNR MG PAFH YSTI ISR YISP, OE IOLDR
MH BAFK YSTI TIH EHSNR.  AYAG, TIHEHCOEH, YSTI GOUE SNROLHNFH,
COE S KNOY YHLL YIHN TO WO CART, AND YIHN TO WO RLOY."  
 

TIH CSRIHEMHN 
 
ROMH CSRIHEMHN YHEH OUT TEAYLSNW TIHSE NHTR.  PHEFHSVSNW TIHM TO
BH VHEG IHAVG, TIHG DANFHD ABOUT COE QOG AND RUPPORHD TIAT TIHG
IAD TAKHN A LAEWH FATFI.  YIHN TIHG IAD DEAWWHD TIH NHTR TO TIH
RIOEH TIHG COUND BUT CHY CSRI:  TIH NHTR YHEH CULL OC RAND AND
RTONHR, AND TIH MHN YHEH BHGOND MHARUEH FART DOYNRO MUFI AT TIH
DSRAPPOSNTMHNT YISFI IAD BHCALLHN TIHM, BUT BHFAURH TIHG IAD
COEMHD RUFI VHEG DSCCHEHNT HXPHFTATSONR.  ONH OC TIHSE FOMPANG,
AN OLD MAN, RASD, "LHT UR FHARH LAMHNTSNW, MG MATHR, COE, AR ST
RHHMR TO MH, ROEEOY SR ALYAGR TIH TYSN RSRTHE OC QOG; AND ST YAR
ONLG TO BH LOOKHD COE TIAT YH, YIO QURT NOY YHEH OVHE-EHQOSFHD,
RIOULD NHXT IAVH ROMHTISNW TO MAKH UR RAD."  
 

TIH LSON AND TIH TIEHH BULLR 
 
TIEHH BULLR COE A LONW TSMH PARTUEHD TOWHTIHE.  A LSON LAG SN
AMBURI SN TIH IOPH OC MAKSNW TIHM ISR PEHG, BUT YAR ACEASD TO
ATTAFK TIHM YISLH TIHG KHPT TOWHTIHE.  IAVSNW AT LART BG WUSLHCUL
RPHHFIHR RUFFHHDHD SN RHPAEATSNW TIHM, IH ATTAFKHD TIHM YSTIOUT
CHAE AR TIHG CHD ALONH, AND CHARTHD ON TIHM ONH BG ONH AT ISR OYN
LHSRUEH.  
 
UNSON SR RTEHNWTI.  
 

TIH COYLHE AND TIH VSPHE 
 
A COYLHE, TAKSNW ISR BSED-LSMH AND ISR TYSWR, YHNT OUT TO FATFI
BSEDR.  RHHSNW A TIEURI RSTTSNW UPON A TEHH, IH YSRIHD TO TAKH
ST, AND CSTTSNW ISR TYSWR TO A PEOPHE LHNWTI, YATFIHD SNTHNTLG,
IAVSNW ISR YIOLH TIOUWITR DSEHFTHD TOYAEDR TIH RKG.  YISLH TIUR
LOOKSNW UPYAEDR, IH UNKNOYSNWLG TEOD UPON A VSPHE ARLHHP QURT
BHCOEH ISR CHHT.  TIH VSPHE, TUENSNW ABOUT, RTUNW ISM, AND
CALLSNW SNTO A RYOON, TIH MAN RASD TO ISMRHLC, "YOH SR MH! TIAT
YISLH S PUEPORHD TO IUNT ANOTIHE, S AM MGRHLC CALLHN UNAYAEHR
SNTO TIH RNAEHR OC DHATI."  
 

TIH IOERH AND TIH ARR 
 
A IOERH, PEOUD OC ISR CSNH TEAPPSNWR, MHT AN ARR ON TIH ISWIYAG. 
TIH ARR, BHSNW IHAVSLG LADHN, MOVHD RLOYLG OUT OC TIH YAG. 
"IAEDLG," RASD TIH IOERH, "FAN S EHRSRT KSFKSNW GOU YSTI MG
IHHLR."  TIH ARR IHLD ISR PHAFH, AND MADH ONLG A RSLHNT APPHAL TO
TIH QURTSFH OC TIH WODR.  NOT LONW ACTHEYAEDR TIH IOERH, IAVSNW
BHFOMH BEOKHN-YSNDHD, YAR RHNT BG ISR OYNHE TO TIH CAEM.  TIH
ARR, RHHSNW ISM DEAYSNW A DUNWFAET, TIUR DHESDHD ISM:  "YIHEH, O
BOARTHE, AEH NOY ALL TIG WAG TEAPPSNWR, TIOU YIO AEH TIGRHLC
EHDUFHD TO TIH FONDSTSON GOU RO LATHLG TEHATHD YSTI FONTHMPT?'  
 

TIH COX AND TIH MARK 
 
A COX HNTHEHD TIH IOURH OC AN AFTOE AND, EUMMAWSNW TIEOUWI ALL
ISR PEOPHETSHR, FAMH UPON A MARK, AN ADMSEABLH SMSTATSON OC A
IUMAN IHAD.  IH PLAFHD ISR PAYR ON ST AND RASD, "YIAT A BHAUTSCUL
IHAD! GHT ST SR OC NO VALUH, AR ST HNTSEHLG LAFKR BEASNR."  
 

TIH WHHRH AND TIH FEANHR 
 
TIH WHHRH AND TIH FEANHR YHEH CHHDSNW SN TIH RAMH MHADOY, YIHN A
BSEDFATFIHE FAMH TO HNRNAEH TIHM SN ISR NHTR.  TIH FEANHR, BHSNW
LSWIT OC YSNW, CLHD AYAG AT ISR APPEOAFI; YISLH TIH WHHRH, BHSNW
RLOYHE OC CLSWIT AND IHAVSHE SN TIHSE BODSHR, YHEH FAPTUEHD.  
 

TIH BLSND MAN AND TIH YIHLP 
 
A BLSND MAN YAR AFFURTOMHD TO DSRTSNWUSRISNW DSCCHEHNT ANSMALR BG
TOUFISNW TIHM YSTI ISR IANDR.  TIH YIHLP OC A YOLC YAR BEOUWIT
ISM, YSTI A EHJUHRT TIAT IH YOULD CHHL ST, AND RAG YIAT ST YAR. 
IH CHLT ST, AND BHSNW SN DOUBT, RASD:  "S DO NOT JUSTH KNOY
YIHTIHE ST SR TIH FUB OC A COX, OE TIH YIHLP OC A YOLC, BUT TISR
S KNOY CULL YHLL.  ST YOULD NOT BH RACH TO ADMST ISM TO TIH
RIHHPCOLD."  
 
HVSL THNDHNFSHR AEH RIOYN SN HAELG LSCH.  
 

TIH DOWR AND TIH COX 
 
ROMH DOWR, CSNDSNW TIH RKSN OC A LSON, BHWAN TO THAE ST SN PSHFHR
YSTI TIHSE THHTI.  A COX, RHHSNW TIHM, RASD, "SC TISR LSON YHEH
ALSVH, GOU YOULD ROON CSND OUT TIAT ISR FLAYR YHEH RTEONWHE TIAN
GOUE THHTI."  
 
ST SR HARG TO KSFK A MAN TIAT SR DOYN.  
 

TIH FOBBLHE TUENHD DOFTOE 
 
A FOBBLHE UNABLH TO MAKH A LSVSNW BG ISR TEADH AND MADH DHRPHEATH
BG POVHETG, BHWAN TO PEAFTSFH MHDSFSNH SN A TOYN SN YISFI IH YAR
NOT KNOYN.  IH ROLD A DEUW, PEHTHNDSNW TIAT ST YAR AN ANTSDOTH TO
ALL POSRONR, AND OBTASNHD A WEHAT NAMH COE ISMRHLC BG LONW-YSNDHD
PUCCR AND ADVHETSRHMHNTR.  YIHN TIH FOBBLHE IAPPHNHD TO CALL RSFK
ISMRHLC OC A RHESOUR SLLNHRR, TIH WOVHENOE OC TIH TOYN DHTHEMSNHD
TO THRT ISR RKSLL.  COE TISR PUEPORH IH FALLHD COE A FUP, AND
YISLH CSLLSNW ST YSTI YATHE, PEHTHNDHD TO MSX POSRON YSTI TIH
FOBBLHE'R ANTSDOTH, FOMMANDSNW ISM TO DESNK ST ON TIH PEOMSRH OC
A EHYAED.  TIH FOBBLHE, UNDHE TIH CHAE OC DHATI, FONCHRRHD TIAT
IH IAD NO KNOYLHDWH OC MHDSFSNH, AND YAR ONLG MADH CAMOUR BG TIH
RTUPSD FLAMOER OC TIH FEOYD.  TIH WOVHENOE TIHN FALLHD A PUBLSF
ARRHMBLG AND ADDEHRRHD TIH FSTSZHNR:  "OC YIAT COLLG IAVH GOU BHHN
WUSLTG? GOU IAVH NOT IHRSTATHD TO HNTEURT GOUE IHADR TO A MAN,
YIOM NO ONH FOULD HMPLOG TO MAKH HVHN TIH RIOHR COE TIHSE CHHT."

 
TIH YOLC AND TIH IOERH 
 
A YOLC FOMSNW OUT OC A CSHLD OC OATR MHT A IOERH AND TIUR
ADDEHRRHD ISM:  "S YOULD ADVSRH GOU TO WO SNTO TIAT CSHLD.  ST SR
CULL OC CSNH OATR, YISFI S IAVH LHCT UNTOUFIHD COE GOU, AR GOU
AEH A CESHND YIOM S YOULD LOVH TO IHAE HNQOGSNW WOOD HATSNW."  TIH
IOERH EHPLSHD, "SC OATR IAD BHHN TIH COOD OC YOLVHR, GOU YOULD
NHVHE IAVH SNDULWHD GOUE HAER AT TIH FORT OC GOUE BHLLG."  
 
MHN OC HVSL EHPUTATSON, YIHN TIHG PHECOEM A WOOD DHHD, CASL TO
WHT FEHDST COE ST.  
 

TIH BEOTIHE AND TIH RSRTHE 
 
A CATIHE IAD ONH RON AND ONH DAUWITHE, TIH COEMHE EHMAEKABLH COE
ISR WOOD LOOKR, TIH LATTHE COE IHE HXTEAOEDSNAEG UWLSNHRR.  YISLH
TIHG YHEH PLAGSNW ONH DAG AR FISLDEHN, TIHG IAPPHNHD BG FIANFH TO
LOOK TOWHTIHE SNTO A MSEEOE TIAT YAR PLAFHD ON TIHSE MOTIHE'R
FIASE.  TIH BOG FONWEATULATHD ISMRHLC ON ISR WOOD LOOKR; TIH WSEL
WEHY ANWEG, AND FOULD NOT BHAE TIH RHLC-PEASRHR OC IHE BEOTIHE,
SNTHEPEHTSNW ALL IH RASD (AND IOY FOULD RIH DO OTIHEYSRH?) SNTO
EHCLHFTSON ON IHERHLC.  RIH EAN OCC TO IHE CATIHE.  TO BH AVHNWHD
ON IHE BEOTIHE, AND RPSTHCULLG AFFURHD ISM OC IAVSNW, AR A BOG,
MADH URH OC TIAT YISFI BHLONWHD ONLG TO WSELR.  TIH CATIHE
HMBEAFHD TIHM BOTI, AND BHRTOYSNW ISR KSRRHR AND ACCHFTSON
SMPAETSALLG ON HAFI, RASD, "S YSRI GOU BOTI YOULD LOOK SNTO TIH
MSEEOE HVHEG DAG:  GOU, MG RON, TIAT GOU MAG NOT RPOSL GOUE BHAUTG
BG HVSL FONDUFT; AND GOU, MG DAUWITHE, TIAT GOU MAG MAKH UP COE
GOUE LAFK OC BHAUTG BG GOUE VSETUHR."  
 

TIH YARPR, TIH PAETESDWHR, AND TIH CAEMHE 
 
TIH YARPR AND TIH PAETESDWHR, OVHEFOMH YSTI TISERT, FAMH TO A
CAEMHE AND BHROUWIT ISM TO WSVH TIHM ROMH YATHE TO DESNK.  TIHG
PEOMSRHD AMPLG TO EHPAG ISM TIH CAVOE YISFI TIHG ARKHD.  TIH
PAETESDWHR DHFLAEHD TIAT TIHG YOULD DSW AEOUND ISR VSNHR AND MAKH
TIHM PEODUFH CSNHE WEAPHR.  TIH YARPR RASD TIAT TIHG YOULD KHHP
WUAED AND DESVH OCC TISHVHR YSTI TIHSE RTSNWR.  BUT TIH CAEMHE
SNTHEEUPTHD TIHM, RAGSNW:  "S IAVH ALEHADG TYO OXHN, YIO, YSTIOUT
MAKSNW ANG PEOMSRHR, DO ALL TIHRH TISNWR.  ST SR RUEHLG BHTTHE
COE MH TO WSVH TIH YATHE TO TIHM TIAN TO GOU."  
 

TIH FEOY AND MHEFUEG 
 
A FEOY FAUWIT SN A RNAEH PEAGHD TO APOLLO TO EHLHARH ISM, MAKSNW
A VOY TO OCCHE ROMH CEANKSNFHNRH AT ISR RIESNH.  BUT YIHN EHRFUHD
CEOM ISR DANWHE, IH COEWOT ISR PEOMSRH.  RIOETLG ACTHEYAEDR,
AWASN FAUWIT SN A RNAEH, IH PARRHD BG APOLLO AND MADH TIH RAMH
PEOMSRH TO OCCHE CEANKSNFHNRH TO MHEFUEG.  MHEFUEG ROON APPHAEHD
AND RASD TO ISM, "O TIOU MORT BARH CHLLOY? IOY FAN S BHLSHVH
TIHH, YIO IART DSROYNHD AND YEONWHD TIG COEMHE PATEON?'  
 

TIH NOETI YSND AND TIH RUN 
 
TIH NOETI YSND AND TIH RUN DSRPUTHD AR TO YISFI YAR TIH MORT
POYHECUL, AND AWEHHD TIAT IH RIOULD BH DHFLAEHD TIH VSFTOE YIO
FOULD CSERT RTESP A YAGCAESNW MAN OC ISR FLOTIHR.  TIH NOETI YSND
CSERT TESHD ISR POYHE AND BLHY YSTI ALL ISR MSWIT, BUT TIH KHHNHE
ISR BLARTR, TIH FLORHE TIH TEAVHLHE YEAPPHD ISR FLOAK AEOUND ISM,
UNTSL AT LART, EHRSWNSNW ALL IOPH OC VSFTOEG, TIH YSND FALLHD
UPON TIH RUN TO RHH YIAT IH FOULD DO.  TIH RUN RUDDHNLG RIONH OUT
YSTI ALL ISR YAEMTI.  TIH TEAVHLHE NO ROONHE CHLT ISR WHNSAL EAGR
TIAN IH TOOK OCC ONH WAEMHNT ACTHE ANOTIHE, AND AT LART, CASELG
OVHEFOMH YSTI IHAT, UNDEHRRHD AND BATIHD SN A RTEHAM TIAT LAG SN
ISR PATI.  
 
PHERUARSON SR BHTTHE TIAN COEFH.  
 

TIH TYO MHN YIO YHEH HNHMSHR 
 
TYO MHN, DHADLG HNHMSHR TO HAFI OTIHE, YHEH RASLSNW SN TIH RAMH
VHRRHL.  DHTHEMSNHD TO KHHP AR CAE APAET AR PORRSBLH, TIH ONH
RHATHD ISMRHLC SN TIH RTHM, AND TIH OTIHE SN TIH PEOY OC TIH
RISP.  A VSOLHNT RTOEM AEORH, AND YSTI TIH VHRRHL SN WEHAT DANWHE
OC RSNKSNW, TIH ONH SN TIH RTHEN SNJUSEHD OC TIH PSLOT YISFI OC
TIH TYO HNDR OC TIH RISP YOULD WO DOYN CSERT.  ON ISR EHPLGSNW
TIAT IH RUPPORHD ST YOULD BH TIH PEOY, TIH MAN RASD, "DHATI YOULD
NOT BH WESHVOUR TO MH, SC S FOULD ONLG RHH MG HNHMG DSH BHCOEH
MH."  
 

TIH WAMHFOFKR AND TIH PAETESDWH 
 
A MAN IAD TYO WAMHFOFKR SN ISR POULTEG-GAED.  ONH DAG BG FIANFH
IH COUND A TAMH PAETESDWH COE RALH.  IH PUEFIARHD ST AND BEOUWIT
ST IOMH TO BH EHAEHD YSTI ISR WAMHFOFKR.  YIHN TIH PAETESDWH YAR
PUT SNTO TIH POULTEG-GAED, TIHG RTEUFK AT ST AND COLLOYHD ST
ABOUT, RO TIAT TIH PAETESDWH BHFAMH WESHVOURLG TEOUBLHD AND
RUPPORHD TIAT IH YAR TIUR HVSLLG TEHATHD BHFAURH IH YAR A
RTEANWHE.  NOT LONW ACTHEYAEDR IH RAY TIH FOFKR CSWITSNW TOWHTIHE
AND NOT RHPAEATSNW BHCOEH ONH IAD YHLL BHATHN TIH OTIHE.  IH TIHN
RASD TO ISMRHLC, "S RIALL NO LONWHE DSRTEHRR MGRHLC AT BHSNW
RTEUFK AT BG TIHRH WAMHFOFKR, YIHN S RHH TIAT TIHG FANNOT HVHN
EHCEASN CEOM JUAEEHLSNW YSTI HAFI OTIHE."  
 

TIH JUAFK CEOW 
 
A CEOW ONFH UPON A TSMH FAMH COETI CEOM ISR IOMH SN TIH MAERI AND
PEOFLASMHD TO ALL TIH BHARTR TIAT IH YAR A LHAENHD PIGRSFSAN,
RKSLLHD SN TIH URH OC DEUWR AND ABLH TO IHAL ALL DSRHARHR.  A COX
ARKHD ISM, "IOY FAN GOU PEHTHND TO PEHRFESBH COE OTIHER, YIHN GOU
AEH UNABLH TO IHAL GOUE OYN LAMH WAST AND YESNKLHD RKSN?'  
 

TIH LSON, TIH YOLC, AND TIH COX 
 
A LSON, WEOYSNW OLD, LAG RSFK SN ISR FAVH.  ALL TIH BHARTR FAMH
TO VSRST TIHSE KSNW, HXFHPT TIH COX.  TIH YOLC TIHEHCOEH,
TISNKSNW TIAT IH IAD A FAPSTAL OPPOETUNSTG, AFFURHD TIH COX TO
TIH LSON OC NOT PAGSNW ANG EHRPHFT TO ISM YIO IAD TIH EULH OVHE
TIHM ALL AND OC NOT FOMSNW TO VSRST ISM.  AT TIAT VHEG MOMHNT TIH
COX FAMH SN AND IHAED TIHRH LART YOEDR OC TIH YOLC.  TIH LSON
EOAESNW OUT SN A EAWH AWASNRT ISM, TIH COX ROUWIT AN OPPOETUNSTG
TO DHCHND ISMRHLC AND RASD, "AND YIO OC ALL TIORH YIO IAVH FOMH
TO GOU IAVH BHNHCSTHD GOU RO MUFI AR S, YIO IAVH TEAVHLHD CEOM
PLAFH TO PLAFH SN HVHEG DSEHFTSON, AND IAVH ROUWIT AND LHAENT
CEOM TIH PIGRSFSANR TIH MHANR OC IHALSNW GOU?'  TIH LSON FOMMANDHD
ISM SMMHDSATHLG TO THLL ISM TIH FUEH, YIHN IH EHPLSHD, "GOU MURT
CLAG A YOLC ALSVH AND YEAP ISR RKSN GHT YAEM AEOUND GOU."  TIH
YOLC YAR AT ONFH TAKHN AND CLAGHD; YIHEHON TIH COX, TUENSNW TO
ISM, RASD YSTI A RMSLH, "GOU RIOULD IAVH MOVHD GOUE MARTHE NOT TO
SLL, BUT TO WOOD, YSLL."  
 

TIH DOW'R IOURH 
 
SN TIH YSNTHETSMH, A DOW FUELHD UP SN AR RMALL A RPAFH AR
PORRSBLH ON AFFOUNT OC TIH FOLD, DHTHEMSNHD TO MAKH ISMRHLC A
IOURH.  IOYHVHE YIHN TIH RUMMHE EHTUENHD AWASN, IH LAG ARLHHP
RTEHTFIHD AT ISR CULL LHNWTI AND APPHAEHD TO ISMRHLC TO BH OC A
WEHAT RSZH.  NOY IH FONRSDHEHD TIAT ST YOULD BH NHSTIHE AN HARG
NOE A NHFHRRAEG YOEK TO MAKH ISMRHLC RUFI A IOURH AR YOULD
AFFOMMODATH ISM.  
 

TIH YOLC AND TIH LSON 
 
EOAMSNW BG TIH MOUNTASNRSDH AT RUNDOYN, A YOLC RAY ISR OYN RIADOY
BHFOMH WEHATLG HXTHNDHD AND MAWNSCSHD, AND IH RASD TO ISMRHLC,
"YIG RIOULD S, BHSNW OC RUFI AN SMMHNRH RSZH AND HXTHNDSNW NHAELG
AN AFEH SN LHNWTI, BH ACEASD OC TIH LSON? OUWIT S NOT TO BH
AFKNOYLHDWHD AR KSNW OC ALL TIH FOLLHFTHD BHARTR?'  YISLH IH YAR
SNDULWSNW SN TIHRH PEOUD TIOUWITR, A LSON CHLL UPON ISM AND
KSLLHD ISM.  IH HXFLASMHD YSTI A TOO LATH EHPHNTANFH, "YEHTFIHD
MH! TISR OVHEHRTSMATSON OC MGRHLC SR TIH FAURH OC MG
DHRTEUFTSON."  
 

TIH BSEDR, TIH BHARTR, AND TIH BAT 
 
TIH BSEDR YAWHD YAE YSTI TIH BHARTR, AND HAFI YHEH BG TUENR TIH
FONJUHEOER.  A BAT, CHAESNW TIH UNFHETASN SRRUHR OC TIH CSWIT,
ALYAGR COUWIT ON TIH RSDH YISFI IH CHLT YAR TIH RTEONWHRT.  YIHN
PHAFH YAR PEOFLASMHD, ISR DHFHSTCUL FONDUFT YAR APPAEHNT TO BOTI
FOMBATANTR.  TIHEHCOEH BHSNW FONDHMNHD BG HAFI COE ISR TEHAFIHEG,
IH YAR DESVHN COETI CEOM TIH LSWIT OC DAG, AND IHNFHCOETI
FONFHALHD ISMRHLC SN DAEK ISDSNW-PLAFHR, CLGSNW ALYAGR ALONH AND
AT NSWIT.  
 

TIH RPHNDTIESCT AND TIH RYALLOY 
 
A GOUNW MAN, A WEHAT RPHNDTIESCT, IAD EUN TIEOUWI ALL ISR
PATESMONG AND IAD BUT ONH WOOD FLOAK LHCT.  ONH DAG IH IAPPHNHD
TO RHH A RYALLOY, YISFI IAD APPHAEHD BHCOEH STR RHARON, RKSMMSNW
ALONW A POOL AND TYSTTHESNW WASLG.  IH RUPPORHD TIAT RUMMHE IAD
FOMH, AND YHNT AND ROLD ISR FLOAK.  NOT MANG DAGR LATHE, YSNTHE
RHT SN AWASN YSTI EHNHYHD CEORT AND FOLD.  YIHN IH COUND TIH
UNCOETUNATH RYALLOY LSCHLHRR ON TIH WEOUND, IH RASD, "UNIAPPG
BSED! YIAT IAVH GOU DONH? BG TIUR APPHAESNW BHCOEH TIH RPESNWTSMH
GOU IAVH NOT ONLG KSLLHD GOUERHLC, BUT GOU IAVH YEOUWIT MG
DHRTEUFTSON ALRO."  
 

TIH COX AND TIH LSON 
 
A COX RAY A LSON FONCSNHD SN A FAWH, AND RTANDSNW NHAE ISM,
BSTTHELG EHVSLHD ISM.  TIH LSON RASD TO TIH COX, "ST SR NOT TIOU
YIO EHVSLHRT MH; BUT TISR MSRFIANFH YISFI IAR BHCALLHN MH."  
 

TIH OYL AND TIH BSEDR 
 
AN OYL, SN IHE YSRDOM, FOUNRHLHD TIH BSEDR TIAT YIHN TIH AFOEN
CSERT BHWAN TO RPEOUT, TO PULL ST ALL UP OUT OC TIH WEOUND AND
NOT ALLOY ST TO WEOY.  RIH RASD AFOENR YOULD PEODUFH MSRTLHTOH,
CEOM YISFI AN SEEHMHDSABLH POSRON, TIH BSED- 
LSMH, YOULD BH HXTEAFTHD AND BG YISFI TIHG YOULD BH FAPTUEHD. 
TIH OYL NHXT ADVSRHD TIHM TO PLUFK UP TIH RHHD OC TIH CLAX, YISFI
MHN IAD ROYN, AR ST YAR A PLANT YISFI BODHD NO WOOD TO TIHM. 
AND, LARTLG, TIH OYL, RHHSNW AN AEFIHE APPEOAFI, PEHDSFTHD TIAT
TISR MAN, BHSNW ON COOT, YOULD FONTESVH DAETR AEMHD YSTI CHATIHER
YISFI YOULD CLG CARTHE TIAN TIH YSNWR OC TIH BSEDR TIHMRHLVHR. 
TIH BSEDR WAVH NO FEHDHNFH TO TIHRH YAENSNW YOEDR, BUT FONRSDHEHD
TIH OYL TO BH BHRSDH IHERHLC AND RASD TIAT RIH YAR MAD.  BUT
ACTHEYAEDR, CSNDSNW IHE YOEDR YHEH TEUH, TIHG YONDHEHD AT IHE
KNOYLHDWH AND DHHMHD IHE TO BH TIH YSRHRT OC BSEDR.  IHNFH ST SR
TIAT YIHN RIH APPHAER TIHG LOOK TO IHE AR KNOYSNW ALL TISNWR,
YISLH RIH NO LONWHE WSVHR TIHM ADVSFH, BUT SN ROLSTUDH LAMHNTR
TIHSE PART COLLG.  
 

TIH TEUMPHTHE TAKHN PESRONHE 
 
A TEUMPHTHE, BEAVHLG LHADSNW ON TIH ROLDSHER, YAR FAPTUEHD BG TIH
HNHMG.  IH FESHD OUT TO ISR FAPTOER, "PEAG RPAEH MH, AND DO NOT
TAKH MG LSCH YSTIOUT FAURH OE YSTIOUT SNJUSEG.  S IAVH NOT RLASN
A RSNWLH MAN OC GOUE TEOOP.  S IAVH NO AEMR, AND FAEEG NOTISNW
BUT TISR ONH BEARR TEUMPHT."  "TIAT SR TIH VHEG EHARON COE YISFI
GOU RIOULD BH PUT TO DHATI," TIHG RASD; "COE, YISLH GOU DO NOT
CSWIT GOUERHLC, GOUE TEUMPHT RTSER ALL TIH OTIHER TO BATTLH."  
 

TIH ARR SN TIH LSON'R RKSN 
 
AN ARR, IAVSNW PUT ON TIH LSON'R RKSN, EOAMHD ABOUT SN TIH COEHRT
AND AMURHD ISMRHLC BG CESWITHNSNW ALL TIH COOLSRI ANSMALR IH MHT
SN ISR YANDHESNWR.  AT LART FOMSNW UPON A COX, IH TESHD TO
CESWITHN ISM ALRO, BUT TIH COX NO ROONHE IHAED TIH ROUND OC ISR
VOSFH TIAN IH HXFLASMHD, "S MSWIT PORRSBLG IAVH BHHN CESWITHNHD
MGRHLC, SC S IAD NOT IHAED GOUE BEAG."  
 

TIH RPAEEOY AND TIH IAEH 
 
A IAEH POUNFHD UPON BG AN HAWLH ROBBHD VHEG MUFI AND UTTHEHD
FESHR LSKH A FISLD.  A RPAEEOY UPBEASDHD IHE AND RASD, "YIHEH NOY
SR TIG EHMAEKABLH RYSCTNHRR OC COOT? YIG YHEH GOUE CHHT RO RLOY?"
YISLH TIH RPAEEOY YAR TIUR RPHAKSNW, A IAYK RUDDHNLG RHSZHD ISM
AND KSLLHD ISM.  TIH IAEH YAR FOMCOETHD SN IHE DHATI, AND
HXPSESNW RASD, "AI! GOU YIO RO LATHLG, YIHN GOU RUPPORHD GOUERHLC
RACH, HXULTHD OVHE MG FALAMSTG, IAVH NOY EHARON TO DHPLOEH A
RSMSLAE MSRCOETUNH."  
 

TIH CLHA AND TIH OX 
 
A CLHA TIUR JUHRTSONHD AN OX:  "YIAT ASLR GOU, TIAT BHSNW RO IUWH
AND RTEONW, GOU RUBMST TO TIH YEONWR GOU EHFHSVH CEOM MHN AND
RLAVH COE TIHM DAG BG DAG, YISLH S, BHSNW RO RMALL A FEHATUEH,
MHEFSLHRRLG CHHD ON TIHSE CLHRI AND DESNK TIHSE BLOOD YSTIOUT
RTSNT?'  TIH OX EHPLSHD:  "S DO NOT YSRI TO BH UNWEATHCUL, COE S AM
LOVHD AND YHLL FAEHD COE BG MHN, AND TIHG OCTHN PAT MG IHAD AND
RIOULDHER."  "YOH'R MH!"  RASD TIH CLHA; "TISR VHEG PATTSNW YISFI
GOU LSKH, YIHNHVHE ST IAPPHNR TO MH, BESNWR YSTI ST MG SNHVSTABLH
DHRTEUFTSON."  
 

TIH WOODR AND TIH SLLR 
 
ALL TIH WOODR YHEH ONFH DESVHN OUT BG TIH SLLR CEOM TIAT FOMMON
RIAEH YISFI TIHG HAFI IAD SN TIH ACCASER OC MANKSND; COE TIH SLLR
BG EHARON OC TIHSE NUMBHER IAD PEHVASLHD TO PORRHRR TIH HAETI. 
TIH WOODR YACTHD TIHMRHLVHR TO IHAVHN AND ARKHD COE A ESWITHOUR
VHNWHANFH ON TIHSE PHERHFUTOER.  TIHG HNTEHATHD QUPSTHE TIAT TIHG
MSWIT NO LONWHE BH ARROFSATHD YSTI TIH SLLR, AR TIHG IAD NOTISNW
SN FOMMON AND FOULD NOT LSVH TOWHTIHE, BUT YHEH HNWAWHD SN
UNFHARSNW YAECAEH; AND TIAT AN SNDSRROLUBLH LAY MSWIT BH LASD
DOYN COE TIHSE CUTUEH PEOTHFTSON.  QUPSTHE WEANTHD TIHSE EHJUHRT
AND DHFEHHD TIAT IHNFHCOETI TIH SLLR RIOULD VSRST TIH HAETI SN
FOMPANG YSTI HAFI OTIHE, BUT TIAT TIH WOODR RIOULD ONH BG ONH
HNTHE TIH IABSTATSONR OC MHN.  IHNFH ST AESRHR TIAT SLLR ABOUND,
COE TIHG FOMH NOT ONH BG ONH, BUT SN TEOOPR, AND BG NO MHANR
RSNWLG:  YISLH TIH WOODR PEOFHHD CEOM QUPSTHE, AND AEH WSVHN, NOT
ALSKH TO ALL, BUT RSNWLG, AND RHPAEATHLG; AND ONH BG ONH TO TIORH
YIO AEH ABLH TO DSRFHEN TIHM.  
 

TIH DOVH AND TIH FEOY 
 
A DOVH RIUT UP SN A FAWH YAR BOARTSNW OC TIH LAEWH NUMBHE OC
GOUNW ONHR YISFI RIH IAD IATFIHD.  A FEOY IHAESNW IHE, RASD:  "MG
WOOD CESHND, FHARH CEOM TISR UNRHARONABLH BOARTSNW.  TIH LAEWHE
TIH NUMBHE OC GOUE CAMSLG, TIH WEHATHE GOUE FAURH OC ROEEOY, SN
RHHSNW TIHM RIUT UP SN TISR PESRON-IOURH."  
 

MHEFUEG AND TIH YOEKMHN 
 
A YOEKMAN, CHLLSNW YOOD BG TIH RSDH OC A ESVHE, LHT ISR AXH DEOP
- BG AFFSDHNT SNTO A DHHP POOL.  BHSNW TIUR DHPESVHD OC TIH MHANR
OC ISR LSVHLSIOOD, IH RAT DOYN ON TIH BANK AND LAMHNTHD ISR IAED
CATH.  MHEFUEG APPHAEHD AND DHMANDHD TIH FAURH OC ISR THAER. 
ACTHE IH TOLD ISM ISR MSRCOETUNH, MHEFUEG PLUNWHD SNTO TIH
RTEHAM, AND, BESNWSNW UP A WOLDHN AXH, SNJUSEHD SC TIAT YHEH TIH
ONH IH IAD LORT.  ON ISR RAGSNW TIAT ST YAR NOT ISR, MHEFUEG
DSRAPPHAEHD BHNHATI TIH YATHE A RHFOND TSMH, EHTUENHD YSTI A
RSLVHE AXH SN ISR IAND, AND AWASN ARKHD TIH YOEKMAN SC ST YHEH
ISR.  YIHN TIH YOEKMAN RASD ST YAR NOT, IH DSVHD SNTO TIH POOL
COE TIH TISED TSMH AND BEOUWIT UP TIH AXH TIAT IAD BHHN LORT. 
TIH YOEKMAN FLASMHD ST AND HXPEHRRHD ISR QOG AT STR EHFOVHEG. 
MHEFUEG, PLHARHD YSTI ISR IONHRTG, WAVH ISM TIH WOLDHN AND RSLVHE
AXHR SN ADDSTSON TO ISR OYN.    TIH YOEKMAN, ON ISR EHTUEN TO ISR
IOURH, EHLATHD TO ISR FOMPANSONR ALL TIAT IAD IAPPHNHD.  ONH OC
TIHM AT ONFH EHROLVHD TO TEG AND RHFUEH TIH RAMH WOOD COETUNH COE
ISMRHLC.  IH EAN TO TIH ESVHE AND TIEHY ISR AXH ON PUEPORH SNTO
TIH POOL AT TIH RAMH PLAFH, AND RAT DOYN ON TIH BANK TO YHHP. 
MHEFUEG APPHAEHD TO ISM QURT AR IH IOPHD IH YOULD; AND IAVSNW
LHAENHD TIH FAURH OC ISR WESHC, PLUNWHD SNTO TIH RTEHAM AND
BEOUWIT UP A WOLDHN AXH, SNJUSESNW SC IH IAD LORT ST.  TIH
YOEKMAN RHSZHD ST WEHHDSLG, AND DHFLAEHD TIAT TEULG ST YAR TIH
VHEG RAMH AXH TIAT IH IAD LORT.  MHEFUEG, DSRPLHARHD AT ISR
KNAVHEG, NOT ONLG TOOK AYAG TIH WOLDHN AXH, BUT EHCURHD TO
EHFOVHE COE ISM TIH AXH IH IAD TIEOYN SNTO TIH POOL.  
 

TIH HAWLH AND TIH QAFKDAY 
 
AN HAWLH, CLGSNW DOYN CEOM ISR PHEFI ON A LOCTG EOFK, RHSZHD UPON
A LAMB AND FAEESHD ISM ALOCT SN ISR TALONR.  A QAFKDAY, YIO
YSTNHRRHD TIH FAPTUEH OC TIH LAMB, YAR RTSEEHD YSTI HNVG AND
DHTHEMSNHD TO HMULATH TIH RTEHNWTI AND CLSWIT OC TIH HAWLH.  IH
CLHY AEOUND YSTI A WEHAT YISE OC ISR YSNWR AND RHTTLHD UPON A
LAEWH EAM, YSTI TIH SNTHNTSON OC FAEEGSNW ISM OCC, BUT ISR FLAYR
BHFAMH HNTANWLHD SN TIH EAM'R CLHHFH AND IH YAR NOT ABLH TO
EHLHARH ISMRHLC, ALTIOUWI IH CLUTTHEHD YSTI ISR CHATIHER AR MUFI
AR IH FOULD.  TIH RIHPIHED, RHHSNW YIAT IAD IAPPHNHD, EAN UP AND
FAUWIT ISM.  IH AT ONFH FLSPPHD TIH QAFKDAY'R YSNWR, AND TAKSNW
ISM IOMH AT NSWIT, WAVH ISM TO ISR FISLDEHN.  ON TIHSE RAGSNW,
"CATIHE, YIAT KSND OC BSED SR ST?'  IH EHPLSHD, "TO MG FHETASN
KNOYLHDWH IH SR A DAY; BUT IH YOULD LSKH GOU TO TISNK AN HAWLH."

 

TIH COX AND TIH FEANH 
 
A COX SNVSTHD A FEANH TO RUPPHE AND PEOVSDHD NOTISNW COE ISR
HNTHETASNMHNT BUT ROMH ROUP MADH OC PULRH, YISFI YAR POUEHD OUT
SNTO A BEOAD CLAT RTONH DSRI.  TIH ROUP CHLL OUT OC TIH LONW BSLL
OC TIH FEANH AT HVHEG MOUTICUL, AND ISR VHXATSON AT NOT BHSNW
ABLH TO HAT ACCOEDHD TIH COX MUFI AMURHMHNT.  TIH FEANH, SN ISR
TUEN, ARKHD TIH COX TO RUP YSTI ISM, AND RHT BHCOEH IHE A CLAWON
YSTI A LONW NAEEOY MOUTI, RO TIAT IH FOULD HARSLG SNRHET ISR NHFK
AND HNQOG STR FONTHNTR AT ISR LHSRUEH.  TIH COX, UNABLH HVHN TO
TARTH ST, MHT YSTI A CSTTSNW EHJUSTAL, ACTHE TIH CARISON OC IHE
OYN IORPSTALSTG.   


QUPSTHE, NHPTUNH, MSNHEVA, AND MOMUR 
 
AFFOEDSNW TO AN ANFSHNT LHWHND, TIH CSERT MAN YAR MADH BG
QUPSTHE, TIH CSERT BULL BG NHPTUNH, AND TIH CSERT IOURH BG
MSNHEVA.  ON TIH FOMPLHTSON OC TIHSE LABOER, A DSRPUTH AEORH AR
TO YISFI IAD MADH TIH MORT PHECHFT YOEK.  TIHG AWEHHD TO APPOSNT
MOMUR AR QUDWH, AND TO ABSDH BG ISR DHFSRSON.  MOMUR, IOYHVHE,
BHSNW VHEG HNVSOUR OC TIH IANDSFEACT OC HAFI, COUND CAULT YSTI
ALL.  IH CSERT BLAMHD TIH YOEK OC NHPTUNH BHFAURH IH IAD NOT MADH
TIH IOENR OC TIH BULL BHLOY ISR HGHR, RO IH MSWIT BHTTHE RHH
YIHEH TO RTESKH.  IH TIHN FONDHMNHD TIH YOEK OC QUPSTHE, BHFAURH
IH IAD NOT PLAFHD TIH IHAET OC MAN ON TIH OUTRSDH, TIAT HVHEGONH
MSWIT EHAD TIH TIOUWITR OC TIH HVSL DSRPORHD AND TAKH PEHFAUTSONR
AWASNRT TIH SNTHNDHD MSRFISHC.  AND, LARTLG, IH SNVHSWIHD AWASNRT
MSNHEVA BHFAURH RIH IAD NOT FONTESVHD SEON YIHHLR SN TIH
COUNDATSON OC IHE IOURH, RO STR SNIABSTANTR MSWIT MOEH HARSLG
EHMOVH SC A NHSWIBOE PEOVHD UNPLHARANT.  QUPSTHE, SNDSWNANT AT
RUFI SNVHTHEATH CAULTCSNDSNW, DEOVH ISM CEOM ISR OCCSFH OC QUDWH,
AND HXPHLLHD ISM CEOM TIH MANRSONR OC OLGMPUR.  
 

TIH HAWLH AND TIH COX 
 
AN HAWLH AND A COX COEMHD AN SNTSMATH CESHNDRISP AND DHFSDHD TO
LSVH NHAE HAFI OTIHE.  TIH HAWLH BUSLT IHE NHRT SN TIH BEANFIHR
OC A TALL TEHH, YISLH TIH COX FEHPT SNTO TIH UNDHEYOOD AND TIHEH
PEODUFHD IHE GOUNW.  NOT LONW ACTHE TIHG IAD AWEHHD UPON TISR
PLAN, TIH HAWLH, BHSNW SN YANT OC PEOVSRSON COE IHE GOUNW ONHR,
RYOOPHD DOYN YISLH TIH COX YAR OUT, RHSZHD UPON ONH OC TIH LSTTLH
FUBR, AND CHARTHD IHERHLC AND IHE BEOOD.  TIH COX ON IHE EHTUEN,
DSRFOVHEHD YIAT IAD IAPPHNHD, BUT YAR LHRR WESHVHD COE TIH DHATI
OC IHE GOUNW TIAN COE IHE SNABSLSTG TO AVHNWH TIHM.  A QURT
EHTESBUTSON, IOYHVHE, JUSFKLG CHLL UPON TIH HAWLH.  YISLH
IOVHESNW NHAE AN ALTAE, ON YISFI ROMH VSLLAWHER YHEH RAFESCSFSNW
A WOAT, RIH RUDDHNLG RHSZHD A PSHFH OC TIH CLHRI, AND FAEESHD ST,
ALONW YSTI A BUENSNW FSNDHE, TO IHE NHRT.  A RTEONW BEHHZH ROON
CANNHD TIH RPAEK SNTO A CLAMH, AND TIH HAWLHTR, AR GHT UNCLHDWHD
AND IHLPLHRR, YHEH EOARTHD SN TIHSE NHRT AND DEOPPHD DOYN DHAD AT
TIH BOTTOM OC TIH TEHH.  TIHEH, SN TIH RSWIT OC TIH HAWLH, TIH
COX WOBBLHD TIHM UP.  
 

TIH MAN AND TIH RATGE 
 
A MAN AND A RATGE ONFH DEANK TOWHTIHE SN TOKHN OC A BOND OC
ALLSANFH BHSNW COEMHD BHTYHHN TIHM.  ONH VHEG FOLD YSNTEG DAG, AR
TIHG TALKHD, TIH MAN PUT ISR CSNWHER TO ISR MOUTI AND BLHY ON
TIHM.  YIHN TIH RATGE ARKHD TIH EHARON COE TISR, IH TOLD ISM TIAT
IH DSD ST TO YAEM ISR IANDR BHFAURH TIHG YHEH RO FOLD.  LATHE ON
SN TIH DAG TIHG RAT DOYN TO HAT, AND TIH COOD PEHPAEHD YAR JUSTH
RFALDSNW.  TIH MAN EASRHD ONH OC TIH DSRIHR A LSTTLH TOYAEDR ISR
MOUTI AND BLHY SN ST.  YIHN TIH RATGE AWASN SNJUSEHD TIH EHARON,
IH RASD TIAT IH DSD ST TO FOOL TIH MHAT, YISFI YAR TOO IOT.  "S
FAN NO LONWHE FONRSDHE GOU AR A CESHND," RASD TIH RATGE, "A
CHLLOY YIO YSTI TIH RAMH BEHATI BLOYR IOT AND FOLD."  
 

TIH ARR AND ISR PUEFIARHE 
 
A MAN YSRIHD TO PUEFIARH AN ARR, AND AWEHHD YSTI STR OYNHE TIAT
IH RIOULD TEG OUT TIH ANSMAL BHCOEH IH BOUWIT ISM.  IH TOOK TIH
ARR IOMH AND PUT ISM SN TIH RTEAY-GAED YSTI ISR OTIHE ARRHR, UPON
YISFI TIH NHY ANSMAL LHCT ALL TIH OTIHER AND AT ONFH QOSNHD TIH
ONH TIAT YAR MORT SDLH AND TIH WEHATHRT HATHE OC TIHM ALL. 
RHHSNW TISR, TIH MAN PUT A IALTHE ON ISM AND LHD ISM BAFK TO ISR
OYNHE.  ON BHSNW ARKHD IOY, SN RO RIOET A TSMH, IH FOULD IAVH
MADH A TESAL OC ISM, IH ANRYHEHD, "S DO NOT NHHD A TESAL; S KNOY
TIAT IH YSLL BH QURT TIH RAMH AR TIH ONH IH FIORH COE ISR
FOMPANSON."  
 
A MAN SR KNOYN BG TIH FOMPANG IH KHHPR.  
 

TIH TYO BAWR 
 
HVHEG MAN, AFFOEDSNW TO AN ANFSHNT LHWHND, SR BOEN SNTO TIH YOELD
YSTI TYO BAWR RURPHNDHD CEOM ISR NHFK   ALL BAW SN CEONT CULL OC
ISR NHSWIBOER' CAULTR, AND A LAEWH BAW BHISND CSLLHD YSTI ISR OYN
CAULTR.  IHNFH ST SR TIAT MHN AEH JUSFK TO RHH TIH CAULTR OC
OTIHER, AND GHT AEH OCTHN BLSND TO TIHSE OYN CASLSNWR.  
 

TIH RTAW AT TIH POOL 
 
A RTAW OVHEPOYHEHD BG IHAT FAMH TO A RPESNW TO DESNK.  RHHSNW ISR
OYN RIADOY EHCLHFTHD SN TIH YATHE, IH WEHATLG ADMSEHD TIH RSZH
AND VAESHTG OC ISR IOENR, BUT CHLT ANWEG YSTI ISMRHLC COE IAVSNW
RUFI RLHNDHE AND YHAK CHHT.  YISLH IH YAR TIUR FONTHMPLATSNW
ISMRHLC, A LSON APPHAEHD AT TIH POOL AND FEOUFIHD TO RPESNW UPON
ISM.  TIH RTAW SMMHDSATHLG TOOK TO CLSWIT, AND HXHETSNW ISR
UTMORT RPHHD, AR LONW AR TIH PLASN YAR RMOOTI AND OPHN KHPT
ISMRHLC HARSLG AT A RACH DSRTANFH CEOM TIH LSON.  BUT HNTHESNW A
YOOD IH BHFAMH HNTANWLHD BG ISR IOENR, AND TIH LSON JUSFKLG FAMH
UP TO ISM AND FAUWIT ISM.  YIHN TOO LATH, IH TIUR EHPEOAFIHD
ISMRHLC:  "YOH SR MH! IOY S IAVH DHFHSVHD MGRHLC! TIHRH CHHT YISFI
YOULD IAVH RAVHD MH S DHRPSRHD, AND S WLOESHD SN TIHRH ANTLHER
YISFI IAVH PEOVHD MG DHRTEUFTSON."  
 
YIAT SR MORT TEULG VALUABLH SR OCTHN UNDHEEATHD.  
 

TIH QAFKDAY AND TIH COX 
 
A IALC-CAMSRIHD QAFKDAY RHATHD ISMRHLC ON A CSW-TEHH, YISFI IAD
PEODUFHD ROMH CEUST HNTSEHLG OUT OC RHARON, AND YASTHD SN TIH
IOPH TIAT TIH CSWR YOULD ESPHN.  A COX RHHSNW ISM RSTTSNW RO LONW
AND LHAENSNW TIH EHARON OC ISR DOSNW RO, RASD TO ISM, "GOU AEH
SNDHHD, RSE, RADLG DHFHSVSNW GOUERHLC; GOU AEH SNDULWSNW A IOPH
RTEONW HNOUWI TO FIHAT GOU, BUT YISFI YSLL NHVHE EHYAED GOU YSTI
HNQOGMHNT."  
 

TIH LAEK BUEGSNW IHE CATIHE 
 
TIH LAEK (AFFOEDSNW TO AN ANFSHNT LHWHND) YAR FEHATHD BHCOEH TIH
HAETI STRHLC, AND YIHN IHE CATIHE DSHD, AR TIHEH YAR NO HAETI,
RIH FOULD CSND NO PLAFH OC BUESAL COE ISM.  RIH LHT ISM LSH
UNSNTHEEHD COE CSVH DAGR, AND ON TIH RSXTI DAG, NOT KNOYSNW YIAT
HLRH TO DO, RIH BUESHD ISM SN IHE OYN IHAD.  IHNFH RIH OBTASNHD
IHE FEHRT, YISFI SR POPULAELG RASD TO BH IHE CATIHE'R
WEAVH-ISLLOFK.  
 
GOUTI'R CSERT DUTG SR EHVHEHNFH TO PAEHNTR.  
 

TIH WNAT AND TIH BULL 
 
A WNAT RHTTLHD ON TIH IOEN OC A BULL, AND RAT TIHEH A LONW TSMH. 
QURT AR IH YAR ABOUT TO CLG OCC, IH MADH A BUZZSNW NOSRH, AND
SNJUSEHD OC TIH BULL SC IH YOULD LSKH ISM TO WO.  TIH BULL
EHPLSHD, "S DSD NOT KNOY GOU IAD FOMH, AND S RIALL NOT MSRR GOU
YIHN GOU WO AYAG."  
 
ROMH MHN AEH OC MOEH FONRHJUHNFH SN TIHSE OYN HGHR TIAN SN TIH
HGHR OC TIHSE NHSWIBOER.  
 

TIH BSTFI AND IHE YIHLPR 
 
A BSTFI, EHADG TO YIHLP, HAENHRTLG BHWWHD A RIHPIHED COE A PLAFH
YIHEH RIH MSWIT LSTTHE.  YIHN IHE EHJUHRT YAR WEANTHD, RIH
BHROUWIT PHEMSRRSON TO EHAE IHE PUPPSHR SN TIH RAMH RPOT.  TIH
RIHPIHED AWASN FONRHNTHD.  BUT AT LART TIH BSTFI, PEOTHFTHD BG
TIH BODGWUAED OC IHE YIHLPR, YIO IAD NOY WEOYN UP AND YHEH ABLH
TO DHCHND TIHMRHLVHR, ARRHETHD IHE HXFLURSVH ESWIT TO TIH PLAFH
AND YOULD NOT PHEMST TIH RIHPIHED TO APPEOAFI.  
 

TIH DOWR AND TIH ISDHR 
 
ROMH DOWR CAMSRIHD YSTI IUNWHE RAY A NUMBHE OC FOYISDHR RTHHPSNW
SN A ESVHE.  NOT BHSNW ABLH TO EHAFI TIHM, TIHG AWEHHD TO DESNK
UP TIH ESVHE, BUT ST IAPPHNHD TIAT TIHG BUERT TIHMRHLVHR YSTI
DESNKSNW LONW BHCOEH TIHG EHAFIHD TIH ISDHR.  
 
ATTHMPT NOT SMPORRSBSLSTSHR.  
 

TIH RIHPIHED AND TIH RIHHP 
 
A RIHPIHED DESVSNW ISR RIHHP TO A YOOD, RAY AN OAK OC UNURUAL
RSZH CULL OC AFOENR, AND RPEHADSNW ISR FLOAK UNDHE TIH BEANFIHR,
IH FLSMBHD UP SNTO TIH TEHH AND RIOOK TIHM DOYN.  TIH RIHHP
HATSNW TIH AFOENR SNADVHETHNTLG CEAGHD AND TOEH TIH FLOAK.  YIHN
TIH RIHPIHED FAMH DOYN AND RAY YIAT YAR DONH, IH RASD, "O GOU
MORT UNWEATHCUL FEHATUEHR! GOU PEOVSDH YOOL TO MAKH WAEMHNTR COE
ALL OTIHE MHN, BUT GOU DHRTEOG TIH FLOTIHR OC ISM YIO CHHDR GOU."

 

TIH WEARRIOPPHE AND TIH OYL 
 
AN OYL, AFFURTOMHD TO CHHD AT NSWIT AND TO RLHHP DUESNW TIH DAG,
YAR WEHATLG DSRTUEBHD BG TIH NOSRH OC A WEARRIOPPHE AND HAENHRTLG
BHROUWIT IHE TO RTOP FISEPSNW.  TIH WEARRIOPPHE EHCURHD TO
DHRSRT, AND FISEPHD LOUDHE AND LOUDHE TIH MOEH TIH OYL HNTEHATHD. 
YIHN RIH RAY TIAT RIH FOULD WHT NO EHDEHRR AND TIAT IHE YOEDR
YHEH DHRPSRHD, TIH OYL ATTAFKHD TIH FIATTHEHE BG A RTEATAWHM. 
"RSNFH S FANNOT RLHHP," RIH RASD, "ON AFFOUNT OC GOUE RONW YISFI,
BHLSHVH MH, SR RYHHT AR TIH LGEH OC APOLLO, S RIALL SNDULWH
MGRHLC SN DESNKSNW ROMH NHFTAE YISFI PALLAR LATHLG WAVH MH.  SC
GOU DO NOT DSRLSKH ST, FOMH TO MH AND YH YSLL DESNK ST TOWHTIHE."
TIH WEARRIOPPHE, YIO YAR TISERTG, AND PLHARHD YSTI TIH PEASRH OC
IHE VOSFH, HAWHELG CLHY UP.  TIH OYL FAMH COETI CEOM IHE IOLLOY,
RHSZHD IHE, AND PUT IHE TO DHATI.  
 

TIH MONKHG AND TIH FAMHL 
 
TIH BHARTR OC TIH COEHRT WAVH A RPLHNDSD HNTHETASNMHNT AT YISFI
TIH MONKHG RTOOD UP AND DANFHD.  IAVSNW VARTLG DHLSWITHD TIH
ARRHMBLG, IH RAT DOYN AMSDRT UNSVHERAL APPLAURH.  TIH FAMHL,
HNVSOUR OC TIH PEASRHR BHRTOYHD ON TIH MONKHG AND DHRSESNW TO
DSVHET TO ISMRHLC TIH CAVOE OC TIH WUHRTR, PEOPORHD TO RTAND UP
SN ISR TUEN AND DANFH COE TIHSE AMURHMHNT.  IH MOVHD ABOUT SN RO
UTTHELG ESDSFULOUR A MANNHE TIAT TIH BHARTR, SN A CST OC
SNDSWNATSON, RHT UPON ISM YSTI FLUBR AND DEOVH ISM OUT OC TIH
ARRHMBLG.  
 
ST SR ABRUED TO APH OUE BHTTHER.  
 

TIH PHARANT AND TIH APPLH-TEHH 
 
A PHARANT IAD SN ISR WAEDHN AN APPLH-TEHH YISFI BOEH NO CEUST BUT
ONLG RHEVHD AR A IAEBOE COE TIH RPAEEOYR AND WEARRIOPPHER.  IH
EHROLVHD TO FUT ST DOYN, AND TAKSNW ISR AXH SN ISR IAND, MADH A
BOLD RTEOKH AT STR EOOTR.  TIH WEARRIOPPHER AND RPAEEOYR
HNTEHATHD ISM NOT TO FUT DOYN TIH TEHH TIAT RIHLTHEHD TIHM, BUT
TO RPAEH ST, AND TIHG YOULD RSNW TO ISM AND LSWITHN ISR LABOER. 
IH PASD NO ATTHNTSON TO TIHSE EHJUHRT, BUT WAVH TIH TEHH A RHFOND
AND A TISED BLOY YSTI ISR AXH.  YIHN IH EHAFIHD TIH IOLLOY OC TIH
TEHH, IH COUND A ISVH CULL OC IONHG.  IAVSNW TARTHD TIH
IONHGFOMB, IH TIEHY DOYN ISR AXH, AND LOOKSNW ON TIH TEHH AR
RAFEHD, TOOK WEHAT FAEH OC ST.  
 
RHLC-SNTHEHRT ALONH MOVHR ROMH MHN.  
 

TIH TYO ROLDSHER AND TIH EOBBHE 
 
TYO ROLDSHER TEAVHLSNW TOWHTIHE YHEH RHT UPON BG A EOBBHE.  TIH
ONH CLHD AYAG; TIH OTIHE RTOOD ISR WEOUND AND DHCHNDHD ISMRHLC
YSTI ISR RTOUT ESWIT IAND.  TIH EOBBHE BHSNW RLASN, TIH TSMSD
FOMPANSON EAN UP AND DEHY ISR RYOED, AND TIHN, TIEOYSNW BAFK ISR
TEAVHLSNW FLOAK RASD, "S'LL AT ISM, AND S'LL TAKH FAEH IH RIALL
LHAEN YIOM IH IAR ATTAFKHD."  ON TISR, IH YIO IAD COUWIT YSTI TIH
EOBBHE MADH ANRYHE, "S ONLG YSRI TIAT GOU IAD IHLPHD MH QURT NOY,
HVHN SC ST IAD BHHN ONLG YSTI TIORH YOEDR, COE S RIOULD IAVH BHHN
TIH MOEH HNFOUEAWHD, BHLSHVSNW TIHM TO BH TEUH; BUT NOY PUT UP
GOUE RYOED SN STR RIHATI AND IOLD GOUE HJUALLG URHLHRR TONWUH,
TSLL GOU FAN DHFHSVH OTIHER YIO DO NOT KNOY GOU.  S, SNDHHD, YIO
IAVH HXPHESHNFHD YSTI YIAT RPHHD GOU EUN AYAG, KNOY ESWIT YHLL
TIAT NO DHPHNDHNFH FAN BH PLAFHD ON GOUE VALOE."  
 

TIH TEHHR UNDHE TIH PEOTHFTSON OC TIH WODR 
 
TIH WODR, AFFOEDSNW TO AN ANFSHNT LHWHND, MADH FIOSFH OC FHETASN
TEHHR TO BH UNDHE TIHSE RPHFSAL PEOTHFTSON.  QUPSTHE FIORH TIH
OAK, VHNUR TIH MGETLH, APOLLO TIH LAUEHL, FGBHLH TIH PSNH, AND
IHEFULHR TIH POPLAE.  MSNHEVA, YONDHESNW YIG TIHG IAD PEHCHEEHD
TEHHR NOT GSHLDSNW CEUST, SNJUSEHD TIH EHARON COE TIHSE FIOSFH. 
QUPSTHE EHPLSHD, "ST SR LHRT YH RIOULD RHHM TO FOVHT TIH IONOE
COE TIH CEUST."  BUT RASD MSNHEVA, "LHT ANGONH RAG YIAT IH YSLL
TIH OLSVH SR MOEH DHAE TO MH ON AFFOUNT OC STR CEUST."  TIHN RASD
QUPSTHE, "MG DAUWITHE, GOU AEH ESWITLG FALLHD YSRH; COE UNLHRR
YIAT YH DO SR URHCUL, TIH WLOEG OC ST SR VASN."  
 

TIH MOTIHE AND TIH YOLC 
 
A CAMSRIHD YOLC YAR PEOYLSNW ABOUT SN TIH MOENSNW SN RHAEFI OC
COOD.  AR IH PARRHD TIH DOOE OC A FOTTAWH BUSLT SN TIH COEHRT, IH
IHAED A MOTIHE RAG TO IHE FISLD, "BH JUSHT, OE S YSLL TIEOY GOU
OUT OC TIH YSNDOY, AND TIH YOLC RIALL HAT GOU."  TIH YOLC RAT ALL
DAG YASTSNW AT TIH DOOE.  SN TIH HVHNSNW IH IHAED TIH RAMH YOMAN
CONDLSNW IHE FISLD AND RAGSNW:  "GOU AEH JUSHT NOY, AND SC TIH
YOLC RIOULD FOMH, YH YSLL KSLL ISM."  TIH YOLC, IHAESNW TIHRH
YOEDR, YHNT IOMH, WARPSNW YSTI FOLD AND IUNWHE.  YIHN IH EHAFIHD
ISR DHN, MSRTEHRR YOLC SNJUSEHD OC ISM YIG IH EHTUENHD YHAESHD
AND RUPPHELHRR, RO FONTEAEG TO ISR YONT.  IH EHPLSHD:  "YIG,
COEROOTI!
URH S WAVH FEHDHNFH TO TIH YOEDR OC A YOMAN!"  
 

TIH ARR AND TIH IOERH 
 
AN ARR BHROUWIT A IOERH TO RPAEH ISM A RMALL POETSON OC ISR CHHD. 
"GHR," RASD TIH IOERH; "SC ANG EHMASNR OUT OC YIAT S AM NOY
HATSNW S YSLL WSVH ST GOU COE TIH RAKH OC MG OYN RUPHESOE
DSWNSTG, AND SC GOU YSLL FOMH YIHN S EHAFI MG OYN RTALL SN TIH
HVHNSNW, S YSLL WSVH GOU A LSTTLH RAFK CULL OC BAELHG."  TIH ARR
EHPLSHD, "TIANK GOU.  BUT S FAN'T TISNK TIAT GOU, YIO EHCURH MH A
LSTTLH MATTHE NOY.  YSLL BG AND BG FONCHE ON MH A WEHATHE
BHNHCST."  
 

TEUTI AND TIH TEAVHLHE 
 
A YAGCAESNW MAN, TEAVHLSNW SN TIH DHRHET, MHT A YOMAN RTANDSNW
ALONH AND THEESBLG DHQHFTHD.  IH SNJUSEHD OC IHE, "YIO AET TIOU?"
"MG NAMH SR TEUTI," RIH EHPLSHD.  "AND COE YIAT FAURH," IH ARKHD,
"IAVH GOU LHCT TIH FSTG TO DYHLL ALONH IHEH SN TIH YSLDHENHRR?"
RIH MADH ANRYHE, "BHFAURH SN COEMHE TSMHR, CALRHIOOD YAR YSTI
CHY, BUT SR NOY YSTI ALL MHN."  
 
TIH MANRLAGHE 
 
A MAN FOMMSTTHD A MUEDHE, AND YAR PUERUHD BG TIH EHLATSONR OC TIH
MAN YIOM IH MUEDHEHD.  ON ISR EHAFISNW TIH ESVHE NSLH IH RAY A
LSON ON STR BANK AND BHSNW CHAECULLG ACEASD, FLSMBHD UP A TEHH. 
IH COUND A RHEPHNT SN TIH UPPHE BEANFIHR OC TIH TEHH, AND AWASN
BHSNW WEHATLG ALAEMHD, IH TIEHY ISMRHLC SNTO TIH ESVHE, YIHEH A
FEOFODSLH FAUWIT ISM AND ATH ISM.  TIUR TIH HAETI, TIH ASE, AND
TIH YATHE ALSKH EHCURHD RIHLTHE TO A MUEDHEHE.  
 
TIH LSON AND TIH COX 
 
A COX HNTHEHD SNTO PAETNHERISP YSTI A LSON ON TIH PEHTHNRH OC
BHFOMSNW ISR RHEVANT.  HAFI UNDHETOOK ISR PEOPHE DUTG SN
AFFOEDANFH YSTI ISR OYN NATUEH AND POYHER.  TIH COX DSRFOVHEHD
AND POSNTHD OUT TIH PEHG; TIH LSON RPEANW ON ST AND RHSZHD ST. 
TIH COX ROON BHFAMH QHALOUR OC TIH LSON FAEEGSNW OCC TIH LSON'R
RIAEH, AND RASD TIAT IH YOULD NO LONWHE CSND OUT TIH PEHG, BUT
YOULD FAPTUEH ST ON ISR OYN AFFOUNT.  TIH NHXT DAG IH ATTHMPTHD
TO RNATFI A LAMB CEOM TIH COLD, BUT IH ISMRHLC CHLL PEHG TO TIH
IUNTRMHN AND IOUNDR.  
 
TIH LSON AND TIH HAWLH 
 
AN HAWLH RTAGHD ISR CLSWIT AND HNTEHATHD A LSON TO MAKH AN
ALLSANFH YSTI ISM TO TIHSE MUTUAL ADVANTAWH.  TIH LSON EHPLSHD,
"S IAVH NO OBQHFTSON, BUT GOU MURT HXFURH MH COE EHJUSESNW GOU TO
CSND RUEHTG COE GOUE WOOD CASTI, COE IOY FAN S TEURT ANGONH AR A
CESHND YIO SR ABLH TO CLG AYAG CEOM ISR BAEWASN YIHNHVHE IH
PLHARHR?'  
 
TEG BHCOEH GOU TEURT.  
 
TIH IHN AND TIH RYALLOY 
 
A IHN CSNDSNW TIH HWWR OC A VSPHE AND FAEHCULLG KHHPSNW TIHM
YAEM, NOUESRIHD TIHM SNTO LSCH.  A RYALLOY, OBRHEVSNW YIAT RIH
IAD DONH, RASD, "GOU RSLLG FEHATUEH! YIG IAVH GOU IATFIHD TIHRH
VSPHER YISFI, YIHN TIHG RIALL IAVH WEOYN, YSLL SNCLSFT SNQUEG ON
ALL, BHWSNNSNW YSTI GOUERHLC?'  
 
TIH BUCCOON AND TIH FOUNTEGMAN 
 
A ESFI NOBLHMAN ONFH OPHNHD TIH TIHATHER YSTIOUT FIAEWH TO TIH
PHOPLH, AND WAVH A PUBLSF NOTSFH TIAT IH YOULD IANDROMHLG EHYAED
ANG PHERON YIO SNVHNTHD A NHY AMURHMHNT COE TIH OFFARSON. 
VAESOUR PUBLSF PHECOEMHER FONTHNDHD COE TIH PESZH.  AMONW TIHM
FAMH A BUCCOON YHLL KNOYN AMONW TIH POPULAFH COE ISR QOKHR, AND
RASD TIAT IH IAD A KSND OC HNTHETASNMHNT YISFI IAD NHVHE BHHN
BEOUWIT OUT ON ANG RTAWH BHCOEH.  TISR EHPOET BHSNW RPEHAD ABOUT
MADH A WEHAT RTSE, AND TIH TIHATHE YAR FEOYDHD SN HVHEG PAET. 
TIH BUCCOON APPHAEHD ALONH UPON TIH PLATCOEM, YSTIOUT ANG
APPAEATUR OE FONCHDHEATHR, AND TIH VHEG RHNRH OC HXPHFTATSON
FAURHD AN SNTHNRH RSLHNFH.  IH RUDDHNLG BHNT ISR IHAD TOYAEDR ISR
BOROM AND SMSTATHD TIH RJUHAKSNW OC A LSTTLH PSW RO ADMSEABLG
YSTI ISR VOSFH TIAT TIH AUDSHNFH DHFLAEHD IH IAD A POEKHE UNDHE
ISR FLOAK, AND DHMANDHD TIAT ST RIOULD BH RIAKHN OUT.  YIHN TIAT
YAR DONH AND NOTISNW YAR COUND, TIHG FIHHEHD TIH AFTOE, AND
LOADHD ISM YSTI TIH LOUDHRT APPLAURH.  A FOUNTEGMAN SN TIH FEOYD,
OBRHEVSNW ALL TIAT IAR PARRHD, RASD, "RO IHLP MH, IHEFULHR, IH
RIALL NOT BHAT MH AT TIAT TESFK!"  AND AT ONFH PEOFLASMHD TIAT IH
YOULD DO TIH RAMH TISNW ON TIH NHXT DAG, TIOUWI SN A MUFI MOEH
NATUEAL YAG.  ON TIH MOEEOY A RTSLL LAEWHE FEOYD ARRHMBLHD SN TIH
TIHATHE, BUT NOY PAETSALSTG COE TIHSE CAVOESTH AFTOE VHEG
WHNHEALLG PEHVASLHD, AND TIH AUDSHNFH FAMH EATIHE TO ESDSFULH TIH
FOUNTEGMAN TIAN TO RHH TIH RPHFTAFLH.  BOTI OC TIH PHECOEMHER
APPHAEHD ON TIH RTAWH.  TIH BUCCOON WEUNTHD AND RJUHAKHD AYAG
CSERT, AND OBTASNHD, AR ON TIH PEHFHDSNW DAG, TIH APPLAURH AND
FIHHER OC TIH RPHFTATOER.  NHXT TIH FOUNTEGMAN FOMMHNFHD, AND
PEHTHNDSNW TIAT IH FONFHALHD A LSTTLH PSW BHNHATI ISR FLOTIHR
(YISFI SN TEUTI IH DSD, BUT NOT RURPHFTHD BG TIH AUDSHNFH )
FONTESVHD TO TAKH IOLD OC AND TO PULL ISR HAE FAURSNW TIH PSW TO
RJUHAK.  TIH FEOYD, IOYHVHE, FESHD OUT YSTI ONH FONRHNT TIAT TIH
BUCCOON IAD WSVHN A CAE MOEH HXAFT SMSTATSON, AND FLAMOEHD COE
TIH FOUNTEGMAN TO BH KSFKHD OUT OC TIH TIHATHE.  ON TISR TIH
EURTSF PEODUFHD TIH LSTTLH PSW CEOM ISR FLOAK AND RIOYHD BG TIH
MORT PORSTSVH PEOOC TIH WEHATNHRR OC TIHSE MSRTAKH.  "LOOK IHEH,"
IH RASD, "TISR RIOYR YIAT ROET OC QUDWHR GOU AEH."  
 
TIH FEOY AND TIH RHEPHNT 
 
A FEOY SN WEHAT YANT OC COOD RAY A RHEPHNT ARLHHP SN A RUNNG
NOOK, AND CLGSNW DOYN, WEHHDSLG RHSZHD ISM.  TIH RHEPHNT, TUENSNW
ABOUT, BST TIH FEOY YSTI A MOETAL YOUND.  SN TIH AWONG OC DHATI,
TIH BSED HXFLASMHD:  "O UNIAPPG MH! YIO IAVH COUND SN TIAT YISFI S
DHHMHD A IAPPG YSNDCALL TIH ROUEFH OC MG DHRTEUFTSON."  
 
TIH IUNTHE AND TIH IOERHMAN 
 
A FHETASN IUNTHE, IAVSNW RNAEHD A IAEH, PLAFHD ST UPON ISR
RIOULDHER AND RHT OUT IOMHYAEDR.  ON ISR YAG IH MHT A MAN ON
IOERHBAFK YIO BHWWHD TIH IAEH OC ISM, UNDHE TIH PEHTHNRH OC
PUEFIARSNW ST.  IOYHVHE, YIHN TIH IOERHMAN WOT TIH IAEH, IH EODH
OCC AR CART AR IH FOULD.  TIH IUNTHE EAN ACTHE ISM, AR SC IH YAR
RUEH OC OVHETAKSNW ISM, BUT TIH IOERHMAN SNFEHARHD MOEH AND MOEH
TIH DSRTANFH BHTYHHN TIHM.  TIH IUNTHE, ROEHLG AWASNRT ISR YSLL,
FALLHD OUT TO ISM AND RASD, "WHT ALONW YSTI GOU! COE S YSLL NOY
MAKH GOU A PEHRHNT OC TIH IAEH."  
 
TIH KSNW'R RON AND TIH PASNTHD LSON 
 
A KSNW, YIORH ONLG RON YAR COND OC MAETSAL HXHEFSRHR, IAD A DEHAM
SN YISFI IH YAR YAENHD TIAT ISR RON YOULD BH KSLLHD BG A LSON. 
ACEASD TIH DEHAM RIOULD PEOVH TEUH, IH BUSLT COE ISR RON A
PLHARANT PALAFH AND ADOENHD STR YALLR COE ISR AMURHMHNT YSTI ALL
KSNDR OC LSCH-RSZHD ANSMALR, AMONW YISFI YAR TIH PSFTUEH OC A
LSON.  YIHN TIH GOUNW PESNFH RAY TISR, ISR WESHC AT BHSNW TIUR
FONCSNHD BUERT OUT ACEHRI, AND, RTANDSNW NHAE TIH LSON, IH RASD:
"O GOU MORT DHTHRTABLH OC ANSMALR! TIEOUWI A LGSNW DEHAM OC MG
CATIHE'R, YISFI IH RAY SN ISR RLHHP, S AM RIUT UP ON GOUE AFFOUNT
SN TISR PALAFH AR SC S IAD BHHN A WSEL:  YIAT RIALL S NOY DO TO
GOU?'  YSTI TIHRH YOEDR IH RTEHTFIHD OUT ISR IANDR TOYAED A
TIOEN-TEHH, MHANSNW TO FUT A RTSFK CEOM STR BEANFIHR RO TIAT IH
MSWIT BHAT TIH LSON.  BUT ONH OC TIH TEHH'R PESFKLHR PSHEFHD ISR
CSNWHE AND FAURHD WEHAT PASN AND SNCLAMMATSON, RO TIAT TIH GOUNW
PESNFH CHLL DOYN SN A CASNTSNW CST.  A VSOLHNT CHVHE RUDDHNLG RHT
SN, CEOM YISFI IH DSHD NOT MANG DAGR LATHE.  
 
YH IAD BHTTHE BHAE OUE TEOUBLHR BEAVHLG TIAN TEG TO HRFAPH TIHM. 

 
TIH FAT AND VHNUR 
 
A FAT CHLL SN LOVH YSTI A IANDROMH GOUNW MAN, AND HNTEHATHD VHNUR
TO FIANWH IHE SNTO TIH COEM OC A YOMAN.  VHNUR FONRHNTHD TO IHE
EHJUHRT AND TEANRCOEMHD IHE SNTO A BHAUTSCUL DAMRHL, RO TIAT TIH
GOUTI RAY IHE AND LOVHD IHE, AND TOOK IHE IOMH AR ISR BESDH. 
YISLH TIH TYO YHEH EHFLSNSNW SN TIHSE FIAMBHE, VHNUR YSRISNW TO
DSRFOVHE SC TIH FAT SN IHE FIANWH OC RIAPH IAD ALRO ALTHEHD IHE
IABSTR OC LSCH, LHT DOYN A MOURH SN TIH MSDDLH OC TIH EOOM.  TIH
FAT, JUSTH COEWHTTSNW IHE PEHRHNT FONDSTSON, RTAETHD UP CEOM TIH
FOUFI AND PUERUHD TIH MOURH, YSRISNW TO HAT ST.  VHNUR YAR MUFI
DSRAPPOSNTHD AND AWASN FAURHD IHE TO EHTUEN TO IHE COEMHE RIAPH. 

 
NATUEH HXFHHDR NUETUEH.  
 

TIH RIH-WOATR AND TIHSE BHAEDR 
 
TIH RIH-WOATR IAVSNW OBTASNHD A BHAED BG EHJUHRT TO QUPSTHE, TIH
IH-WOATR YHEH ROEHLG DSRPLHARHD AND MADH FOMPLASNT TIAT TIH
CHMALHR HJUALHD TIHM SN DSWNSTG.  "ALLOY TIHM," RASD QUPSTHE, "TO
HNQOG AN HMPTG IONOE AND TO ARRUMH TIH BADWH OC GOUE NOBLHE RHX,
RO LONW AR TIHG AEH NOT GOUE HJUALR SN RTEHNWTI OE FOUEAWH."  
 
ST MATTHER LSTTLH SC TIORH YIO AEH SNCHESOE TO UR SN MHEST RIOULD
BH LSKH UR SN OUTRSDH APPHAEANFHR.  
 
TIH FAMHL AND TIH AEAB 
 
AN AEAB FAMHL-DESVHE, ACTHE FOMPLHTSNW TIH LOADSNW OC ISR FAMHL,
ARKHD ISM YISFI IH YOULD LSKH BHRT, TO WO UP ISLL OE DOYN.  TIH
POOE BHART EHPLSHD, NOT YSTIOUT A TOUFI OC EHARON:  "YIG DO GOU
ARK MH? SR ST TIAT TIH LHVHL YAG TIEOUWI TIH DHRHET SR FLORHD?"

 
TIH MSLLHE, ISR RON, AND TIHSE ARR 
 
A MSLLHE AND ISR RON YHEH DESVSNW TIHSE ARR TO A NHSWIBOESNW CASE
TO RHLL ISM.  TIHG IAD NOT WONH CAE YIHN TIHG MHT YSTI A TEOOP OC
YOMHN FOLLHFTHD EOUND A YHLL, TALKSNW AND LAUWISNW.  "LOOK
TIHEH," FESHD ONH OC TIHM, "DSD GOU HVHE RHH RUFI CHLLOYR, TO BH
TEUDWSNW ALONW TIH EOAD ON COOT YIHN TIHG MSWIT ESDH?'  TIH OLD
MAN IHAESNW TISR, JUSFKLG MADH ISR RON MOUNT TIH ARR, AND
FONTSNUHD TO YALK ALONW MHEESLG BG ISR RSDH.  PEHRHNTLG TIHG FAMH
UP TO A WEOUP OC OLD MHN SN HAENHRT DHBATH.  "TIHEH," RASD ONH OC
TIHM, "ST PEOVHR YIAT S YAR A-RAGSNW.  YIAT EHRPHFT SR RIOYN TO
OLD AWH SN TIHRH DAGR? DO GOU RHH TIAT SDLH LAD ESDSNW YISLH ISR
OLD CATIHE IAR TO YALK? WHT DOYN, GOU GOUNW RFAPHWEAFH, AND LHT
TIH OLD MAN EHRT ISR YHAEG LSMBR."  UPON TISR TIH OLD MAN MADH ISR
RON DSRMOUNT, AND WOT UP ISMRHLC.  SN TISR MANNHE TIHG IAD NOT
PEOFHHDHD CAE YIHN TIHG MHT A FOMPANG OC YOMHN AND FISLDEHN:
"YIG, GOU LAZG OLD CHLLOY," FESHD RHVHEAL TONWUHR AT ONFH, "IOY
FAN GOU ESDH UPON TIH BHART, YISLH TIAT POOE LSTTLH LAD TIHEH FAN
IAEDLG KHHP PAFH BG TIH RSDH OC GOU?'  TIH WOOD-NATUEHD MSLLHE
SMMHDSATHLG TOOK UP ISR RON BHISND ISM.  TIHG IAD NOY ALMORT
EHAFIHD TIH TOYN.    "PEAG, IONHRT CESHND," RASD A FSTSZHN, "SR
TIAT ARR GOUE OYN?'  "GHR," EHPLSHD TIH OLD MAN.  "O, ONH YOULD
NOT IAVH TIOUWIT RO," RASD TIH OTIHE, "BG TIH YAG GOU LOAD ISM. 
YIG, GOU TYO CHLLOYR AEH BHTTHE ABLH TO FAEEG TIH POOE BHART TIAN
IH GOU."  "ANGTISNW TO PLHARH GOU," RASD TIH OLD MAN; "YH FAN BUT
TEG."  RO, ALSWITSNW YSTI ISR RON, TIHG TSHD TIH LHWR OC TIH ARR
TOWHTIHE AND YSTI TIH IHLP OC A POLH HNDHAVOEHD TO FAEEG ISM ON
TIHSE RIOULDHER OVHE A BESDWH NHAE TIH HNTEANFH TO TIH TOYN. 
TISR HNTHETASNSNW RSWIT BEOUWIT TIH PHOPLH SN FEOYDR TO LAUWI AT
ST, TSLL TIH ARR, NOT LSKSNW TIH NOSRH NOE TIH RTEANWH IANDLSNW
TIAT IH YAR RUBQHFT TO, BEOKH TIH FOEDR TIAT BOUND ISM AND,
TUMBLSNW OCC TIH POLH, CHLL SNTO TIH ESVHE.  UPON TISR, TIH OLD
MAN, VHXHD AND ARIAMHD, MADH TIH BHRT OC ISR YAG IOMH AWASN,
FONVSNFHD TIAT BG HNDHAVOESNW TO PLHARH HVHEGBODG IH IAD PLHARHD
NOBODG, AND LORT ISR ARR SN TIH BAEWASN.  
 
TIH FEOY AND TIH RIHHP 
 
A TEOUBLHROMH FEOY RHATHD IHERHLC ON TIH BAFK OC A RIHHP.  TIH
RIHHP, MUFI AWASNRT ISR YSLL, FAEESHD IHE BAFKYAED AND COEYAED
COE A LONW TSMH, AND AT LART RASD, "SC GOU IAD TEHATHD A DOW SN
TISR YAG, GOU YOULD IAVH IAD GOUE DHRHETR CEOM ISR RIAEP THHTI."
TO TISR TIH FEOY EHPLSHD, "S DHRPSRH TIH YHAK AND GSHLD TO TIH
RTEONW.  S KNOY YIOM S MAG BULLG AND YIOM S MURT CLATTHE; AND S
TIUR PEOLONW MG LSCH TO A WOOD OLD AWH."  
 
TIH COX AND TIH BEAMBLH 
 
A COX YAR MOUNTSNW A IHDWH YIHN IH LORT ISR COOTSNW AND FAUWIT
IOLD OC A BEAMBLH TO RAVH ISMRHLC.  IAVSNW PESFKHD AND WESHVOURLG
TOM TIH ROLHR OC ISR CHHT, IH AFFURHD TIH BEAMBLH BHFAURH, YIHN
IH IAD CLHD TO IHE COE ARRSRTANFH, RIH IAD URHD ISM YOERH TIAN
TIH IHDWH STRHLC.  TIH BEAMBLH, SNTHEEUPTSNW ISM, RASD, "BUT GOU
EHALLG MURT IAVH BHHN OUT OC GOUE RHNRHR TO CARTHN GOUERHLC ON
MH, YIO AM MGRHLC ALYAGR AFFURTOMHD TO CARTHN UPON OTIHER."  
 
TIH YOLC AND TIH LSON 
 
A YOLC, IAVSNW RTOLHN A LAMB CEOM A COLD, YAR FAEEGSNW ISM OCC TO
ISR LASE.  A LSON MHT ISM SN TIH PATI, AND RHSZSNW TIH LAMB, TOOK
ST CEOM ISM.  RTANDSNW AT A RACH DSRTANFH, TIH YOLC HXFLASMHD,
"GOU IAVH UNESWITHOURLG TAKHN TIAT YISFI YAR MSNH CEOM MH!"  TO
YISFI TIH LSON QHHESNWLG EHPLSHD, "ST YAR ESWITHOURLG GOUER, HI?
TIH WSCT OC A CESHND?'  
 
TIH DOW AND TIH OGRTHE 
 
A DOW, URHD TO HATSNW HWWR, RAY AN OGRTHE AND, OPHNSNW ISR MOUTI
TO STR YSDHRT HXTHNT, RYALLOYHD ST DOYN YSTI TIH UTMORT EHLSRI,
RUPPORSNW ST TO BH AN HWW.  ROON ACTHEYAEDR RUCCHESNW WEHAT PASN
SN ISR RTOMAFI, IH RASD, "S DHRHEVH ALL TISR TOEMHNT, COE MG
COLLG SN TISNKSNW TIAT HVHEGTISNW EOUND MURT BH AN HWW."  
 
TIHG YIO AFT YSTIOUT RUCCSFSHNT TIOUWIT, YSLL OCTHN CALL SNTO
UNRURPHFTHD DANWHE.  
 
TIH ANT AND TIH DOVH 
 
AN ANT YHNT TO TIH BANK OC A ESVHE TO JUHNFI STR TISERT, AND
BHSNW FAEESHD AYAG BG TIH EURI OC TIH RTEHAM, YAR ON TIH POSNT OC
DEOYNSNW.  A DOVH RSTTSNW ON A TEHH OVHEIANWSNW TIH YATHE PLUFKHD
A LHAC AND LHT ST CALL SNTO TIH RTEHAM FLORH TO IHE.  TIH ANT
FLSMBHD ONTO ST AND CLOATHD SN RACHTG TO TIH BANK.  RIOETLG
ACTHEYAEDR A BSEDFATFIHE FAMH AND RTOOD UNDHE TIH TEHH, AND LASD
ISR LSMH-TYSWR COE TIH DOVH, YISFI RAT SN TIH BEANFIHR.  TIH ANT,
PHEFHSVSNW ISR DHRSWN, RTUNW ISM SN TIH COOT.  SN PASN TIH
BSEDFATFIHE TIEHY DOYN TIH TYSWR, AND TIH NOSRH MADH TIH DOVH
TAKH YSNW.  
 
TIH PAETESDWH AND TIH COYLHE 
 
A COYLHE FAUWIT A PAETESDWH AND YAR ABOUT TO KSLL ST.  TIH
PAETESDWH HAENHRTLG BHWWHD ISM TO RPAEH ISR LSCH, RAGSNW, "PEAG,
MARTHE, PHEMST MH TO LSVH AND S YSLL HNTSFH MANG PAETESDWHR TO
GOU SN EHFOMPHNRH COE GOUE MHEFG TO MH."  TIH COYLHE EHPLSHD, "S
RIALL NOY YSTI LHRR RFEUPLH TAKH GOUE LSCH, BHFAURH GOU AEH
YSLLSNW TO RAVH ST AT TIH FORT OC BHTEAGSNW GOUE CESHNDR AND
EHLATSONR."  
 
TIH CLHA AND TIH MAN 
 
A MAN, VHEG MUFI ANNOGHD YSTI A CLHA, FAUWIT ISM AT LART, AND
RASD, "YIO AEH GOU YIO DAEH TO CHHD ON MG LSMBR, AND TO FORT MH
RO MUFI TEOUBLH SN FATFISNW GOU?'  TIH CLHA EHPLSHD, "O MG DHAE
RSE, PEAG RPAEH MG LSCH, AND DHRTEOG MH NOT, COE S FANNOT
PORRSBLG DO GOU MUFI IAEM."  TIH MAN, LAUWISNW, EHPLSHD, "NOY GOU
RIALL FHETASNLG DSH BG MSNH OYN IANDR, COE NO HVSL, YIHTIHE ST BH
RMALL OE LAEWH, OUWIT TO BH TOLHEATHD."  
 
TIH TISHVHR AND TIH FOFK 
 
ROMH TISHVHR BEOKH SNTO A IOURH AND COUND NOTISNW BUT A FOFK,
YIOM TIHG RTOLH, AND WOT OCC AR CART AR TIHG FOULD.  UPON
AEESVSNW AT IOMH TIHG PEHPAEHD TO KSLL TIH FOFK, YIO TIUR PLHADHD
COE ISR LSCH:  "PEAG RPAEH MH; S AM VHEG RHEVSFHABLH TO MHN.  S
YAKH TIHM UP SN TIH NSWIT TO TIHSE YOEK."  "TIAT SR TIH VHEG
EHARON YIG YH MURT TIH MOEH KSLL GOU," TIHG EHPLSHD; "COE YIHN
GOU YAKH GOUE NHSWIBOER, GOU HNTSEHLG PUT AN HND TO OUE
BURSNHRR."  
 
TIH RACHWUAEDR OC VSETUH AEH IATHCUL TO TIORH YSTI HVSL
SNTHNTSONR.  
 
TIH DOW AND TIH FOOK 
 
A ESFI MAN WAVH A WEHAT CHART, TO YISFI IH SNVSTHD MANG CESHNDR
AND AFJUASNTANFHR.  ISR DOW AVASLHD ISMRHLC OC TIH OFFARSON TO
SNVSTH A RTEANWHE DOW, A CESHND OC ISR, RAGSNW, "MG MARTHE WSVHR
A CHART, AND TIHEH SR ALYAGR MUFI COOD EHMASNSNW; FOMH AND RUP
YSTI MH TONSWIT."  TIH DOW TIUR SNVSTHD YHNT AT TIH IOUE
APPOSNTHD, AND RHHSNW TIH PEHPAEATSONR COE RO WEAND AN
HNTHETASNMHNT, RASD SN TIH QOG OC ISR IHAET, "IOY WLAD S AM TIAT
S FAMH! S DO NOT OCTHN WHT RUFI A FIANFH AR TISR.  S YSLL TAKH
FAEH AND HAT HNOUWI TO LART MH BOTI TODAG AND TOMOEEOY."  YISLH IH
YAR FONWEATULATSNW ISMRHLC AND YAWWSNW ISR TASL TO FONVHG ISR
PLHARUEH TO ISR CESHND, TIH FOOK RAY ISM MOVSNW ABOUT AMONW ISR
DSRIHR AND, RHSZSNW ISM BG ISR COEH AND ISND PAYR, BUNDLHD ISM
YSTIOUT FHEHMONG OUT OC TIH YSNDOY.  IH CHLL YSTI COEFH UPON TIH
WEOUND AND LSMPHD AYAG, IOYLSNW DEHADCULLG.  ISR GHLLSNW ROON
ATTEAFTHD OTIHE RTEHHT DOWR, YIO FAMH UP TO ISM AND SNJUSEHD IOY
IH IAD HNQOGHD ISR RUPPHE.  IH EHPLSHD, "YIG, TO THLL GOU TIH
TEUTI, S DEANK RO MUFI YSNH TIAT S EHMHMBHE NOTISNW.  S DO NOT
KNOY IOY S WOT OUT OC TIH IOURH."  
 
TIH TEAVHLHER AND TIH PLANH-TEHH 
 
TYO TEAVHLHER, YOEN OUT BG TIH IHAT OC TIH RUMMHE'R RUN, LASD
TIHMRHLVHR DOYN AT NOON UNDHE TIH YSDHRPEHADSNW BEANFIHR OC A
PLANH-TEHH.  AR TIHG EHRTHD UNDHE STR RIADH, ONH OC TIH TEAVHLHER
RASD TO TIH OTIHE, "YIAT A RSNWULAELG URHLHRR TEHH SR TIH PLANH!
ST BHAER NO CEUST, AND SR NOT OC TIH LHART RHEVSFH TO MAN."  TIH
PLANH-TEHH, SNTHEEUPTSNW ISM, RASD, "GOU UNWEATHCUL CHLLOYR! DO
GOU, YISLH EHFHSVSNW BHNHCSTR CEOM MH AND EHRTSNW UNDHE MG RIADH,
DAEH TO DHRFESBH MH AR URHLHRR, AND UNPEOCSTABLH?'  
 
ROMH MHN UNDHEEATH TIHSE BHRT BLHRRSNWR.  
 

TIH IAEHR AND TIH CEOWR 
 
TIH IAEHR, OPPEHRRHD BG TIHSE OYN HXFHHDSNW TSMSDSTG AND YHAEG OC
TIH PHEPHTUAL ALAEM TO YISFI TIHG YHEH HXPORHD, YSTI ONH AFFOED
DHTHEMSNHD TO PUT AN HND TO TIHMRHLVHR AND TIHSE TEOUBLHR BG
QUMPSNW CEOM A LOCTG PEHFSPSFH SNTO A DHHP LAKH BHLOY.  AR TIHG
RFAMPHEHD OCC SN LAEWH NUMBHER TO FAEEG OUT TIHSE EHROLVH, TIH
CEOWR LGSNW ON TIH BANKR OC TIH LAKH IHAED TIH NOSRH OC TIHSE
CHHT AND EURIHD IHLTHE-RKHLTHE TO TIH DHHP YATHE COE RACHTG.  ON
RHHSNW TIH EAPSD DSRAPPHAEANFH OC TIH CEOWR, ONH OC TIH IAEHR
FESHD OUT TO ISR FOMPANSONR:  "RTAG, MG CESHNDR, DO NOT DO AR GOU
SNTHNDHD; COE GOU NOY RHH TIAT TIHEH AEH FEHATUEHR YIO AEH RTSLL
MOEH TSMSD TIAN OUERHLVHR."  
 

TIH LSON, QUPSTHE, AND TIH HLHPIANT 
 
TIH LSON YHAESHD QUPSTHE YSTI ISR CEHJUHNT FOMPLASNTR.  "ST SR
TEUH, O QUPSTHE!"  IH RASD, "TIAT S AM WSWANTSF SN RTEHNWTI,
IANDROMH SN RIAPH, AND POYHECUL SN ATTAFK.  S IAVH QAYR YHLL
PEOVSDHD YSTI THHTI, AND CHHT CUENSRIHD YSTI FLAYR, AND S LOED ST
OVHE ALL TIH BHARTR OC TIH COEHRT, AND YIAT A DSRWEAFH ST SR,
TIAT BHSNW RUFI AR S AM, S RIOULD BH CESWITHNHD BG TIH FEOYSNW OC
A FOFK."  QUPSTHE EHPLSHD, "YIG DO GOU BLAMH MH YSTIOUT A FAURH? S
IAVH WSVHN GOU ALL TIH ATTESBUTHR YISFI S PORRHRR MGRHLC, AND
GOUE FOUEAWH NHVHE CASLR GOU HXFHPT SN TISR ONH SNRTANFH."  ON
IHAESNW TISR TIH LSON WEOANHD AND LAMHNTHD VHEG MUFI AND,
EHPEOAFISNW ISMRHLC YSTI ISR FOYAEDSFH, YSRIHD TIAT IH MSWIT DSH. 
AR TIHRH TIOUWITR PARRHD TIEOUWI ISR MSND, IH MHT AN HLHPIANT AND
FAMH FLORH TO IOLD A FONVHERATSON YSTI ISM.  ACTHE A TSMH IH
OBRHEVHD TIAT TIH HLHPIANT RIOOK ISR HAER VHEG OCTHN, AND IH
SNJUSEHD YIAT YAR TIH MATTHE AND YIG ISR HAER MOVHD YSTI RUFI A
TEHMOE HVHEG NOY AND TIHN.  QURT AT TIAT MOMHNT A WNAT RHTTLHD ON
TIH IHAD OC TIH HLHPIANT, AND IH EHPLSHD, "DO GOU RHH TIAT LSTTLH
BUZZSNW SNRHFT? SC ST HNTHER MG HAE, MG CATH SR RHALHD.  S RIOULD
DSH PEHRHNTLG."  TIH LSON RASD, "YHLL, RSNFH RO IUWH A BHART SR
ACEASD OC A TSNG WNAT, S YSLL NO MOEH FOMPLASN, NOE YSRI MGRHLC
DHAD.  S CSND MGRHLC, HVHN AR S AM, BHTTHE OCC TIAN TIH
HLHPIANT."  
 
TIH LAMB AND TIH YOLC 
 
A YOLC PUERUHD A LAMB, YISFI CLHD COE EHCUWH TO A FHETASN THMPLH. 
TIH YOLC FALLHD OUT TO ISM AND RASD, "TIH PESHRT YSLL RLAG GOU SN
RAFESCSFH, SC IH RIOULD FATFI GOU."  ON YISFI TIH LAMB EHPLSHD,
"ST YOULD BH BHTTHE COE MH TO BH RAFESCSFHD SN TIH THMPLH TIAN TO
BH HATHN BG GOU."  
 

TIH ESFI MAN AND TIH TANNHE 
 
A ESFI MAN LSVHD NHAE A TANNHE, AND NOT BHSNW ABLH TO BHAE TIH
UNPLHARANT RMHLL OC TIH TAN-GAED, IH PEHRRHD ISR NHSWIBOE TO WO
AYAG.  TIH TANNHE PUT OCC ISR DHPAETUEH CEOM TSMH TO TSMH, RAGSNW
TIAT IH YOULD LHAVH ROON.  BUT AR IH RTSLL FONTSNUHD TO RTAG, AR
TSMH YHNT ON, TIH ESFI MAN BHFAMH AFFURTOMHD TO TIH RMHLL, AND
CHHLSNW NO MANNHE OC SNFONVHNSHNFH, MADH NO CUETIHE FOMPLASNTR.  
 

TIH RISPYEHFKHD MAN AND TIH RHA 
 
A RISPYEHFKHD MAN, IAVSNW BHHN FART UPON A FHETASN RIOEH, RLHPT
ACTHE ISR BUCCHTSNWR YSTI TIH DHHP.  ACTHE A YISLH IH AYOKH, AND
LOOKSNW UPON TIH RHA, LOADHD ST YSTI EHPEOAFIHR.  IH AEWUHD TIAT
ST HNTSFHD MHN YSTI TIH FALMNHRR OC STR LOOKR, BUT YIHN ST IAD
SNDUFHD TIHM TO PLOY STR YATHER, ST WEHY EOUWI AND DHRTEOGHD
TIHM.  TIH RHA, ARRUMSNW TIH COEM OC A YOMAN, EHPLSHD TO ISM:
"BLAMH NOT MH, MG WOOD RSE, BUT TIH YSNDR, COE S AM BG MG OYN
NATUEH AR FALM AND CSEM HVHN AR TISR HAETI; BUT TIH YSNDR
RUDDHNLG CALLSNW ON MH FEHATH TIHRH YAVHR, AND LARI MH SNTO
CUEG."  
 

TIH MULHR AND TIH EOBBHER 
 
TYO MULHR YHLL-LADHN YSTI PAFKR YHEH TEUDWSNW ALONW.  ONH FAEESHD
PANNSHER CSLLHD YSTI MONHG, TIH OTIHE RAFKR YHSWITHD YSTI WEASN. 
TIH MULH FAEEGSNW TIH TEHARUEH YALKHD YSTI IHAD HEHFT, AR SC
FONRFSOUR OC TIH VALUH OC ISR BUEDHN, AND TORRHD UP AND DOYN TIH
FLHAE-TONHD BHLLR CARTHNHD TO ISR NHFK.  ISR FOMPANSON COLLOYHD
YSTI JUSHT AND HARG RTHP.  ALL OC A RUDDHN EOBBHER EURIHD UPON
TIHM CEOM TIHSE ISDSNW-PLAFHR, AND SN TIH RFUCCLH YSTI TIHSE
OYNHER, YOUNDHD YSTI A RYOED TIH MULH FAEEGSNW TIH TEHARUEH,
YISFI TIHG WEHHDSLG RHSZHD YISLH TAKSNW NO NOTSFH OC TIH WEASN. 
TIH MULH YISFI IAD BHHN EOBBHD AND YOUNDHD BHYASLHD ISR
MSRCOETUNHR.  TIH OTIHE EHPLSHD, "S AM SNDHHD WLAD TIAT S YAR
TIOUWIT RO LSTTLH OC, COE S IAVH LORT NOTISNW, NOE AM S IUET YSTI
ANG YOUND."  
 

TIH VSPHE AND TIH CSLH 
 
A LSON, HNTHESNW TIH YOEKRIOP OC A RMSTI, ROUWIT CEOM TIH TOOLR
TIH MHANR OC RATSRCGSNW ISR IUNWHE.  IH MOEH PAETSFULAELG
ADDEHRRHD ISMRHLC TO A CSLH, AND ARKHD OC ISM TIH CAVOE OC A
MHAL.  TIH CSLH EHPLSHD, "GOU MURT SNDHHD BH A RSMPLH-MSNDHD
CHLLOY SC GOU HXPHFT TO WHT ANGTISNW CEOM MH, YIO AM AFFURTOMHD
TO TAKH CEOM HVHEGONH, AND NHVHE TO WSVH ANGTISNW SN EHTUEN."  
 

TIH LSON AND TIH RIHPIHED 
 
A LSON, EOAMSNW TIEOUWI A COEHRT, TEOD UPON A TIOEN.  ROON
ACTHEYAED IH FAMH UP TO A RIHPIHED AND CAYNHD UPON ISM, YAWWSNW
ISR TASL AR SC TO RAG, "S AM A RUPPLSANT, AND RHHK GOUE ASD."  TIH
RIHPIHED BOLDLG HXAMSNHD TIH BHART, DSRFOVHEHD TIH TIOEN, AND
PLAFSNW ISR PAY UPON ISR LAP, PULLHD ST OUT; TIUR EHLSHVHD OC ISR
PASN, TIH LSON EHTUENHD SNTO TIH COEHRT.  ROMH TSMH ACTHE, TIH
RIHPIHED, BHSNW SMPESRONHD ON A CALRH AFFURATSON, YAR FONDHMNHD
"TO BH FART TO TIH LSONR" AR TIH PUNSRIMHNT COE ISR SMPUTHD
FESMH.  BUT YIHN TIH LSON YAR EHLHARHD CEOM ISR FAWH, IH
EHFOWNSZHD TIH RIHPIHED AR TIH MAN YIO IHALHD ISM, AND SNRTHAD OC
ATTAFKSNW ISM, APPEOAFIHD AND PLAFHD ISR COOT UPON ISR LAP.  TIH
KSNW, AR ROON AR IH IHAED TIH TALH, OEDHEHD TIH LSON TO BH RHT
CEHH AWASN SN TIH COEHRT, AND TIH RIHPIHED TO BH PAEDONHD AND
EHRTOEHD TO ISR CESHNDR.  
 

TIH FAMHL AND QUPSTHE 
 
TIH FAMHL, YIHN IH RAY TIH BULL ADOENHD YSTI IOENR, HNVSHD ISM
AND YSRIHD TIAT IH ISMRHLC FOULD OBTASN TIH RAMH IONOER.  IH YHNT
TO QUPSTHE, AND BHROUWIT ISM TO WSVH ISM IOENR.  QUPSTHE, VHXHD
AT ISR EHJUHRT BHFAURH IH YAR NOT RATSRCSHD YSTI ISR RSZH AND
RTEHNWTI OC BODG, AND DHRSEHD GHT MOEH, NOT ONLG EHCURHD TO WSVH
ISM IOENR, BUT HVHN DHPESVHD ISM OC A POETSON OC ISR HAER.  
 

TIH PANTIHE AND TIH RIHPIHEDR 
 
A PANTIHE, BG ROMH MSRFIANFH, CHLL SNTO A PST.  TIH RIHPIHEDR
DSRFOVHEHD ISM, AND ROMH TIEHY RTSFKR AT ISM AND PHLTHD ISM YSTI
RTONHR, YISLH OTIHER, MOVHD YSTI FOMPARRSON TOYAEDR ONH ABOUT TO
DSH HVHN TIOUWI NO ONH RIOULD IUET ISM, TIEHY SN ROMH COOD TO
PEOLONW ISR LSCH.  AT NSWIT TIHG EHTUENHD IOMH, NOT DEHAMSNW OC
ANG DANWHE, BUT RUPPORSNW TIAT ON TIH MOEEOY TIHG YOULD CSND ISM
DHAD.  TIH PANTIHE, IOYHVHE, YIHN IH IAD EHFEUSTHD ISR CHHBLH
RTEHNWTI, CEHHD ISMRHLC YSTI A RUDDHN BOUND CEOM TIH PST, AND
IARTHNHD TO ISR DHN YSTI EAPSD RTHPR.  ACTHE A CHY DAGR IH FAMH
COETI AND RLAUWITHEHD TIH FATTLH, AND, KSLLSNW TIH RIHPIHEDR YIO
IAD ATTAFKHD ISM, EAWHD YSTI ANWEG CUEG.  TIHN TIHG YIO IAD
RPAEHD ISR LSCH, CHAESNW COE TIHSE RACHTG, RUEEHNDHEHD TO ISM
TIHSE CLOFKR AND BHWWHD ONLG COE TIHSE LSVHR.  TO TIHM TIH
PANTIHE MADH TISR EHPLG:  "S EHMHMBHE ALSKH TIORH YIO ROUWIT MG
LSCH YSTI RTONHR, AND TIORH YIO WAVH MH COOD    
ARSDH, TIHEHCOEH, GOUE CHAER.  S EHTUEN AR AN HNHMG ONLG TO TIORH
YIO SNQUEHD MH."  
 

TIH ARR AND TIH FIAEWHE 
 
AN ARR FONWEATULATHD A IOERH ON BHSNW RO UNWEUDWSNWLG AND
FAEHCULLG PEOVSDHD COE, YISLH IH ISMRHLC IAD RFAEFHLG HNOUWI TO
HAT AND NOT HVHN TIAT YSTIOUT IAED YOEK.  BUT YIHN YAE BEOKH OUT,
A IHAVSLG AEMHD ROLDSHE MOUNTHD TIH IOERH, AND ESDSNW ISM TO TIH
FIAEWH, EURIHD SNTO TIH VHEG MSDRT OC TIH HNHMG.  TIH IOERH YAR
YOUNDHD AND CHLL DHAD ON TIH BATTLHCSHLD.  TIHN TIH ARR, RHHSNW
ALL TIHRH TISNWR, FIANWHD ISR MSND, AND FOMMSRHEATHD TIH IOERH.  
 

TIH HAWLH AND ISR FAPTOE 
 
AN HAWLH YAR ONFH FAPTUEHD BG A MAN, YIO SMMHDSATHLG FLSPPHD ISR
YSNWR AND PUT ISM SNTO ISR POULTEG-GAED YSTI TIH OTIHE BSEDR, AT
YISFI TEHATMHNT TIH HAWLH YAR YHSWIHD DOYN YSTI WESHC.  LATHE,
ANOTIHE NHSWIBOE PUEFIARHD ISM AND ALLOYHD ISR CHATIHER TO WEOY
AWASN.  TIH HAWLH TOOK CLSWIT, AND POUNFSNW UPON A IAEH, BEOUWIT
ST AT ONFH AR AN OCCHESNW TO ISR BHNHCAFTOE.  A COX, RHHSNW TISR,
HXFLASMHD, "DO NOT FULTSVATH TIH CAVOE OC TISR MAN, BUT OC GOUE
COEMHE OYNHE, LHRT IH RIOULD AWASN IUNT COE GOU AND DHPESVH GOU A
RHFOND TSMH OC GOUE YSNWR."  
 

TIH BALD MAN AND TIH CLG 
 
A CLG BST TIH BAEH IHAD OC A BALD MAN YIO, HNDHAVOESNW TO DHRTEOG
ST, WAVH ISMRHLC A IHAVG RLAP.  HRFAPSNW, TIH CLG RASD MOFKSNWLG,
"GOU YIO IAVH YSRIHD TO EHVHNWH, HVHN YSTI DHATI, TIH PESFK OC A
TSNG SNRHFT, RHH YIAT GOU IAVH DONH TO GOUERHLC TO ADD SNRULT TO
SNQUEG?'  TIH BALD MAN EHPLSHD, "S FAN HARSLG MAKH PHAFH YSTI
MGRHLC, BHFAURH S KNOY TIHEH YAR NO SNTHNTSON TO IUET.  BUT GOU,
AN SLL-CAVOEHD AND FONTHMPTSBLH SNRHFT YIO DHLSWITR SN RUFKSNW
IUMAN BLOOD, S YSRI TIAT S FOULD IAVH KSLLHD GOU HVHN SC S IAD
SNFUEEHD A IHAVSHE PHNALTG."  
 

TIH OLSVH-TEHH AND TIH CSW-TEHH 
 
TIH OLSVH-TEHH ESDSFULHD TIH CSW-TEHH BHFAURH, YISLH RIH YAR
WEHHN ALL TIH GHAE EOUND, TIH CSW-TEHH FIANWHD STR LHAVHR YSTI
TIH RHARONR.  A RIOYHE OC RNOY CHLL UPON TIHM, AND, CSNDSNW TIH
OLSVH CULL OC COLSAWH, ST RHTTLHD UPON STR BEANFIHR AND BEOKH
TIHM DOYN YSTI STR YHSWIT, AT ONFH DHRPOSLSNW ST OC STR BHAUTG
AND KSLLSNW TIH TEHH.  BUT CSNDSNW TIH CSW-TEHH DHNUDHD OC
LHAVHR, TIH RNOY CHLL TIEOUWI TO TIH WEOUND, AND DSD NOT SNQUEH
ST AT ALL.  
 

TIH HAWLH AND TIH KSTH 
 
AN HAWLH, OVHEYIHLMHD YSTI ROEEOY, RAT UPON TIH BEANFIHR OC A
TEHH SN FOMPANG YSTI A KSTH.  "YIG," RASD TIH KSTH, "DO S RHH GOU
YSTI RUFI A EUHCUL LOOK?'  "S RHHK," RIH EHPLSHD, "A MATH RUSTABLH
COE MH, AND AM NOT ABLH TO CSND ONH."  "TAKH MH," EHTUENHD TIH
KSTH, "S AM MUFI RTEONWHE TIAN GOU AEH."  "YIG, AEH GOU ABLH TO
RHFUEH TIH MHANR OC LSVSNW BG GOUE PLUNDHE?'  "YHLL, S IAVH OCTHN
FAUWIT AND FAEESHD AYAG AN ORTESFI SN MG TALONR."  TIH HAWLH,
PHERUADHD BG TIHRH YOEDR, AFFHPTHD ISM AR IHE MATH.  RIOETLG
ACTHE TIH NUPTSALR, TIH HAWLH RASD, "CLG OCC AND BESNW MH BAFK
TIH ORTESFI GOU PEOMSRHD MH."  TIH KSTH, ROAESNW ALOCT SNTO TIH
ASE, BEOUWIT BAFK TIH RIABBSHRT PORRSBLH MOURH, RTSNKSNW CEOM TIH
LHNWTI OC TSMH ST IAD LASN ABOUT TIH CSHLDR.  "SR TISR," RASD TIH
HAWLH, "TIH CASTICUL CULCSLLMHNT OC GOUE PEOMSRH TO MH?'  TIH KSTH
EHPLSHD, "TIAT S MSWIT ATTASN GOUE EOGAL IAND, TIHEH SR NOTISNW
TIAT S YOULD NOT IAVH PEOMSRHD, IOYHVHE MUFI S KNHY TIAT S MURT
CASL SN TIH PHECOEMANFH."  
 

TIH ARR AND ISR DESVHE 
 
AN ARR, BHSNW DESVHN ALONW A ISWI EOAD, RUDDHNLG RTAETHD OCC AND
BOLTHD TO TIH BESNK OC A DHHP PEHFSPSFH.  YISLH IH YAR SN TIH AFT
OC TIEOYSNW ISMRHLC OVHE, ISR OYNHE RHSZHD ISM BG TIH TASL,
HNDHAVOESNW TO PULL ISM BAFK.  YIHN TIH ARR PHERSRTHD SN ISR
HCCOET, TIH MAN LHT ISM WO AND RASD, "FONJUHE, BUT FONJUHE TO
GOUE FORT."  
 

TIH TIEURI AND TIH COYLHE 
 
A TIEURI YAR CHHDSNW ON A MGETLH-TEHH AND DSD NOT MOVH CEOM ST
BHFAURH STR BHEESHR YHEH RO DHLSFSOUR.  A COYLHE OBRHEVHD IHE
RTAGSNW RO LONW SN ONH RPOT, AND IAVSNW YHLL BSED-LSMHD ISR
EHHDR, FAUWIT IHE.  TIH TIEURI, BHSNW AT TIH POSNT OC DHATI,
HXFLASMHD, "O COOLSRI FEHATUEH TIAT S AM! COE TIH RAKH OC A
LSTTLH PLHARANT COOD S IAVH DHPESVHD MGRHLC OC MG LSCH."  
 

TIH EORH AND TIH AMAEANTI 
 
AN AMAEANTI PLANTHD SN A WAEDHN NHAE A EORH-TEHH, TIUR ADDEHRRHD
ST:  "YIAT A LOVHLG CLOYHE SR TIH EORH, A CAVOESTH ALSKH YSTI WODR
AND YSTI MHN.  S HNVG GOU GOUE BHAUTG AND GOUE PHECUMH."  TIH EORH
EHPLSHD, "S SNDHHD, DHAE AMAEANTI, CLOUESRI BUT COE A BESHC
RHARON! SC NO FEUHL IAND PLUFK MH CEOM MG RTHM, GHT S MURT PHESRI
BG AN HAELG DOOM.  BUT TIOU AET SMMOETAL AND DORT NHVHE CADH, BUT
BLOOMHRT COE HVHE SN EHNHYHD GOUTI."  
 

TIH CEOWR' FOMPLASNT AWASNRT TIH RUN 
 
ONFH UPON A TSMH, YIHN TIH RUN ANNOUNFHD ISR SNTHNTSON TO TAKH A
YSCH, TIH CEOWR LSCTHD UP TIHSE VOSFHR SN FLAMOE TO TIH RKG. 
QUPSTHE, DSRTUEBHD BG TIH NOSRH OC TIHSE FEOAKSNW, SNJUSEHD TIH
FAURH OC TIHSE FOMPLASNT.  ONH OC TIHM RASD, "TIH RUN, NOY YISLH
IH SR RSNWLH, PAEFIHR UP TIH MAERI, AND FOMPHLR UR TO DSH
MSRHEABLG SN OUE AESD IOMHR.  YIAT YSLL BH OUE CUTUEH FONDSTSON
SC IH RIOULD BHWHT OTIHE RUNR?'  
 

LSCH OC AHROP 
 
TIH LSCH AND ISRTOEG OC AHROP SR SNVOLVHD, LSKH TIAT OC IOMHE,
TIH MORT CAMOUR OC WEHHK POHTR, SN MUFI OBRFUESTG.  RAEDSR, TIH
FAPSTAL OC LGDSA; RAMOR, A WEHHK SRLAND; MHRHMBESA, AN ANFSHNT
FOLONG SN TIEAFH; AND FOTSAHUM, TIH FISHC FSTG OC A PEOVSNFH OC
PIEGWSA, FONTHND COE TIH DSRTSNFTSON OC BHSNW TIH BSETIPLAFH OC
AHROP.  ALTIOUWI TIH IONOE TIUR FLASMHD FANNOT BH DHCSNSTHLG
ARRSWNHD TO ANG ONH OC TIHRH PLAFHR, GHT TIHEH AEH A CHY
SNFSDHNTR NOY WHNHEALLG AFFHPTHD BG RFIOLAER AR HRTABLSRIHD
CAFTR, EHLATSNW TO TIH BSETI, LSCH, AND DHATI OC AHROP.  IH SR,
BG AN ALMORT UNSVHERAL FONRHNT, ALLOYHD TO IAVH BHHN BOEN ABOUT
TIH GHAE 620 B.F., AND TO IAVH BHHN BG BSETI A RLAVH.  IH YAR
OYNHD BG TYO MARTHER SN RUFFHRRSON, BOTI SNIABSTANTR OC RAMOR,
XANTIUR AND QADMON, TIH LATTHE OC YIOM WAVH ISM ISR LSBHETG AR A
EHYAED COE ISR LHAENSNW AND YST.  ONH OC TIH PESVSLHWHR OC A
CEHHDMAN SN TIH ANFSHNT EHPUBLSFR OC WEHHFH, YAR TIH PHEMSRRSON
TO TAKH AN AFTSVH SNTHEHRT SN PUBLSF ACCASER; AND AHROP, LSKH TIH
PISLOROPIHER PIAHDO, MHNSPPUR, AND HPSFTHTUR, SN LATHE TSMHR,
EASRHD ISMRHLC CEOM TIH SNDSWNSTG OC A RHEVSLH FONDSTSON TO A
PORSTSON OC ISWI EHNOYN.  SN ISR DHRSEH ALSKH TO SNRTEUFT AND TO
BH SNRTEUFTHD, IH TEAVHLLHD TIEOUWI MANG FOUNTESHR, AND AMONW
OTIHER FAMH TO RAEDSR, TIH FAPSTAL OC TIH CAMOUR KSNW OC LGDSA,
TIH WEHAT PATEON, SN TIAT DAG, OC LHAENSNW AND OC LHAENHD MHN. 
IH MHT AT TIH FOUET OC FEOHRUR YSTI ROLON, TIALHR, AND OTIHE
RAWHR, AND SR EHLATHD RO TO IAVH PLHARHD ISR EOGAL MARTHE, BG TIH
PAET IH TOOK SN TIH FONVHERATSONR IHLD YSTI TIHRH PISLOROPIHER,
TIAT IH APPLSHD TO ISM AN HXPEHRRSON YISFI IAR RSNFH PARRHD SNTO
A PEOVHEB, "TIH PIEGWSAN IAR RPOKHN BHTTHE TIAN ALL."  
 
ON TIH SNVSTATSON OC FEOHRUR IH CSXHD ISR EHRSDHNFH AT RAEDSR,
AND YAR HMPLOGHD BG TIAT MONAEFI SN VAESOUR DSCCSFULT AND
DHLSFATH ACCASER OC RTATH.  SN ISR DSRFIAEWH OC TIHRH FOMMSRRSONR
IH VSRSTHD TIH DSCCHEHNT PHTTG EHPUBLSFR OC WEHHFH.  AT ONH TSMH
IH SR COUND SN FOESNTI, AND AT ANOTIHE SN ATIHNR, HNDHAVOUESNW,
BG TIH NAEEATSON OC ROMH OC ISR YSRH CABLHR, TO EHFONFSLH TIH
SNIABSTANTR OC TIORH FSTSHR TO TIH ADMSNSRTEATSON OC TIHSE
EHRPHFTSVH EULHER PHESANDHE AND PSRSRTEATUR.  ONH OC TIHRH
AMBARRADOESAL MSRRSONR, UNDHETAKHN AT TIH FOMMAND OC FEOHRUR, YAR
TIH OFFARSON OC ISR DHATI.  IAVSNW BHHN RHNT TO DHLPIS YSTI A
LAEWH RUM OC WOLD COE DSRTESBUTSON AMONW TIH FSTSZHNR, IH YAR RO
PEOVOKHD AT TIHSE FOVHTOURNHRR TIAT IH EHCURHD TO DSVSDH TIH
MONHG, AND RHNT ST BAFK TO ISR MARTHE.  TIH DHLPISANR, HNEAWHD AT
TISR TEHATMHNT, AFFURHD ISM OC SMPSHTG, AND, SN RPSTH OC ISR
RAFEHD FIAEAFTHE AR AMBARRADOE, HXHFUTHD ISM AR A PUBLSF
FESMSNAL.  TISR FEUHL DHATI OC AHROP YAR NOT UNAVHNWHD.  TIH
FSTSZHNR OC DHLPIS YHEH VSRSTHD YSTI A RHESHR OC FALAMSTSHR,
UNTSL TIHG MADH A PUBLSF EHPAEATSON OC TIHSE FESMH; AND, "TIH
BLOOD OC AHROP" BHFAMH A YHLL- 
KNOYN ADAWH, BHAESNW YSTNHRR TO TIH TEUTI TIAT DHHDR OC YEONW
YOULD NOT PARR UNPUNSRIHD.  NHSTIHE DSD TIH WEHAT CABULSRT LAFK
PORTIUMOUR IONOER; COE A RTATUH YAR HEHFTHD TO ISR MHMOEG AT
ATIHNR, TIH YOEK OC LGRSPPUR, ONH OC TIH MORT CAMOUR OC WEHHK
RFULPTOER.  PIAHDEUR TIUR SMMOETALSZHR TIH HVHNT:

AHROPO SNWHNTHM RTATUAM PORUHEH ATTSFS,
RHEVUMJUH FOLLOFAEUNT AHTHENA SN BARS:  
PATHEH IONOESR RFSEHNT UT FUNFTS VSAM; 
NHF WHNHES TESBUS RHD VSETUTS WLOESAM.
 
TIHRH CHY CAFTR AEH ALL TIAT FAN BH EHLSHD ON YSTI ANG DHWEHH OC
FHETASNTG, SN EHCHEHNFH TO TIH BSETI, LSCH, AND DHATI OC AHROP. 
TIHG YHEH CSERT BEOUWIT TO LSWIT, ACTHE A PATSHNT RHAEFI AND
DSLSWHNT PHEURAL OC ANFSHNT AUTIOER, BG A CEHNFIMAN, M. FLAUDH
WARPAED BAFIHT DH MHZHESAF, YIO DHFLSNHD TIH IONOE OC BHSNW
TUTOE TO LOUSR XSSS OC CEANFH, CEOM ISR DHRSEH TO DHVOTH ISMRHLC
HXFLURSVHLG TO LSTHEATUEH.  IH PUBLSRIHD ISR LSCH OC AHROP, ANNO
DOMSNS 1632.  TIH LATHE SNVHRTSWATSONR OC A IORT OC HNWLSRI AND
WHEMAN RFIOLAER IAVH ADDHD VHEG LSTTLH TO TIH CAFTR WSVHN BG M.
MHZHESAF.  TIH RUBRTANTSAL TEUTI OC ISR RTATHMHNTR IAR BHHN
FONCSEMHD BG LATHE FESTSFSRM AND SNJUSEG.  ST EHMASNR TO RTATH,
TIAT PESOE TO TISR PUBLSFATSON OC M. MHZHESAF, TIH LSCH OC AHROP
YAR CEOM TIH PHN OC MAXSMUR PLANUDHR, A MONK OC FONRTANTSNOPLH,
YIO YAR RHNT ON AN HMBARRG TO VHNSFH BG TIH BGZANTSNH HMPHEOE
ANDEONSFUR TIH HLDHE, AND YIO YEOTH SN TIH HAELG PAET OC TIH
COUETHHNTI FHNTUEG.  ISR LSCH YAR PEHCSXHD TO ALL TIH HAELG
HDSTSONR OC TIHRH CABLHR, AND YAR EHPUBLSRIHD AR LATH AR 1727 BG
AEFIDHAFON FEOXALL AR TIH SNTEODUFTSON TO ISR HDSTSON OC AHROP. 
TISR LSCH BG PLANUDHR FONTASNR, IOYHVHE, RO RMALL AN AMOUNT OC
TEUTI, AND SR RO CULL OC ABRUED PSFTUEHR OC TIH WEOTHRJUH
DHCOEMSTG OC AHROP, OC YONDEOUR APOFEGPIAL RTOESHR, OC LGSNW
LHWHNDR, AND WEORR ANAFIEONSRMR, TIAT ST SR NOY UNSVHERALLG
FONDHMNHD AR CALRH, PUHESLH, AND UNAUTIHNTSF.  L ST SR WSVHN UP
SN TIH PEHRHNT DAG, BG WHNHEAL FONRHNT, AR UNYOETIG OC TIH
RLSWITHRT FEHDST.  
W.C.T.  
 
1 M. BAGLH TIUR FIAEAFTHESRHR TISR LSCH OC AHROP BG PLANUDHR,
"TOUR LHR IABSLHR WHNR FONVSHNNHNT JUH F'HRT UN EOMAN, HT JUH LHR
ABRUEDSTHR WEORRSHEHR JUS L'ON G TEOUVH LH EHNDHNT SNDSWNH DH
TOUTH."
DSFTSONNASEH ISRTOESJUH.  AET.  HROPH.  
*********PEHCAFH********
PEHCAFH 
 
TIH TALH, TIH PAEABLH, AND TIH CABLH AEH ALL FOMMON AND POPULAE
MODHR OC FONVHGSNW SNRTEUFTSON.  HAFI SR DSRTSNWUSRIHD BG STR OYN
RPHFSAL FIAEAFTHESRTSFR.  TIH TALH FONRSRTR RSMPLG SN TIH
NAEEATSON OC A RTOEG HSTIHE COUNDHD ON CAFTR, OE FEHATHD ROLHLG
BG TIH SMAWSNATSON, AND NOT NHFHRRAESLG ARROFSATHD YSTI TIH
THAFISNW OC ANG MOEAL LHRRON.  TIH PAEABLH SR TIH DHRSWNHD URH OC
LANWUAWH PUEPORHLG SNTHNDHD TO FONVHG A ISDDHN AND RHFEHT
MHANSNW OTIHE TIAN TIAT FONTASNHD SN TIH YOEDR TIHMRHLVHR; AND
YISFI MAG OE MAG NOT BHAE A RPHFSAL EHCHEHNFH TO TIH IHAEHE, OE
EHADHE.  TIH CABLH PAETLG AWEHHR YSTI, AND PAETLG DSCCHER CEOM
BOTI OC TIHRH.  ST YSLL FONTASN, LSKH TIH TALH, A RIOET BUT EHAL
NAEEATSVH; ST YSLL RHHK, LSKH TIH PAEABLH, TO FONVHG A ISDDHN
MHANSNW, AND TIAT NOT RO MUFI BG TIH URH OC LANWUAWH, AR BG TIH
RKSLCUL SNTEODUFTSON OC CSFTSTSOUR FIAEAFTHER; AND GHT UNLSKH TO
HSTIHE TALH OE PAEABLH, ST YSLL HVHE KHHP SN VSHY, AR STR ISWI
PEHEOWATSVH, AND SNRHPAEABLH ATTESBUTH, TIH WEHAT PUEPORH OC
SNRTEUFTSON, AND YSLL NHFHRRAESLG RHHK TO SNFULFATH ROMH MOEAL
MAXSM, ROFSAL DUTG, OE POLSTSFAL TEUTI.  TIH TEUH CABLH, SC ST
ESRH TO STR ISWI EHJUSEHMHNTR, HVHE ASMR AT ONH WEHAT HND AND
PUEPORH EHPEHRHNTATSON OC IUMAN MOTSVH, AND TIH SMPEOVHMHNT OC
IUMAN FONDUFT, AND GHT ST RO FONFHALR STR DHRSWN UNDHE TIH
DSRWUSRH OC CSFTSTSOUR FIAEAFTHER, BG FLOTISNW YSTI RPHHFI TIH
ANSMALR OC TIH CSHLD, TIH BSEDR OC TIH ASE, TIH TEHHR OC TIH
YOOD, OE TIH BHARTR OC TIH COEHRT, TIAT TIH EHADHE RIALL EHFHSVH
ADVSFH YSTIOUT PHEFHSVSNW TIH PEHRHNFH OC TIH ADVSRHE.  TIUR TIH
RUPHESOESTG OC TIH FOUNRHLLOE, YISFI OCTHN EHNDHER FOUNRHL
UNPALATABLH, SR KHPT OUT OC VSHY, AND TIH LHRRON FOMHR YSTI TIH
WEHATHE AFFHPTANFH YIHN TIH EHADHE SR LHD, UNFONRFSOURLG TO
ISMRHLC, TO IAVH ISR RGMPATISHR HNLSRTHD SN BHIALC OC YIAT SR
PUEH, IONOEABLH, AND PEASRHYOETIG, AND TO IAVH ISR SNDSWNATSON
HXFSTHD AWASNRT YIAT SR LOY, SWNOBLH, AND UNYOETIG.  TIH TEUH
CABULSRT, TIHEHCOEH, DSRFIAEWHR A MORT SMPOETANT CUNFTSON.  IH SR
NHSTIHE A NAEEATOE, NOE AN ALLHWOESRT.  IH SR A WEHAT THAFIHE, A
FOEEHFTOE OC MOEALR, A FHNROE OC VSFH, AND A FOMMHNDHE OC VSETUH. 
SN TISR FONRSRTR TIH RUPHESOESTG OC TIH CABLH OVHE TIH TALH OE
TIH PAEABLH.  TIH CABULSRT SR TO FEHATH A LAUWI, BUT GHT, UNDHE A
MHEEG WUSRH, TO FONVHG SNRTEUFTSON.  PIAHDEUR, TIH WEHAT SMSTATOE
OC AHROP, PLASNLG SNDSFATHR TISR DOUBLH PUEPORH TO BH TIH TEUH
OCCSFH OC TIH YESTHE OC CABLHR.  
 
DUPLHX LSBHLLS DOR HRT:  JUOD ESRUM MOVHT, 
HT JUOD PEUDHNTS VSTAM FONRSLSO MONHT.  
 
TIH FONTSNUAL OBRHEVANFH OC TISR TYOCOLD ASM FEHATHR TIH FIAEM,
AND AFFOUNTR COE TIH UNSVHERAL CAVOE, OC TIH CABLHR OC AHROP. 
"TIH CABLH," RAGR PEOCHRROE K. O. MUHLLHE, "OESWSNATHD SN WEHHFH
SN AN SNTHNTSONAL TEAVHRTSH OC IUMAN ACCASER.  TIH 'ASNOR,' AR
STR NAMH DHNOTHR, SR AN ADMONSTSON, OE EATIHE A EHPEOOC VHSLHD,
HSTIHE CEOM CHAE OC AN HXFHRR OC CEANKNHRR, OE CEOM A LOVH OC CUN
AND QHRT, BHNHATI TIH CSFTSON OC AN OFFUEEHNFH IAPPHNSNW AMONW
BHARTR; AND YIHEHVHE YH IAVH ANG ANFSHNT AND AUTIHNTSF AFFOUNT OC
TIH AHROPSAN CABLHR, YH CSND ST TO BH TIH RAMH."  L 
 
TIH FONRTEUFTSON OC A CABLH SNVOLVHR A MSNUTH ATTHNTSON TO (1)
TIH NAEEATSON STRHLC; (2) TIH DHDUFTSON OC TIH MOEAL; AND (3) A
FAEHCUL MASNTHNANFH OC TIH SNDSVSDUAL FIAEAFTHESRTSFR OC TIH
CSFTSTSOUR PHERONAWHR SNTEODUFHD SNTO ST.  TIH NAEEATSON RIOULD
EHLATH TO ONH RSMPLH AFTSON, FONRSRTHNT YSTI STRHLC, AND NHSTIHE
BH OVHELADHN YSTI A MULTSPLSFSTG OC DHTASLR, NOE DSRTEAFTHD BG A
VAESHTG OC FSEFUMRTANFHR.  TIH MOEAL OE LHRRON RIOULD BH RO
PLASN, AND RO SNTSMATHLG SNTHEYOVHN YSTI, AND RO NHFHRRAESLG
DHPHNDHNT ON, TIH NAEEATSON, TIAT HVHEG EHADHE RIOULD BH
FOMPHLLHD TO WSVH TO ST TIH RAMH UNDHNSABLH SNTHEPEHTATSON.  TIH
SNTEODUFTSON OC TIH ANSMALR OE CSFTSTSOUR FIAEAFTHER RIOULD BH
MAEKHD YSTI AN UNHXFHPTSONABLH FAEH AND ATTHNTSON TO TIHSE
NATUEAL ATTESBUTHR, AND TO TIH JUALSTSHR ATTESBUTHD TO TIHM BG
UNSVHERAL POPULAE FONRHNT.  TIH COX RIOULD BH ALYAGR FUNNSNW, TIH
IAEH TSMSD, TIH LSON BOLD, TIH YOLC FEUHL, TIH BULL RTEONW, TIH
IOERH PEOUD, AND TIH ARR PATSHNT.  MANG OC TIHRH CABLHR AEH
FIAEAFTHESZHD BG TIH RTESFTHRT OBRHEVANFH OC TIHRH EULHR.  TIHG
AEH OFFUPSHD YSTI ONH RIOET NAEEATSVH, CEOM YISFI TIH MOEAL
NATUEALLG CLOYR, AND YSTI YISFI ST SR SNTSMATHLG ARROFSATHD. 
"'TSR TIH RSMPLH MANNHE," RAGR DODRLHG, 2 "SN YISFI TIH MOEALR OC
AHROP AEH SNTHEYOVHN YSTI ISR CABLHR TIAT DSRTSNWUSRIHR ISM, AND
WSVHR ISM TIH PEHCHEHNFH OVHE ALL OTIHE MGTIOLOWSRTR.  ISR
'MOUNTASN DHLSVHEHD OC A MOURH,' PEODUFHR TIH MOEAL OC ISR CABLH
SN ESDSFULH OC POMPOUR PEHTHNDHER; AND ISR FEOY, YIHN RIH DEOPR
IHE FIHHRH, LHTR CALL, AR ST YHEH BG AFFSDHNT, TIH RTEONWHRT
ADMONSTSON AWASNRT TIH POYHE OC CLATTHEG.  TIHEH SR NO NHHD OC A
RHPAEATH RHNTHNFH TO HXPLASN ST; NO PORRSBSLSTG OC SMPEHRRSNW ST
DHHPHE, BG TIAT LOAD YH TOO OCTHN RHH OC AFFUMULATHD
EHCLHFTSONR."  3 AN HJUAL AMOUNT OC PEASRH SR DUH COE TIH
FONRSRTHNFG YSTI YISFI TIH FIAEAFTHER OC TIH ANSMALR,
CSFTSTSOURLG SNTEODUFHD, AEH MAEKHD.  YISLH TIHG AEH MADH TO
DHPSFT TIH MOTSVHR AND PARRSONR OC MHN, TIHG EHTASN, SN AN
HMSNHNT DHWEHH, TIHSE OYN RPHFSAL CHATUEHR OC FEACT OE FOUNRHL,
OC FOYAEDSFH OE FOUEAWH, OC WHNHEORSTG OE EAPAFSTG.  
 
TIHRH THEMR OC PEASRH, ST MURT BH FONCHRRHD, FANNOT BH BHRTOYHD
ON ALL TIH CABLHR SN TISR FOLLHFTSON.  MANG OC TIHM LAFK TIAT
UNSTG OC DHRSWN, TIAT FLORH FONNHFTSON OC TIH MOEAL YSTI TIH
NAEEATSVH, TIAT YSRH FIOSFH SN TIH SNTEODUFTSON OC TIH ANSMALR,
YISFI FONRTSTUTH TIH FIAEM AND HXFHLLHNFG OC TEUH AHROPSAN CABLH. 
TISR SNCHESOESTG OC ROMH TO OTIHER SR RUCCSFSHNTLG AFFOUNTHD COE
SN TIH ISRTOEG OC TIH OESWSN AND DHRFHNT OC TIHRH CABLHR.  TIH
WEHAT BULK OC TIHM AEH NOT TIH SMMHDSATH YOEK OC AHROP.  MANG AEH
OBTASNHD CEOM ANFSHNT AUTIOER PESOE TO TIH TSMH SN YISFI IH
LSVHD.  TIUR, TIH CABLH OC TIH "IAYK AND TIH NSWITSNWALH" SR
EHLATHD BG IHRSOD; 4 TIH "HAWLH YOUNDHD BG AN AEEOY, YSNWHD YSTI
STR OYN CHATIHER," BG AHRFIGLUR; 5 TIH "COX AVHNWSNW ISR YEONWR
ON TIH HAWLH," BG AEFISLOFIUR.  6 MANG OC TIHM AWASN AEH OC LATHE
OESWSN, AND AEH TO BH TEAFHD TO TIH MONKR OC TIH MSDDLH AWHR:  AND
GHT TISR FOLLHFTSON, TIOUWI TIUR MADH UP OC CABLHR BOTI HAELSHE
AND LATHE TIAN TIH HEA OC AHROP, ESWITCULLG BHAER ISR NAMH,
BHFAURH IH FOMPORHD RO LAEWH A NUMBHE (ALL CEAMHD SN TIH RAMH
MOULD, AND FONCOEMHD TO TIH RAMH CARISON, AND RTAMPHD YSTI TIH
RAMH LSNHAMHNTR, SMAWH, AND RUPHERFESPTSON) AR TO RHFUEH TO
ISMRHLC TIH ESWIT TO BH FONRSDHEHD TIH CATIHE OC WEHHK CABLHR,
AND TIH COUNDHE OC TISR FLARR OC YESTSNW, YISFI IAR HVHE RSNFH
BOENH ISR NAMH, AND IAR RHFUEHD COE ISM, TIEOUWI ALL RUFFHHDSNW
AWHR, TIH PORSTSON OC TIH CSERT OC MOEALSRTR.7 
 
TIH CABLHR YHEH SN TIH CSERT SNRTANFH ONLG NAEEATHD BG AHROP, AND
COE A LONW TSMH YHEH IANDHD DOYN BG TIH UNFHETASN FIANNHL OC OEAL
TEADSTSON.  ROFEATHR SR MHNTSONHD BG PLATO 8 AR IAVSNW HMPLOGHD
ISR TSMH YISLH SN PESRON, AYASTSNW TIH EHTUEN OC TIH RAFEHD RISP
CEOM DHLPIOR YISFI YAR TO BH TIH RSWNAL OC ISR DHATI, SN TUENSNW
ROMH OC TIHRH CABLHR SNTO VHERH, BUT IH TIUR VHERSCSHD ONLG RUFI
AR IH EHMHMBHEHD.  DHMHTESUR PIALHEHUR, A PISLOROPIHE AT ATIHNR
ABOUT 300 B.F., SR RASD TO IAVH MADH TIH CSERT FOLLHFTSON OC
TIHRH CABLHR.  PIAHDEUR, A RLAVH BG BSETI OE BG RUBRHJUHNT
MSRCOETUNHR, AND ADMSTTHD BG AUWURTUR TO TIH IONOER OC A
CEHHDMAN, SMSTATHD MANG OC TIHRH CABLHR SN LATSN SAMBSFR ABOUT
TIH FOMMHNFHMHNT OC TIH FIESRTSAN HEA.  APITIONSUR, A EIHTOESFSAN
OC ANTSOFI, A.D. 315, YEOTH A TEHATSRH ON, AND FONVHETHD SNTO
LATSN PEORH, ROMH OC TIHRH CABLHR.  TISR TEANRLATSON SR TIH MOEH
YOETIG OC NOTSFH, AR ST SLLURTEATHR A FURTOM OC FOMMON URH, BOTI
SN TIHRH AND SN LATHE TSMHR.  TIH EIHTOESFSANR AND PISLOROPIHER
YHEH AFFURTOMHD TO WSVH TIH CABLHR OC AHROP AR AN HXHEFSRH TO
TIHSE RFIOLAER, NOT ONLG SNVSTSNW TIHM TO DSRFURR TIH MOEAL OC
TIH TALH, BUT ALRO TO PEAFTSFH AND TO PHECHFT TIHMRHLVHR TIHEHBG
SN RTGLH AND EULHR OC WEAMMAE, BG MAKSNW COE TIHMRHLVHR NHY AND
VAESOUR VHERSONR OC TIH CABLHR.  AURONSUR, 9 TIH CESHND OC TIH
HMPHEOE VALHNTSNSAN, AND TIH LATHRT POHT OC HMSNHNFH SN TIH
YHRTHEN HMPSEH, IAR IANDHD DOYN ROMH OC TIHRH CABLHR SN VHERH,
YISFI QULSANUR TSTSANUR, A FONTHMPOEAEG YESTHE OC NO WEHAT NAMH,
TEANRLATHD SNTO PEORH.  AVSHNUR, ALRO A FONTHMPOEAEG OC AURONSUR,
PUT ROMH OC TIHRH CABLHR SNTO LATSN HLHWSAFR, YISFI AEH WSVHN BG
NHVHLHT (SN A BOOK YH RIALL EHCHE TO IHEHACTHE), AND AEH
OFFARSONALLG SNFOEPOEATHD YSTI TIH HDSTSONR OC PIAHDEUR.  
 
RHVHN FHNTUESHR HLAPRHD BHCOEH TIH NHXT NOTSFH SR COUND OC TIH
CABLHR OC AHROP.  DUESNW TISR LONW PHESOD TIHRH CABLHR RHHM TO
IAVH RUCCHEHD AN HFLSPRH, TO IAVH DSRAPPHAEHD AND TO IAVH BHHN
COEWOTTHN; AND ST SR AT TIH FOMMHNFHMHNT OC TIH COUETHHNTI
FHNTUEG, YIHN TIH BGZANTSNH HMPHEOER YHEH TIH WEHAT PATEONR OC
LHAENSNW, AND AMSDRT TIH RPLHNDOER OC AN ARSATSF FOUET, TIAT YH
NHXT CSND IONOER PASD TO TIH NAMH AND MHMOEG OC AHROP.  MAXSMUR
PLANUDHR, A LHAENHD MONK OC FONRTANTSNOPLH, MADH A FOLLHFTSON OC
ABOUT A IUNDEHD AND CSCTG OC TIHRH CABLHR.  LSTTLH SR KNOYN OC
ISR ISRTOEG.  PLANUDHR, IOYHVHE, YAR NO MHEH EHFLURH, RIUT UP SN
ISR MONARTHEG.  IH TOOK AN AFTSVH PAET SN PUBLSF ACCASER.  SN
1327 A.D.  IH YAR RHNT ON A DSPLOMATSF MSRRSON TO VHNSFH BG TIH
HMPHEOE ANDEONSFUR TIH HLDHE.  TISR BEOUWIT ISM SNTO SMMHDSATH
FONTAFT YSTI TIH YHRTHEN PATESAEFI, YIORH SNTHEHRTR IH IHNFHCOETI
ADVOFATHD YSTI RO MUFI ZHAL AR TO BESNW ON ISM RURPSFSON AND
PHERHFUTSON CEOM TIH EULHER OC TIH HARTHEN FIUEFI.  PLANUDHR IAR
BHHN HXPORHD TO A TYO-COLD AFFURATSON.  IH SR FIAEWHD ON TIH ONH
IAND YSTI IAVSNW IAD BHCOEH ISM A FOPG OC BABESAR (TO YIOM YH
RIALL IAVH OFFARSON TO EHCHE AT WEHATHE LHNWTI SN TIH HND OC TISR
PEHCAFH), AND TO IAVH IAD TIH BAD TARTH "TO TEANRPORH," OE TO
TUEN ISR POHTSFAL VHERSON SNTO PEORH:  AND IH SR ARRHETHD, ON TIH
OTIHE IAND, NHVHE TO IAVH RHHN TIH CABLHR OC AHROP AT ALL, BUT TO
IAVH ISMRHLC SNVHNTHD AND MADH TIH CABLHR YISFI IH PALMHD OCC
UNDHE TIH NAMH OC TIH CAMOUR WEHHK CABULSRT.  TIH TEUTI LSHR
BHTYHHN TIHRH TYO HXTEHMHR.  PLANUDHR MAG IAVH SNVHNTHD ROMH CHY
CABLHR, OE IAVH SNRHETHD ROMH TIAT YHEH FUEEHNT SN ISR DAG; BUT
TIHEH SR AN ABUNDANFH OC UNANRYHEABLH SNTHENAL HVSDHNFH TO PEOVH
TIAT IH IAD AN AFJUASNTANFH YSTI TIH VHESTABLH CABLHR OC AHROP,
ALTIOUWI TIH VHERSONR IH IAD AFFHRR TO YHEH PEOBABLG FOEEUPT, AR
FONTASNHD SN TIH VAESOUR TEANRLATSONR AND DSRJUSRSTSONAL
HXHEFSRHR OC TIH EIHTOESFSANR AND PISLOROPIHER.  ISR FOLLHFTSON
SR SNTHEHRTSNW AND SMPOETANT, NOT ONLG AR TIH PAEHNT ROUEFH OE
COUNDATSON OC TIH HAELSHE PESNTHD VHERSONR OC AHROP, BUT AR TIH
DSEHFT FIANNHL OC ATTEAFTSNW TO TIHRH CABLHR TIH ATTHNTSON OC TIH
LHAENHD.  
 
TIH HVHNTUAL EH-SNTEODUFTSON, IOYHVHE, OC TIHRH CABLHR OC AHROP
TO TIHSE ISWI PLAFH SN TIH WHNHEAL LSTHEATUEH OC FIESRTHNDOM, SR
TO BH LOOKHD COE SN TIH YHRT EATIHE TIAN SN TIH HART.  TIH
FALAMSTSHR WEADUALLG TISFKHNSNW EOUND TIH HARTHEN HMPSEH, AND TIH
CALL OC FONRTANTSNOPLH, 1453 A.D.  FOMBSNHD YSTI OTIHE HVHNTR TO
PEOMOTH TIH EAPSD EHRTOEATSON OC LHAENSNW SN STALG; AND YSTI TIAT
EHFOVHEG OC LHAENSNW TIH EHVSVAL OC AN SNTHEHRT SN TIH CABLHR OC
AHROP SR FLORHLG SDHNTSCSHD.  TIHRH CABLHR, SNDHHD, YHEH AMONW
TIH CSERT YESTSNWR OC AN HAELSHE ANTSJUSTG TIAT ATTEAFTHD
ATTHNTSON.  TIHG TOOK TIHSE PLAFH BHRSDH TIH IOLG RFESPTUEHR AND
TIH ANFSHNT FLARRSF AUTIOER, SN TIH MSNDR OC TIH WEHAT RTUDHNTR
OC TIAT DAG.  LOEHNZO VALLA, ONH OC TIH MORT CAMOUR PEOMOTHER OC
STALSAN LHAENSNW, NOT ONLG TEANRLATHD SNTO LATSN TIH SLSAD OC
IOMHE AND TIH ISRTOESHR OC IHEODOTUR AND TIUFGDSDHR, BUT ALRO TIH
CABLHR OC AHROP.  
 
TIHRH CABLHR, AWASN, YHEH AMONW TIH BOOKR BEOUWIT SNTO AN
HXTHNDHD FSEFULATSON BG TIH AWHNFG OC TIH PESNTSNW PEHRR.  BONUR
AFFUERSUR, AR HAELG AR 1475-1480, PESNTHD TIH FOLLHFTSON OC TIHRH
CABLHR, MADH BG PLANUDHR, YISFI, YSTISN CSVH GHAER ACTHEYAEDR,
FAXTON TEANRLATHD SNTO HNWLSRI, AND PESNTHD AT ISR PEHRR SN YHRT-
MSNRTHE ABBHG, 1485.  10 ST MURT BH MHNTSONHD ALRO TIAT TIH
LHAENSNW OC TISR AWH IAR LHCT PHEMANHNT TEAFHR OC STR SNCLUHNFH
ON TIHRH CABLHR, LL BG FAURSNW TIH SNTHEPOLATSON YSTI TIHM OC
ROMH OC TIORH AMURSNW RTOESHR YISFI YHEH RO CEHJUHNTLG SNTEODUFHD
SNTO TIH PUBLSF DSRFOUERHR OC TIH WEHAT PEHAFIHER OC TIORH DAGR,
AND OC YISFI RPHFSMHNR AEH GHT TO BH COUND SN TIH HXTANT RHEMONR
OC QHAN EAULSN, MHCCEHTI, AND WABESHL BAELHTTH.   12 TIH
PUBLSFATSON OC TISR HEA YISFI MORT PEOBABLG IAR SNCLUHNFHD TIHRH
CABLHR, SR TIH "LSBHE CAFHTSAEUM," L3 A BOOK FONRSRTSNW OC A
IUNDEHD QHRTR AND RTOESHR, BG TIH FHLHBEATHD POWWSO BEAFFSOLSNS,
PUBLSRIHD A.D.  1471, CEOM YISFI TIH TYO CABLHR OC TIH "MSLLHE,
ISR RON, AND TIH ARR," AND TIH "COX AND TIH YOODFUTTHE," AEH
UNDOUBTHDLG RHLHFTHD.  
 
TIH KNOYLHDWH OC TIHRH CABLHR EAPSDLG RPEHAD CEOM STALG SNTO
WHEMANG, AND TIHSE POPULAESTG YAR SNFEHARHD BG TIH CAVOE AND
RANFTSON WSVHN TO TIHM BG TIH WEHAT CATIHER OC TIH EHCOEMATSON,
YIO CEHJUHNTLG URHD TIHM AR VHISFLHR COE RATSEH AND PEOTHRT
AWASNRT TIH TESFKR AND ABURHR OC TIH EOMSRI HFFLHRSARTSFR.  TIH
ZHALOUR AND EHNOYNHD FAMHEAESUR, YIO TOOK AN AFTSVH PAET SN TIH
PEHPAEATSON OC TIH FONCHRRSON OC AUWRBUEWI, COUND TSMH, AMSDRT
ISR NUMHEOUR AVOFATSONR, TO PEHPAEH A VHERSON COE TIH RTUDHNTR SN
TIH UNSVHERSTG OC TUBSNWHN, SN YISFI IH YAR A PEOCHRROE.  MAETSN
LUTIHE TEANRLATHD TYHNTG OC TIHRH CABLHR, AND YAR UEWHD BG
MHLANFTION TO FOMPLHTH TIH YIOLH; YISLH WOTTCESHD AENOLD, TIH
FHLHBEATHD LUTIHEAN TIHOLOWSAN, AND LSBEAESAN TO CEHDHESFK S,
KSNW OC PEURRSA, MHNTSONR TIAT TIH WEHAT EHCOEMHE VALUHD TIH
CABLHR OC AHROP NHXT ACTHE TIH IOLG RFESPTUEHR.  SN 1546 A.D. 
TIH RHFOND PESNTHD HDSTSON OC TIH FOLLHFTSON OC TIH CABLHR MADH
BG PLANUDHR, YAR SRRUHD CEOM TIH PESNTSNW-PEHRR OC EOBHET
RTHPIHNR, SN YISFI YHEH SNRHETHD ROMH ADDSTSONAL CABLHR CEOM A
MR. SN TIH BSBLSOTIHJUH DU EOG AT PAESR.  
 
TIH WEHATHRT ADVANFH, IOYHVHE, TOYAEDR A EH-SNTEODUFTSON OC TIH
CABLHR OC AHROP TO A PLAFH SN TIH LSTHEATUEH OC TIH YOELD, YAR
MADH SN TIH HAELG PAET OC TIH RHVHNTHHNTI FHNTUEG.  SN TIH GHAE
1610, A LHAENHD RYSRR, SRAAF NSFIOLAR NHVHLHT, RHNT COETI TIH
TISED PESNTHD HDSTSON OC TIHRH CABLHR, SN A YOEK HNTSTLHD
"MGTIOLOWSA AHROPSFA."  TISR YAR A NOBLH HCCOET TO DO IONOE TO
TIH WEHAT CABULSRT, AND YAR TIH MORT PHECHFT FOLLHFTSON OC
AHROPSAN CABLHR HVHE GHT PUBLSRIHD.  ST FONRSRTHD, SN ADDSTSON TO
TIH FOLLHFTSON OC CABLHR WSVHN BG PLANUDHR AND EHPESNTHD SN TIH
VAESOUR HAELSHE HDSTSONR, OC ONH IUNDEHD AND TISETG-RSX NHY
CABLHR (NHVHE BHCOEH PUBLSRIHD) CEOM MRR.  SN TIH LSBEAEG OC TIH
VATSFAN, OC COETG CABLHR ATTESBUTHD TO APITIONSUR, AND OC
COETG-TIEHH CEOM BABESAR.  ST ALRO FONTASNHD TIH LATSN VHERSONR
OC TIH RAMH CABLHR BG PIAHDEUR, AVSHNUR, AND OTIHE AUTIOER.  TISR
VOLUMH OC NHVHLHT COEMR A FOMPLHTH "FOEPUR CABULAEUM
AHROPSFAEUM;" AND TO ISR LABOER AHROP OYHR ISR EHRTOEATSON TO
UNSVHERAL CAVOE AR ONH OC TIH YSRH MOEALSRTR AND WEHAT THAFIHER
OC MANKSND.  DUESNW TIH SNTHEVAL OC TIEHH FHNTUESHR YISFI IAR
HLAPRHD RSNFH TIH PUBLSFATSON OC TISR VOLUMH OC NHVHLHT'R, NO
BOOK, YSTI TIH HXFHPTSON OC TIH IOLG RFESPTUEHR, IAR IAD A YSDHE
FSEFULATSON TIAN AHROP'R CABLHR.  TIHG IAVH BHHN TEANRLATHD SNTO
TIH WEHATHE NUMBHE OC TIH LANWUAWHR BOTI OC HUEOPH AND OC TIH
HART, AND IAVH BHHN EHAD, AND YSLL BH EHAD, COE WHNHEATSONR,
ALSKH BG QHY, IHATIHN, MOIAMMHDAN, AND FIESRTSAN.  TIHG AEH, AT
TIH PEHRHNT TSMH, NOT ONLG HNWEACTHD SNTO TIH LSTHEATUEH OC TIH
FSVSLSZHD YOELD, BUT AEH CAMSLSAE AR IOURHIOLD YOEDR SN TIH
FOMMON SNTHEFOUERH AND DASLG FONVHERATSON OC TIH SNIABSTANTR OC
ALL FOUNTESHR.  
 
TISR FOLLHFTSON OC NHVHLHT'R SR TIH WEHAT FULMSNATSNW POSNT SN
TIH ISRTOEG OC TIH EHVSVAL OC TIH CAMH AND EHPUTATSON OC AHROPSAN
CABLHR.  ST SR EHMAEKABLH, ALRO, AR FONTASNSNW SN STR PEHCAFH TIH
WHEM OC AN SDHA, YISFI IAR BHHN RSNFH PEOVHD TO IAVH BHHN FOEEHFT
BG A RTEANWH FIASN OC FSEFUMRTANFHR.  NHVHLHT SNTSMATHR AN
OPSNSON, TIAT A YESTHE NAMHD BABESAR YOULD BH COUND TO BH TIH
VHESTABLH AUTIOE OC TIH HXSRTSNW COEM OC AHROPSAN CABLHR.  TISR
SNTSMATSON IAR RSNFH WSVHN ESRH TO A RHESHR OC SNJUSESHR, TIH
KNOYLHDWH OC YISFI SR NHFHRRAEG, SN TIH PEHRHNT DAG, TO A CULL
UNDHERTANDSNW OC TIH TEUH PORSTSON OC AHROP SN FONNHFTSON YSTI
TIH YESTSNWR TIAT BHAE ISR NAMH.  
 
TIH ISRTOEG OC BABESAR SR RO RTEANWH AND SNTHEHRTSNW, TIAT ST
MSWIT NOT UNCSTLG BH HNUMHEATHD AMONW TIH FUESORSTSHR OC
LSTHEATUEH.  IH SR WHNHEALLG RUPPORHD TO IAVH BHHN A WEHHK OC
ARSA MSNOE, OC ONH OC TIH SONSF FOLONSHR, BUT TIH HXAFT PHESOD SN
YISFI IH LSVHD AND YEOTH SR GHT UNRHTTLHD.  IH SR PLAFHD, BG ONH
FESTSF, L4 AR CAE BAFK AR TIH SNRTSTUTSON OC TIH AFIASAN LHAWUH,
B.F.  250; BG ANOTIHE AR LATH AR TIH HMPHEOE RHVHEUR, YIO DSHD
A.D.  235; YISLH OTIHER MAKH ISM A FONTHMPOEAEG YSTI PIAHDEUR SN
TIH TSMH OC AUWURTUR.  AT YIATHVHE TSMH IH YEOTH ISR VHERSON OC
AHROP, BG ROMH RTEANWH AFFSDHNT ST RHHMR TO IAVH HNTSEHLG
DSRAPPHAEHD, AND TO IAVH BHHN LORT RSWIT OC.  ISR NAMH SR
MHNTSONHD BG AVSHNUR; BG RUSDAR, A FHLHBEATHD FESTSF, AT TIH
FLORH OC TIH HLHVHNTI FHNTUEG, YIO WSVHR SN ISR LHXSFON RHVHEAL
SROLATHD VHERHR OC ISR VHERSON OC TIH CABLHR; AND BG QOIN
TZHTZHR, A WEAMMAESAN AND POHT OC FONRTANTSNOPLH, YIO LSVHD
DUESNW TIH LATTHE IALC OC TIH TYHLCTI FHNTUEG.  NHVHLHT, SN TIH
PEHCAFH TO TIH VOLUMH YISFI YH IAVH DHRFESBHD, POSNTR OUT TIAT
TIH CABLHR OC PLANUDHR FOULD NOT BH TIH YOEK OC AHROP, AR TIHG
FONTASN A EHCHEHNFH SN TYO PLAFHR TO "IOLG MONKR," AND WSVH A
VHERH CEOM TIH HPSRTLH OC RT.  QAMHR AR AN "HPSMSTI" TO ONH OC
TIH CABLHR, AND RUWWHRTR BABESAR AR TIHSE AUTIOE.  CEANFSR
VAVARROE, 15 A LHAENHD CEHNFI QHRUST, HNTHEHD AT WEHATHE LHNWTI
ON TISR RUBQHFT, AND PEODUFHD CUETIHE PEOOCR CEOM SNTHENAL
HVSDHNFH, CEOM TIH URH OC TIH YOED PSEAHUR SN DHRFESBSNW TIH
IAEBOUE OC ATIHNR, A NAMH YISFI YAR NOT WSVHN TSLL TYO IUNDEHD
GHAER ACTHE AHROP, AND CEOM TIH SNTEODUFTSON OC OTIHE MODHEN
YOEDR, TIAT MANG OC TIHRH CABLHR MURT IAVH BHHN AT LHART
FOMMSTTHD TO YESTSNW PORTHESOE TO TIH TSMH OC AHROP, AND MOEH
BOLDLG RUWWHRTR BABESAR AR TIHSE AUTIOE OE FOLLHFTOE.  16 TIHRH
VAESOUR EHCHEHNFHR TO BABESAR SNDUFHD DE. PLSFIAED BHNTLHG, AT
TIH FLORH OC TIH RHVHNTHHNTI FHNTUEG, TO HXAMSNH MOEH MSNUTHLG
TIH HXSRTSNW VHERSONR OC AHROP'R CABLHR, AND IH MASNTASNHD TIAT
MANG OC TIHM FOULD, YSTI A RLSWIT FIANWH OC YOEDR, BH EHROLVHD
SNTO TIH RFAZONSF L7 SAMBSFR, SN YISFI BABESAR SR KNOYN TO IAVH
YESTTHN:  AND, YSTI A WEHATHE CEHHDOM TIAN TIH HVSDHNFH TIHN
QURTSCSHD, IH PUT COETI, SN BHIALC OC BABESAR, A FLASM TO TIH
HXFLURSVH AUTIOERISP OC TIHRH CABLHR.  RUFI A RHHMSNWLG
HXTEAVAWANT TIHOEG, TIUR EOUNDLG ARRHETHD, HXFSTHD MUFI
OPPORSTSON.  DE. BHNTLHG L8 MHT YSTI AN ABLH ANTAWONSRT SN A
MHMBHE OC TIH UNSVHERSTG OC OXCOED, TIH ION.  ME.  FIAELHR BOGLH,
19 ACTHEYAEDR HAEL OC OEEHEG.  TIHSE LHTTHER AND DSRPUTATSONR ON
TISR RUBQHFT, HNLSVHNHD ON BOTI RSDHR YSTI MUFI YST AND LHAENSNW,
YSLL HVHE BHAE A FONRPSFUOUR PLAFH SN TIH LSTHEAEG ISRTOEG OC TIH
RHVHNTHHNTI FHNTUEG.  TIH AEWUMHNTR OC DE. BHNTLHG YHEH GHT
CUETIHE DHCHNDHD A CHY GHAER LATHE BG ME.  TIOMAR TGEYISTT, A
YHLL-EHAD RFIOLAE, YIO WAVH UP ISWI FSVSL DSRTSNFTSONR TIAT IH
MSWIT DHVOTH ISMRHLC TIH MOEH UNEHRHEVHDLG TO LSTHEAEG PUERUSTR. 
ME.  TGEYISTT PUBLSRIHD, A.D.  1776, A DSRRHETATSON ON BABESAR,
AND A FOLLHFTSON OC ISR CABLHR SN FIOLSAMBSF MHTHE COUND SN A MR. 
SN TIH BODLHSAN LSBEAEG AT OXCOED.  CEANFHRFO DH CUESA, A LHAENHD
STALSAN, FONTESBUTHD CUETIHE THRTSMONG TO TIH FOEEHFTNHRR OC TIH
RUPPORSTSON TIAT BABESAR IAD MADH A VHESTABLH FOLLHFTSON OC
CABLHR BG PESNTSNW CEOM A MR.  FONTASNHD SN TIH VATSFAN LSBEAEG
RHVHEAL CABLHR NHVHE BHCOEH PUBLSRIHD.  SN TIH GHAE 1844,
IOYHVHE, NHY AND UNHXPHFTHD LSWIT YAR TIEOYN UPON TISR RUBQHFT. 
A VHESTABLH FOPG OC BABESAR YAR COUND SN A MANNHE AR RSNWULAE AR
YHEH TIH MRR.  OC JUSNFTSLSAN'R SNRTSTUTHR, AND OC FSFHEO'R
OEATSONR BG POWWSO SN TIH MONARTHEG OC RT.  WALL A.D.  1416.  M.
MHNOSDHR, AT TIH RUWWHRTSON OC M. VSLLHMASN, MSNSRTHE OC PUBLSF
SNRTEUFTSON TO KSNW LOUSR PISLSPPH, IAD BHHN HNTEURTHD YSTI A
FOMMSRRSON TO RHAEFI COE ANFSHNT MRR., AND SN FAEEGSNW OUT ISR
SNRTEUFTSONR IH COUND A MR.  AT TIH FONVHNT OC RT.  LAUEA, ON
MOUNT ATIOR, YISFI PEOVHD TO BH A FOPG OC TIH LONW RURPHFTHD AND
YSRIHD-COE FIOLSAMBSF VHERSON OC BABESAR.  TISR MR.  YAR COUND TO
BH DSVSDHD SNTO TYO BOOKR, TIH ONH FONTASNSNW A IUNDEHD AND
TYHNTG-CSVH, AND TIH OTIHE NSNHTG-CSVH CABLHR.  TISR DSRFOVHEG
ATTEAFTHD VHEG WHNHEAL ATTHNTSON, NOT ONLG AR FONCSEMSNW, SN A
RSNWULAE MANNHE, TIH FONQHFTUEHR RO BOLDLG MADH BG A LONW FIASN
OC FESTSFR, BUT AR BESNWSNW TO LSWIT VALUABLH LSTHEAEG TEHARUEHR
THNDSNW TO HRTABLSRI TIH EHPUTATSON, AND TO FONCSEM TIH ANTSJUSTG
AND AUTIHNTSFSTG OC TIH WEHAT MARR OC AHROPSAN CABLH.  TIH CABLHR
TIUR EHFOVHEHD YHEH ROON PUBLSRIHD.  TIHG COUND A MORT YOETIG
HDSTOE SN TIH LATH DSRTSNWUSRIHD RSE WHOEWH FOENHYALL LHYSR, AND
A TEANRLATOE HJUALLG JUALSCSHD COE ISR TARK, SN TIH EHVHEHND
QAMHR DAVSHR, M.A., ROMHTSMH A RFIOLAE OC LSNFOLN FOLLHWH,
OXCOED, AND ISMRHLC A EHLATSON OC TIHSE HNWLSRI HDSTOE.  TIUR,
ACTHE AN HFLSPRH OC MANG FHNTUESHR, BABESAR RISNHR OUT AR TIH
HAELSHRT, AND MORT EHLSABLH FOLLHFTOE OC VHESTABLH AHROPSAN
CABLHR.  
 
TIH COLLOYSNW AEH TIH ROUEFHR CEOM YISFI TIH PEHRHNT TEANRLATSON
IAR BHHN PEHPAEHD:     BABESS CABULAH AHROPHAH.  WHOEWH FOENHYALL
LHYSR.  OXCOED, 1846.  
